New Year is always an invitation to establish goals for the next 365 days . There are some areas where I 'm pleased , like improving my knowledge in idioms , writing , speaking and presenting scientific articles . There are also areas that I should improve , like statistics , AI , algorithms and how to present the work I have developed . So I need to have some strategies for achieving goals . 1 - Improving a new language : I need to study daily , at least a little time , like 15 minutes . And this study should include writing and reading a lot . 2 - Presenting scientific articles : It 's important to search for innovative findings , read , study and try to spread these new ideas . When I consider being a presenter , I need to study a lot . 3 - Improving my knowledge in statistics : a challenge , but not impossible . Like the previous goals , I 'll need to study systematically and never give up . 4 - Understanding algorithms - new knowledge and very difficult to understand for whom it is not a specialty in this area , but I think that if I am persistent , I will learn . So many challenges , but if I meet all my goals , it will contribute to my happiness , of course . 
