There are people who say , it does not matter how long you live , but what counts is how you live . So as for them , the quality of life is something that really matters . It would be hard to deny it , but on the other hand , our desire to live is so strong and obvious that we are eager to extend our life span every possible way . In the first place , there are a lot of advantages to leading a peaceful and long life . The longer you live , the more opportunity there is to share your time with your loved ones , such as friends and family . Each day has its unique importance and beauty . People have the possibility of learning something new day in day out , which makes life purposeful and meaningful . But there are people eager to push their limits and try whatever is possible in their lives . They set themselves some goals and feel the tremor of excitement when achieving them . For example , they want to see the ocean and learn how to dive in its deep water and they are convinced in their heart of hearts that only if they do it , they will truly feel fulfilled and exhilarated . Such people would not like a boring and quiet life without risky and adventurous situations . If I had to choose , I would go for a longer and calm life to enjoy life and the people I love day by day , taking advantage of each single joy . 
