The way we travel will certainly change in the future and now I 'm going to tell you what my opinion is . I think cars will no longer work with oil : the pollution level will not let it be possible . In my opinion , cars will be charged with electricity . In fact , nowadays , scientists have begun doing research into this topic : the first prototypes have already been produced . I also think that cars and buses will have automatic drivers . I think that this is a negative thing as lots of people will be out of work because of that . I think trains and aeroplanes will be faster : in my opinion , scientists soon will develop a prototype which is able to go from London to New York in a very short time . Around Europe , there are already some trains that go at high speed . Let 's talk about ships now . I think the engines of ships will improve a lot . I think there will be devices on ships that consent not to cause accidents and there will be present more comforts on cruise ships . Moving from an isle to another will be easier and will take less time because of better ferries . 
In this decade , we have ran into many innovations that have been affected by technology . Many of them have got used easily by people because the producers of those products have been providing new models in our lives in every year , such as computers , tablets or smartphones . People get adapted to those devices and use them the whole time of their lives . Hence companies increase their sales figures . Everyone is grateful to technology and they do not want to turn back to old techniques , like books , magazines or newspapers . For example , nowadays , children prefer computers , tablets or the internet to learn something , so that situation reminds us of this question , “ Should computers and tablets replace books in educational areas of study ? ” In general , technology has a lot of magnificent benefits . If we talk about educational stations , it has more . For instance , tablets and e -readers are very useful for students because you can find out or take note about anything that you want without pen . It stores as much information as 3 or 4 libraries does have books . Simple , quick and useful . Furthermore , using that product is a good way to be against deforestation because every year many trees are cut down to publish a book . On the other hand , many scientists suggest that books are a good guide to learn because when you look up any information but cannot see quickly the review , you have to keep to scanning until you find it . So you have more chance of memorizing after you finish your searching . In my opinion , both sides have good benefits but I support that books should still be in school and universities . Before to pass technological innovations , every person should try old techniques to learn any information . 
