Books and technology I am a music teacher . I work at a small school . All my students get their notes in paper format . But the newest trend is to work with a tablet . We do not need paper and , for the environment , this is good . At the moment , my biggest job is to scan all the music notes that I need . My tablet is very good , but I have to learn to need it . The biggest question is : " What is the easiest form to find the notes on the computer ? . " only I have a computer , the students do not have one . Also a problem is that not all schools have wireless to send a message to print what I need . At the moment , this is for me the future . Primary schools have the facilities and the students learn early to work with a computer . I see the problem not in the school but at home ! The children are often alone at home and they do not only work for school on the computer , the temptation is to surf on the internet . We all know what happens next . 
