--- MY REASONS FOR LEARNING ENGLISH --- By School Newspaper Hi , everyone , how are you ? Today , we are writing this school newspaper to report the results of the questionnaire . We asked other students the following question . --- What is the biggest reason to study English ? --- Many respondents answered " To make my life fruitful . " ---> 65 % Some said , they learn English " To expand the field of activity . " ---> 25 % Others said , " Now , we 're living in the 21st century , and it 's the society of globalization , it will surely come in handy in the near future . " ---> 5 % The rest of the students had a different opinion . ( Other ) ---> 5 % From this questionnaire , we can see that different people have a different opinion . I think that 's good . We must accept each other 's opinion . In my case , I 'm studying English because I have a certain aim that I want to achieve in the future . I strongly believe in saying " Hard work does pay off . " I will study English hard and I hope I will be able to achieve the goal . 
