I am using Write and Improve to improve my English writing . It is an online learning programme , which does not only improve your writing , it also improves your speed with way of writing . As we know , to be perfect in English writing is very necessary . English is the language which is universally accepted and functional across the world . In the market , there are so many online programmes for English learners , but only a few are useful , and Write and Improve is one of them . Here , you can check your writing in a few moments and get an idea about your writing skills with feedback . Your feedback is about all the parameters which are required to improve your writing . One of the important points is that you can learn in any part of world at any time and take suggestions in a limited time , which makes this online software awesome . In my opinion , friends , we should use the Write and Improve online learning programme to improve our learning . 
It is often said that health is wealth , so people should consider health before money . I agree with the statement because healthy people can live independently . However , I believe that money is equally important to live a healthy life . Some people believe that healthy people are less dependent on their family . Because they can learn new things more quickly by concentrating for a long time on their work . Nowadays , employers prefer people with new skills and are highly paid , which is enough for them to survive on their own . , . they can work until the time they want to retire . For instance , a report from 2012 from Oxford university found that healthier people learn 5 times faster than the people who are not able to concentrate . Therefore , health must be taken seriously . On the other hand , I think that , nowadays , money plays a vital role in keeping you healthy . Rich people can stay away from disease by eating organic food , which is very difficult to afford for normal people . In this way , people are less prone to getting diseases and they can stay healthy for a longer time as compared to people with less income . For example , a survey in India found that 90 % of the rich people have their own farms for growing organic vegetables . To sum up , it is undeniable that health should be given the highest importance as compared to other urgent items . It is also true that money should not be ignored . 
My favourite film Hi Sylvi . Yesterday evening , I was watching the movie : " A Beautiful Mind . " It was not the first time . I have seen the film three times . The best on about this film is that it is the truth . When I saw it the first time , I did not understand everything , but every time , I understand it better . The story talks about a young man at university . He has a very good friend , but in reality , he does not exist . It takes a long time to detect that he is schizophrenic . But life is good to him . He has a wonderful wife and , with her help , he quits university and is appointed professor . The highest point was the Nobel prize in mathematics for him . At many points , I have cried and the first time I do not sleep . Too many thoughts bothered me . So I hope you have time to see it . Have a good time . Astrid 
