What I want to achieve this year is to get a score of 100 in the TOEFL test . To achieve my goal , I have to enhance my reading , listening , speaking and writing skills . Especially , my speaking skills are my weak point . So I have to improve my speaking skills . Luckily , I like to communicate with people , so the score in speaking will be better with joy . To improve my English skills , I have made 4 rules for myself . First , I have to read the newspaper for 30 minutes every day to improve my reading skills . Second , I have to speak with my friends in English every day to improve my listening and speaking skills . Third , I have to take " Write and Improve " lectures , at least 2 materials every day , to enhance my writing skills . Fourth , I have to take a TOEFL trial test every two months to confirm my ability at that time . If I can do these things and make great efforts , the result will be good for me . I will start to do it today to achieve my goal . 
There are many ways to be healthy . One of them is doing sports , it is so important because it makes the body energetic and active . There are many kinds of sports , like football or basketball and other sports . All of them are important in our life . Doing sports is not the only way to be healthy , there are many other ways . One of them is breathing some fresh air , not the pollution from factories . The garden and the coast are the most places that have fresh air . Eating some food that has calcium and magnesium is so important for your body . This kind of food helps you to get strong muscles . There is also another way of eating healthy food , for you to eat a specific meal at a specific time to be completely right in this way . You should eat a meal that has all the kinds of protein . With all this way of keeping healthy , there is an important thing which is that you should not eat junk food from any restaurant . I hope eat people spot thinking that the sport and this ways are wrong . 
