A new year has started here in Liceo Classico . We are all coming back from our vacations , and it 's now time to focus on the goal we want to reach this year . I am really interested in the Greeks . This year , we will start studying Greek poetry and I ca not wait to do so . Saffo 's words have always enchanted my mind and now I am really excited to learn something more about her style and her living . However , I am not interested only in the Greeks . I know this year we will start to study English literature too , so I know it is a really great opportunity to improve my English . I would really like to be able to get an English certification this year or maybe the next . To achieve my goals , I will work hard because I know that nothing comes from nothing . I want to build my future day by day , learning as much as possible . Every new skill I get is a bigger possibility to get what I want in life . 
I really like to travel around the world , especially with my boyfriend . For the moment , we go on low cost vacations , we do not really have much money . We went to Kracow two years ago and we stayed there for a week . Although Poland became part of the European Union , they still do not have the Euro . For this reason , it is really convenient for us European people to spend a period there : one Euro is worth four of their Zloty . Moreover , Krakow is rich in history : we saw lots of interesting buildings , from synagogues to castles . In Krakow , there is a strong Hebraic culture , they have seven synagogues , all located in the same district . In the older synagogue , there 's now a museum , but other ones are still used to pray and to celebrate religious functions . The Kupa Synagogue , so small but so colourful , is one of the most beautiful monuments I have ever visited . One hour and a half by bus from Krakow , there are Birkeanau and Auschwitz Lagers , two of the sadly famous German Lagers in where Nazists imprisoned Hebras during the Nazi regime . I strongly recommend everyone to visit these places to realize how human beings can be cruel and not to forget . 
I think the following three things may be different in the future . First , the way of accessing and its speed . The train and the car may be faster than now and new machines which we cannot imagine may happen to appear someday . Second , the place where we can go . In the near future , we will be able to go to the Moon or Mars . Besides , we can go to another planet for the future . Third , the spots for sightseeing and traditional spots may decrease due to worldwide globalization and the amount of information . Otherwise , the following three things will be the same in the future . The first is communication with the people who live there . It is one of the main purposes now and in the future . Second , packing is always tired . Third , we are very tired after coming back home . The different point may differ more than I thought , but the same point may be true . Because the journey is what changes oneself and very hard . 
Although my experience with " Write and Improve " is too short ( a week ) , I have learned and progressed a lot . First of all , I like that this website can correct your common mistakes , because you realize that you have to pay more attention . Furthermore , it encourages to have a better English writing level , because you can take up studying harder the language . However , there are some things I ca not deal with . Looking for help , I 've found " Write & Improve " does not help so much and it bothers me because , sometimes , I do not know why one thing is wrong or another is right . Moreover , when my feedback says " you need to improve more ... " and does not say what I have to improve , it 's so annoying . In conclusion , even though there are some errors in app , I think it 's a good help for people searching for training to do Cambridge tests , so I recommend it to my classmates . 
