In my opinion , exercise is important for our health , but it is not enough . Our health is a key in our happiness . NA , . healthy food is more important than exercise . We must eat fruit , vegetables . For our health , we must cook healthy food : chicken with vegetables , fish with rice , soups and deserts just like fruit : apples , pears , pineapples , kiwis , grapefruits . NA , . I think that our zen is more important . Life is all about problems , stress , running and running again . I think that we must stay calm every day and in every situation and we will find the key to success and a happy life . In conclusion , exercise is important for our health , but it must come with healthy food and a happy and peaceful life . Our happiness depends on our smile and then smiling every day to become healthy people ! 
Today is 1 September , today is autumn . This summer was incredible . I visited tree countries : France , Italy and Romania . I like Romania very much , but Paris is my favourite . I think that French people are happy all the time . They really smile all day . I love their food : pizza , pasta , burgers and croissants . This country is amazing . I saw the famous " Le Tour Effel " and the cathedral of " Notre Damme . " I visited a lot of parks and gardens . Italy is very beautiful too . But I think the France is my favourite because it is cleaner than Italy and people are more educated . Romania is home for me and that 's all . Home is love , home is the most beautiful thing that I know . Romania has beautiful places with smart people and Romania grow every day . I was in Sibiu , Brasov , Constanta , Sinaia . They are 4 of the many perfect cities in Romania . The clean air of mountains was my happiness last summer . 
Yes , it is . Health is important but it is not to be healthy than to be rich , I think both are important to live a good life because health and wealth can make our life happy and easy . For example , if you have a lot of money and you are a rich man , you can buy a car to go everywhere and every place you want at any time . Also when you are rich , you can marry and make a family , you can even buy an apartment and you can eat healthily every day . Also when you are in a good health , you can sleep very well and you can work and exercise and play football and any game you want . But when you have one of these " health or wealth , " that means you will have trouble in your life because if you are not rich , that means you are a poor person and when you are a poor person , you do not have money to buy a car or eat well or buy an apartment . Also if you are rich and you do not have good health , that means you do not sleep very well and you can not play any game . Also you can not work and walk . I think you should balance health and wealth in your life to live a good life . So that is what I have today . See you next day with a new essay . It is Ali and thank you . 
The best holiday that I ever had was last summer 's holiday . My boyfriend Andrea and I went to Spotorno , in Italy . We booked a big house in front of Bergeggi island . The house was so big and there were a lot of facilities , such as a big swimming pool , sea view and a gym . We stayed there one month . This house was next to the beach and we had a private beach with all the facilities . We played volleyball all day and , in the evening , we organised a lot of parties on the beach . We also ate a lot of delicious Ligurian dishes , like pasta with pesto sauce or " focaccia . " But there is another thing that I 'll never forget in all my life . It was the best holiday I ever had because on 21st of the month , it was our 6th anniversary and Andrea asked me to marry him in front of our families and friends . Now , we are officially engaged ! 
There is no doubt that having fortune could be one of the most important reasons for making you happy . However , the question is : what is more important to be rich or to be healthy ? It is considered one of the controversial issues today . In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from both view points . On one side of the argument , there are people who argue that being rich is more important than being healthy . The main reason for believing this is they think about having a completely wonderful life . These days , you need to have a lot of money or you will just live a less than ordinary life . Moreover , it is also possible to say that those people also claim that you can have the perfect medical service by being wealthy . On the other side , there are people who argue that being a healthy person is much better than being wealthy and losing you health . People often have this opinion because they believe that your health is priceless and it is the most important factor to live a good life at any time . A particularly good point here is that , by being healthy , you can try and be rich by studying and achieving your goals . It is much safer for you and your life . 
Thanks to the spread of the internet , we can have many choices in the way of studying . We do not need to go to school because we can study connecting to the internet . We can enter a school which is located far from us or abroad . We can make the style of our school of the future automatic using the internet , but I think the real school of the future wo not change a lot . Because what we should do in school is not only study subjects but also get our social mind . For students , what is most important to learn is how we face difficult problems . We learn it through friends and classmates , and sometimes , the people who you hate . Social mind cannot be learned where you are alone . So the school of the future will be convenient thanks to the internet , but will not change its essence at all . 
There is no doubt that these days technology has become a magnificent tool in our life in all aspects . However , the question is : should we depend more on technology than traditional materials ? It is considered one of the controversial issues today . In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from both view points . On one side of the argument , there are people who argue that the advantages of using technology outweigh the disadvantages . The main reason for believing this is that using computers and other devices could save so many different sorts of information in very limited space and you can search for the things you want . On the other hand , it is possible to consider it with the opposite case . People often argue that using technology could damage the students very badly . People often think that it could hurt their eye vision , especially at an earlier age . 
There is no doubt that these days the world has become a smaller place due to the improvement of the latest technology . However , the question is : is learning a new language becoming more important than in the past ? It is considered one of the controversial issues of today . In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from both view points . On one side of the argument , there are people who argue that learning a new language is an extremely important thing to do , especially these days . People often have this opinion because they believe that learning languages could give you incredible results , such as getting smarter and gaining self -confidence , and most significantly opening the door for you to discover the differences between cultures and people 's way of communication . On the other hand , it is also possible to consider it with the opposing case . There are people who argue that learning a new language is not comletely an ideal idea . The main for believing this is they think that you can get the benefit of the language you speak just in the country which speaks the same language , so its use would be limited by the geographical differences . 
Dear Gheorge , Last weekend , I was at a music concert . Guess who ? Exactly ! You know my favourite music band is Carla 's Deams and I did not have the patience to wait to hear their voices before the concert started . It was a unique experience . Obviously , I decided to go because I am very keen on their music , but my sister decided to go with me to have fun . I had no doubts that the band 's singer , Sergiu , would perform and it was exactly that . The boys sang a lot of their old songs but , the surprise arrived when they decided to share with us some lyrics from their new song , , The wings " . The atmosphere was incredible , people danced and sang with the band . I cannot describe my feelings about that concert , and I am so sorry I could not share those moments with you . How about going to another concert together ? All the best , Corina 
I am writing about my best season of the year . I believe that all seasons of the year are important and we cannot possibly remove or change one . However , I do prefer two seasons than the others . Firstly , I like summer and that is seemingly quite common , the majority of people have constantly chosen this season as their favourite one . There is no doubt about that . Summer season is commonly preferred due to the weather and the temperature . Summer weather is the most perfect weather ever , with less rain and sunlight brightly shining , most people see it as a great period of time for a picnic or playing outdoors . Temperature is another factor , people find it comfortable because they do not have to wear many clothes because the temperature is more than perfect . Moreover , summer is considered to be days of holiday , which is considred to be in days of holiday , whic is excepted to be approriate to many people , it is the perfect time to go to the beach and do sport or swim . 
