English is very important for our future . There are many reasons for learning English . The first reason is if you want to immigrate to country which speaks English to study or to work or live there , like Canada or the USA or the UK or any other country . That means you should learn English to connect with the people there and the second reason is English these days is everywhere . If you want to learn about technology , you should learn English first because all technology uses the English language . Almost every technology is made by the countries which speak English . And the third reason , currently , English is a global language that makes people around the world learn English to connect with each other to buy things and to sell things . Also when you learn a new language , that will make our minds be on a high level of intelligence and will make our communication skills high level and everyone has a reason why they learn English or any other language . So that is what I think and this is my article and see you in a new article and new information , it is Ali . 
It depends on how people think about this . An extreme argument is quite meaningless here . For example , even if you are very rich , it is meaningless to live in bed for life or even if you have a good condition , it is meaningless that you have no money . It 's nonsense . Of course , both of them are important . For me , I come to think that being healthy is important as me becoming older . It is clear that I can not live and feed my family if I could not earn enough money . But the basis of daily life is the family 's health . Because if we are healthy enough , we come to have a desire such as to be rich . If we are not healthy , all we want is to be healthy , I guess . Therefore , my opinion is that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . 
