Why I must learn English is that it is the minimum requirement for me to be a doctor . To be a doctor , I studied for 4 years to enter the university , but I could not pass the exam . When I gave up my dream of being a doctor , the only way that was left for me was to study at the medical university in Bulgaria . So all the lectures were spoken in English , I had to study English . Generally speaking , learning Engrish gives you some good efforts . For example , because the English speaking population is the biggest in the world , we can learn worldwide common sense through communication with them . Another reason why it is better for us to learn English is to make many friends . Making friends who are from various countries is good for you because you can get chances where you think about other people and it can spread or change your mind . This is why learning English is important to us . 
