I think that learning to speak a foreign language is more and more important than in past times . Of course , the invention of the high quality translator , we may not need to learn a foreign language . But when you meet someone , like a business or you make friends , communicating with each other face to face is the best way to make and keep a good relationship . Learning a foreign language also leads to understanding their culture . It will be your legacy . Another reason why we learn a foreign language is that we get more and more chances to speak with the people from various countries . With the invention of the airplane and the bullet train , we can travel all over the world . And the improvement of information technology , mainly the internet , can make us communicate with each other even if we are in different countries . Therefore , learning a foreign language is more important than in the old times . 
