Nowadays , we well know that if you have a healthy living , you will be more delighted with yourself . Firstly , it is undeniable that exercise is important for our health , as a result of having a good physical appearance and maybe for having a good quality of life because if you move your body , you will get distracted from the thing that you were doing before . Secondly , having a balanced diet is an important point to consider because if you eat healthily , you will be fit . Therefore , you might increase your fitness and also your psychological condition . Last but not least , the relationship with friends should be mentioned since if you have a problem , your friend can help you with it . Besides that , friends could be very necessary in your life because , with them , you can improve your lifestyle and your psychological condition . In conclusion , from my point of view , I think that exercise could not be the most important thing about having a healthy living because there are a lot of things that could be more essential . 
I completely agree with this statement . It 's more important to be healthy than to be rich . Health is more important because the money could run out , and also money enables people to exert influence over others , and this is not a good thing . But , sadly , money is vital for survival . Money , in my opinion , is of little consolation to those who are suffering from health problems . Despite the fact that , with money , you can pay for the best medical treatment and care available , this is no guarantee of a longer life . Even if an individual is extremely rich , this does not necessarily lead to happiness , also in some cases , it 's the contrary . Rich people think that with money they can buy everything , sadly love too , but genuine happiness cannot be bought . At the end , money can be an important thing in life , but health is more important than the others . 
Learning a foreign language is more important these days than it was in the past . The cause is globalization . Now , English is the most widely spoken language all around the world , it 's the language of economics , of science . Now , when you are looking for a job , companies look for language skills because , nowadays , companies cooperate with foreign companies and speaking a foreign language is very important work -wise . In the past , learning a foreign language was only for rich people , who could pay expensive language courses , now , for example , English is begins to be taught in elementary school and continues to be taught until high school together , In some cases , with other foreign languages . The foreign languages that can be taught in high school are French , German and Spanisch , but also Russian and Chinese in some cases . In sum , learning a foreign language widens the knowledge , also in the working field . 
Books and technology are an interesting essay . Nowadays , technology is everywhere in our life . This development , however , has pron and cons . Technology can help us , but I think that the human mind cannot be replaced . Sadly , now , computers and tablets are slowly replacing books in schools and university . Now , the students prefer to " Google " a summary of a book than read it . They prefer to translate a piece of novel on the net than use a dictionary , and this is a very sad fact . Almost all young people have never been to a library because , nowadays surfing the net , we can find everything we are looking for . At university , almost all the courses are composed of multimedia material too , that 's why at university there are some working students who cannot attend the lessons at the university . At the end , technology help students to raise their knowledge , but the parents of young people must involve children in reading books and also going to libraries too ! 
