I have had many great holidays , but there was a diverse one of them . This one was different because it had a learning purpose . Instead of going to a hotel , we went to a camp . The trip was to Spain . There , we met a person called Mr . Jackson , who was sent with us to camp for learning how to deal with the forest and its wild animals . There was a tall large man called Mr . Browne who taught us how to treat animals and how to prevent them from harming us if they are hungry . We learned how to know what is in the animal 's mind . We also had a lot of fun watching the sunrise in the morning . That was the most beautiful thing I had ever seen before , and we ate and drank hot things and played soccer in our time off . When we finished learning , we had a week to explore things about animals to fill out a book of facts about the forest and we had to present it to the teacher after that week . When we were going back to Egypt , we felt upset because we left the camp . It was the best holiday ever . 
