Hi Cristina ! I am so sorry about your accident , I hope you are okay . Is there anything I can help you with , I 'd be glad to help you out . I hope I can visit you soon . Could I visit you next weekend to see how you are doing ? Hope you get better ! Bye Cristina ! 
Write and Improve is a simple tool for improving language skills . I just started using it and I have to admit that it can really help you . By entering texts for the given tasks , you train your ability to use a foreign language . Moreover , it is possible to get a feedback in the end . Owing to this , you can focus on your individual weaknesses in order to turn them into strengths . Though some of the topics may seem a little bit out of context , it is a good possibility to train yourself . Concerning the tasks themselves , it would be necessary to focus on relevant topics for exams in my opinion . Maybe I just have to explore whether there are any tasks I would like to do . Still , I would highly recommend using " Write and Improve " since no similar program exists at the moment . 
The school of the future To start with , it has to be mentioned that school nearly stayed the same for decades . However , a real change is definitely needed . How may this look ? Nobody knows yet , but some ideas already exist . First , grades in general will be abandoned because they do not lead to higher student motivation any more . What is more is that they only create much more pressure that keeps students from being interested in school . Therefore , I think the emphasis should be put on how to get kids to learn voluntarily . If there is a good relationship between teachers and students , the results will be better as well . On the other hand , some structures will possibly last . Organising classes in separate rooms is still up to date . Furthermore , I think that books will also stay for a few more years , just because kids should remember how it is to use them . But maybe , there will be other changes we cannot even think of nowadays . Let 's just wait and find out . 
My reasons for learning English If you do something , there is always some kind of intention behind it . Exercising for getting fit or watching TV series to learn something about other people . For me , learning English is something I do not want to stop in the near future . The main reason may be clear : Improving language skills will help me in my future business as well as in my general life of work . However , for me , there is more than this side of the coin . First , I want to travel a lot and the language needed is English . Of course , other languages would be useful as well . Still I think that English is the most important one . Due to the many people who have at least basic knowledge in speaking or writing English , it is the most required language . Communicating is necessary both in private life and in the world of work . Therefore , do not let anyone stop you from learning English and always try your best ! 
Hi Rie , Thank you for inviting me for dinner . I am looking forward to your big dinner tomorrow . As you asked me what I would like to eat , the answer is vegetarian food . I started eating vegetarian food two months ago because it is good for my health . Would it be a bother if you prepared vegetarian food for me ? I want us to try this food together . See you tomorrow night . Por 
In my home town there are important landmarks like the " Cake statue " and the " Donout Fountain . " You can also shop in our big mall like the " Cute Mall . " You can live in our houses too . There is a park called " Orchid Park . " There is a museum in our square called the " Natural History Museum . " There are restaurants with fast food , Italian food and all kinds of food in the world . You can go to the cinema and to the theatre in the night time . 
Do you know there are four seasons ? The winter , the spring , the summer and the autumn and , for me , it is difficult to choose which is the best of them . The winter is amazing because you can see the all things white and there is silence all around me . The spring is green with many new flowers . The summer is warm with a big sun and blue sea . The autumn has many leaves that fly in the sky like beautiful butterflies . In the end , I have to choose . I prefer summer because I like swimming and , in the summer , I have my holidays so I can go to the sea . I spend forty days on the sea with my family . Also during this season , I can eat much good food , like strawberries , tomatoes , salads . In the end , it is incredible to sit on a tree with a big ice cream to eat and close your eyes and dream ... 
