Hi teacher ! I want to learn another subject , apart from English . I want to do the Gastronomy subject , because I want to learn how to make delicious desserts for my family . I want to do this course next week if it is possible , please . Could you help me , please ? I really need your help . Bye teacher , see you soon ! 
I think that banning the use of mobile phones in public places is a terrible idea . It is nonsense to ban everyone from using mobile phones . Of course , some functions of mobile phones in particular situations should be prohibited . Talking with a mobile phone on public transport and in restaurants and theatres are good examples . But almost all functions that mobile phones have should not be prohibited . Because mobile phones have many functions not to be annoying to people in public spaces . We can do many things with mobile phones silently . We can communicate with friends or business partners by using e -mail and enjoy watching SNS or movie sites like YOUTUBE . We can also study or work connecting on the internet . Today , we pack many things in our mobile phone . If you totally ban the use of mobile phones , you must ban reading a book , listening to music , writing something , answering crosswords and so on . This is what you are going to do . Banning the use of mobile phones in public places gave us only negative influences . It robs us of thinking about cases whether it is right to use mobile phones or not . Totally banning the use of mobile phones is a kind of insult to us . If you think of us seriously and you treat us not ridiculously , please give us the chance to think about using phones in several situations . 
Having a healthy lifestyle is nowadays important for everyone and , though everyone knows how to accomplish that goal , it does not happen that often . The problem is that school children or university students often do not do enough sports during the week . But still , it would not be a solution to force them to do sport activities at least three times a week . Everyone should be able to decide on their own if they want to do sport and how often . Of course , school children often spend most of their time inside with their mobile phones or else , but not everyone of them . If you force those who are inactive to be active and do some sport , it might happen that they hate it afterwards . They hear about the necessity of health often enough to have an opinion about it and make their own decision whether to move or not . Doing sports activities three times a week while maybe having two different exams in one week means a lot of stress . It occurs often that young people want to be active , but simply do not have enough time for it because school and university can be so physically demanding . Of course , going for a run can be really relaxing because you can organize your thoughts . But when you have to think about analysis , it can be really stressful as well . Especially if you are forced to do so . It basically gives the whole situation a negative aspect and you do not have as much fun as you could possibly have . Still , sport is very important for every one of us and , therefore , there would be other opportunities instead . For motivating young people in school or in university to become active , you could introduce different kinds of sports to them . One possible way would be to simply organize a trip to a climbing hall and show them how wonderful this sport could be . 
Here comes a new school year . It is my last year in this school . I am looking forward to the graduation , I am already fed up of this system . I have got some challenges this year and I have to pass them all to graduate . The first one is to reach level one in STANAG6001 exam of German . Then I have to reach 100 % of the credits . For that , I have to serve one month in Prostejov . That is the most exciting part . After school , I will serve there so I have a chance to learn a lot about my future working place and about my subordinates . After that , comes the hard part . I have to finish my diploma work and if I pass , I will be allowed to do the finex exams . Once I pass everything , I can start the next phase of my life . However , it would be great to improve in my English before I go , so I will try to reach a higher level in English by taking part in the STANAG3 exam . 
