Dear Rie , Thank you so much for inviting me to your dinner . I will be there on time . We have not seen each other since last month . I have so many things to share with you . I like almost all kinds of food , except cheese , which is the only thing that I will never enjoy . Could you cook something spicy ? Should I take my own chilli sauce ? See you tomorrow ! Yours , Tian 
I think it is acceptable to tell a lie . Of course , I do not like a lie which is told for selfish reasons or helping only myself . But you need to tell a lie in several specific situations . For example , the situation is that your grandfather or grandmother is in a hospital and his or her rest life is only a month . Do you need to say the truth in this situation ? I want them to live vividly without any concerns instead of telling them the truth . Of course , his or her opinion should have priority . Another situation is that you and your classmates ride on a bus to go to picnic . Then , one girl feels bad and gets carsick , but it takes more than an hour to arrive to the destination . Then , you should tell her that we will arrive soon and take it easy . If you think it is important to always tell the truth , it it very easy and simple to live . But I think that you throw away the chance of thinking about other people . If you take part in society , you should treat others more preciously . Do you think that always telling the truth is not for everyone but only for yourself ? I think that if you tell a lie for the people , it is more important than you always telling the truth . 
At first , you should put goals when you want to learn a new language . The goals of learning a language are known , they are : you should be fluent in listening and reading and writing and speaking . In addition , you should get some vocabulary every day . So these are the most important to learn any language , so if you want to learn any language , so if you want to start , you should begin with listening . Listening is very important for those who are beginners . If we look at a kid begin listening to his family , then he speaks and , in the end , he enters a school and starts to learn reading and writing . In fact , learning a new language is important for your IQ because when you learn a new language , it means your IQ will be at a high level , and it is up to you which language you should learn . Your goals are up to you , those you want to achieve , but I think English is the most important out of other languages because it is an international language . So in each country , you can speak Engilsh around the world , so this is what I have today . See you the next day with a new essay . This is Ali . 
I know you have heard about it a lot as the most crowded city in India , and it 's true . This is the city of dreams , the place where people do not sleep , the place where dreams are more important than a peaceful sleep . Yes , you guessed it right , it 's none other than Mumbai . My beautiful home town Mumbai . As you know , Mumbai is famous for its food and also for its museums , such as the Shivaji Art museum . There are different parks and restaurants in the city . 
