In my opinion , animals belong in nature , but I am not against zoos . Please do not confuse my words . I think zoos are important . Zoos allow people to learn about animals , their environment and what they eat . Furthermore , zoos are family spaces where children can enjoy nature without out the wild life risk . Also , the most important zoos in the world have helped to conserve some animal species which are disappearing . For example , many animals in danger of extinction have reproduced in zoos . On the other hand , I do not agree with people who have wild animals locked in cages . In my country , there are many homes where there are exotic birds in cages . Others have squirrels and turtles as pets . In my opinion , that is animal cruelty . Ordinary people do not know about wild animal health care . Also , people do not supply suitable food to the animals . These animals could not reproduce in captivity because , most of the time , they do not have a couple . 
