No doubt video games are too popular among children and , because of this , most of the parents are anxious . Playing video games , whether good or bad , is a big matter of debate in society . In my opinion , playing video games is not good for children . There are a lot of problems created by video games . If any students are in the habit of it , they will not give proper time to studying while at child age group the mental make up were decided . Behaviour and attitude is crucial for growth in life . Most of the boys who used to play video games , their behaviour is aggressive . As we know , looking at an LCD screen or mobile screen for a long time causes a problem for the eyes . If any kids get problems in their eyes , then how will they study better in their teenage years while , at this age , they will have to spend most of the time studying . They will always complain of headaches , eye irritation , and other things . Their studying would get affected , their performance would decrease , which results in a less secure position in companies . 
