Nowadays , in almost all cities around the world , we can find a zoo , but in my opinion , these are places where most animals suffer and we should close most of them . Firstly , people think that zoos are places where kids will have a very enjoyable time because they can see exotic animals , but they do not think about how stressed and scared this will make them feel . On the other hand , it is true that the fact of being able to see such astonishing animals that we probably would not have the opportunity to see again in our lives is an awesome experience . A further point is that animals in zoos are locked in usually not very ample spaces , and these animals , as wild animals , must be free in their own habitat . Moreover , they do not receive the best food and that is why most of them die . In conclusion , from my point of view , I believe that zoos must be closed because although we can see a lot of incredible animal species , while we enjoy it , they suffer and we should let them live free . 
