In this day and age , most of the time , young people feel that the educational system is not suited for them . Some students can learn things very easily and find that they are not using their capacities to their fullest or the opposite , being this the students who cannot have good grades regardless of what they study , as they do not have the ability to make the most of it . If a school is considering this when giving the certificate of graduation to their students , they ought to be aware of the opportunities in the surroundings to better facilitate the connection between both sides . Youngsters sometimes have low self -esteem , which makes it difficult for them to decide what to do , fearing the approach they have with others . As for adults , they should stimulate creativity , giving them tools to develop their integration , helping them and encouraging the demonstration of their points of view . Certainly , this type of work will help young people to engage with society , develop a better mindset , learn by doing , and build intergenerational relationships and it will bring people closer to each other as there is always an opportunity to find solutions for problems when there is solidarity . Bearing this in mind , volunteering could create a space for alternative means of community support , it could also help the economic system , raise humanitarian values as there is no technical obligation which would only require respect between one another . 
