Understanding is one of the main concerns in teaching . While engaging for a long period with one group of teachers , a good relationship between the students and teacher develops and they can understand the psychology of each other . I think one teacher is sufficient to teach the students well . I feel this way for two reasons , which I wish to explore in this essay . Firstly , I would like to discuss the point of psychology . If people live for a long time together , then they can understand their body language very well and their way of presenting or teaching . Grasping study material is not so easy if the student is unable to understand the teacher 's personality and it takes time to build between the student and teacher . If they have the same teacher for a long time , then they could understand which subject or specific point to focus on more . Secondly , if the teacher is changed each year for the students , then the teacher will teach the students professionally . 
