It 's an interesting question . We have the same family , parents for our whole life . And it 's important to build the relationship based on respecting and loving each other . With a teacher , it could be like that . But the question is that in our life we will have to relate with many kinds of people and their different personalities . So we need to have experiences with many different people in our childhood to strengthen our knowledge about relationships . Doing that , we would learn to respect other opinions , understand their feelings , their cultures and why they are so . Having different teachers in our life will contribute to having contact with different techniques , behaviour , speaking . Another special point is empathy . So if you do not like someone , you do not need to be with this same person each year . In my opinion , I think we have the right to know different people , so it 's important to have a different teacher each year . 
There are 2 main reasons why there are few doctors in rural areas . First , the number on the whole of doctors is not enough . If the problem is its imblance , there should be many doctors who do not earn much money in cities . Seeing from doctors , it is natural that they live and work in convenient places unless they have special reasons to go to rural areas . Next , rural areas do not have several support systems so that doctors can keep working there . I think a good business is made from a good relationship . Once I heard the following news . A doctor goes to a rural area to work there . This village has only 500 people . The locals envy the doctor and they ignore him . After all , they could not communicate well and the doctor came to get a mental disease . The medical system collapsed . To solve this problem , a cooperation between the government and the doctors ' association is needed . Of course , we should increase the number of doctors , but it is meaningless if the quality falls . And it is similarly important to spread the range of co -medical worker jobs . It is quite important to do well as a team . It leads to more efficient work . Considering the speciality of doctors , the government should assign doctors to specific areas . Having ' public ' doctors may improve this situation . 
