Nowadays , a lot of students choose to study abroad in countries with usually another language and culture , which I think is such an educational and unforgettable experience to have . Firstly , studying in another country for a year or even some months will benefit students by giving them a great deal of knowledge and experience about a language and the traditions of the country , because while they are learning and studying at a high school or university , they are also discovering the way of thinking and living in a completely different country . On the other hand , being an exchange student could be not as exciting as it seems . For example , if a student is too shy or not very gregarious , they can find adapting to a new country a very harsh experience . Also , they can feel so homesick , which can be harmful for their school course . A further point is that the fact of traveling alone and at first finding yourself alone in a place you have never been to , it 's also a maximum change for the young people to become more independent , learn how to look after themselves and also they will make and meet new friends . In conclusion , despite some disadvantages that having an exchange year in another country might bring , I believe that if someone has the opportunity , they must take it , because I bet it will be an astonishing year , which in addition to making you learn a lot , will change your life completely . 
