We live in an age when most of us have a bad lifestyle . Not because we do not exercise , but because we eat a lot of junk foods , which cause a bad health condition . There are some reasons that I can explain in this statement . First , we can workout inside of our own house without going out , whenever we want . However , sometimes we are poorly equipped . For instance , you have to drive or walk to the gym to do some exercise , which means you still have to go out . Secondly , exercising outside of our house can have its benefits , such as taking some fresh air . But on the other hand , you cannot do it all the time , for example , in the case of bad weather . Therefore , an indoor workout is not that bad . Another thing to consider is eating healthy food that can keep us fit without doing any exercise . However , healthy food can cost a lot . When it comes to eating healthy food , we have to provide the ingredients ourselves . To sum up , doing exercises is not a bad thing . But you need to have time . For me , I prefer eating healthily . 
Yes , I usually do exercise every day at various times , depending on my schedule . Actually , I do my exercise outside because of time and because I do not have a subscription to the gym . The types of exercise I usually do are : walking , using a bike device and body exercise . 
From my point of view , 60 percent of the teaching process depends on the way that a teacher presents the materials and lessons . What strategies he uses and exercises and methods to navigate , these benefit the course . In addition is how he does assessments for the students to make sure they understand the lessons . The second 40 percent walks around the teacher , his charisma , the techniques he provides to attract the attention of the students . In my opinion , it is not about the years the teacher teaches or having a new teacher each year . Many students tend to a good teacher 's reputation . Also , the views of his learners , are they satisfied with him or frustrated because of him , the scores the students got when he taught them . Obviously it is more than the teacher , it is the learning organization , teaching procedures and skilled teachers in the end of the circle . 
Nowadays , the computer is very popular . It plays an important role in our lives . Like other people , especially teenagers , I usually use a computer . I use it 2-3 times a day . The computer has a lot of functions that has made it become popular . Firstly , we can use it to study . We can study online on the Internet , and study by ourselves through many websites . Secondly , we can read a lot of newspapers or magazines without going out to buy them every day . The computer is very useful , right ? Thirdly , the computer is also a device for us to relax . We can watch a lot of films and movies on a computer screen , listen to the music we like or chat with our friends . Sometimes , we can make a video call to someone we love . In my opinion , what I enjoy doing most with a computer is studying . I can learn a lot of things and the lessons are extremely useful all the time . The computer has many benefits but do not abuse it and depend on it too much . 
My favourite season of the year is summer . Summer is special for me because I was born in this season and my family too . During the summer , you can wear whatever clothes you want , because it is very warm and sunny and you do not need to worry about snow or rain or something else . Also , you can go to the beach , which is my favourite activity out of all of them . After going to the beach , you can go to an aqua park , which is fun to do with your buddies . You can do a lot of fun activities in this season with your friends or family . I 'm happy when summer comes , because I 'm a tennis player and the season starts during summer , so I can go to tournaments , meet new people and play tennis with them . This is my favourite part of the year , what 's yours ? 
Hi Mike , Last week I went to a rock concert with a couple of friends . I decided to go to this concert because it was my first time going to this type of concert . All the artists were very well known , they did a really great job and we had a lot of fun dancing to their music , a great time , but during the concert something bad happened . One of my friends passed out and we called an ambulance because he was not responding . I had a very nice time at that concert . What about you , what did you do last week ? Looking forward to hearing from you . See you soon , John 
I think animals belong to nature . The idea of forcing an animal to live outside its natural environment is not good to me . I do not like it . If we want to learn about them , we could prepare and adapt natural places . We could enjoy a safari too . There are many different things we could to do to enjoy and learn about them . I firmly believe those animals suffer in captivity . Why make them suffer ? In the end , these zoos are businesses . Should we trade with these animals ' feelings ? I do not think so . I think we could do it better as a society and respect the place of nature . Our children and scientists would agree with a different way to manage this situation , for sure . Please , let them enjoy a life in their environment , this is the only way to grow as a society . 
Learning can be difficult if we do not use the appropriate tools . For example , learning English with many tools at the same time will make learners confused since different tools have different unique features . This text is a suggestion to learn English using a web -based tool named Write and Improve . Write and Improve is an English learning tool developed by Cambridge University . It has many features which allow a learner take most benefit of the tool . At first , it invites the learner to write in English on broad topics within different levels , from beginner to business level . It also offers a preparation for the IELTS test , a test that is used for university entrance in some Commonwealth countries . Apart from that , the learners can create their own workbook or join other workbooks . This feature can also be used by English teachers to share the homework with their students and to make online assessments . Let 's give a more detailed example . When learners enter a Write and Improve workbook , for instance beginner level , they are asked to choose a topic and write an article ( it can be review , summary , or argumentation ) about that topic . Write and Improve ( W&I ) requires a minimum word numbers to qualify that a task is done . When learners accomplish this requirement , they can submit their works by clicking the " Check " button . W&I will assess that work and give feedback . The learners can revise their writing based on the given feedback and submit it again to obtain such improvements . W&I will show the score of the writing sequentially . 
As the new year starts , I have a few resolutions to make . First , I have to say that I am pretty satisfied with my school performance in general . Especially , accounting , math and information technology are subjects I am pretty pleased with . The minor subjects could not be better either . I am a very ambitious student , which is why my grades are always As . On the other hand , improvements are still possible . Language courses are the ones that would need the most improvement , in my point of view . I would really like to be able to speak unprepared on every topic that may come up . Moreover , I also want to focus on grammar structures and my writing skills . In order to reach these goals , I intend to practice every day using the help of certain online platforms . Next to this , I really want to keep up the work I already do for school . Never give up ! 
In my opinion , offices in separate rooms are more comfortable than offices where most employees are in one room . Indeed , it is easier to help each other , but if an amount of your colleagues has to call important partners of the company the whole time , it can be really disturbing . Therefore , employees are not able to focus and concentrate on their own work and that is very inconvenient . Due the fact that most people work more slowly and more carelessly while they are being disturbed , not only the company suffers from it , but also the staff themselves . For instance , my dad is a clerk in a company , where all employees work in one room and he describes the situation as very uncomfortable and annoying , because his colleagues are on the phone the whole day . It takes him twice as long to finish his projects now . To put the main in a nutshell , an office with an open design is not quite right for employees who have to focus on their own work . 
I think that it is better to have walls to separate the offices of different employees . First of all , it can be very destructive if there are no walls between different offices . There are employees who prefer to work in a calm environment . It is very important to protect those employees and give them right so that they can work in a suitable environment . Furthermore , not all employees in a company conduct the same work , so it is illogical to put all employees in an open office . 
My favorite indoor activity is practicing table tennis . I like table tennis because you need a faster movement than your opponent to get points , and that makes this sport quite a dynamic game . I can remember exactly the last time that I practiced table tennis , however that time was when I was in the university with a group of students from my department one or two years ago . 
I use my computer quite often , I would say that every day I am checking my computer . I usually use my computer for many and diverse tasks . One is to check my email out and another is to write down about my research . When I am not doing those tasks , I can stay in front of my computer checking facebook , watching videos on You Tube or reading the news . If I had to select one task that I enjoy the most , I would say that watching videos on You Tube such as documentaries about nature and music videos . 
Hi Ana , That 's right , I am super motivated about learning English once again . As you must know , I want to travel around Australia and New Zealand and then to visit Europe next summer . Traveling is my passion and good communication in English is a must to get the best out of any traveling adventure . This is a dream that I want to fulfil as soon as possible . That 's why I am learning this language . Kind regards , 
I think that the future of travel is going to be not so polluting for the environment . I think that soon we are going to have flying cars , robots that are going to tell us to stop , all of the usual things that we do today are going to be done by robots . I do not think that human beings can be replaced by robots , I do not think that is a good idea . We do not know what they are capable of . I do not trust robots with artificial intelligence . So I think the best thing to do is to keep our head on our shoulders , to try to think more about the dangers and less about the money , to think more about humans and less about some bills . I think that our safety is more important than what robots can offer us . I think that what recommends them is : the speed , the fact that they will not be paid , they wo not be late to work , they are never tired . 
I think that this subject is a very boring one . I just woke up and my head is full of other stuff . I think that the " School of the Future " is going to change . Some of our schools have already changed , some of them have improved their teaching methods , some have invested lots of money in order to improve and make education easier for their students . The only problem is the big difference between the schools ' levels . Some schools have invested lots of money and are using technology to come closer to their students . For example , in Romania , we still do not have toilets in most of our schools . We still do not have drinking water in our schools , we still pay for our education even if the government should pay for it . So first , I think we should change the people that are responsible for those things , then invest in education . 
I think that the first purpose of television was to bring information closer to people . After a period , TV channels started to produce entertainment videos and movies . There are a couple of channels that can bring education closer to the audience , but most of them are used to control the masses . A couple of them are TV news channels , other are specialized only in playing movies , and there are a couple of channels that are doing all in one . The most watched channel in Romania I think is Pro TV . It is one of the oldest channels . Sometimes , I watch Digi TV , but most of the times , I watch movies on Netflix . As you know , Netflix is an online platform that gives you access to hundreds of online movies , the only condition is to pay your monthly bill . 
Hi there Leyla , How are you ? Thanks for the invitation to your birthday party , it is such an exciting place where you are going to organise a DJ , and lots of your friends . I need to tell you that I ca not go , not because I do not want to , you know that you are my best friend , it is just that my father has had an accident in a car , and I need to go and help him in his house . But I really want to celebrate your birthday . What if I invite you next Friday for dinner , if you have time ? Let me know what you think about this . Regards , 
I have a lot of indoor activities that I do , especially in my home . The sigficant one is to do exercises like : walking or using the Orbitrac . The second one is cooking , I really enjoy cooking for my family cakes , sweets and main courses . When I do my hobbies , I feel relaxed and useful . The last time I cooked for my family was today , I made kunafa , it is a kind of eastern sweet , I made it with cream , sugar , butter and chocolate . Moreover , exercise is a habit for me and my hobby , I usually do it every day in different ways : walking , running , and swimming . 
In my opinion , I think a zoo is a better place to let people learn about animals , such as families take their children to the zoo and also schools take their students to get information about animals , because of the high level of safety and security . But in other words , the way to save animals ' rights and people 's rights is putting animals in a zoo during a specific period of time , to let people see them and take pictures to learn or whatever . The reason is if we let people visit animals in their living place or forest , that surely would put a danger on their life , due to there being no barriers or cages to prevent an attack from the animals , and the risk is too high . To find the best solution and to make a balance between them is to leave the animals living in their place and create a schedule to transfer them to a zoo for available visits by families and schools . 
Video games are a double -edged sword . If we use it in the right way that is allowed to the children play 1 to 2 hours on video games . The advantage of video games is letting the child interact with an electronic device and learn the basic words and steps of using any electronic device . Also it is helpful for the parents to use video games as a reinforcement if their son or daughter completes their homework or task . The disadvantage of using video games allowed to the children sit on it a long period of time , without telling them about the consequences of that , like eye problems and stress on their bodies , heavy weight , lack of concentration . In my opinion , the solution is to create an activity schedule for the children to manage their time and distribute the activities in specific periods during the day , furthermore , making a balance between priorities . 
If I had to choose between money or my health , I would choose my health . Money is not so important if you ca not enjoy it , if you do not have time to spend it . I think that we should keep a balance between work and our personal life . Life is too short just to make money . Life is passing by and no fortune can buy it back . I think that the biggest fortune is our health . If we lose it , it 's very hard to get it back . The strange thing is that people are running after money all their lives and after they have it , they use it to be healthy again . Then they run after money again , but this time they ca not get their health back . After that , most of them are dying and have many regrets about how they lived their lives . I think our biggest treasure is our health and we should try our best to keep it . 
I do not have a favourite film . The type of movies that I like are comedies , action movies and love stories . My favourite movie is Nemo . Nemo is a small fish that had memory problems from the beginning of her life . She had a problem with short time memory , long time memory was not affected . The movie presents Nemo and her friends ' adventures in searching for her way home . The road was full of challenges , but they managed to help Nemo to get home . The story ends with a beautiful scene with Nemo and her friends playing . I think that everything turned out the way it should . 
I like to exercise every day , on a busy day or a free day , because it makes my psychological and physical health better . I love exercising outdoors but not in a gym . I like walking in the garden and getting fresh air , and also at my home I am trying on a machine . My favorite activities are going to my family park and walking , it is in the countryside , and there the place is quiet , clean , with nature , and without pollution , and I can exercise all that I want . In the summertime all my family swim in the swimming pool : my parents , sisters , brothers , and our kids , all of us can swim . 
Studying at the university is a challenging time for both parents and children . Very often , children have to move from their parents ' because the university is in another city . Whereas children , who live in a big city , where they have a university , decided to stay at home with parents . However , sometimes , even if the university is in the same city , children prefer living without parents . In my view , a better choice is to live without parents while children are attending university . First of all , this is an excellent opportunity to let children mature . Children start to live on their own and they have to take responsibility for their decisions and choices . They can ask their parents for advice , obviously . But they have to dotted their I 's . And another thing is a fact that , as we know , student life is a time when children get to know new friends . In consequence , children want to invite new people to their house , for instance , to party . Therefore , it 's more comfortable to invite them to their own house not to their parents ' house . Without a doubt , a more enjoyable meeting is with age - mates . Nevertheless , as we know , there are two sides to every story . , . living with parents when studying has positive sides too . While children are students and live with their family , they need not worry about many things , such as money . After all , not everybody needs to have a free house to invite many friends . In summary , I honestly believe that it is better to move away during your studying time . It 's the start of a new independent adult life . Everybody ought to have time to grow up and mature . To me , the best time for that is studying time , exactly . 
It is maybe the most challenging decision for every student to find the university where they want to study . Besides the question of what they want to study , they will also question where they want to study and , last but no least , where they want to live . After the students successfully apply for a university , they might need to move out . Luckily , there are plenty options , where they can live . For some students , campus life will be the first choice because they need other students around them . They like to share a bedroom and spend as much time as possible with other people . On the other hand , there are also cozy single bedroom apartments near universities . Some students are more introverted and do not like to have a crowd of other students around them . However , living on your own will let you also learn how to take care of yourself . There will be no mom , who cooks a nourishing lunch for you or washes your stinky , dirty socks . This will be all part of your experience . You will learn how to deal with it and it will be the best time of your life ! Your family will always be by your side and they will also support you . 
Today , video games have divided the population into two sides . The first side is made of people who think that video games have a negative impact on children , boys and men . The second side is made of people who think that video games are a way that can let you be whoever you want . Honestly , I 'm on the second side because I think that video games are not negative , the only thing that is negative is the time you spend playing them . For example , playing 10 hours or more without taking a break can cause serious damage in the children/boys . This is the true problem . I do not know why some people think that video games are dangerous , but everyone is free to say everything they wants . There are so many scientific studies that show the benefits of playing video games , such as letting you take difficult decisions in the least time possible , or maybe the fact that the eyes are more powerful . With this , I mean the ability to see more things moving , etc ... But also , on the other side , there are negative effects , like I said before , playing too long ( 10 hours or more a day ) can have a negative impact , it can make people to have bad views or strong headaches and more . Personally , I love video games , they let me go to places where I ca not go , do things that normal people can only dream . I see them like a playable book . 
The teacher is an important figure in the world of school . They are an important entity because they can teach you so many important things . Having the same teacher every year , personally for me , is a good thing , because this allows the student to study without problems , while having a different teacher every year makes things more difficult for the student , because they have a different type of explaining method , which can be bad or maybe aggressive . I remember when I was in the second year of high school , my French teacher changed , and me and my classmates were so disappointed because we had to learn another type of French lessons , but the teacher was so right and we liked her . 2 years later , this teacher left her job because her husband died . Then we had another teacher , but we had so many problems with her because she made things so easy , our grades were high , but our skills were so low . In conclusion , having the same teacher is better . 
I think that doing exercise is important , but there are some more important things , like a wedding , your kid 's ceremony , a ceremony of a loved one , or do you prefer to do exercise than attend those important events ? It is better to attend those more important events to show that you care . When you have free time , you can do exercise , you can do sport with your children , that is doing exercise , you can do a competition to make it more fun . Also it is very important to exercise , because it is important to our health , to keep a healthy body and a healthy mind . You need to do exercise when you have free time to be healthy . You can also enjoy exercise by listening to your favourite podcast or music . I think it is best to attend special events than doing exercise , but you should do exercise when you can . 
Some high schools have a requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate . Volunteer work can offer a large range of diversity . It can be to help homeless people , to teach a language to foreigners , or to pick up trash on the beach . They do not need to be in a large non -governmental organisation to discover what volunteer work is . Students will encounter many opportunities , and can choose a realm where they feel comfortable in . High school is a period where children become adults and are questioning their beliefs and opinions . In my opinion , that 's an excellent idea for many reasons . Volunteer work presents many advantages for students . First , it 's work experience . And like any work experience , it will help students to develop new skills and to build a professional network . Secondly , some teenagers might discover a new interest while working as a volunteer , and find out their path . Finally , volunteer work will confront young adults with people in need and will make them realise in which society they are living . It will open their mind , and their beliefs , and it will help them to become more responsible adults . Even though I believe that 's a great initiative , I think it might be difficult for young adults to manage their time . High school is already very demanding in terms of homework , adding volunteer work can lead them to some difficulties . The lack of free time can be very stressful for some teenagers . High schools requiring a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate must keep in mind these difficulties . Nevertheless , I am convicted that 's a great idea . 
Whether people should always tell the truth in any situation remains a highly continuous public discourse . Although it is undeniable that honesty is of great importance , I strongly believe that , in some circumstances , not revealing the truth is an effective choice to protect both speakers and listeners . On the one hand , honesty is a valuable personality trait that everyone should have in order to archive a better life . In contemporary society , people are likely to broaden their horizons and develop their soft skills by working with people . The fact has demonstrated that people can only co -operate with one another through trust and honesty , which play an essential role in building a long -term relationship . Honest people will never flatter another and will make progress by their own qualification . Moreover , telling the truth is considered as one of the most effective ways to not only increase understanding and sympathy among people , but also help people to respect and appreciate the differences of others . Therefore , many companies today choose employees , who are both qualified and reliable , because they believe that these people will become powerful workforces for development of society . 
In my free time , I play the saxophone . I 've been playing the saxophone for almost two years . I play it twice a week . Music stimulates my creativity and brings me to the present , that 's what I like most about the instrument . Last time I practiced was a Victor Jara 's song called " La Partida , " it 's an instrumental song from the 70 's , simple but beautiful . Now I 'm getting out of reads , and I ca not go outside to buy some more , so I 'm a little worried because I need them to practice . 
My favorite indoor activity is cooking . I got a new microwave machine recently , because my previous one was broken . This microwave has many functions , such as baking , roasting , heating , and steaming . I 'm interested these functions . That 's the reason why I continue cooking . Of course I cooked my dinner last night by using this machine , and got delicious food . 
Studying abroad is very popular these days . Many students decide to go abroad to high school or university . It 's a fantastic way to make your CV better . However , it does not have only advantages . Nevertheless , as far as I can tell , I 'm a person who would like to go to university abroad too . First of all , as I said , studying abroad is a very good way to make your CV better . Nowadays , many companies would rather take a person with a foreign university degree than local . To my mind , that person can seem to be bolder , more self -assured , which are meaningful attributes for directors . Equally important is that studying abroad is a valuable life lesson . A student goes abroad on his or her own , so he or she had take control of his or her life . There will be no one , of course , who will do things except him or her . It does not mean that he or she will be alone , obviously . Studying abroad is a superb way to make new friends , of course , but friends wo not make him or her dinner or clean his or her room . Actually , we have here another paramount advantage , which is making new friends and exploring the world . As we know , people who travel the world are more open -minded than someone who stays in one place all their life . But on the other hand , studying abroad can be stressful . A student goes to a place where he or she does not know anybody . It is a new place , a new world for him or her . Another disadvantage could be a language problem . Sometimes the student can have a big problem with understanding something , and of course , it makes him or her feel stressed , as I mentioned earlier . In summary , I honestly believe that there are more advantages than disadvantages . Due to that , in my mind , students should study abroad , if they have a chance . 
Every school class has at least two students who love to do sports activities . On the other hand , there are also some students who are very lazy and hate sports . Many schools offer a gym or classes but not all of them are compulsory . The hard part of every school or university is now to find the ultimate balance between forcing their students to be active and not to over do it . Before I write more about the amount of sports activities , I would like to catch up on the main importance of sports . Many clinical studies have proven that any kind of physical movement can boost your immune system , improve your cardiovascular system and prevent depression . Those three examples are just a brief insight into the benefits of sports . Of course , no school or university has the ability to offer thousands of different sports options . They may give you a choice of elected classes . For example , a running group , football team , cheerleading classes or even a small gym with free weights . However , it does not matter what kind of sports you prefer , it just matters that you focus on your well -being and health . Now , we can talk more about the amount of exercise per week . First of all , there is no golden rule for this . It really depends on what kind of sports you do and what goals each person has . To come back to the main question of forcing students to do at least 3 sports activities per week , it would be miracle to follow this system , but it 's not realistic . Students should have at least one to two classes in their weekly school calender where they need to do some kind of sports activity . They should have the possibility to choose their preferences , but they should not be forced to do three sports activities per week . Sports should still be a hobby and not a must ! 
I 'm used to using a computer around two times a day , I need to do it for my English practise and because I have to write a big variety of documents . These are not the only reasons I use a computer , its usefulness is also related to the way I keep in touch with my friends . The most enjoyable thing I do is to play chess and follow online English lessons , apart from when I do not have a good internet connection . 
Well , I think it 's better to have the same teacher for several years . It 's better for the educational process , you know , the teacher can create something suitable for the student , an individual educational plan , because he knows him better . I think the relationship between student and teacher must be close , from an educational point of view . If that relationship does not work , if it 's uncomfortable for the student or the teacher , just in that case , there has to be a change . Education has an emotional side that is important , I 've been reading some experts that say : " Emotion goes before reason " which means , emotion influences rational thinking more than we suspect . All the things that we think we feel them first . If we have a comfortable space to learn , we 'll learn how to think better . In the same vein , that comfortable space ca not last forever , we must overcome stages as we grow and that stage has to come with different teachers . 
I agree with the opinion that zoos are good places for people to learn about animals . Because we will have many less chances to touch and think about animals if zoos are prohibited . We also might not be concerned about various animal problems . Of course , some people worry about animals which are tamed in a zoo . But unfortunately , nobody knows that animals really feel sad or have bad feelings . This is just an imagination of humans . Then what we should do for animals is think about animals and do actions like a conservation . I think that there are mainly 2 tasks for zoo managers . First , they should not run only for their profit . They should take part in some actions for animals . They should never forget that they run with living creatures and they should partly work for animals . Second , they must tell visitors true stories about each animal . There might be a future zoologist . I hope that managers help children be more interested in animals . Anyway , I want managers to run with a social responsibility . If they keep this condition , the above 2 things will come to be true . 
I think that foreign languages are very important nowadays . If you manage to learn one or two foreign languages , your chances of being hired are increased by more than 50 % . If you want to learn a foreign language , I think the best way you could do that is following an English course , also to learn more easily the language , you could also watch movies , try to find a native person that could help you learn more easily , doing exercises at home will help you a lot . I recommend you also use Duolingo to learn a foreign language . It 's really helpful because you can write , learn and also speak using Duolingo . One of the most important aspects if you want to learn a new language I think is your determination . If you have the ambition to learn it , you will succeed . 
I use my computer every day . I use it for many reasons , for instance , I learn English online , and I take some lessons every day . I use it to research the updates of my speciality . I check online news to know what is happening all over the world . I look for the cooking recipe for today 's dinner , and so on . When I chat with my friends on the SNS website , I feel very fun and comfortable . 
I think students benefit more from having new teachers each year . Every teacher has their speciality and character . If students have the same teacher for several years , they ca not get new knowledge which the teacher does not know , they ca not notice other points of view which the teacher does not have and they ca not feel comfortable if the teacher 's character is not fit for them . Students can get new experience from new teachers each year . Such experience can change their mind against their opinion about something , the purpose of their life and their future dream . Even if the new teacher is not fit to the students , they just stand it for only one year and they can meet another new one next year . It may take several days or weeks to become fit to a new teacher every year , but it should give students a great opportunity to know how to interact with other people . 
I 'm not only a generous and introvert person , but also a social person , so I really want to be a volunteer , especially when I am sitting on the school chair . I felt really happy when I saw that requirement . In my opinion , students like me will have a lot of benefits when they take part in some social work and become volunteers . Firstly , they will feel happy when they help people or protect the environment . From that , they will have more and more motivation to do much good work and have good behavior . Secondly , they will have lots of chances to practise many skills necessary for their future , such as community skills , problem -solving skills and so on . Thirdly , they will recognise their advantages , also their disadvantages , through real work . From that , they can promote their advantages and fix their disadvantages . Fourthly , if they become a volunteer , they can contact with many people so they can improve their ability for teamwork . Fifthly , through what they do when they are volunteers , they will have a lot of good memories and much useful experience . Finally , after graduating , they will have a good relationship and more friends . I hope the students will be a volunteer before they graduate . 
Hi Tom , Thank you for your last e -mail . Indeed , " The Boy in the Striped Piyjamas " is a really touching movie . I understand why it 's your favourite movie . What about me ? Oh , it 's really hard to say what is my favourite movie . Actually , I enjoy many movies . But I reckon I can choose " Gladiator . " Have you ever seen it ? As you know , I 'm a fan of historical movies , so , as you can see , the topic of this movie suits excellently . I would say this movie is very touching too , like yours . Honestly speaking , you should see this movie . I 'm sure you will love it . There are many conspiracies and plot twists , just as you like ! Please , write to me soon about whether you enjoy this movie . I 'm really curious . Love , Ann 
I loved zoos when I was a child . Animals are so amazing . We could learn about life seeing them . And we could also learn about respecting them . But today I have another opinion . In some zoos they ca not be happy . They have the right to live in their own environment , as we have . And in some zoos it 's not possible , because they do not offer good living conditions . But at the same time , to get to know them , it 's impossible to visit them in the wild . We will be an invader in their home . So zoos will continue to be an option . But they have to be bigger , to provide a home like their environment . It wo not be cheap ! ! But if we think it will be the fair option . I ca not see another . But it has other problem . Being expensive to maintain these zoos , who will get to know the animals ? Will it be available for poor children ? Well , they have the internet , but it , of course , will not be the same . 
