What is the most important thing in our life ? We have a lot of different answers for this question . Somebody says the money , lots of money , other people say happy family , . . . For me , the most important and precious thing in our life is health . I guess there are a lot of people who think like me , but most of them do not care about their health much , especially young people , like university students and school children . I 'm also a school student , so I will understand a part of young people 's thinking and the things they care about much . Before , I was a lazy person about taking care of myself , especially exercise and health . I just concentrated on studies , my goals and the way I could achieve them . I used to hate doing exercise in the morning very much because I thought it wasted my precious time . Even my mother always reminded me do exercise or play some sports . But I often ignored them . Then some little problems with health came to me . Suddenly , I realized my faults at that time and I started caring about my health more than before . There are a lot of reasons for us to be concerned our health , especially doing more exercise at least 3 times a week . Firstly , health is the most important thing in our life . Our parents gave birth to us very strong , having good health , so we must have the responsibility to protect our health through doing exercise , playing sports , changing our bad habits and also lifestyle . Secondly , a bad lifestyle affects our yield of work and studying . We always feel tired , exhausted and do not have energy to continue the work . Finally , we are usually unconscious , so we will have negative thinking and make a not good decision . So young people should play sports at least 3 times a week . We will feel better and have more energy after each training session . We also have a lot of friends . It will improve relationships . There are a lot of benefits when we play sports . Therefore , we should play it more time . 
Since we have all been locked down in our houses because of the Covid -19 virus , I have been doing my workouts at home . Before the Corona crisis , I was doing semi -professional running . I also participated in a quarter marathon race , and I got the second place . Therefore , nowadays I need the appropriate workouts to keeps my cardiovascular activity high . I tried the Nike app , and it was fabulous . I defined my terms at first , then the app gave me the suitable exercises based on my level . I feel really active and energized after each workout , and I am so hopeful that after Corona , I will be completely ready to continue my sport . I am practicing with this application every day , and the last time was 20 minutes ago . 
My favorite indoor activity is yoga . Yoga does not need hardly any active movement . I pose in a specific position and change positions slowly with calm breathing during yoga . Those activities strengthen my inner muscles and let my thoughts clear . I did yoga this weekend at home , for 30 minutes so I refreshed myself well . 
