A NEW SCHOOL YEAR Introduction The purpose of this report is to think and plan my new school year including things that I already achieved , subjects that I can improve and establish new goals to achieve during the year . My comfortable areas of study Since I was really small , I 'm good at mathematics , English and Geography . I have always been keen on those subjects so my plan for this year , although it will be a little bit more complicated than last year , is to maintain that level . Improving subjects On the other hand , I 'm used to struggling in areas like the Spanish language , physics or arts , so during this course , I 'll try to give more attention to those things in order to get better marks so next year wo not be that difficult . Motivation and effort Finally , encouragement and endeavour , these are going to be the keys for me this year . Working really hard during school time and relaxing on holidays are my plans so that I can achieve all my aims . Moreover , being organised and constant are indispensable too . Conclusion If you really work hard , you can get whatever you want , all you need is willpower . At the end , you will be proud of what you have achieved , so I 'm feeling really confident and elated to start this new year . 
