I think there are two things that are more important for our health than exercise . They are sleep and diet . Unless we have a standard healthy body , we cannot do appropriate exercise to improve our health . In order to get a good body , enough sleep and a balanced diet are essential . Firstly , without enough sleep , we suffer from disordered conditions , such as anemia . In addition to that , we will have rough skin . It will make us sad to live a healthy life . Secondly , without a balanced diet , we suffer from less energy , such as dizziness . In addition to that , we will get fat . It will make us lack motivation to do anything . For these reasons , I think sleep and diet are more important . 
