People use mobile phones everywhere , at home , in the park , on the street , on public transport , in cafes and restaurants . They use them to make calls , use social media , or just listen to music . This practice has been growing from year to year . On public transport , for example , we almost see no one using their mobile phones . These people 's habits often disturb the comfort of using public facilities including public transport . To reduce or avoid this practice , banning the use of mobile phones should be implemented . Among all activities , using mobile phones , the use of mobile phones to make calls , including video calls , should be strictly prohibited . This policy will prohibit people from overusing mobile phones . Other activities like listening to music , including watching videos ; reading books or articles , and other activities which do not make any noise should be allowed . This rule should be clearly written in every pubic facility including public transport . The implementation of the rule could be different between public facilities . For instance , we prohibit making calls on public transport and in restaurants , but we allow it in train station buildings . There should be an exception in which all people are allowed to make emergency calls wherever they are . Furthermore , the exact rules should be discussed among different kinds of people : workers , civil servants , and students . By implementing the ban of mobile phone usage , the convenience of using public facilities , like public transport and restaurants , should be improved . 
I have studied on the website Write and Improve for a long time , probably since two years ago . Casually , I found this website when I talked with my friend . She reviewed for me about a helpful website to improve writing skills and I tried it . This website is really useful and it has a lot of interesting functions for me to improve my writing skills . Firstly , Write and Improve has different levels , from beginner to advanced or higher , which is business and just for fun . So you can easily choose the level suitable for you . For me , when I just started practicing on this website , I chose the beginner level to be familiar with writing , then I tried a higher level , intermediate , and , now , it is advanced . Secondly , it has a lot of varied topic and fields so you have many options , you can choose any topic you like . I 'm an introvert person , so I usually choose a topic relevant to society and some topics about issues in life . My favourite topic is the debate about whether to become a volunteer in school or not . Thirdly , it also has a good system to check your mistakes in your essay , point out the mistakes you made and the way to fix them . It is very convenient and useful , right ? Fourthly , it has a process board to let you know your progress . Fifthly , it also has a timer regime for you to check your writing ability . Finally , the screen of website is completely in English , so it will help you to improve the language you are learning . My advice is you should try to learn this website Write and Improve . 
