I want to tell you more about a new tool I have discovered lately . As I am myself a learner of English , I am always looking for new supports that can be instructive . Being curious is , in my opinion , the first step to achieve something , and looking for a solution by yourself is an excellent way to go . So , let me tell you more about my finding : Write and Improve . To start , I will describe to you the main features of the tool , and how useful it is . Write and Improve is an easy way to improve your English writing skills . The website is nice and you go straight to the point . On the main page , you will have a certain amount of subjects which will be graded regarding the English level ( for example : advanced ) . Then you will write about the subject you chose . When you have completed your argumentation , you can check your result immediately . And guess what ? Within a minute , you can have interesting feedback thanks to artificial intelligence . Your text is highlighted where something does not seem right , and it gives you your academic level ( A , B , C ) right away . You can then correct it to improve . Write and Improve is adaptable to any level , so everyone is welcome to try , and you do not even need to sign in to access it . Of course , it is better , in my opinion , because you can follow your tracks , and your improvement from day to day . I only wish there were more tests to take ! Anyway , I recommend it ! 
