For many people , honesty one of the most important virtues . People generally dislike liars . But could it be true that , in some situations , it is better to lie than to always speak the truth ? In my opinion , lying is not always bad . In fact , sometimes telling a lie is the only right thing to do , and I would like to explain why . To begin with , sometimes , it is more convenient for yourself and others to lie than to tell the truth . For example , complimenting a friend 's new outfit despite you not liking the clothes , you are just being polite . In this particular case , lying is the easiest way to avoid unpleasant situations . It would be unkind if you did not say anything at all , but being honest and saying their clothes are ugly would be rude too . Therefore , telling a white lie like in the given example is not that bad after all . Secondly , lying could also save lives . To illustrate , in the Second World War , some brave people had Jews in hiding in their homes . It is due to those selfless people that some Jews managed to survive the war . If those people did not risk their lives , lying to the Nazis and disobey their orders , even more people would have died . Clearly , we should be thankful some people are dishonest from time to time . 
I went to Alkhobar city three months ago . It was a great trip , with my beautiful sister and brother . It has a great vibrant scene on the beach at sunset , and furthermore , in the center of town , the magnificent architecture attracts many people to see it . So colourful and with lighting at night , it has a special view at midnight with the lights . As well as that , we went to King Abdulaziz center for diversity of cultures , which includes a lot of people from every corner of the globe . Each of them introduces information about their culture to the visitors . It is located in Dhahran city , it is so close to Alkhobar city . I tried some delicious cuisines in some restaurants that only have one branch in Alkhobar city . Also , it has friendly citizens I 've never met before . In addition , the stunning parks with pretty flowers and daily activities make it a fun time for the tourist . What I am trying to say is it is the most beautiful city in Saudi Arabia , and I will visit it again . 
I accidentally stumbled upon ' Write and Improve ' , while searching online for English courses . I have to say that I am very happy that it happened . ' Write and Improve ' is a useful and free tool for improving your English . It provides random topics and tasks for practising your writing . You can easily choose your level in which you would like to improve . It varies from beginner ( A1 ) to Business ( C2 ) . You even have a ' Just for fun ' section . The site is very easy to use . This makes it really accessible for everyone . When you finish your assignment , the application will immediately check your text tekst on grammar . It will afterwards provide you with additional feedback . A ranking ( A1 -C2 ) of your skills is also provided . The application gives you the option for improving your work . You can resend ( recheck ) your work after improving it . A diagram shows your progression while practising . There is only one small thing that could improve . You will sometimes get an orange highlight on a sentence . But it is never very clear what it means . You have to figure it out by yourself . Additional feedback would be nice . I would definitely recommend ' Write and Improve " to everyone who wants to practise his or her English writing . It is easy , free and quick . 
