I use the computer every day . All my work is done through a computer . Also , when I stay at home , I sometimes use my personal computer to study or resolve something . But there is something that I enjoy doing with my computer , I like to watch videos on You Tube . I usually watch videos about fitness or cooking recipes . 
In my free time I like watching movies and I do that at least once a week . Nowadays it is very hard to have any free time because we are in quarantine and I have a lot of things to do . I like this activity because I can pretend that things are different and I can forgot about everything . I watched a movie yesterday with my daughters and it was about mermaids . The kids loved it . 
In my opinion , it is better to have many teachers throughout the years . Each teacher has value , some problems to teach , some tips to get better , so it is important for children and teenagers to have several teachers . I guess that any opportunity needs to use it . My daughters have different teachers , each for each disciplines . My younger girl prefers the science teacher . My older girl rather the mathematics teacher , so different children need different teachers . In the future , they can meet other great teachers that will influence all their lives . The trajectory of the students , they have various moments , it depends on the age , of the mood , of the stage of life , so several teachers can help them . Despite these questions , I think that meeting different people is very important to learn to confront challenges , so I think that the same teacher along the years could not offer this for their lives . 
School will be different in future . In what ways ? Modern schools want different aspects from past ones . Previously schools had certain thoughts about the subjects traditionally taught there but now the scenario has changed and there are higher expectations . Nowadays , schools teach a diverse range of subjects in different fields . Further , today , in the cut throat competition of school survival , school management expects to fight against newer technology involvement and its application . Future schools will have advanced instruments and equipment in the laboratory , advanced high tech classrooms . Student will enjoy their own laboratory with their own ideas . Students learn new things in moments in a faster way . I think there are vast similarities between will be in present and future syllabus . Students will get more joy from their own designed syllabus and experiments with unbound freedom . In conclusion , there are measurable predictions which will be done in future school as well as other aspects . I think all are will be well for a better life for humankind . 
Some people believe that zoos are good places to learn about animals , but belonging in nature is a good way . In my viewpoint , they both have their own benefits and drawbacks . To begin with , if the government provides zoos , people will have more chance to keep in touch with animals , their living style and transformation . Even though you are not a zoologist , you can also learn about their life cycle and their strengths and weaknesses . For example , monkeys are almost like humans , which are 99.2 % the same as humans . If zoos are not open , people will never have the chance to study their behaviors and features . On the other hand , animals should not be kept in cages , which can affect their life cycle , reproduction and even cause death . For instance , crocodiles , you can see their life changing in nature and their transformation in zoos is thoroughly different . In nature , they have more strength and are wilder than in a cage . Another example , keeping them in a cage can affect their reproductive system , due to the fact that the place is tiny and they have monotonous partnerships . I believe that if you want to research their lifestyles or life cycles , why do not we go to see their habitats ? You can see not only their changes , but also the landscape of the natural views and also you can take a selfie . For instance , in Singapore , they occupy people under ground underground water tunnel which was built under the Pacific Ocean . From there you can see many kinds of sea animals , such as whales , sea cucumbers and jellyfish , etc . In conclusion , keeping animals in zoos is advantageous and disadvantageous , hence , I prefer to keep them free . 
I always jog in my free time . Whenever I have spare time , I go out jogging , it means I jog almost every day . I like jogging because I can easily get a sense of fulfillment . Also I can run much faster as I practice . Last weekend was the last time I did this exercise . I jogged 20 kms in 2 hours and I enjoyed the beautiful flowers and leaves in the park nearby . 
Hello Jack , Happy Birthday subsequently . We celebrate birthdays in our country in almost the same way . But we do not go to a restaurant . We eat cake and make dinner at home . But I think that it is not that much different . I can tell you about my birthday in September . Yours sincerely , Eva 
In my spare time I often play table tennis . Additionally I play in the school theater . I go to my table tennis training every week on Tuesdays and on Saturdays . On Thursdays I do theater . I have lots of fun with these activities . 
Hello Leyla , Sorry , I could not come to your party . I had to take care of my little sister . Our nanny cancelled at the last minute and we could not find another one . What happened at the party ? Any funny or exciting things ? Did another guest cancel coming to your party or did all the invited guests come ? We can go to Elena 's party next week , or we can have a brunch at the coffee shop . What do you mean ? Best regards , Eva 
Health and exercise are qualities in our life . There are many factors that influence your health , but there are three major components which contribute to general well -being : self -awareness , a balanced diet and regular physical activity , in addition pairing these with our mental health . In terms of nutrition , how to feed our body and listen to it , there are prizel says " you are what you eat , " beings to fade , forgetting about the importance of a balanced diet , eating fattening food without taking care about clogging the heart with cholesterol and fat , which results in a slowed metabolism . Obviously , if we have a good lifestyle and time to exercise , this makes our body active and we have energy to complete our day . We also eliminate calories . Being fit is not hard , but we need the desire and to think about our physical and mental health , to make a balance between them . 
The future school Did you like school , school life , the teachers or subjects ? And also , what did you wish ? I think some points might change in the future . Some schools will change to online class , for example countryside schools , because there are not enough students or the school is too far . Of course , city or town schools will also change in the same way . However , teachers who do not change to robots will still continue to be human . A robot teacher does not do anything wrong , but it 's difficult to understand students ' feelings . In this change , there is a disadvantage , which is students ca not make face -to -face friends or have real contact with other people and parents or grandparents need to stay at home together . On the other hand , fixed grades will disappear . This means if a student understands everything more quickly than other students , he or she can go up to the next grade sooner . Some students will graduate earlier than others and then their ability will be used in many fields . Schools are important for students , that 's why they need to change to a much better way . 
Health and wealth influence each other . In poor countries , with no healthcare , people try to stay alive and , in rich countries , they are healthy and change their body for beauty reasons . I agree with the statement : " It is more important to be healthy than rich . " On the one hand , you cannot enjoy your riches if you are sick . On the other hand , you have no chance to get better if you have not any money . In Germany , we have a really good health system and everyone can have health insurance . On the contrary is America with no access to healthcare for everyone . In this country , to be poor means eventually to die . But I think health is the most important subject and we need to think about how to improve it . All in all , it is necessary to find a balance between wealth and health . Every person needs to find this balance on their own . However , it is also important to create or provide healthcare for more people . Nevertheless , health is the most important . 
Working is part of our lives , when we reach adult age , we need to get a job in order to earn money to survive . Only if you have your own company , you wo not start being just a simple employee . By being a simple employee , you have to submit yourself to the conditions the company you work for gives you . In some companies , you work in enclosed workstations or cubicles , in other offices , you have a more open design , in which there are no walls separating employees from their co -workers . These two different models of offices have pros and cons : the first example gives you more privacy , silence and concentration ; whereas the second type of office can provide you more interaction with your partners , it ´s easy to dialogue with others and you never feel alone . To sum up , if it were me , I would prefer to work in a cubicle as I would be more concentrated and if I need help , I would go to the next office and ask for an opinion . 
Millions of travelers start planning their holiday by exploring different destinations via their computers , tablets and mobile apps , even engaging with their social networks . Nowadays , we have multiple choices to book your flight and hotel and the car that will pick you up when you arrive at your destination . In addition , you are able to make reservations with apps in the restaurants you want and also , the tickets for activities . As I imagine , the future may have a flying car for traveling and applications that show you the temperature in each country and various market places at the destination . Furthermore , you will see many websites preparing schedules for travelers to shorten the time making the timetable for their journey . The media makes everything regarding travel easier than before . You look for a great place from your friends ' snaps or from a travel show . I am so optimistic about the future of travel , how the methods will be astonishing . 
Hello everyone ! Today , I will talk about " The school of the future . " I 'm going to explain to you my personal opinion about the future school . Of course , this is a personal opinion , therefore you could agree or disagree with me , so if you disagree , you could speak with me about this subject in my email . Personally , I think the school of the future should be more technological because technology is growing very quickly in the world and also because technology is really useful for many things , there is no doubt about it . For example , you can do your work faster , you can search for everything and also learn more easily thanks to the many websites on the internet . Moreover , in the future , all students will have a computer or tablet for working in the classroom I guess . But on the other hand , I think schools might still be the same in many ways , like the device in the classroom or the relationship between students and teachers . 
Matsue Castle is the symbol of my home town . It was built 400 years ago . It is one of the national treasures of Japan . There is a big lake in my town named Lake Shinji . The sunset view from the lake is really good . 
Hi Leyla , I could not go to the party because I was abroad meeting important customers . I am really sorry about that . So what happened at the party ? Did you have a big big cake and candles ? I think I missed a lot of memorable moments . Instead of an apology , can you go to Rome with me next weekend ? I really want to hear you say yes . Miss you ! Lily 
Class discussion , the purpose of television Television entertains , but can it also educate ? Class discussion is one of the healthy education environments , creating good conversation among students . Television provides good entertainment as well as news related information . Today , lot of television programmes serve entertainment with education . Today , I will discuss television programmes with education . Furthermore , television is the best invention for visual entertainment . With the advancement of technology , school students are now involved in entertainment with education . For instance , rhymes , kids ' science project videos , online games , etc . The above mentioned programme gives diverse education to the students . Rhymes give social education and better education of society knowledge . Science project videos provide better understanding of science rules with its mechanism . Research said that playing video games , children have wider brain knowledge adaptability as well as creativity . Research also said that videos or visual materials help students remember things , and for longer . In conclusion , television is the best source for the understanding of student life . An educational television programme should be involved in the subject syllabus . 
I took up Zumba dancing one year ago and now , in my free time , I am always dancing . I 'd just got over some health problems . I 'm a thin person and I have always wanted to improve my weight , learning Zumba has been the best choice . 
