Dear Matt , Have you seen The Moon movie ? It 's my favourite film . It 's a science -fiction film that I love . Science -fiction is a genre that uses speculative , fictional science -based depictions of phenomena that are not fully accepted by mainstream science but it is amazing . I think you will enjoy it when you are watching them . Lily 
Hi Matt , Thanks for your letter . I have received your letter and I felt so glad when I knew that you were starting school again on Monday . I hope you will pass the coming examination . Anyway , I am still practicing speaking , reading , listening , and writing to improve my English . I spend most of my time learning English . Next year I hope I will go abroad to make my dream to be a businessman come true . Well , that 's all for now . Looking forward to hearing from you again . Lily 
In my free time , I love to read books and paint . I do it every day when I have free time and need to relax . I like painting more because painting helps me practice my art skills and I feel relaxed , too . I just did it yesterday and I will do it again now . 
I love to exercise and sometimes I do it . I prefer exercising outside more because I love to breathe the fresh air and I can chat with everybody . I am an extrovert . The world has a lot of activities , so I like walking , swimming and yoga more for my exercise . 
Today , but also years ago , students decide to study in another country . This method is particularly good because it is the best way to learn something , for example , studying a new language in a new country is the best method to improve . However , it has a huge difficulty in the beginning because you do not understand what other people are telling you , or explain to you . Once time has passed in that country , the difficulty subsides , you understand what people are telling you , etc ... Another negative aspect of living in another country is following their traditions , leaving your traditions in the past and having a new lifestyle . Despite the difficulty , this is the best way to improve , make new friends that can help you to learn faster . If I can suggest which way I prefer to study , I will say that going to another country is the best experience you can have . 
Studying English is the most beautiful thing to do . I started to say some words when I was 5 years old , then when I was 8/9 years old , my family and I decided to have trip . We went to America from my uncle 's family . When I went there , I was so surprised to see that I had English mother tongue cousins , I was so excited because that gave me a reason to test myself . When I came back , I became number one in English in my class , I was so happy to see my classmates so jealous of my skills . Then I went to high school when I started to study the English grammar , and once I realized I was able to make sentences , my decision was taken : I had to get better in this language . Now I 'm studying to pass the B2 exam . After this exam , my first and most important goal is to pass the C1/C2 exams , and I know that the journey will be very hard . And this is why I love English and I want to get better . 
When I was 10 years old , me and my family went to America . We decided to go to my uncle 's family . It was my second holiday , my first was in Egypt . We took the plane and this too was my first experience flying , it was so awesome . Once we arrived at the American airport , my uncle was waiting for us . Immediately , he took our baggage and put it in his car , then he took us to his home . We met all the family members . I was shocked , because I saw my American cousins . We stayed there for about 2 weeks , hosted in my uncle 's house . Then we decided to visit New York City , also known as " The Big Apple . " We saw a lot of awesome monuments . like the Empire State Building , Central Park , the M&M 's tower . I was so amazed by that city , but we did not see Times Square . That place is my favourite , and remembering that I did not go is so painful . This was the best holiday I have had . I had the opportunity to hear and speak a little bit of English , which was epic and funny . 
In the beginning of 2020 , almost of the world locked down because of the Covid -19 virus . Many people must live inside to restrict the infection . Therefore , travel has become impossible at this time . Travel may return in the next year , when we have a vaccine . But everyone will have to be careful going overseas . I think travelers will visit some places in their country , or go to some countries which have successfully controlled the pandemic . Otherwise , after the pandemic , the economy will be depressed , so people have to reduce travel costs by going to a country that is cheap . In the next years , when everything is going to be normal , the number of travelers will increase . I think they will still want to travel to the countryside and the mountains , that is the same way as a few years ago , because after the stressful quarantine , people will want to breathe some fresh air . I think everyone will still want to have more experiences in nature . Finally , that is my opinion about " The Future of Travel . " 
Some people believe that studying for several years with the same teacher is superb , but new teachers for each year are more advantageous . Based on my knowledge , I am going to outline that the same teacher for studying several years has its upsides . They believe that by studying with the same teacher , students already know about their teacher 's likes and dislikes , thus they will behave like good people . Students and teacher can keep in touch with each other like friend , open -minded without being paranoid . If the teacher 's age tends to be young , she will behave with her pupils like her brothers and sisters . However , the same teacher for four or five years teaching the students who may not have respect for her or guide to their subjects will be monotonous . Sometimes , she loves her students , forgiving their mistakes gives them more marks and favour , which is going to trouble them if they are planning on studying further . Besides that , it is mentioned that diverse teachers have their own benefits and drawbacks . They believe that a different teacher chases dissimilar styles and new methods , which can make them brainstorm and more creative . Students will be terrified and look up to the teachers who can boost them to study more and more . On the other hand , they might misunderstand what she is talking about . For instance , when I was young , my mother encouraged me to get better experiences , hence , she pushed to change many teachers which idea drove up to the wall . I did not used to know about their lectures , thus I did not get sensationally high marks . And last but not least , some teachers want to show their power to students to look up to her , sometimes she might be strict . From my view , I prefer to go with the same teacher because students and teacher have already built their relationships and know each other , which students are weak in which subjects , other students have strengths in other that is why she can thoroughly control them to get an A + grade . So , in a nutshell , students have the same teacher for several years , having new teachers both has upsides and downsides . In my opinion , Undoubtedly , I would definitely go for the same teacher for several years . 
Hello Jack , Happy birthday to you . I would have come to your celebration , but I promise you I will come next year . In my country we have a similar style , a big cake with candles and also balloons sepicall for the children to celebrate . Some families prefer to have a celebration in a restaurant , others have it in their home and make their hands , they like engoying with their own hands , they like to enjoy themselves with their kids making and decorating the cake . From my side , I have not celebrated my birthday ever in my life , I prefer to celebrate when I achieve some success like graduating from university , memorising the Quran , and the birth of a baby . I think these things are worth celebrating . 
Studying abroad is the best choice for every student . Just a few people have the opportunity to study abroad . If you have this opportunity , you should take it . There are many advantages to studying abroad : 1 . You will get independence : your parents wo not be with you , for that reason , you are going to learn to solve the problems by yourself . 2 . You will get new cultural habits : in other countries , there are many different habits which will enrich your knowledge and behavior . 3 . More opportunities to get a better job when you come back to your home country , in comparison with the rest of people . 4 . Bilingual professional : if you study in a country where people speak a language different to yours , you will learn it very well . It will upgrade your professional profile because many companies look for bilingual executives . 5 . International friends : I am sure you will have friends from many countries . That means there are many countries of opportunity to visit , live or work . 
In life , everything has a good side , but it also has a bad side . If you overuse , it will bring you negative effects and vice versa . Playing video games is also like that . There are some benefits from playing a video game , but at the same time , it also has negative effects . I will talk about the benefits first . First of all , playing video games makes you feel relaxed and comfortable . You can solve your stress and enjoy the rest of the time , but not think and worry so much about life and your work . Secondly , your reflexes will be faster , your eyes and hands will combine better than before . Thirdly , it will improve your mindset , especially it is really good for those who make plans or strategies . Fourthly , you will more patient than before . Fifthly , it also improves your teamwork ability . Finally , it also makes you become more assertive . If you realize the benefits of playing video games and do not abuse them , it will be awesome . Besides the benefits , there are also some disadvantages . Firstly , if you ca not control yourself , it will be addictive to play them . It is not good for you , right ? Secondly , if you are spending a lot of time on it , it means you would waste your precious time . Thirdly , your process of studying will go down quickly . Your parents especially will certainly be very upset about your study results . Fourthly , playing games a lot , your brain is not conscious and you will acquire some diseases . Fifthly , you do not have time to communicate with family and the people around you . The consequence is you will get depressed . Sixthly , your emotions are also effected . You will become an irritable person . Finally , it will affect your health , such as heart disease and so on . Therefore , you should not overuse video games . 
Hi Billal , Last week I went hiking with boyfriend in the Himalayan mountains . Did you know that there is a nice view and fresh air ? We were camping , had a BBQ and made a live show with friends . In the night , there was music , and the firelight atmosphere was so awesome . I loved that trip a lot because this was the five year anniversary of our love . We are always near each other in every emotion : sad , happy , nervous , or crying . We are grateful all the time for each other and it was the best trip . 
The majority of people are made for social contact and interaction . The walls of cubicle offices rob you of making these connections with your colleagues . You do get the same additional own space and privacy with walls , but this comes with a social cost . When you open up your office , a couple of things will happen . People will be able to see one another . This means that you will not be able to slag anymore . You could get away with this in a cubicle . At the same time , you will be able to see your colleagues at work that can give you the motivation to keep working . And when you need some help , you can easily ask . The feeling at the office will be different . It will not only be everybody for themselves , but more a feeling of working in a group . This will al create a more colleague friendly environment . People in general do not prefer small and tight spaces . We come from ancestors who roamed around over open fields . Having the ability to overlook you direct space gives the feeling of safety and peace . You create this feeling by opening up your office . But it is important to do it in the correct manner . So give everybody his own space and do not place people directly in front or next to each other . Otherwise , the threshold to get distracted will be lowered . Natural light is something that is important for a lot of people . Walls of cubicles are light barriers that lead to tl lighting . This is different in an open workspace . 
There are secondary schools where you first need to spend a certain amount of time on charity work before earning your degree . This can , for example , mean that students help by giving Englisch English to refugees or maybe work at a homeless shelter . There are a lot of lessons students are able to learn from doing this type of work . Volunteer work teaches children to not only think about their own situation , but also about the situations of people less fortunate than themselves . Not everybody has the same opportunities in life . A little help can make a lot of difference to somebody in need . Because volunteer work is made part of their graduation progress , it will force people that would normally not do charity work to try it . These students are pushed out of their comfort zone . You never know , maybe it will even change their opinion about it . It can broaden their view . Starting volunteer work at a young age will make it feel more normal . It will also increase the chance of students doing more volunteer work in the future . We need new volunteers every year . Inspiring young people to step up can make a difference in maintaining a steady stream of volunteers . 
I usually use Write and Improve from Cambridge to practice my English writing . I think it is a good tool . You can prepare and write about different topics and subjects . At the end of the writing , you have the possibility to check your mistakes and try to improve your text . This tool gives you some recommendations about what you should fix and change . Finally , you get a grade based on your capacity to develop a good text . The page keeps your track record updated and offers you some advice to improve your skills . Definitely , I would recommend this tool to my classmates . I believe you can achieve great results if you are constant . I would advise them to start from the beginner level and check their grade . After that , they can start to work in the appropriate level they need to find the motivation needed to keep pushing . 
In my free time , I play video games for many hours . I usually play video games twice a week , since the quarantine begun . I like this activity because there are amazing stories and interesting characters inside the games . The last time that I played video games was on Sunday and I played my favorite one for a long time . 
Speaking is thinking . The way people think can be measured by their spoken words . If people tell a lie , they cannot be trusted . Lying is an acceptable action , except in emergency conditions . Always telling the truth is important . By always saying the truth , the people could obtain the trust . Trust from the people is one of the important in life . When we study at university or work at a company , obtaining trust is a top priority once we entered a new environment . Lying , in opposite , will put us in marginal zone at which we can easily be dropped off from that zone . Telling the truth is also safer than telling a lie . Although it is difficult to tell the truth in some conditions , telling the real case not only makes us unloaded physically but also mentally . The habit of telling the truth , without any addition and deduction , will strengthen our quality of life . True data will deliver a right decision . In contrast , fake data will result in a wrong decision . It is a case of when telling a lie is an acceptable action . A lie can be accepted when someone is in danger and telling the truth will put their safety in danger . In this case , the only way is to tell a lie . Nevertheless , everything should be explained in truth once the problem is solved . 
Hi Leyla , How are you ? I hope you are feeling good . I am so sorry about my absence , my daughter was sick and I took her to the hospital . Tell me what you did ? How many came to your party ? How was the cake , was it delicious or not ? And the buffet was tasty , was not it ? I want to meet you , I really miss you . Could you come to my home next Saturday ? I will engoy if you accept my invitation , it would be my pleasure . I am having a barbecue and there will be fried fish with mashed potatoes . Regards , Khawlah 
Currently , I think you have to speak a foreign language more than all of the last decade . Indeed , speaking another language is very useful for many things , like for your job or to get around , there is no doubt about it . Therefore , some people try to learn a new language , such as a native speaker , from their target language . Indeed , today , more and more people are learning a foreign language to find a job more easily . To give you an example , in 2012 , when I worked for a travel company , I did not speak English but I had to do it , so I learnt English until I spoke it very well because I needed it to exchange with some foreigners . Moreover , I think today you should be able to speak a foreign language because of metropolization . To explain to you what metropolization means , this is a kind of open border , this a political device made to do more business and also have more exchange between some countries , like in Europe with the " Schengen space . " Consequently , you may be related to someone who does not speak your language and this is actually true . 
Hi Ana , Recently , I wanted to get various of information from around the world . Catching news and communicating in English is the best way so far . English is the most useful language to communicate with non -native people . So I am learning English now and then . Hope you have luck ! Moe 
My favourite season of the year Are you one of those people who love going on holiday and summer vibes ? If the answer is yes , this article is for you . As everybody knows , summer is that season of crazy adventures , unforgettable romances , breathtaking experiences as well as great weather and sunny days . I 'm sure that I have reminded you of a summer holiday or moment , have not I ? Anyway , it goes without saying that summer is my favourite time of the year because I do not have to study and I 've got a lot of free time , I 'm able to enjoy everything that I have not during the school year . For example , hanging out with my friends , traveling to different places , meeting new people ... And that is why I enjoy these three months of joy as they were my last ones . As they say , actions speak louder than words , so if I were you , I would try to live as much as possible this summer and do not worry , you 'll thank me later . 
