It is Khawlah , in grade 10 , I have studied English for two years since 2018 . I have some strength and weakness in my English language , this is because it is my second language . I think I have good skills in reading and listening , these are the areas I was working hard on . In other words , I was practicing them every day , listening to podcasts and reading Oxford stories . However , on the other hand , I have weakness in some areas like writing and speaking . I make a lot of mistakes in my writing tasks in grammar , spelling , and the sentence structure . Also when speaking , in a serious situation , I lose my confidence , I stop after every sentence , it is fluency problem . To achieve my goals , firstly , I will practice English as much as I can . In other words , talking in English everywhere I go , even at my home with my family or at work . 
