Yes I do like to exercise because it is healthy for my body . I usually exercise twice a week . I prefer going to a gym , because I get motivated by the people who come to a gym to exercise . But , sometimes I exercise at my home in my backyard if I do not have enough time to go to the gym , especially when I have lots of activities to do at home . I like listening to music while exercising . I like lifting light weights to strengthen my arm muscles . 
In my free time I use my computer to learn English and use social media sites . I learn English every day , and I watch videos and listen to audio podcasts online . I like English because it 's an international language and it gives me the opportunity to expand my horizons and travel the world . 
I have been using Write and Improve for several weeks and have written many articles . I can now talk about the things that I liked and disliked . Write and Improve provides a huge number of topics and all of them are divided into three categories : beginner , intermediate , and advanced . Users as per their convenience choose the topic and write up to 300 words . They have also provided a business category in which the topics are related to business activity . This is useful for professional people who want to improve their business English . The topics in this category are few and limited in subject . Write and Improve must include more variety of topics so that an over all practice related to business English can be performed . One more feature they have included is a test zone . This category is for people who are preparing for IELTS . Here , the topics are listed similar to what comes in the IELTS exam . Sadly , this category is charged for , and after one review , they continuously ask for a subscription . Now , the most important part of this portal is the feedback and progress . Here , they check , mark the mistakes , and give suggestions for correction . The over all review system is good but lacks in detail , like the highlighted part does not mention the mistake detail and also it does not suggest the best way of writing . However , it shows the proficiency and CEFR level . To summarise , this is a best website I have found where topics and proofreading are both available . I recommend Write and Improve to include more business topics and provide a more detailed review system . 
I think television can also educate . The purpose of television is to entertain people , but learning is one of the entertainments . For TV programs , there are news , discussion , and education programs . As TV broadcasts them , people input a wide variety of information passively , even though they are not interested in them . It not only broadcasts them , but also explains if we need it . People acquire wanting information just watching TV . Moreover , we could learn even from entertainment programs , for example , comedy and music . We could get the knowledge of how to occur laugh or compose songs . When we watch TV from a different perspective , we could find new things which we have not noticed . Everything is a seed of learning . TV will never be a tiring device , it should be enjoyable forever . From these two reasons , I think television educates people as well as entertains them . 
I have had many exiting vacations in my life , but the greatest was my trip to Europe . I visited four countries , Italy , France , Germany and Switzerland . My tour in Europe was three weeks . I saw technology everywhere , like parking , I saw the technolge in every where like parking , the health power in Germany , they get electricity from the wind . The nature was unbelievable , which makes you feel in heaven . Trees with fruits and green lands . It leads you to pick the fruits and eat more and more . Also , the handmade chocolate , the most delicious chocolate I have ever had , made from native cows ' milk and fresh nuts . I have not seen anything like this amazing nature in my life . And the clothes in Italy were stylish and cheaper than in my country . I bought a dress , bags and make -up . I think European countries have millions of tourists during the year , because they have everything the tourists want , nature , safety , wonderful weather and great shopping . Therefore , I believe that it was the best expensive option . It needs a lot of money , but it is worth it . 
The indoor activities I do when I am at home . Usually I do things that I do not have a lot of opportunity to do when I am working all day . I like : reading books , watching interesting videos about social life , subjects about social science and kids ' education on You Tube . It 's very normal in my free time for me to look for take time for improve my understand about subjecties that I like know more and take the time to improve my understanding about subjects that I would like to know more about and this helps me with this . In my last indoor activity I watched a video about immigration to Canada . 
For children , video games are more popular than in the last decade . Some people believe that video games can influence negatively on children and other people do not believe it . From my point of view , they both have their own drawbacks and benefits . Based on my knowledge , I am going to outline the negative impact on children . Most people , especially parents , do not control their children , hence the children will be playing some 18 + video games , thrilling or about ghost hunting , which could be a threat to them . Sometimes , one who plays video games too much will behave in real life like in the games . For example , I read in an article , a young man of just around 10 years old who played PUBG games . In those games , you can jump from the fourth storey to the ground , so his brain was impacted with that knowledge a lot . Consequently , he jumped from the fourth floor , which killed him . However , beside that , it is mentioned that playing video games can have many positive effects , such as being brighter , brainstorming and being able to calculate faster . If she plays video games like creative games , she gets in danger , encouraged by herself . At school , some scientists have researched that playing video games , children can calculate faster , better and more correctly than without playing . For instance , undoubtedly , when I was young , I was not a bookworm and punctual . Even though I played games and watched videos every day , I never failed an exam . When the examination was near , I did some tricks on how to pass the exam , due to the fact of playing video games . From my view point , playing video games has more advantages than disadvantages . Playing video games , you can keep in touch with international people , which can progress not only personal abilities and mindset , but also language skills . Some parents desire to go back to nineteenth century thinking . Video games are designated a sport , which includes sports . So , in the nutshell , elderly people must keep up to the minute with changing things . Video games are also included in the 21st century trends . Most people had better accept video games . If their children play video games early , they will have more opportunities than without playing them . 
It seems to me that working in cubicles is more effective . Because when you work with no walls separating one another , it ’s going to be noisy . Even the sound of someone clicking the keyboard by your side might make you out of focus . Focus is really important for us while doing something . You can be more productive when you , all by yourself , think about what you ’re going to finish . Even though you ca not communicate with anybody , all the attention moves to your duty so you can easily focus on it . Sometimes , being alone by ourselves makes us know ourselves better than ever . And all of a sudden , you might find some creative ideas that you never expected before . Do not worry about the other workers , we can still catch up with them when the break time comes . If your duty is finished properly , it can bring happiness and satisfaction to you . All workers deserve a cozy office plus a cozy cubicle . Therefore , they will work with an amazing spirit to finish the day . I know for some offices it ’s not easy to establish cubicles , but slowly but surely , they can make it . Everything need a process . And the process must indicate betterment . 
I want to study Programming because technology has become familiar among these days and I think Programming will be a necessary language to be able to live . I want to start this course immediately so that I can adjust my schedule to make time . I will try to learn it in English . Please let me take topics related to programming in this course . 
It is obvious that studying overseas at high school or university has its own benefits and drawbacks . In this essay , I am exploring both sides of studying aboard . Based on my knowledge , I am going to outline the downsides of studying overseas . Definitely , you have to live away from your family and friends which can lead to you suffering from loneliness and depression . And also , if she goes there to university or high school , she had better keep up with their mother tongue . Even though you can be versatile in cold or hot weather , the weather is also one thing you have to face if you study aboard . For instance , she comes from hot weather ( Myanmar ) to the United Kingdom , and she will face cold weather of sub -zero degrees Celsius . After around a year , she will get used to it . If you come to the United Kingdom , you apply to uni as an international student , which is expensive at about 30000 to 50000 British Pounds . And another disadvantage is that , just depending on your abilities and backgrounds , you must prepare to enroll in the university , such as IELTS or TOEFL , maths and sciences , depending on your specialization . On the other hand , besides that , it is mentioned that studying overseas can make you progress , such as in language skills , you might be bilingual or multilingual . And also , you are on your own without relatives , friends or parents so you have to learn how to manage on your own and use your money properly . Undoubtedly , you have to take part -time jobs which make you know how hard and tricky life is . However , some people desire to stick their neck out because challenges are opportunities to get satisfactory step . From my opinion , taking the risk is better than living in the save zone . Sometimes , making you courageous and trying the new language or studying new things could make your life better and big break , do not hesitate and take a risk that will make you better . I am also planning to study overseas that is why I am learning English language intensively . As , in the nutshell , everything has upsides and downsides . Living in a safe zone cannot make you progress , do not be a coward , follow your aims , which would be better in future . 
I have been using Write and Improve for about 12 days and I really feel the improvement when I am writing new essays . As per the positive aspects of this platform , I can mention that I have become more aware of the vocabulary dictation and its use in the text . Also , I am trying to use the appropriate collocations and writing a little bit longer sentences . Furthermore , my progress motivates me to not give up and not underestimate small steps toward success in writing a high -quality essay . On the other hand , I think the website needs to be more specific about the candidate 's mistakes and give a better suggestion . For example , I searched for one of the collocations that the website detected as a mistake , and I found that it was right . Maybe it was that that collocation could not be embedded in that topic . Generally , the Write and Improve website has been very helpful for me until now and I recommend you to use it on a daily basis . The consistency in the writing practise and tracking your progress is the key factor to gain a higher score in IELTS writing . 
