Write and Improve In April , I realized that my English level was very bad and I wanted to improve this . My sister advised me to use this website to write more often in English . At the beginning , it was very difficult for me , because my vocabulary was very limited . Now , with practice , it 's easier , even if I make many mistakes . I 'm trying to practise each day . It 's difficult , but I am succeeding for the moment . I like the diversity of the exercises on this website , because there is a lot of writing to be done . We can progress slowly and the correction helps me improve my level . It could be better , for example , they have no lessons to discover new vocabulary . Finally , I obviously recommend a classmate to try it , because it 's really fun and instructive . 
Nowadays , many teenagers have become and not intersted in life members of their family and not interested in the life of the members of their family and friends . They pay all their attention to life on social media . In my opinion , it is a wonderful idea that some high schools require students to do some compulsory volunteer work . Firstly , volunteer work teaches responsibility for others . It puts emphasis on how important it is to give helping hands to homeless or elderly people . It could improve relationships between grandparents and grandchildren . Teenagers are able to learn many useful abilities from the experience which comes from their grandparents . Secondly , many factories or corporations look for people who are keen on volunteer work . It shows them that the candidate has a wide range of discipline and responsibility . What 's more , they know how to find balance between work and relax . On the other hand , if teenagers do something under pressure , they became rude . They ignore advice from their parents or teacher . Next , they try to invent as many excuses as they can to avoid volunteer work . It is a waste of time for them . To sum up , doing volunteer work at school is useful . Students have the opportunity to develop their personality . As a result , they become more responsible and sensitive citizens of the country and more attractive candidates to work in a company . 
This school year represents a challenge to me , specifically in terms of learning English . This year has to be the year I reach my goals in reference to English . I am putting all my enthusiasm and optimism into achieving my goal , that is to be fluent in English . I have identified some strengths . I feel that I have improved my reading skills and also my vocabulary has increased , but I am still feeling stuck . I suppose I need to improve my level of confidence when I am talking with native English speakers . I am pleased with my reading skills . My main weakness is writing . I feel overwhelmed when I need to start writing . This is something that I really need to improve . The most difficult part is starting to write , the process itself is not easy even in your native language . In addition , I have a lot of grammar rules in my mind , sometimes I feel it is too much . My personal achievement is to get the IELTS Academic test . I need to get a high score . Without this , I am going to be stuck in my degree . My plan is to dedicate some hours a day , focusing my learning between reading , writing , listening and speaking . I promised that I shall do my best to achieve my goal . 
