I like to do exercise . I do exercise every day . In the morning , I prefer exercising outside because the weather is very nice , there is fresh air and I have a chance to meet interesting people . I like running , cycling and exercises that are helpful for preventing a heart attack and high blood pressure . 
Some schools oblige their students to study music and to play a musical instrument . For example , in France , every student from 10 to 14 years old takes music classes two hours a week . Other countries do not have these policies and young people do not learn about music . In my opinion , students should have to study music , but not learn how to play a musical instrument . Of course , studying music and learning how to play a musical instrument can help students to develop creativity and amusement . Like any art , music has the power to be universal and everyone can enjoy some of it . Learning about music will open the mind of young students , and they will discover another kind of culture , or re -enforce what they already know . Studying music can have many aspects like reading the music or learning about former famous singers or musicians , or even singing some songs . Some students might discover a new hobby , and as it happened to me , study music outside the walls of the school . Playing a musical instrument can be more difficult to organise . Most musical instruments are very expensive , and most schools cannot afford such an expense . I believe if only rich schools can make it happen , it will worsen inequalities among students , and in society in general . Of course , if the state is funding all the equipment , I believe every student should learn a musical instrument because it will give them new skills and open even more their mind to art and musical culture . 
Some people say if you have plenty of money , you can buy anything you want . This statement is partly true , but being healthy is what you cannot buy with money . Suppose you have terminal cancer . No matter how much money you have , any treatment you can afford today may not be able to cure it . For example , Steve Jobs , one of the co -founders of Apple , was extremely wealthy , but he died of pancreatic cancer . Money cannot always deal with health problems . That said , being rich enables you to beef up your health . It costs you a decent amount of money to eat healthy food , to get regular check -ups , and receive medical treatment . I think that though being healthy is more important than being rich , being healthy requires being rich , at least not poor . 
Some people consider that students must study music and learn to play a musical instrument , but other students do not bother to study music and musical instruments . In this essay , I am going to outline the upsides of studying music . Based on my knowledge , music is powerful and people can feel about nature with melody is the perfect one on the earth . Music could make all individual people full of energy and strength ; as a consequence , some people may say " music is part of their life . " Especially , if you are feeling alone or depressed , you can open full of energetic and lively song which can give you up . And also , some types of music like sleep or meditation songs which could calm your mind and let you let your hair down . Some people say that they have to sleep with music . If her sleep is without music , she cannot sleep the whole night because of the power of music . Music is key to creating the whole kind of their meanings in one music , for instance , national anthems which are full of meaning including sadness , dynamism and strength . And last but not least , the music subject is desired by most people in the 21st century , not only in Asia , but also all over the world ; thus , in China and Taiwan , the music subject is most hard to get into and the price is higher than others . From my view point , why do not we study the music subject ? If you have some free time , do not waste it and keep trying the music subject which could give you more opportunities . I think all schools had better study music due to the fact that they are going to know how beautiful the music melody is and when they feel alone that can liven them up . If somebody asks me " Will you study the music subject ? , " I will undoubtedly say " Yes . " Because what follows shows , in a nutshell , why we should study music . " Music is love and marvellous . " 
Let me introduce my point of view . It is important to say that I am studying at military university and it is a bit of a different education system . Our military university is part of our defence forces so it prepares soldiers for their duty . With that , you are not allowed to study in a foreign civil university . So if you want to study abroad , you have to choose some of the military schools . It is true that it can be useful to know tactics of other armies . But we are offered to study only in countries like Austria . Their armed forces are not equal to ours at all . I do not believe that a Czech soldier can profit from such an education . In my opinion , the only reason why students want to study in a foreign military university is just entertainment and money . We are studying important things about our future job every day . It fits our forces . You ca not learn such things somewhere else and you ca not catch up with the rest of the class . It is because you will miss some important practical lessons . 
The main reason is obviously money because that 's what makes everyone do something , also there is the disadvantage of only contacting with old patients that need more attention than others . 
People think that money gives happiness . I personally think that being healthy is much more valuable and important . First of all , money can buy a lot and make your life easier , however it will not buy your health . In my opinion , we should be physically active as much as possible and try to find that spare 30 min to exercise at least 3 times a week . Nowadays , processed unhealthy food , stressful situations , pollution and busy day to day life can affect our wellness . And money cannot change it . But we can , by simply eating healthier , change bad habits avoiding fast food . Personally , I think that being healthy means much more to me than being rich . I believe that I can prevent poor health conditions by an active lifestyle . To sum up , I truly believe that being healthy is more important than being rich . I personally would love to live as long as possible to see my children and future grandchildren grow and to make memories of those priceless moments which money cannot buy . 
To be honest , I do not like zoos . It is because all the animals in zoos seem to be dead in their eyes . Having said that , people visiting there looks fun to meet a lot of rarely seen animals . Do you think they show us their real lives in the cage ? Do you think we can recognize their habits , culture and favorite game in zoos ? I believe lions in nature run fast , they never lay down on the nature field all day long . I know every animal in nature struggles to find food , they never wait to be fed . As far as we enclosure them in zoos , we never know the animal 's real instinct . I think we should figure out another way to meet animals . A safari park is better to meet them but they are " fed " eventually , so we ca not see their " real life . " If you want to learn about animals , you should go to forests or the savanna and get to u they are really ferocious . 
My reason for learning English is to achieve my ultimate goal , which is work around the world . I want to work with a variety of people . I want to work on a variety of projects . Experiencing a lot of things makes my life enjoyable and satisfying . To achieve this goal , I have set some attainable goals . One of them is to take part in a cross boarder project in early years . To be recommended for the project , I need to use English fluently . That is why I am studying English now . Besides this studying site , I use online speaking lessons . Only a month has passed , I recognize that my speaking skills has been developing rapidly . In addition to that , knowing the world is my pleasure . As English is a global language , once I understand it , I will be able to read many articles about this world . This makes me really happy and satisfied . I 'll continue to make efforts to achieve my goal . 
The issue of volunteer work is widely debated , with some students claiming that it is for university students or who have been had a lot of money person . However , I personally agree with this , and I will explain why in this essay . Firstly , doing volunteer work is full of benefits which outweigh the disadvantages . This is not only for students , but also for majority which can give you real life skills , especially communication skills and socialisation . Most of the students are weak in communication skills in presentations or on the stage when they have had experience in volunteering which can fix their panic . For instance , volunteer work , you have to go to every place such as low proverty , suburban regions and the countryside , where places of people are being given about do and do not things in front of pack of people . That kind of competence can fix them from their shyness and panic . Some students are not good at socialization whether he lacks parents or a single person must join volunteer work where give you a lot of strengths and knowledge . That work not only can build your personal skills but also give you a sweet smile or wishes from the . I do appreciate that some students think alternatively , saying that it is better to study instead of doing volunteer work . Volunteer work is only need for undergraduate or postgraduate students to get better credit scores and who have already had a rich person do this work . In the nutshell , I believe that doing volunteer work livens you up and you get more new experience and know about how to consider other people 's feelings . 
There is a new aptitude in Italian schools that is becoming always more common , and this is the opportunity to study music . It should not be seen like a waste of time , but in contrast , it is supposed to be a workable method to stimulate the students ' curiosity and their willing to deepen their knowledge in a specific topic . All of us know how young people are interested in music , but what they likely miss is a general tuition in the history of the music and a better knowledge about some of the most famous and important composers . An always increasing number of schools has already decided to give lectures where students can choose what fields of music to study . The experiments seem to work and students not only get high scores , but they also read up on the subjects they are more interested in . What is absolutely amazing , students often come up with new ideas regarding how to update their knowledge learnt at school . The study of music is supposed to sharpen our sensibility and it should make our brain more prompt and able to catch the most apparently insignificant details of an issue . This is the main reason to fight the social phenomenon of brainwashing , something that is affecting students who are used to listening to some music that damages their nervous system and their logical capabilities . However , this is not the only reason , I think music should be taught at school in order to widen the general culture of young people , and this is certainly something that can help to make more wise , sensitive and well -educated adults . 
In these special days that people should be at home and avoid going out , indoor activities can have a big role to keep them healthy . I used to go for a walk before these critical condition but now , but now I should stay at home , and so I have tried to be creative and have found a new way of walking at home . So I moved the furniture and made a large space in which to walk , because walking always refreshes me and also it lets me manage my thoughts , so I do it every morning . This morning I woke up and walked for 30 minutes before I started my day . 
My favorite indoor activity is reading historical books and doing all the housework to keep my room clean and with the smell of flowers . I like every activity in which I must tidy up my personal things , and I do not think it 's a tiring activity , in contrast , it 's something that relaxes me . Just this afternoon I had some pairs of socks , shirts and trousers to put in my wardrobe , then it took me around half an hour . 
Nowadays computers have a big role in our lives , we need them for almost everything , such as , paying the bills , listening to music etc . I have a desktop computer which is something for me , I carry out all my assignments , send my e - mails , write my music and also listen to it . So every day , I am used to spending a lot of time on my computer , but the most favourite time for me is when I am watching TV shows . I always go to Netflix . com and check for new episodes and watch every new series . 
Nowadays , more and more people use electronic devices when they study . It helps them improve their learning ability and increase motivation . In my opinion , computers and tables can replace books in schools and university . Firstly , children are growing up with electronic devices , which become a natural environment of their growing up . As a result , books are for them old -fashioned and boring . They want to have everything now . What 's more , they hate reading . They would rather watch films on the internet than read books . Secondly , using computers or tablets helps to reduce the amount of books in children 's bags . What 's more , this situation helps protect the environment by avoiding deforestation . On the other hand , books help students develop their attention span . They have to focus on the topic for more than 5 minutes . Next , to find true information for homework , it is better to use books , because on the Internet , students can find fake news . To sum up , in the near future , all schools and universities will be able to use computers or tablets instead of books . It is more useful , convenient and more attractive for students . 
The importance of zoos focuses on several talks when environmental workers are together . To the people who support zoos in cities , these places have a great importance for human beings to be aware of their impact on nature , because only when you know about something can you protect it . When the zoos attract people to them , a lot of activities can happen , whatever the age of the public . On the other hand , a lot of people think that animals must live free . In this conception , zoos are bad places for animals , because there are very small cages there and they do not provide enough interaction with other species , as would happen in their natural habitats . However , I think the best way to make people become more aware about their role as a being belonging in nature is to provide fair conditions for animals to live in freedom . For example , in South Africa , the savanna 's animals can live free and human beings pay to visit them in their natural habitat . This practice is called " safari " and it has been seen as a positive way to improve human awareness about the environment . 
When I was a university student , I was living with my parents . I do not think it was the best choice . My parents ' house is located outside the city . Travelling from my parents ' house to the university takes two hours . I remember I did not usually study enough because I often felt tired . On the other hand , my husband was living alone in another city , he grew as a person , he became more independent , learnt to manage his money and to solve problems . Also he usually spent his time on extracurricular activities like baseball , gym or parties . I never had time for extracurricular activities because I did not have time and my mother did not allow me . That was boring and sad . I remember that most of my partners were living alone because their parents ' houses were so far . They usually spent the time studying in the library . They had the weekend for parties as well . I usually spent my weekend studying because I did not have enough time to do my homework . 
My favorite film is " Shingeki no Kyojin , " Attack on Titan . Its original comic is a bestseller , because its development is very rapid , and because as the story goes on , its foreshadowing comes together elegantly . But the movie is good -for -nothing . If you know the original , you will realize that no matter how meticulously an original story is written , picturization version can spoil it to the extent you can laugh . You are a comic artist , so this movie will give you a lesson that even if someone offers you picturization , of your work , you had better rethink whether or not it is good offer . 
TV is one of the advanced technologies that impacts on our lives in several ways . The most use of this technology is for leisure , since the various channels provide us with different sorts of films , cartoons , animation and news . Furthermore , a handful of educational channels are offering people numerous courses in different majors . As I remember , at a certain time in the afternoon , my mother used to watch a cooking channel and learn new methods of cooking from it . Nowadays , even more channels with such content are broadcast on television during the day . I recently saw a channel which gives people at home some exercises and teaches them how to do the workouts correctly . Also , some channels have some useful courses for high school students who want to enter university and do not have a clear vision of college and university . In conclusion , while TV has plenty of programmes to entertain people , it contains educational content too . 
I used to play video games in my free time for almost ten years , but since last year I decided to use my free time to learn some skills by taking part in some online courses which exist around the world . Well , they really make my free time be more helpful and awesome , for instance , in these weeks I have been searching on the university 's website to find some courses about learning English . What I like most about learning Enlish online is getting the chance to communicate with native speakers , which can help me in terms of pronunciation . My last class was this morning . 
I like exercise and I like to do it in the gym but because I do not have enough time to go to a gym , I do it in my home every day , it helps me feel refreshed and healthy . Research has shown that doing exercise early in the morning may not help the body to work better but if we do exercise a while after we wake up , it can improve our body 's activities . As I am an accountant and I always sit behind a desk , I need to do some exercise that will help me to move my neck and my back . 
Two years ago , I was on my best holiday ever . I went to the Maldives with my boyfriend . Actually , that holiday was a surprise for me . First , I had no idea where we were going . I finally knew our destination at the airport . I was really astonished , obviously . That journey was really exciting . I could not believe what a magical place the Maldives was . A clear , blue ocean and soft sand . That was the most magnificent place I have even seen . The time there was very intense . We did a lot of wonderful things . That was the first time I saw a real dolphin . What 's more , we had an opportunity to swim with those animals . It was an incredible experience , indeed . We also saw many beautiful views , especially during the sunsets . That was unbelievably magical . We had another reason why that holiday was special . My boyfriend asked me to marry him during our walk along the bay . Of course , it was so remarkable . To be honest , I started to cry , but of course , I said yes . That was such a surprise for me . I 'm sure , I will remember that holiday forever . The best holiday of my life . 
