Improving writing skills is affected by several important factors that completely depend on the methods which writers have used to train . Some days ago , my dear teacher introduced me to a website called " Write and Improve . " Soon after , I found it so useful to improve my writing skills , such as modifying my spelling , using familiar words correctly and so on . By registering on this site , you can write some essays . Soon after , the site is going to check your essay and send you some feedback about your writing , which is so helpful and gives you a chance to find out what was wrong with your essay . I have tried the website for almost 6 months and now I think my writing has been affected by its awesome methods , because " Write and Improve " offers a lot of titles to write about and by accomplishing those , you can modify your skills and visions about different subjects and also find more vocabulary to use in the future . In conclusion , I would recommend you use this amazing website and its wonderful features to improve your writing skills . 
Different teachers have different methods and styles of teaching concepts , so because of these differences between teachers , some people think that it can be more useful for students to change their teacher every year , and try different methods . But some others believe that it is not a reliable way to learn because students will get used to their teacher 's behavior and changing teachers constantly can cause irreparable harm . By considering all the main points about this title , we should mention that both of these thoughts have some strengths and weaknesses which we interfere them in continue . In terms of learning issues , we should consider the behavior of both teachers and students . On the one hand , it can be helpful for some students to have different teachers because it will help them to have varied perspective on concepts and they will end up with better understanding . For example , when a student wants to learn verbs , a teacher may tell him/her some words that do not make sense to him/her , but another teacher may say this concept in a better way . On the other hand , some students are not adaptable and changing their teacher can not be helpful because coordinating with a new method and behavior will be stiff for them , so they are not going to make a great progress . In conclusion , many different elemen have role - depends on personality and age - which people find the best way to learn concepts therefore , the main point is try to find best way without any prejudge . 
I believe that men do not posses the right to be unfit . It should be the duty of every single citizen to reach at least some level of physical fitness . As a society , we have got to be able to stand shoulder to shoulder with the defence forces when a crisis comes . But you ca not force anybody to be healthy . You ca not demand hard work from lazy people . You can nurture them , but you do not control them . It is people 's mentality that stands against everything imposed on them . Here is the way to nurture people . They have to realise that hard work and training may be unpleasant . But it is nothing in comparison with diabetes or a heart stroke . It is much easier to carry eighty kilograms instead of hundred and sixty or more . All you have got to do is simply do something . Anything . And what about the idea of activities at least three times a week ? It is definitely more than nothing . But it is slack . You can and you should do something every single day . Every day is a new day and your body needs to get some healthy dopamine from exercise . This dopamine is much more important than that from junk food or alcohol . They are deserved . The opposite option is this . Do not do anything . Just sit on your couch and wait . It wo not take a long time and your culture will decay . Another culture will come and push you away . They will annihilate your lazy and fat population . Here is one beautiful saying . Hard times make hard men . Hard men make good times . Good times make soft men . And soft men make hard times . So stop eating your doughnut , throw away your milkshake and go after it . 
In my free time , I do a variety of things : playing games on my pc , fishing at my local pond and drawing . When the weather is right I prefer fishing , but when the weather is rainy or I do not feel like it , I start gaming or drawing . 
