Nowadays , so many people are obsessed with exercise , or they think that this it is the most important thing to be fit and healthy , and although I think that it is necessary too , it is not as important as other things . Firstly , whether you ask a doctor or a nutritionist , everyone is aware that sport is an essential activity for our well -being because it prevents us from coming down with illnesses , such as obesity , cardiac problems , it helps us to make faster recoveries , it strengthens us ... So it is indispensable to exercise at least 30 minutes every day . But , however , a lot of people are wrong when they think that they only need to do that to be healthy because there are other fundamental issues in our life that are necessary as well to be wholesome , for example , our social life , our mental health , the conditions and environment where we live ... . A further point is that another super needed matter is our diet because if you do not eat salubriously , exercise will not help you as much as it could . In conclusion , sport is an indispensable activity in our life , but there are other things that are important too and we should not underestimate them . 
Health is an essential part of our life because it lets us maintain our lifestyle . Good health gives us the opportunity to develop different activities and projects in a physical and mental way . On the other hand , wealth is also important to maintain this lifestyle , being that to maintain good health , people need to invest in healthy food , exercise , even hobbies to preserve a good health , that is why both aspects of life are important . Keeping healthy is not an easy challenge because of different aspects which are expensive nowadays . But , health is not only about money or buying material things ; health is also about being kind , grateful and charitable to others , which means in simple words being a good human being . Without good health , people ca not maintain themselves to become wealthy . Besides , being wealthy is also important because it lets us keep a good life quality , helping other people to overcome each difficulty . To sum up , being healthy is a key element to be wealthy because both aspects are important for a human being 's development to enhance a good lifestyle . 
