For maintaining an excellent level of health , three important things should be considered , which are like the three essential edges of a triangle ; Sleep , Food and Exercise . None of these three things can diminish the importance of other factors ' roles and influence in gaining body health . An adequate diet is an essential key to having a healthy body and mind . Since our food intake is the source of energy that our body has , following a balanced diet can impact our health in a serious way . Furthermore , looking after a healthy body can not be achieved if the body does not have enough time to recover , which can only be covered with by having enough time for sleeping . In this period of time , our body not only finds the time to release the tension which we experienced during the day , but it also allows the body to perform its duty properly . On the other hand , the body needs regular movement to keep the percentage of body fat and energy balanced and it only can be achieved by exercising . Therefore , while exercise is important for our well -being , it is solely not enough to maintain it , and it should be besides a suitable diet and sleep . 
Write and Improve This review is focused on a special tool to improve your writing skills . You need just a computer and internet connection so you can enjoy this tool at your home . The principle of the tool is really simple . You can choose one of the many tasks . The tasks are divided by difficulty . You then have to write the text to accomplish the task . It can be an essay , review , story or anything . Every task includes requirements for minimum or/and maximum words . Once you finish , it will give you results and , most importantly , it shows you your mistakes . You can rewrite your answers until you get it right . Every time you receive an evaluation . And that is the most important thing to me . When I started , I received A " results regularly . After a while , I reached B1 and then B2 . Today , I received a C1 evaluation for the first time . It is proof that it has really improved my writing skills . So I can honestly recommend this useful tool to you . If you want to improve your writing skills from your home and you do not have someone to help you , you could help yourself with this tool . It is for free and it can be fun , too . If nothing else , you cold find out something interesting about yourself . Writing improves not just your language skills but it helps your mind , too . 
I think learning to speak a foreign language is less important these days than in the past , except English . Besides your interest , you do not need to speak any language except English . I have two reasons which support my opinion . Firstly , English has become a global language . As everyone in this world speaks English , once you master it , it 's enough . You do not need to learn any other language to communicate with people . Actually , when I went on a trip to Germany , whose mother tongue is German , there was English everywhere . Clerks spoke English and English signs were everywhere . Secondly , technology has developed rapidly . As interpreting devices are on sale , we do not need to speak the same language to talk together . Actually , I used it sometimes and it was very useful . It did not waste time , or was not stressful . I hope it is going to be more popular . 
