While language is one of the widely used communication tools in the world , learning English as an international language is very important . In this day and age , English is known as the first language in the world , and most of the academic and political communications in the world are conducted in this language , therefore , it has become a vital language in our lives . As I am a master 's student and need to read English papers in my field and also be able to write new papers about my subject , thus I need to master English . Secondly , I am in the procedure of applying to universities abroad and one of the first essential requirements is passing an English academic test . Thirdly , with the rapid growth of this language everywhere , it could unlock career opportunities for me , especially if I want to work in an international company . What is more , since I like travelling abroad and my first language is not widely used in the world , I need to learn English to be able to connect with other people in other countries . 
I nearly always use a computer . As I study Chemistry and also we are fighting against the Coronavirus , it has become common to use a computer at home . The schools are closed and we are studying at home or working at home . Well , I used to use it to do my homework , do interviews and learn English . I have an English schedule for the weekend . I love to use the CORELDraw to make my plans for the weekend and I love watching videos on You Tube and Instagram . I a couple of watching watch Teacher Sam who teaches English on Instagram . 
