For many people , music is a very important part of their life . It helps them to find the best solution for the problem or it is the easiest way of entertainment . In my opinion , students should learn to play musical instruments . Firstly , playing instruments develops our brain . We are able to focus on the subjects for a longer time than somebody who has never tried to do it . What 's more , students become more patient and hard -working because if they want to be a master , they must practise many hours a day . Secondly , studying music develops general knowledge . They learn about famous composers and conductors . Furthermore , people who learn to play a musical instrument become more sensitive . They know how to find a balance between relaxing and working . On the other hand , playing a musical instrument steals a lot of free time . Students who want to be the best need practise a long time . They do not have enough spare time to develop their relationship with friends . As a result , they are shy and lonely . To sum up , studying music is a very important part of education . It opens our view on the word and other people . 
We are living in the communication era , which means we need to communicate with people with different languages and cultures , so as we all know , English is most international language that many people in the world are able to speak , therefore we need to know it as well as we can . Nowadays , many resources are prepared for those that want to learn English and all of these resources have a lot of things which learners can use . There are some books , podcasts , social media pages , websites , etc , but one of the most effective of these resources which I found so useful is a website that helps learners with their writings , " Write&Improve . " This website has some helpful features which help all the users with different levels . On this website , users can write their essays and the site is going to check it and give them some feedback , so users have access to a lot of positive points which help them to improve their levels . Besides , the website offers a wide variety of services , such as creating a workbook and showing some diagrams which are very useful for finding your progress graph . As you know , assessment is one of the most important factors in making a good progress because , on the one hand , it let learners find their weakness and , on the other hand , by correcting their mistakes and allowing them to rewrite their essay , they can get a chance to move forward . Although , checking the essay by robots can cause some misunderstanding , yet the feedback is so accurate and useful . 
A lot of things change every day in life sestem , travel is one of them . In the past , travel was through animals like horses and camels . These days we have trains , planes , also cars , to travel faster than before . In the future , I think some things will be faster than now , some quick , maybe reborts who which could arrive in the same moment , and these can check passengers ' passports and be a captain for a plane . But others against me say everything is going to be the same , there will be no more inventions more than the airplane , subway and underground . It will be impossible to invent faster transportation than those . It will affect people and cause millions of accidents . Therefore , I believe if I could invent some faster transportation , I would show it to people and help them to travel . But until now , we do not have anything new . 
Many countries in the world are still in lockdown amid the COVID -19 fear . Some of them have eased restrictions , however , travel could have new norms . The transportation to go abroad remains the same , aircraft . A passport will also be required as usual . The most different procedure in the future will be the negative certification of the virus . All countries will take up submitting the certification that ' I have not contracted COVID -19 ' at immigration in the airport , otherwise the previous fear could come again . If you used to take part in the tour group whenever you travel abroad , the kind of tour group will become a small group , such as less than 10 people . This small group tour raises the total travel cost due to less discount . It leads to fewer people joining the trips , therefore , all travel industries face on something new lures . ." A human is a thinking reed , " said Pascal . Now is the time to become the thinking reed ! 
There are many people who lived for a hundred years and never started their journey . A calm and relaxing life is comforting . You can feel in your comfort zone . But you have to deserve it . I believe that you should suffer for ninety percent of your life . Why ? Because it will make the remaining ten percent special . Nothing interesting , nothing unforgettable and nothing exciting happens in your comfort zone . I do not live to be calm . I want the rush and excitement . I believe that it is not important how long you live . It was Marcus Aurelius who said that it does not matter . All you have to do is to live a life you can be proud of . Do not waste your time and go after it every day . Just imagine that you die and you go to heaven . There stands Saint Peter and recalls what you have done and , most importantly , what you could have done but did not . You could be that and that and reach so many things . But you chose another way . You chose to live a calm life in your comfort zone . You chose to waste your life . You could help so many people , for example , but you did not . So do not count your years . You will have enough time to rest once you die . Now live and savour every day . 
