In contemporary times , many people in our society value being rich very highly . However , a lot of research implies that it is better to be healthy than to be rich , if you have to choose one . This essay discusses why being healthy is more important than being rich . Firstly , a lot of research shows that the people who are rich value their lives less than those who are not rich . Less confidence causes many health problems . For example , rich people who are less satisfied with their life consume proportionately more alcohol and they do less activities to stay fit . There are many diseases coming more for rich people than less affluent people . Those diseases include heart disease and obesity . Secondly , health is more important than wealth , because if you do not feel physically fit , but you have money , it would be very difficult to do every activity that you like . If you are not able to things that you like because of health problems , it can cause mental problems . For example , you will estimate the value of life less and you can do things which can weaken your health further , both physical and mental . Another point that makes being healthy more important than being rich is if you are healthy , you are be able to become rich . The reverse is , in most cases , not possible or easy . There are many diseases that you cannot eradicate in your body , you will live with those diseases forever . To summarize , being healthy is very important . If you are healthy , you can do many activities which can make your life better and richer . The reverse is , in many cases , not possible . 
I have studied on the website Write and Improve for a long time , probably since two years ago . , . I found this website when I talked with my friend . She reviewed for me about how the website would be helpful to improve my writing skill and I tried . This website is really useful and it has a lot of interesting functions for me to improve my writing skill . Firstly , Write and Improve has different levels , from beginner to advanced , or higher is business and just for fun . So you can easily choose the level suitable for you . For me , when I had just started practising on this website , I chose the beginner level to get familiar with writing , then I tried a higher level , intermediate and now it is advanced . Secondly , it has a lot of various topics and fields , so you have many options , you can choose any theme you like . I 'm an introvert person , so I usually choose a topic relevant to society and some topic arguments about issues in life . The theme I found best is the debate about becoming a volunteer in school or not . Thirdly , it also has a good system to check your mistakes in your essay , point out the mistakes you made and the way to fix them . It is very convenient and useful , right ? Fourthly , it has a progress board to let you know your progress . Fifthly , it also has a timer for you to check your ability in writing . Finally , the screen of the website is completely in English , so it will help you to improve the language you are learning . My advice is you should try to learn on this website Write and Improve . 
This is an idea which is supposed to work because it will strengthen young people 's helping aptitude . I must admit I did not completely agree with this proposal , but after having seen the achievements in British schools , l changed my opinion and l am trustful that the good results can be got also in Italy . The project was initially managed by Rome -based schools that are going to give some lectures with distance learning for students who live not only in other Italian cities , but also abroad . In other words , students can decide to follow on -line instructions in order to plan their volunteer activities around their neighbourhood and get a score for all the satisfactory results ; the score , over the next weeks will be computed for the final score of the degree . This kind of activity should be always promoted because many areas of our society need consistent help to overcome their problems , but what is more important , schools should be funded by the local and national government . There is already a large number of students who have tried this kind of experience , this is because they are simply invited to brush up on the notes they made . Newly interested students wise , what they are called to do is to read up about volunteer activities and how to deal with people in disadvantaged social and economical conditions . Contrary to popular belief , a volunteer experience is something that enriches youngsters and adults . In order to make the volunteer experiences as satisfactory as possible , we need to make a precise timetable where all the activities are carefully planned . For example , let students go to migrant assistance centers where they will likely have the opportunity to practise their foreign language skills . 
In my opinion , moving alone is a hard way to become independent . Moreover , when you are in the first years of college , you need some help to overcome the stress . For instance , homework could be difficult and if you panic about that , there is nobody for tell you : " everything is right " or " you are the best , " something like that . Furthermore , if you feel bad owing to some strange food , nobody can help you either . In fact , if you can have a roommate , this is more fun than being alone and you pay just half of the bills . Also if you know you will have a roommate , you can choose a bigger apartment . In addition , if you 're busy and your roommate is not , she or he can cook the dinner . However , staying at home with your family is a good choice too . For example , you do not have to clean an apartment or cook , you just have to focus on your studying . Besides , your parents will support you and help you with your homework if that 's not too difficult for them . So long as you have a desk where it 's calm and you have your own room . Sometimes , you do not have the money for an apartment which is next to the college , moreover , an apartment can be really expensive and if you have some project , getting married or buying a house , you need to keep your money . At last , I think the best is to have a roommate , but if you are ready to live alone and you have the money for it , go ! On the contrary , you are not ready at all to stay with your parents and , do not worry , you can exchange next year and take an apartment . Just enjoy your college years ! 
Most medical doctors prefer to work in cities rather than in the countryside . There are a few reasons for such a situation . Firstly , working in an urban area brings more chances for career development . Secondly , hospitals located in cities are far better equipped than those in rural areas , which gives medics the possibility to fully use their aptitudes and abilities . Lastly , being a doctor in a city is undoubtedly more beneficial than in the countryside . However , this generates a predicament of a not sufficient number of medics in rural areas and , under such circumstances , the lives of the people living in those places are endangered . One obvious solution to this problem could be an increment of doctors ' salaries , who work in those regions . It might convince some medics to change their workplace . Another thing could be supply hospitals with larger number of ambulances and mainly with helicopters , which in theory could guarantee greater accessibility to medical healthcare for people whose lives are at risk . 
Hi , Billal , I went on a trip to Los Angeles with my classmates last week . We ate around and went to some tourist spots . I enjoyed the trip so much and I was so excited before it because it was my first time in the United States , and also visiting Los Angeles was a very important event for me . Let me talk a little about my family history . There was my great -grandfather in Hiroshima , Japan in the early 20th century . He decided to migrate to Los Angeles . After that , he began to run his own businesses there , which were a Japanese inn and a grocery store to sell soy sauces . He started a family , which means my grandfather was born in Los Angeles ! A few years later , they came back to Hiroshima because of the World War II . Tetsuo 
