After high -school graduation , students have to make choices about their studies . They need to decide what and where they want to study . In the process , other choices have to be made such as : should I stay living at home while I am studying , or should I move away and live on my own ? For some , the choice is simple , as their university is not close to their homes , they have to get their own apartment . Others have to decide whether or not they will move out from their parents ' . When students can decide , there are few questions that need to be taken into account . First : how will you pay your rent ? There are two options . Your parents will fund you , or you will have to take a part -time job to pay for it . In the second scenario , students need to be aware that they will have less free time , and less time for their homework . Secondly : will I feel comfortable living on my own ? Indeed , some young students would not feel able to live by their own , and still need the support of their parents . And last but not least : will it be a benefit for my studies ? It is important to know if living on my own will be a true benefit or contreversily if it will bring difficulties . In my opinion , moving away to study can be a great opportunity , and young students will become more independent living on their own if they can manage it . Nevertheless , it is important to be aware that it wo not fit all students , and everyone is different . I do not have a yes or no answer to this question . 
I always exercise in my free time . I exercise every morning and evening . Because exercising can help me strengthen myself and lose weight . I am really fond of exercising by working out following a trainer on You Tube or doing yoga . The exercise that I did last time was yoga . I can concentrate my mind while doing yoga and I do not think about anything . It is good for me to do any exercise every day , I am always fresh after doing exercise and ready for some hard work in a new day . 
Research recently has shown that playing musical instruments can be considered an effective phenomenal for people to feel more peaceful and improve their mental health . As a way to manage people to achieve this goal , some schools have started teaching music to students and some of them have avoided doing that , due to what scientists have found , music would help people to concentrate much more . When a musician starts playing a piece , different organs get involved in this activity and because it asks for more compatibility , doing such a thing can help us to enhance our brain working . Although preparing a proper environment and adequate musical instruments may cause a high expense for schools , the outcomes that playing instrument bring back are more influential than this expense . So , if the governments start encouraging schools to change their curriculum and incorporate some music courses for students , it can be like an insurance for students ' mental health . 
My reasons for learning English I have studied English since I was in kindergarten . Twice a week there was a class in which a teacher taught us animals and colours . However , I do not know if I remember these from then . When I started school , my parents wanted me to learn English , even though I did not like it . They used to say that it would help me later , but at what ? They did not say . Later on , I started to like English classes because of a teacher who made these seem funny . Only then did I think about why I should learn English . First of all , since I was a little child I have wanted to travel the world , so I realised that if it ever happened , I should be ready to communicate with the local people . But how could I do it if I do not know any worldwide language ? That is the main reason why I decided to learn English . Another reason for learning English is the perspective of a well -paid job . Nowadays , almost every employer ask you to know at least one foreign language . So it does not matter if you are very good at doing something , if you do not know one more language besides your mother tongue . Moreover , I would love to have the chance to study abroad and that 's why I must learn English . All in all , one can never know what life brings , so it is better to be prepared for any opportunity one might receive . 
