Is speaking a foreign language still important nowadays ? I believe it 's more important than ever . In the past , speaking a foreign language was important , especially to get a good job . However , today , with globalization , all the countries have become more connected . More connection between countries means that speaking another language is relevant to work , to study or for friendship . I will explore the reasons in the essay below . First of all , in the past , speaking a foreign language was related to work . Usually people who spoke another language worked in big companies overseas . Theses days , even in small companies , a second language is required . For example , I worked in a family company in Brazil and it was necessary to speak and write and English to talk to the customers . Second , today , with the internet , it has become easier to have contact with people around the world . To talk to a foreigner , you have to speak his language . In conclusion , it 's important to speak a foreign language these days , more than in the past . 
I love watching a movie in my free time , and I would like to recommend one of my favourite movies of all time , " When Harry Met Sally . " This movie is about Harry and Sally . They have been friends for almost their whole lives . Though they might have known each other well , they do not know what they truly want for love . This movie has the simplest yet very interesting way to tell a story of two different people . It is not just an ordinary romantic comedy , I promise ! If you have some free time , I really do recommend you to go watch it ! 
In terms of school improvement , there many different things that will happen , such as In material , the the study ways and the school . The future will change plenty of study strategies . Technology will in the whole teaching process . For instance : a smart board rather than a black board and smart laps for scientific materials , also there will be sorts of new classes about art and theater . In addition , about social science and the environment . In the school building , for example , the diversity of playgrounds , furthermore , add swimming sports and hiking . A marathon in mathematics or science experiments and , moreover , foe for computer sciences . I am assured the the future version will be different than before and it will be useful for next generations , perhaps for teachers the procedures will be easier than before . 
I believe cultural exchange is one of the most important things we can do in life . I do not see any disadvantage if you can afford it . Maybe the only disadvantage is related to the money you should spend . Studying in another country could be expensive , especially if you do it in a great university or high school . Apart from that , I see the exchange as an opportunity . Being in touch with new cultures allows the student to grow as a person . Learning new languages could be one of the most important skills you could acquire . At the end of the process , you should be able to speak fluently another language . The networking effect is an advantage of experience too . Knowing different people in different countries could be a great opportunity to increase your career . As I mention in the beginning , in my view , almost all are advantages if you finally decide to study abroad . 
In this new school year , I have the determination to study hard . I want to improve my English skills to get a better job in the future . The areas I am pleased with are listening and speaking . Watching TV shows on Netflix has improved my listening skills . On the other hand , I practice speaking with a friend of mine twice a week . The areas I need to improve are clearly writing and reading . Writing is very difficult to train . This Cambridge tool is great for me , but I would like to write better so I want to take advantage of this new year to do it . About reading , I have no time to do it . To achieve my goals , I will buy some books that I can read in my free time . I will also practice with Cambridge English to write better and ask some doubts to my teacher . 
Nowadays , studying abroad has become popular among students of different levels and this kind of opportunity has pros and cons to consider . In my opinion , I agree with the idea of studying abroad because there are more pros than cons . Some of the most important pros about studying abroad are : more options to study ; international students have the opportunity to progress in their studies and more job opportunities with enhanced CVs , students also make more friends , become more independent and learn new languages and cultures , that is why abroad study trips or scholarships are good chances to students . On the other hand , students also have to deal with difficulties and cons during their abroad journeys . Some of the problems are the school place cost , culture shock , no fluency in language , even some students have issues on the return to their country and their studies there . To sum up , studying abroad is a wonderful experience for each person , but people also consider some things before they decide to go on this kind of study adventure . 
My favourite season of the year By : Carla Parr I like both seasons in my country , but if I have to choose one , definitively the winter season will be the chosen one . For me , the winter season is the best season ever because , during this season , I can snuggle with a mug of hot chocolate and watch movies . I can also share with friends on a camping trip making smores . In general , I can do different activities with people that I love . Some advantages of the winter season are the holidays . During the winter season , Christmas and New Year 's eve come . These holidays give us a great opportunity to share with family and friends , spending time together or doing funny activities , such as a secret Santa , special dinners , or small trips near to my town . In conclusion , winter is my favourite season ever because it is the perfect opportunity to share and create moments with relatives and fellows I love ; some of the people who I am not able to see frequently , that is why this is my favourite season . 
Exercise is obviously important for our health . If you do not do exercise at all , your muscles will be vulnerable , it causes easy wounded , bad metabolism , and loss of vitality . However , is exercise the only way to keep healthy ? Let 's talk about a disabled person . They can keep healthy somehow , though they ca not do exercise easily . Do not you think there are things that are more important ? Exercise is physically good , but how about mentally ? Are you satisfied with exercise only ? The answer is " not exactly . " I 'm sure when you eat whatever you want or whenever you are hungry , your stomach is satisfied . When you get round to reading your most favorite book , I believe that your sentiment is satisfied . This means that your body is satisfied with them , and you are meant to be healthy at this time . Moreover , loving yourself or other people is also important mentally and emotionally to keep healthy . Consuming , such as shopping or going out , may be occasionally important for relaxing . I think health contains many aspects and a variety of things are important activities . 
Dear sir , I heard you are considering banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants . I have to say this is a bad idea , and may cause a strike in our lovely town . Why ? Due to convince and multiple functions , people depend on their phone to get information , communicating with others , surfing on the internet , and so on . Although people may deeply adhere to their phone , even be addicted while sometimes checking their mobile unconsciously . It seems dangerous depending on how the user uses the tool . In fact , the tool is innocent . In addition , the mobile phone was created to improve the efficiency of communication , when sometimes we need to talk or confirm with someone , for instance , you went to the shop but suddenly forgot what your family requested you to purchase . It 's easy to check the list immediately . Therefore , forbidding to use the mobile phone is definitely backset to a previous time . I believe this is unwise and not worth it for the council to make the law . Furthermore , it 's breaking the constitution , which acclaimed to guard the people 's right , such as freedom and secret talking . The council should stand with people to protect their natural right in the constitution , instead of depriving it . It 's a shame to go against a superior law and neglect the opinion of the public . To boil it down , banning the use of mobile phones is not only against the personal will but also break the institution in our country . I sincerely recommend you to retreat this proposal . 
Living away on your own during school is a good way to get to know new possibilities and overcome challenges . Some students prefer to live at home with their family while they are at school , that is because they can save money and it is more comfortable having your parents around to support you . However , I can say from my own experience that living away is the best option if you are open to new challenges . I will explore below . I went to a university far from my hometown . Firstly , I took a bus in Vinhedo to go to Sao Paulo , where my university is located . I watched the classes and then I took the bus back to Vinhedo . During this period , I lived with mom and it was good having my mom 's support . Nevertheless , it was a long trip every day . I spent around three hours on a bus and I was getting tired . After a few months , I decided to move to Sao Paulo to live on my own . That was the best decision I ever made ! I saved time , I learned how to cook , how to take care of my house . And this was a learning that I took for the rest of my life . In conclusion , despite all the facilities of living with our parents , living on your own is an amazing experience which brings you personal development . 
Volunteer work is always the most important thing which unites you to whole world . This exercise is about people , love and happiness . In my opinion , volunteering could help you to become a better person with interesting abilities . You should be a communicative person , with high aspirations and a different talent : to help people . I believe that a student is a child who dreams of becoming an adult . This difficult process is easier when humanity becomes helpful . Certainly , volunteer work must be a challenge for every man who does it , but when you realise the opportunities , you are the happiest . " The more , the better " says a celebrity proverb . So , your happiness depends on the difficulty and hard work . The more people helped , the happier you are . Everyone looks for help and other people give love every second . When I was a student , I participated in BOS , a business organization for students . This is very interesting volunteer work . It helped me so much to be a better person with better abilities in economics and communication . I was in this program for one year and I think that I was a lucky person to be there . I love this organization with al great people . I believe it is so important to practice different programs and a variety of things which could help you to become a complete human . All humans in the world could be better if they progress every day . I think that this is the key to success . 
