Opinions widely diverge on studying abroad . Some believe that it may have positive points for students to live off shore and others explain the reasons which might prove it not being helpful for young people . In this essay , we are going to interefere the different aspects of this issue . Studying in a foreign country might help young people to become familiar with a new culture , hobbies , tradition , lifestyle , etc . , so that these can help young adults to find a different perspective on life . These students get a chance to be independent and make their own way to live , but on the other hand , they may also find it difficult to live in a new country because of some issues that they have to deal with . The main problem that they might have is about learning , understanding and speaking a new language . For example , imagine a student who does not know well the language of the destination country that he wants to go , it will be like a nightmare and he will absolutely face many problems in high school or university , and this problem might cause him not to be able to manage to understand his lesson . NA , . when we start to evaluate the issue , we discover the advantages of studying abroad outweigh the disadvantages and it depends on the students ' awareness of the destination country . Today , studding abroad is regarded as a new opportunity to rise the level of education , which helps people with cultural transmission . 
