My experience with Write and Improve . Write and Improve is a website where you can improve your writing through exercises . These exercises will be checked for you and it will show you where there is room for improvement . A simple concept really , but it has proven to be very successful for me ; ever since I 've started using Write and Improve , I 've improved my writing a lot , without a great deal of effort . I only wished it was a bit more organized . At first glance , the website is a mess , but this is a small price to pay when using Write and Improve . You can see your progress in the graph on the right , this is a great feature . Sadly , however , you ca not scroll to previous results that do not fit in the graph , which comes as a rather significant annoyance . in spite of these flaws , the website is a real lifesaver . I 'd recommend it to anyone hoping to improve their English . 
There is no doubt , these days , many children are addicted to video games . The question is , do video games have a good effect on children or not ? In this essay , I will discuss both views and draw my own opinion . In terms of a positive side , video games could teach kids some skills . The main reason given to support this idea is it can help them learn another language while playing by speaking with other players from other counties . To illustrate that , a lot of teenagers around the world join these games online and speak with others . In other words , they have fun studying . But others said video games have many disadvantages . Firstly , they waste their time on nothing useful . Secondly , sometimes , there are sexy people playing or they show you while you are playing . Also , maybe it will hurt kids ' eyes if they use it for a long time . Therefore , some people said it really important to avoid children from these games , but others are against them and said it improves their skills . From my side , I believe video games have many cons , more than pros , because of that , I feel avoied them is the best choice . 
