Opinions widely diverge about the functions of TV in societies . If it just has an entertainment role or it can also help the governments to promote public awareness about different aspects of life . Today , TV is an integral part of our life . Generally , people spend 2 or 3 hours a day watching different programs , so it seems like a powerful phenomenal to lead public thoughts to a certain point . If governments want to change the specific habits and behavior of their society , then TV can be beneficial . But sometimes , there are downsides to consider . In some countries , where the governments have the control of the media , they usually use this leading power to guide people to certain points which are not exactly helpful for people . For example , when a government wants to start a war , the media can help it to provide public thoughts about the benefits of war , which assuredly is not true . In my opinion , due to the era that we are living in , TV can have an important role to educate societies or not for it to depend on what it wants to do . 
Nowadays , many people want to live healthily . Many of them exercise very hard almost every day . For sure , exercise is important for our health . However , to me , there is one more meaningful thing in healthy living . Similarly important in a healthy life is healthy food . Some people forget that they need a balanced diet . Even if they exercise hard every day , without a proper diet , they gain nothing . Our diet should be high -fibre . It should also be rich in other valuable ingredients , such as protein and vitamins . With bad food habits , people do not achieve a healthy life . Even when we exercise , but we eat fast foods , we ca not say that our life is healthy . Fast foods cross throught our health . Of course , some people can think that they ca not make valuable meals with all these ingredients . But nowadays there are many companies which prepare appropriate meals for us . All we need to do is to send off for them . Those companies prepare our meals and even deliver them to every place we want . For that reason , we can focus on our exercise . And of course , with training and a balanced diet , we set our lives right . Then we can say , we live healthily . 
In my opinion , experiencing volunteer work is a great requirement for students who want to graduate . I think that would help students in several ways . Firstly , from the philanthropic aspect , the youngsters will learn how to help others and raise their collaboration spirit without expecting any payment . Secondly , volunteer work experience can be a bright spot in the students ' CV , which can be an effective thing in their college or university acceptance . Moreover , this type of work makes them be in contact with more people with different beliefs , which will teach them to behave in different situations and , in my opinion , this experience is not easily achievable . On the other hand , maybe students see it as a burden on their shoulders before graduation , but they will find its value when they finish it . In conclusion , maybe expecting a volunteer activity as a requirement from the students before graduation is a little unfair for a person who needs to graduate soon , but this adventure will benefit them in their future life and career . 
From a psychological point of view , working in a stimulating office may help employees feel more lively and have more satisfaction . Employees in such an office can communicate with others , talk , have fun and so on . On the other hand , having an cubicle or enclosed workstation provides more privacy for staff and improves their concentration . Due to this prelude , choosing each of these kinds of office has downsides to be considered . On the one hand , an open office may help coworkers be more eager to do their job , of course , without privacy , and on the other hand , an enclosed work station has privacy without feeling lively , but indeed , there are more options available to design an office . Some offices that were made by expert architects always have a specific spot for co -workers that helps them to be together and also such offices have separate rooms for employees , which helps them to have privacy and concentration while doing their jobs . In conclusion , an appropriate office should be made based on human necessities and it is the main point to compatible with different staff feelings . 
