My reasons for learning English . I am working very hard to enhance my English for many reasons . Firstly , I have to speak and write English fluently for the continuation of my studies . After my current studies , I would like to follow a master 's degree at University . One of the requirements that you have to meet to be admitted to this master 's is an English level of at least C1 in all language aspects , reading , listening , writing and speaking . Furthermore , I live a country that has an open economy . In the Netherlands , you have many international companies and if you look at each vocational job that is available , they require a high English level . 
I have been using Write and Improve for a month . I realize that writing English sentences every day makes my English abilities improve . There are three reasons below . Firstly , practising repeatedly and continuously is really important to improve in something . Secondly , you can focus on only writing English sentences without searching what you should write because the service offers a lot of topics to practice writing English . The only thing you have to do is pick it out from those ones . Lastly , there are many features there to encourage you to study . For instance , you can see your progress , feedback , topic lists on a dashboard if you log into the service . Overall , writing English sentences on Write and Improve is useful . You should try it if you are struggling with writing in English , or searching for the solution to improve your English abilities . 
