The impact of exercise in a healthy lifestyle is a common discussion topic in our times . The long working days and the stressful pace of life do not allow us to dedicate more time to our body , but , are there more important things than our physical condition ? My answer is yes . I think mental health is more important than our physical condition . What happens is both are linked . There are several aspects to cover if we want to keep our mind in a good condition , family , food , salary , work -life balance and of course our body . Getting some exercise is not the only way to keep our body healthy , we have to care about other things too . To conclude , I would like to mention again the importance of a proper balance . A healthy life is a combination of a trained body , a peaceful mind , a fun and interesting job and a stable family life . If we work in all these dimensions , we will enjoy a healthier life ! 
Nowadays , more and more people choose to study English through self -study . This may be a real challenge , the experience being beyond comparison from the classical form of learning , in a classroom with a teacher . The writing part was never my strength as I often find it difficult to write a purely genuine text , but I can say that since I have discovered the free writing tool offered by Cambrige , Write and Improve , my life has radically changed ! The thing about this educational website is that it is very handy , offering instant feedback of your writing . It suggests possible changes in order to get the best out of your work . Just think that you select your level in English and you are at a click 's distance from thousands of exam tasks . How handy is that ? Undoubtedly , you are never alone . Or at least , you can choose not to be . If you sign up for a workbook , you are eligible to feedback from other participants and that is how learning becomes collective ! Sharing is caring , is not it ? Write and Improve is more appealing , more interactive than any other learning platform , as it uses artificial intelligence in favour of education , which I think is a tremendous opportunity to challenge young learners to practice more and to get familiar with the exam tasks . 
I have a negative impression about children playing video games . Children are addicted to the games and cannot manage their time . I often see children who are playing games when they are at school to study , when they have dinner with their family and so on . They play games until midnight and they cannot get enough sleep , which may affect their health . They need to stare at the screen to play them , therefore their vision becomes worse . They play with their friends via video games and they do not communicate together in the real world . I 'm afraid that they ca not get communication skills through play . Some video games are so attractive , that children cannot stop playing them . They may continue to play them for a long time and have a harmful effect on their physical and mental health . If they manage their time and stop playing games in a short time , it does not do tremendous damage , but it is difficult , especially for immature people . Adults have to manage them beside their children . 
Dear editor , I would like to tell you and tell the magazine readers about my experience with the site Write & Improve . I am trying to use it every day , and it is helping me a lot to improve my English skills , especially my redaction capacity . It has many different lessons , and at several levels . The challenge is not easy , for me , it is difficult , learning English is hard , however the site is important because it does the text correction quickly , and we can see the writing problems . We review , fix the text , as many times as necessary , so it corrects it again . For me , using this site is very important because I am a researcher , and many articles that I want to publish need to be in English because I am a researcher , and many articles that I want to publish need to be in English , because thus I can achieve more readers . You should know how scientific journals are rigorous with English writing , I always need to ask for an English review before submitting an article , sometimes this is very expensive . So I need to be capable in the future . Finally , I guess that your readers can use this site in the same way . It is free , and it is always available for everybody . 
My English teacher is my sister and a big fan of Cambridge too . So , she recommended me this website and I decided to try it because I feel that my English writing level is not at the same as my English reading and listening levels . Because of that , I need to work hard . My first text had as a my opinion about zoos . As I 'm a biologist , I got excited to do that . So , I tried to use advanced words , like phrasal verbs , to reach a higher level . But , instead of , I realized that this website does not want to order anyone , it just wants to help and correct the main mistakes made by people . Weeks later , I was trying to get a habit into my routine of leaning English writing more on this website . Nowadays , once per week ( every Thursday morning ) , I write here and send it to my teacher to tell me what I need to change to write better . I recommend this website because it gives you the subtitles for you think about them and write . Before , I had difficulty to find an interesting subtitle to write about , and now , I have a website that does it for me ! 
In my opinion , television does both , entertain as well as educate . Meanwhile , everything has its specific pros and cons . A lot of scientific and educational channels are available for specific age groups , even for specific class students . Firstly , I would like to discuss some programmes and TV channels which provide study materials and classes , not only for remote areas , but also for metro cities . Just for those students who live in villages where skilled teachers are not available as much is needed , so in that case , students can easily learn with a good teacher by TV classes . 
The point is the " salary . " Doctors working in cities earn a lot , but those who work in rural areas earn less . This problem is more intricate than we think . You may think that all the doctors should make the same amount of salary . However , the salary depends on the amount of patients . City doctors work much harder than dispensary doctors due to the quantity of patients . This means city doctors earn much money than those who work in rural areas . Therefore , the point is not only the " salary , " but also " how busy their job is . " No one can control the population , thus the solution is not easy . One of my suggestions is the implementation of " doctor helicopters . " Huge hospitals are constructed near rural areas , substantial medical equipment is there , and adequate doctors work there . Those hospitals possess some helicopters for emergency patients living in rural areas . It might be a huge cost to keep helicopters , however the amount of patients in collective rural areas will have increased eventually . The salary would be pretty much the same . 
The future of travel is very near . Today 's transport system is very evolved . We have made giant steps since its birth . Now we have so many types of transport , such as a bus , car , plane and train . Every one of them is still evolving . For example , we are introducing the electric car , which can allow us to pollute less than before . There are also other different types of inventions . One of these could be the rise of the speed of some vehicles , like trains or cars too . Now we are thinking about another type of travel , space travel . It will be awesome ! Just think about what it would be like to travel in space ! We will be able to see planets and stars from a very close distance , take a selfie in front of some planets , make a video , etc ... Maybe in late 2100 , we could drive a flying car , like in futuristic movies . I hope to see this type of car in my future , because I really want to know how strange it is to drive in the air . This method can allow us to travel from country to country without taking a ship or plane . We could go from Europe to America driving our car . Awesome ! I really hope for a future like this . 
