I think it is wrong to keep animals in zoos . If we go to zoos , we can observe the lives of many species of animals live . It 's an amazing experience for young children and it may make them notice the importance of living animals . Some children may choose biology or veterinary medicine as their speciality in the future . But the lives in zoos are virtual in a way . Animals in zoos do not get food , water , and living places themselves . They eat and drink what they are given and sleep in concrete buildings . They do not search for their spouses and they do not take care of their children themselves . Humans make and take care of their family . Humans keep their health in zoos . It is not a natural way for animals . If we want to see a real life animal , we have to jump into nature , but it takes a lot of time and money . Otherwise , we can feel the essence of animal life in a movie or TV video program . I think it is a better way to know the real animal life than going to zoos . 
