The school of the future will be different compared to right now . Due to the quarantine situation , people have learned the benefits of the home office . Maybe , the school of the future will be more virtual , like online classes , and the students will take their exam online . However , I think this is not healthy . The role of school is much bigger than learning math or biology . School is like a microcosm of the world . In school , you coexist with different people , you learn how to be a citizen ( or it should be like this ) . The teaching methods are antiquated , they separate subjects . Maybe , in the future , the subjects can be more connected . If we can do this , as Edgar Morin dreamed , this can benefit all humankind . This way , morals and biology will be more connected , and people will realize their role in the environment . They will understand why t is wrong to degrade the environment . 
I think that zoos are good places to learn about animals for people , especially young children . There are two reasons below : Firstly , zoos offer opportunities to have contact with many kinds of animals . I believe that spending time with animals has a positive impact on children 's emotional development . If they did not exist , children living in a big city , such as Tokyo , New York , and so on , might not be able to see and have contact with any animals in their daily life , and it might give them a negative impact . Secondly , they have really important features , such as not only being a an entertainment for people but also contribution of preservation of species by providing information about the lives of several kinds of animals to some organizations . We should tell children how zoos help our society through those activities . For those reasons , zoos are good places for young children to learn about animals . 
Recently , I have discovered a great tool for learning writing in English without losing my time with useless ways for learning to write . This tool I found on a website for improving writing , such as an essay or leaflet and letter or whatever is relevant to writing skills . In terms of increasing your score in English exams , for example , the IELTS exam or TOEFL , specifically the writing section , because this is the most important skill to complete your learning of English . The tool helps you to create your sentence by using a strong word or rarely to make your sentence clear and a unique phrase , also how to put a figure mark and arrange the words into series of sentences and improve your spelling . In addition , there are some books and magazines about improving learning in English , for instance , completing the gaps in the story , matching words with their meaning , writing clarifications about bar graphs or pie charts , doing exercise by reading articles and answering questions . Furthermore , there are some applications on smartphones and you can practice learning English everywhere . The last advice I would like to share with you is every day choose any subject and read , write , listen , speak about it , and gradually , you will see the improvement in your language . 
I think the advantages are much more than the disadvantages of studying abroad . The advantage of studying abroad is that students can have many experiences in foreign countries which they cannot experience in their own country . They may feel a culture gap between these countries . They notice that there are various types of people and societies around the world . They will know the importance of diversity , and they will respect each other even if each of them has a different philosophy , religion , customs , and culture . Understanding each other is quite difficult , but young people can adapt to a specific situation more easily than old people do . I think the younger , the better . The disadvantage of studying abroad is the cost of it . They need much money for their studies and living there . In addition , they have to leave their home and live by themselves apart from their family members . It may cause some mental problems . 
I think that there are two advantages and one disadvantage for students studying abroad during high school or university . The first advantage is that you can see several perspectives by studying abroad instead of studying in your country at an early age . It would definitely broaden your insight and way of thinking . The second one is that having experiences might be beneficial for your career . For instance , if you wanted to tell your experiences to people who were eager to study abroad , it would be really helpful for you to recognize the difference between education in your country and the country where you are studying . Whereas , the only disadvantage of studying abroad is the security . If you live in a secure place such as Japan , something dangerous might happen during your stay abroad . So you should be more careful and try to be alert to protect yourself in another country . 
