The Write and Improve website has many fabulous features , although there is something that needs to be optimized . On the one hand , the thing that I like the most about this website is its ability to correct my mistakes . I received responses about my writing quickly after I hit the check button . Furthermore , I also know where I make mistakes and how to correct them . The topics of the website are very common and varied , which makes me practice my writing in many situations in life . Overall , my writing skills have improved a lot since I started to use Write and Improve . On the other hand , there is also something that I do not like about this website . Firstly , it needs to add more topics for IELTS writing . The second thing is reducing the price . I think it would be great if the administrators resolve these problems . In conclusion , I would definitely recommend my friends and classmates to use this website to improve their writing skills . 
