There are many entertainment shows on television . It can be good , but can also bring huge negative impacts . Despite television 's entertainment purpose , there are also communities of people who say that television could also be used for educational purposes . Is that a logical statement ? Well , since there are so many non -educational shows on television , it is hard to say that television can give education . I know that there are also many educational shows , but in my country , people prefer to watch entertaining but non -educational shows . Those entertainment shows can have a positive impact if the audiences can show their discretion . But mostly , entertainment shows have enormous negative impacts , especially on children and teenagers because they tend to follow what they have seen ; in this case , the actors of the entertainment shows . Besides that , there are also television shows which are produced for educational purposes . If most people show their discretion in filtering television shows , we can finally say that television entertains , but it can also educate . 
