The best holiday for me was a trip to Guam in Feburary , 2013 , our boss took all the employees there for the 10th anniversary , since the company was established in 2003 . Actually , I was a little nervous before leaving Japan because it was my first trip abroad . Moreover , I am afraid of heights so it was like a nightmare during the four -hour flight from Narita Airport to Guam . However , as soon as I got to the airport there , my best journey got started . Everything I could see there , such as the Pacific Ocean , beautiful palms , local food , clean and organized hotel rooms , and kind and nice people , was amazing . I went shopping to buy something for my family and friends , hung around the island , and went to some places where Japanese soldiers were killed during World War II . I prayed for them . Anyways , these experiences were so memorable for me , I stayed there for only three days though . If my English got much better , I would definitely like to visit Guam again and communicate with the local people . 
Controversy over incorporating volunteer work into the requirements of enrolling in high school has been continued over the past years . Some laud its benefits while others do not . In this essay , I intend to argue about the subject and infer the advantages and disadvantages . Due to the research recently done , teenagers who are used to working as volunteers in different fields have more responsibility to accept their role in society . As they devote some hours of the week to sacrificing stuff , therefore , their understanding of difficult situations is increased and they have more potential to make decisions in crises . On the other hand , some families prefer to enroll their teenagers in different classes and endow the most advantages from teenagers ' free time , they think young people should learn various skills to have more options in the future to choose from . By way of conclusion , I believe that , as the personality of teenagers can be entirely different , parents and school authorities should consider their behavior as the determining key to help them to improve themselves and volunteer work . although it is a sign of a sacrificed soul , it must not be a requirement for registration in high school . 
