There is no doubt , these days , there are a lot of doctors moving to impratent cities . The question is , what are the causes for doctors moving and how could we solve this problem ? In this essay , I will discuss the causes and solutions and draw my own opinion . In terms of reasons , moving to the towns has different causes . Firstly , the significant one is less income in the countryside compared with other places . Because people who live in those places do not have so much money , then they cannot pay all the bills of the doctor . A lot of them are very poor without any money . Secondly , in villages , they miss improveing machens machines which help doctors to do their job in a perfect way . However , there are some solutions which could help . Firstly , increase doctors who work in the countryside 's salary to encourage them to work in these places . Also , bring a teachenacal machens machines to their clinics . In conclusion , there are reasons for this problem and some people give solutions . Therefore , I believe that to encourage doctors to stay and work for ever in villages , we must give them financial offers , like a free home and facilities or a special promotion . 
