This report looks into Write and Improve my English . I have used this app for about 6 months . I really love it . When I write an essay on Write and Improve , I can check grammar , vocabulary and typos . Your progress will be checked and counted by a chat bot after you have sent your essay . On the interface , there is a task timer if you want to count the time and task help if you need help . Pros , you will receive a result immediately and you can edit , check again and again until you do not have any bugs . Cons , sometimes the results are not exact , because it is robot and they are programmed . I think if your level is A1 or A2 like me , you can consider using this application . My English has improved after using this application . I hope you will be a nagative England in the future and do not forget to recommend it to your friends . It is really useful . 
