Who does not want to have a healthy , intense life ? Each individual desires to have a long lifespan with a meaningful life . However , they do know how to adjust life to become a beautiful and meaningful one whether it is short or long , do not they ? Let discuss this scenario . The majority of people are nowadays choosing to go in ancient and identical pathway like others . They do not prefer to stand out , they sustain to imitate others in the way others live , others ' daily lives . They have no courage to upgrade their lives into a different story even if they possess enough ability , quality , to a better life . This makes their lives oddly calm , which means nothing special , outstanding , remarkable and extraordinary . This is always ugly for everyone else . For me , the way you spend life is really vital . It would possible to transfer your life into a better one if you actually know certain methods . In my opinion , I would say I like to spend life much more intensely by doing what I want to do , being myself with no struggles , controls , by anyone even if it is a bit challenging and problematic . I believe I can still pass those difficulties through by trying best , making progress and efforts , accumulating experience from mistakes , doing preparation for the process of being successful . Furthermore , life can be more intense and meaningful when you devote time to your close relatives , friends and your family who are always your side all the time , who encourage and motivate you to do the best thing . It is a really respectful and glorious thing in the world . 
I think an office which has a more open design is more effective for workers . In addition to that , it is safer for workers ' health to protect them from the virus under this urgent situation or under the coming new normal situation . I have three reasons to support my opinions of open office efficiency . Firstly , we do not have anxiety from concentrating too much on our tasks . I mean just looking up , we can change our mind if we are in a difficult situation . It is very effective to do the work as soon as possible . Secondly , it is easy to communicate with co -workers . We do not need to hesitate to ask questions or for advice . It is also effective for team building . Thirdly , it is useful to understand each other . We can know how co -workers work . Some people can steal the way which an active worker does , others can learn from negative examples . It is effective to make performance better . Furthermore , we have to protect from COVID -19 wherever we are from now on . With open offices , we can put spaces between workers . It will calm us down to work in the office . In conclusion , I think that open workstations are more effective . 
My town is in Romania . It is a small and peaceful town , it is old with an important historical wich , which makes it special and visited by many people from around the world . There are not too many landmarks because like I said , this town is not so extinse . Also , there are not too many shops or markets where you can choose to buy food , but there are enough . People are friendly and peaceful so the accommodation should not represent a problem . There are two big parks in the whole town , a few museums and multiple restaurants . About the night time entertainment , there are so many clubs and free concerts in different restaurants or in open -air concerts . 
The Future of Travel Currently , we have a lot of options to travel all around the world . Highly -developed transportation systems , such as an airplane , ferry and train , make it much easier to travel wherever we want to visit . However , the world is dramatically changing in 2020 because of the COVID -19 pandemic . Our activities are being strictly limited and we have to stay home and work remotely without commuting . I imagine that this situation will make our travel experiences change in the future . For instance , it would be difficult to get a visa to travel or stay in other countries , because each government hesitates to approve it to prevent spreading the virus . As a result , the value of traveling to another country would increase . However , our trip to the major sightseeing spots could be more comfortable and enjoyable because of the decrease in the crowds of people . Anyways , because of the coronavirus situation , the future of travel will change . 
