Hello . My name is Sam and I am 14 years old . I like playing games and all kids and people like it , but some parents do not want their children to play games . They think it is a bad habit for their child . Of course , they think it is not good for children , but sometimes kids or adults need to play games in their free time and parents need to watch their kids , like how many hours he/she plays games . Then it can be more helpful and if you ca not watch your kids or you do not have free time , then play with your children at the weekend . At the weekend , all jobs and schools are closed . At the weekend , you will play with or watch your kids . That 's the best way to control your children . In the 20th century , most kids like to play games in their free time . I think that 's alright and I also play games at the weekend , but if you want to play games , you have to play for 2 hours or 3 hours at the weekend . Then your parents think , their child is playing games for a little bit and you have to do your school homework and your parents will say their child plays games and also does homework . After that , they will be happy and are not gonna stop you playing games . That 's all for my suggestions . 
I think there are mostly three reasons why doctors are few in rural areas . Firstly , it is difficult to install enough equipment . I mean it 's difficult to distinguish which is installed or not because predicting the patients ' character is hard . Secondly , it is difficult to hire nurses and receptionists . There are not many expert nurses and receptionists in the countryside as well as doctors . Doctors cannot open their clinics alone . Thirdly , it is difficult to gather patients . Many are elderly people in the countryside . Since they tend to have chronic diseases , they go to a big hospital in the city center . That is why they have a family doctor there , it is hard to gather patients in a town clinic . Well , I think we can solve it now . We need to develop online medical care . Wherever the patients are , they can see a doctor in a city . It is beneficial for not only the elderly people in the countryside but also for everyone who is sick . These are all of my opinions . I hope everyone who needs medical care can get enough treatment . 
Hey , thank you for your help ! My aunt is going to deliver my keys to you , so you do not need to think about it ! Please , check and take my mail once a week , because I 'm waiting for an important letter . You will find my plants in my room , you must water them every day ! When I come back , we can go to a restaurant for dinner ! 
I have studied for a lot of years . I have studied in a school , in an Institute , in a University and in different skills throughout my life . I have known different teachers and I have had good teachers and bad teachers . I will never forget a special teacher and friend for me . His name was " Txus . " He was my Spanish language teacher in the Institute . He was a good teacher and finally he was my friend . He taught me a way of writing my texts that I had never known before . He was a friendly man with everybody . I would have liked to have had this teacher for other years , but they changed our teachers every two years . I remember a bad teacher . His name was " Carlos . " He was a friendly man , but he gave us a very difficult exam . I hated him , but I was lucky , because the next year , he was unemployed . I think that it is good to change teachers every year if it is possible , because I can meet different people and that is good to build my education , but I think it is a pity when I meet amazing people and I must change teachers every two years and maybe I have moodie and bad teachers . This situation is happening to our younger son now . 
In my opinion , volunteer work for high school students is a good idea for various reasons . First , volunteer work enables the students to learn something about the community they are part of . This can be related to health care , culture or education . For example , students who conduct volunteer work in a nursing home become familiar with how a part of their community spends their time each day . They will also learn more about the needs of the elderly people who live in care homes . For instance , inhabitants of care homes need social contact and students will enable them to have social contact . Secondly , in many wealthy countries , the government subsidises the school cost . So it is very important for students to have conduct volunteer work in attempt to endorse the community who finances their schools . Lastly , volunteer work enriches the social development of the student . Through volunteer work , students will come in contact with people who work in different fields or have different backgrounds . 
Hi there ! Thank you for looking after my house while I am on holiday , I really appreciate the effort ! Please be careful with the keys , feed the pets , check my inbox emails and write to me if there are any problems with these , and do not forget to water the plants . Thank you again for doing this ! Good luck ! Georgiana 
Music class brings students fun ! It also encourages them to take up music professionally in their future . In general , lots of experiences provide students a variety of thoughts , deep sentimentalism , and knowledge of human beings . Firstly , I think studying music is good for students , not bad at all , however , it does not mean forcing to take music class . This is simply because some of them might prefer art , drawing and painting rather than music . Back in the day , my high school had a mandatory class which you could choose . You could select one from art , music and DT . I strongly recommend the students have an experience , but it should be the class which they prefer . Secondly , I would like to talk about an " experience . " When I was a high school student , I did not fancy any of them , thus I took a music class . The class offered me to sing Beethoven No.9 in German . It seemed to be amazingly impossible , however , we pronounced German like Japanese " Katakana " and accomplished it . This experience reminds me of a satisfactory accomplishment . I can still sing it in German . I feel experience makes your life confidence . Therefore , I do not think all students should have to study music , but I think they need to get some experience in their youthful days . 
The best holiday I went on was a camping tour around the US national parks . It was 25 years ago , but I can still remember every scene of this tour . This tour lasted two weeks and its members came from several countries , such as England , Germany , France and Japan . I was the only Japanese and the others came from Europe . We had to talk to each other in English and it was a hard time for me , but I did it . We visited several national parks in the western part of the United States . We hiked in the mountains , rode on horses and learned about nature and wild animals at the visitors ' centers . We stayed at the campsites and cooked ourselves . Each of us cooked their country 's food and served it to everyone . We really enjoyed the international foods and cultures during the tour . It was an amazing and interesting experience for me . I think this holiday made me focus on foreign people and gave me the opportunity to join volunteer work in foreign countries . 
Learning a language can prove to be a very useful thing to do . Why do I think so ? It 's pretty obvious , the more languages we know , the easier it becomes for us to communicate with large communities of people around the entire world . But what if I do not want any new friends ? Is there any other reason why I should be eager to even start learning some brand new foreign language ? If you ask me , yes , there are a bunch of other reasons to consider starting this amazing journey . For example , you get exposed to a completely new culture and oftentimes you fall in love with it . It should not be that hard to conclude on your own , but because this argument is so obvious , a lot of people tend to avoid it whenever they encounter this subject of learning a new language . Also , being a language user can be extremely helpful when you decide that you 'd like to spend your holidays abroad , because let 's not deceive ourselves , not everybody in the country that you want to visit speaks English . They inhabit some countries where various languages are spoken , so essentially , they do not see any need to study some other language . 
I believe that I have two favourite seasons of the year . On the one hand , it is Spring , because the weather is cold and hot at the same time , so you can wear light clothes and cold clothes . In Spring , you do not sweat because it 's not very hot and it is windy . Moreover , I was born in March and in this month , the season is Winter and Spring , so I celebrate my birthday in these two seasons . On the other hand , I like Winter too , because I celebrate Christmas with my family . In Winter , I am fond of the snow , because I find it fantastic , amazing and unbelievable . I also love Winter , because it 's the birthday of my best friend Cruz and I celebrate it with him . I do not really like Summer because the weather is too hot for me . 
Many people contend that exercising contributes to a healthy lifestyle . Still , very few of them are actually living according to these standards , especially students . Schools are questioning whether to force their pupils to participate in sports at least three times a week . However , is forcing children to exercise really a way to improve their lifestyles ? Obviously , a daily schedule involving exercising should rather be considered as habitual . Despite this fact , it should not be forced upon students by their school to implement exercising in their schedules . This , because every individual has individual needs and , therefore , it could provide complications for people who are not made to exercise so many times a week . They might suffer from health problems or are sensitive to injuries . While there is nothing wrong with encouraging pupils to live a healthy lifestyle , it could induce major health problems for those who are not strong enough to exercise at least three times a week . Secondly , forcing people to execute something they might not be interested in , has proven to be ineffective throughout history . When someone is forced to perform all the enjoyment gets taken out of the particular activity . This might not need to be a problem when they are still in school , while there is no other choice but to obey . But it could lead to a life -long negative association with certain sports , which could prevent them from seeking enjoyment in exercising ever again . Automatically , this leads to a preposterous effect compared to the initial aspiration . I can honestly say that forcing pupils to exercise is not the right way to achieve the aim of them living a healthy lifestyle . This could be accomplished in various ways , such as motivating them to reach a personally set target . Surely , schools need to accept that not everyone is interested in accomplishing a healthy lifestyle by performing physical exercise . So as long as " forcing " is not altered into " motivating " schools should execute absolutely nothing . 
Hello . My name is Sam and I am 14 years old . At my age , I have seen many teachers in my life . Some people say having a different teacher is good , but I think that it is not good , because in your life you may have a lot of teachers and they have their hobby . One teacher teaches as a job , but another teacher teaches as their hobby . Those 2 teachers are different . The first teacher teaches us as a hobby and that teacher is kinder and more polite to the children and the children will also like them . The second teacher is a teacher who teaches us as a job and that teacher is also kind , but some are polite and some are not polite . That is all I think and I have said that those 2 different teachers will be true or not . I do not know , because that 's my thinking and reasons . 
There is no doubt these days , the media is an important tool for governments , TV is the most important kind of media . The question is , could television educate or just entertain ? I will discuss both views and draw my own opinion . In terms of the negative side , people say television is just for entertainment . The main reason they give is TV could waste time for everyone . even if they are engoing through it . To illustrate that , usually the media teaches bad habits , like drinking alcohol , smoking or taking drugs . In other words , it shows criminals as good people . However , other people against it are optimistic about TV . Like everything , it has advantages and disadvantages . Firstly , we could get knowledge from channels , like science , math and politics . Secondly , it shows us the environment everywhere around the world , also under the sea . Lastly , it gives a chance for everybody to study and learn new things , like languages or religion . In conclusion , some people say we can learn a lot of new things from the media , but others are against it . Therefore , I believe that media and television have a really important position and influence people 's beliefs . 
In my opinion , both of these choices have their positive and negative aspects . Since I have experienced both situations , I can say that living away from my family for a while has developed my personality and it was a valuable experience for me . When I was a student in high school , I lived with my family . At that time , I was not worried about my food or my expenses at all , I knew that when I arrived home , everything was ready for me . The only thing which was expected for me was only studying . Furthermore , when I got sick , my parents were taking care of me , and I healed very soon . But when I decided to get out of my comfort zone and choose to live away from my family , I knew that it would be an awkward situation but it would help me to become independent . I have lived 6 years away from my family , and I have learned to manage my expenses and take care of my health and build a strong personality without my parents ' help . However , I am not suggesting this way to all students because it depends on the person 's personality and characteristics . In conclusion , may the experience of living alone when studying at university is hard , but I think it has this ability to pull out one person 's ability and is helpful to be a more independent and responsible person . 
This topic is very interesting nowadays . Why the villages and rural areas are so lacking in more services and , moreover , the quality of them . In my opinion , this problem is popular in many countries . Village citizens usually complain about the long hours they spend when they travel to the main cities to do some work , especially in treatment or government services , that is what the people face living in rural areas . In terms of solutions , there are many ways to repair this obstacle . One of these methods is creating a project to build a healthcare center in each village with a high level of quality and services and provide some offers for the doctors who accept the vacancy to work in rural areas , such as a high salary , strong health insurance , registration in school for their kids and housing without charge . I think giving some incentives for doctors to leave their home and work in areas with low living potential is considered the right way to attract them to serve those people living there and solve the problem . 
My home town is João Pessoa , Paraiba 's capital . There are many shopping centres , but the most important are the Mangabeira and Manaira shopping centres ! There are also many hotels on the beach for your accommodation , but they are very expensive , so if you want to visit my home town , bring a lot of money with you ! My favourite museum is the Science Station , and it 's an important landmark in the city ! On the other hand , if you want some night -time entertainment , I recommend you visit the Empório Café , it 's a nightclub with good drinks and karaoke ! I would like you to visit our parks too ! My favourite park is the lagoon park , there are many tourists and citizens who go walking there , playing games and taking photos ! I hope that you enjoy visiting my home town . Please , you can call me if you need something ! 
Hello teacher , I would like to study anatomy , because my dream is to be a doctor ! I usually talk to doctors and they always say that anatomy is very important to be a good doctor ! I want to do an anatomy course as a vacation activity in the summer . Can you help me to find this course , please ? 
I have been a student and I know that , in that period , you do not think only about studying , but you think about hanging out with your friends , having a good time . So it 's an age when you ca not appreciate the importance of studies , the importance of school , so it 's not simple at all to be a teacher . For this reason , in my opinion , it is good for the students to have new teachers each year because , in this way , they can be more stimulated , they can learn several things , they can have a different view of the life from each teachers and they can also get their experience and all these things could make them better people . You have to consider that usually the students do not know what they want , so having different types of teachers could help them to find their road , instead of a single teacher , probably if you imagine it , in a long time , it could get boring . 
When I stay at home there are several things that I can do , but probably my favorite indoor activity is to do logical tests . I love it because each time you do it , you have to find the solution to a logical problem . Generally a logical problem is a tricky problem and I like hard problems because if I have to solve a simple problem it gets boring . Yesterday I did one of these logical tests and I thought about it for almost the whole day and , at the end , I found the solution , so I was so happy . 
In my opinion , I think students benefit more from having new teachers each year . Firstly , the students will have a lot of opportunities to learn with other ways of teaching . They also have many new experiences through many ways of teaching . Secondly , the students will be boler to interact with new teachers each year . Thirdly , each teacher will have their own experience talking with the students . Thereby , the students will understand their teacher . Fourthly , each teacher also has their own methods to study , so they can share them with students . Fifthly , if the students learn with a new teacher each year , they will adapt quickly to a new study environment . So it improves the adaptive skills of students . Finally , each teacher will have a sight to students , many teachers will have a comprehensive sight to assess students . From that , they will give proper methods and advice to their students . I hope the students would try to learn with a new teacher each year . 
I strongly believe having new teachers each year is better than the same teacher for several years . I will prove it with 4 reasons below : The first , if we have a new teacher each year , we can compare two teachers between each other regarding their teaching method and choose the appropriate method yourself . The second , variety method and teacher method and teacher you will get a lot experience from them . The third , you will have more memories during this time and you will have open relationships . Finally , each teacher has characteristics , this is key for you . This is the first big learn before you go to work . You experience exprience other genitive you know what to do when you meet the same people . You learn the way to resolve a problem , a trouble and fight in a small social . By the way , you could always prepare a strong mind and knowledge every time and every day . 
I think my favourite season of the year is spring . I like this season because it 's the season that brings life back to all nature . It 's a season that is not so cold and it 's not so hot , it 's just the perfect weather . I like to see the trees coming back to life , I like to hear the birds singing . What I want to do in this season is to go and visit different places and meet new people . The best thing about this season is the fact that it brings back the power of the sun , it brings everything back to life . I would like next spring to go and visit Deva with my family , Deva is a really great city . I remember that I saw it last autumn and it was great . The only problem is that I have to take the airplane to Timisoara and then rent a car so I can go to Deva , and that is a problem . 
We know that doctors want to get a lot of money , if they can go to big cities , with a lot of opportunities , they will go . However , the small cities and rural areas need doctors , they do not have enough doctors . I suggest that the government should make a program to give reasons to the doctors to go to these places . For instance , an additional salary or some kind of advantage , like a free house to live in , or a yearly bonus in money . I guess that when the doctor goes to a small city or to a rural area , in a short time , he will be so happy with the value the population gives to him , he is going to be interested in continuing in these places . Of course , doctors can want to receive money , but they need to understand that this kind of profession is so important for society , they must consider some things behind the cash . 
Dear Cristina , How are you feeling now ? I heard about your accident yesterday and it was too late to visit you . When I heard the news I was really anxious for you . Are you OK now ? Are you seriously injured ? What can I help you with ? Do you need something ? Please be rest assured that while you recover , I am going to write down the lessons for you . After two weeks , you can go back to school , if you are not able to keep up with the pace , I 'm sure I will show detail for you . So do not worry , Cristina . The hospital name is Hong Ngoc International , right ? I am going to visit you at 4 o 'clock in the afternoon . See you soon . Your friend , Nguyen Nguyen 
I like playing video games , but I do not have enough time . My children like playing video games a lot . I think that playing video games has good things and bad things . Video games are good because they can teach us a lot of things . There are a lot of types of video games . Some are strategic video games , so we should use our brain to win a competition . Other types of video games are sports games . My younger son knows all the countries with their flags with he is only 11 years old . He sees this flags in a football video game . Which is the problem with video games ? In my opinion , a lot of children spend many hours sitting in front of a TV playing video games . Some have problems to talk with people , to have friends and they are often shy . We should put a limit on the use of video games . My children play one hour in the summer season because they do not go to school . They only play at the weekend during the course period . 
I agree with the people that claim the idea that it is a good clue for students to have the same teacher for several years . The first argument I am bringing to the idea that I support is represented by the fact that the teacher that teaches a subject in the same class for several years gets to know his pupils ' knowledge of what he teaches , and this skill is gained over time . Over the teacher gets to interact with his students , over the teacher gets to interact with his students , over the the teacher gives his students several projects , tests , homework to complete . The second argument that I am bringing to support my clue consists in the fact that the teacher that teaches for several years gets to know the level of the class that he is teaching so he will be able to teach his pupils lessons that they do not understand or know . He will be able to interact more easily with them and give them tasks that they are going to understand and improve their schooling and societal behaviour compared to a teacher that teaches the pupils for the first time that year . To conclude , I would like to admit that there is more privilege in a teacher who teaches several years a class than a teacher that teaches for a year . 
I like exercising but unfortunately I ca not do it very often because I 'm busy with my job . Generally I 'm able to do it once per week and I prefer exercising outside and not in the gym because in this way you can stay more in contact with nature . Regarding the kinds of activities I like are playing football and I like swimming . 
Hi Charlie , I was thinking about you a few days ago and now I would like to tell you about my favourite film . It is the " Back to the future " series where the main role is played by Michael J . Fox . The first part of the series was released around 1980 and it was a big success all around the world . Generally , the story of the film talks about time travelling . Doctor Emmet Brown discovers a machine which allows him to travel in time . From that , a movie starts and , after that , we have a great story to watch . The series has three parts and each of them is placed in different times . You should see this movie because , beside a great plot , you can , while watching , have a laugh or be scared . 
In my free time , I usually play football with my friends . Typically , I do it once a week . Actually , I wish I could do it every day , but I 'm often busy with my work . I like playing football because it is a sport where the whole team fights for the same objective and that is trying to score more points than the other team . The last time I played football was a week ago , I played a match with my colleagues at work and at the end , after a hard match , my team was able to win . 
I have recently discovered a new tool to improve English writing : Write and Improve . It 's an app by Cambridge University where you can find perfect essay indications to write really good texts . You only have to log on , enter the workbooks and choose the essay you prefer . I think it is helpful because it corrects your mistakes and says what you have to improve . Moreover , you can see your writing level on the top right , and if you get better at this topic , the level goes up . Although this will help you , there are some things that I would like to change : First , it could have a vocabulary book or something similar for weak English students who want to do Cambridge exams , then essay models , to know how to do more or less in your texts , and finally , more help with corrections . However , since I have known this app , I have improved much more my English level and it is OK . In conclusion , I recommend it to all English learners because it is a useful tool to develop new abilities in essays and writings . 
I agree with the statement above . In my opinion , health is more important than wealth . Wealth could help you very much to be healthy , but if you have a very serious illness , wealth does not have any worth . Like I said , if you are rich , you could buy good medicines , you could go to a private hospital with the best specialists , you could eat only the best quality food and all of that could allow you to live in health and maybe longer . But in my opinion , if you do not have money , you could also live long in good shape . You have to care about your diet and , generally , about your shape . Do not drink , do not smoke and stuff like that . The main problem is when you have a lot of money , but you are ill and doctors do not give you too many years of life , Then your wealth is worth nothing for you . 
