Office design Nowadays , due to the lively changes in the office working environment , more and more employers get to crowd all their employees into a large room and their activity is supposed to be accomplished due to very efficient teamwork . I believe that all this is nonsense , that this is just a myth that would cover the money that the employer is making by renting a much cheaper space that will maximize the company 's earning . I truly believe that the employees are in their right to benefit from a personal workplace that will provide them with a quiet and private work experience that will allow them to focus better and be even more productive . Employers should take notice of the fact that a shared workplace can not be properly aired and so respiratorical issues appear . If the place they work in was not jeopardizing their health , the employees would work longer and it will be beneficial in the long run for the company they work for . Moreover , working separately will prevent diseases from being spread , as the workers will be less in contact with each other , especially during the cold season when the flu is viral . The fewer people breathe the same air , the better . In addition , claustrophobic people will feel safer and their affection will not encounter with their work . It is proven that a better organisation brings a consistent increase in productivity . To sum up , each and every employee should be provided with his own place in order to focus on his work and to not jeopardize his health and the others ' . 
Hello Billal , I wish you good health . I am writing to you about my last school trip . We went to Palum Island , it is in the west , in the ocean . We were sailing for two weeks , and the captain was Suaud . On the fourth day we arrived at the island and tied up our ship on the coast . Life on it was peaceful and quiet , nothing brought any noise , except the waves . There were different kinds of animals : I saw monkeys , wild cows , sheep , horses and so many birds . I had a really fantastic time . I learnt important things , the greatest one was how to meditate to clear my head and think about myself . It is the best chance , if you want to organize yourself , and , if I were you , I would take this experience to be alone for a while and count trees , and watch the waves moving every six hours . 
There is no doubt these days that university students need to decide where they should live . The question is , what is the best choice for them ? Is it away from their home or with their family ? In this essay , I am going to discuss both views and draw my own opinion . In terms of theadvantages of living away from their home . The main reason they give is they need to develop independence , which is really important to live life . To illustrate that , moving will teach them how be responsible , do everything by themselves . In other words , they have to take their responsibilities without any help . On the opposite side , others said being at home with parents is useful for students at university . Firstly , at this early age of their life , they need support and courage from family , baccalaureate is tough , hared without family support , students will maybe fail . Secondly , improving social skills through contacting with family members at home . In conclusion , people have different ideas for the students ' living . Therefore , I believe that the best choice for students during university days if they are studying in the city where their family lives , it is with family where they will find support and do not need to take significant responsibilities . 
As you know , television entertains us , but can it also educate us ? Absolutely , yes . I would like to show you why and how it educates us with three reasons . The first reason is that there are a lot of broadcasters which offer several kinds of educational programs . Some are for kids , some are for teenagers , and the others are for adults . We can learn a lot of things from these programs . The second is that it is a good opportunity for us to watch TV programs in order to cultivate our media literacy . Unfortunately , you can find that there are horrible shows that are completely useless for the education of your kids . However , you and your kids could learn which programs are good or bad by choosing them by yourselves . The third reason why and how television educates us is that watching TV shows really help you learn languages . For those reasons , I think that television can educate us . 
Zoo are where animals from around the world are kept to display to people . Animals are shown in a cage which is built imitating the normal habitat of those animals to reduce their stress , however , it cannot entirely replace a real habitat in nature . In my opinion , people should not study about animals kept in zoos for these reasons . First , when animals are raised in zoos , they change their behaviour to adjust to the new environment . They would normally hunt their preys or hide themselves in nature , but zoos provide them enough food and safe places to live in comfort . For example , penguins are waiting to be fed by a zookeeper , and tigers do not hunt anymore . Moreover , zoos divide each animal separately depending on its species . Therefore , there is no interaction between different species . In nature , animals from each species would form a food chain to control each other 's population , which cannot be formed in a zoo environment . In conclusion , it is the best to have animals roaming free in nature . A zoo is not a proper place for learning about animals . 
Studying abroad has both good and bad points . Many students choose their school in a foreign country to get more opportunities to improve their knowledge and language . Furthermore , students who have graduated from high school tend to be accepted into that country 's university more . They can adapt to their new environment and friends easier than students who never studied abroad . On the other hand , studying abroad requires more budget for living and school expenses , even if students get a scholarship . Moreover , some universities do not accept a foreign student in the same course as its country 's local students because of the language barrier . So , when students come back to their home country , some of them do not meet the job 's knowledge requirement or have a lack of experience in working in a local company . Therefore , every student should think carefully before they apply to a university abroad so that they will get more good experiences than a disadvantage . 
Travelling in the future might be totally different from travelling now . We recently use virtual reality . Especially in this COVID -19 situation , most of us use web conference systems both our jobs and in private . We do not have to travel to meet with somebody . We can connect with somebody online . We can visit anywhere all over the world in virtual reality systems with specific goggles . Someone might say that we cannot taste local foods unless we go there . We can not snooze the smell of something . We cannot feel the temperature and humidity in some places . But digital technology will improve rapidly . I believe we can get these feelings via the internet and we can have magnificent experiences using virtual reality as we travel there . This story seems to be a dream . But we did not know about the COVID -19 situation one year ago . We do not know how the world will change in the future and we look forward to the unbelievable travel experiences . 
Volunteer work is something that is of great importance for our community as we could not accomplish many aims without it . Therefore , I personally rate the idea of requiring a specific amount of volunteer work in order to graduate really exquisitely . Of course , you need to spend some time on those activities , but every student can help our community with volunteering and meanwhile they do good , which should make them feel good as well . Working voluntarily is also helpful for forming your character : It makes you more confident and reliable after you were given such great responsibilities . If you are used to working with volunteers , you know that it is not always easy and sometimes devastating . Therefore , gaining those experiences should prepare college students for later complications in their work life . Another very important aspect are universities . They often want to know your extracurricular activities as they are often required for scholarships . Therefore , pupils are automatically given a better chance of achieving them . In conclusion , it is very honorable to do volunteer work and , as many teenagers spend a lot of time inside , it would not hurt them at all to do so . 
