There is no excuse about how exercise is important to our lives . The human body needs energy and enough activity to burn it to maintain a normal physiology . However , exercise is not the most important thing for our health . In fact , a human needs the 4 most important factors to survive , that are food , shelter , clothes and medication . Also , our wellness is varied due to the differences in these factors . We need food and water to build up energy and prevent disease . Many kinds of food are considered as a medicine to reduce inflammation or improve immunity . There is a trend , nowadays , of eating ' clean food ' , believed to prevent disease , as well as a trend of daily exercise . Some food is put into the ' junk food ' category , which means it damages the health of the person who consumes it . In conclusion , exercise is important to our health , but there are many things that are more important than that . Therefore , we need to focus not only on exercising , but also on other things to maintain our good health too . 
