Living healthily requires sacrifices , determination and concentration . From the outside , it could seem the simplest thing in the world , but from the inside , the truth comes out . Healthy habits are very difficult to follow and acquire . Our society tells us we should eat vegetables and fruits from biological cultures , but then we see on TV snacks and junk food which are extremely cheaper and more inviting . Although exercise is certainly fundamental for healthy living , I strongly believe that eating good products is what really makes the difference . In order to satisfy the always increasing food request , vegetables , fruits and animals are bombarded with chemical products , hormones and anthycorps , to make them grow more quickly . This completely destroys our organism and our digestive system . In addition to that , our lives have become more sedentary , so we do not burn all the calories we eat , and more stressful , so we eat more to find consolation in food . 
