Two people can communicate with each other only if they speak a common language . Knowing more than one language is always a benefit . This essay concludes some of my points of view . In addition to everyone 's first language , it is also important to learn a foreign one , because it has become increasingly necessary and has advantages . Firstly , having the same language allows two different people to get to know each other by chatting . You are able to make friends with everybody from your country , where all the people understand perfectly what you say . But the situation will be changed if you go aboard without learning the foreign language . In that case , you will have difficulty in communicating with them , as well as them with you . Thanks to the developments of trains and airplanes , everybody can travel far away from where they live . So , in order to be in contact with someone who comes from a different place , the knowledge of that person 's language is essential . Well , learning a second language enables you to travel to another nation without communication problems , chat and discuss with a foreigner . To sum up , in my personal opinion , it is more and more necessary for people to know at least a second language . Nowadays , we travel more often than in the past . For that reason , we are usually in contact with people with different cultures . So , studying a foreign way of speaking is very important . 
Nowadays , it is undeniable that volunteer work is a useful action at the same time as helpful work . Thousands of people need volunteers ' hands . Firstly , it is true students must learn about great actions , since they prepare them for real life and they learn to be concerned for poor people , furthermore , ecosystems and the country 's economy . Secondly , as a con , for many years , university access has been truncated by tough exams . Adding a new activity , such as volunteer work , knowing high school learners have to prepare their future studying very hard , it could be very stressful for them to pass the year through a complementary activity . Finally , volunteer work is for qualified people in many subjects and , moreover , for people who are going to do their best . I genuinely think that only volunteer people are the people who can do those activities , so it is terrific to include them in school program , moreover it must be optional , to not stress busy students . 
