Well , the advantages are that in other countries there are more opportunities than in poor countries . Also , there are more choices for careers and it is easier to be recognised or have a better job . But the disadvantages are that you 're far from your family , and also the language , because the most important universities are in English or Chinese . Also , you do not know very many people abroad . In conclusion , it is a good idea to study abroad , but it depends on each family . If you are studying very much and you want to have a go at a good career , it is an option to study abroad , but if you want to have an easy career , you can study at a local university . Also , it depends on the economic situation , because studying abroad is so expensive . But if you are intelligent and you do not have very much money , some universities have options of big discounts if you 're intelligent . 
Sport is very important exercise for our health . Doing exercise , especially in the morning , has a huge benefit for our moral , as well as mood and spirit . Personally , I prefer doing jogging . This old sport is easy and helpful . We can do it either in cities or in gardens . As I live near the sweet beaches , what I like so much is obviously swimming , as well as surfing . These two sports have many advantages and have numerous good effects on our health . We can do them regularly and easily , either during spring or summer . Besides sport , I continue to believe that there are many other activities that we can do , like yoga and meditation . These two Asian disciplines are widely practiced , not only in India , but also in other countries around the world . To summarize my opinion , I ’m convinced that sport is the main activity that has a good and deep impact on our health and consequently on our heart . 
I went to see the white cliffs of Dover . I had not been there for years , and for some reason I felt like I had to see them again . I just did some walking along the coast and breathed fresh sea air . I enjoyed the trip very much , it was interesting and quite challenging for my legs ; long walks are difficult for me as I get older and my cardio is not the same anymore . I try my best , but still struggle , even small breaks did not help me , and I was so tired by the end of the day . 
Travelling as we know it and did it for decades will come to an end . Due to the ongoing discussion about the environmental costs of easy travelling , things have started to change . In the future , fewer people will use cheap flights for unnecessary weekend trips to sunny spots . More and more people will become conscious and will try to avoid putting stress on the environment when starting over for holidays . So , having fun in the neighbourhood , for example by doing bicycle tours or walking and hiking , will see a renaissance . This will also strengthen the rural economy , so that money could be spent on developing local infrastructures and local offers . This will lead to a broader variety of possibilities . In the end , lots of people will find options for their vacation nearby . Spending gallons of fuel and polluting the sky and environment to allow people to have weekends in Spain for less than 30 € will soon be a thing of the past . So I hope . 
In high schools , there are a lot of different groups who do some voluntary projects . There may be assamble who organizes prom , another group makes different merch with the high school logo and another grows plants and flowers in the school garden . And there are always students who are in thousands of communities and other students are in none . But what if joining a voluntary team was mandatory ? On the one hand , by doing some work high school students learn a lot of skills they will need later in their adult life . Skills like working in a team or carrying responsibility are very important regardless of where you are going to work later . In addition , high schools also get profit from such work , because students mostly know better what other students need and how to make their school day better . On the other hand , there are students who are already in sports clubs or music schools . And they maybe do not have time for any voluntary work at high school , so it can get very difficult for them to manage everything and to do homework too . In summary , I think that obligatory work for high schools is a good thing if it does not need too much time and you still have a choice about what kind of work you would like to do . 
In fact , video games are very popular nowadays with children . Recently , technology has made it possible for children to have fun in the comfort of their homes , compared to the times when children very often needed to be taken outdoors to have entertainment , and that 's very good . However , there are indeed some positive and negative effects . The positive effects of video games on children is that children can have more fun at home - playing and expressing themselves through games . In addition , parents of children will have the chance to do home activities while the children are busy playing video games . In spite of that , video games ' contents can be very aggressive nowadays , and not appropriate for young children who are under 18 years old , because this will pose a negative impact on the child 's personality , because they are at an age when they are not allowed to view violent or aggressive content , even when they are on the Internet . However , parents can still have control over what their children are viewing , whether on television or the Internet or a video game . And apparently , computer devices now have parental control settings , where parents can restrict or trace their children 's activity online . With the appearance of some video games that contain violent scenes , children are becoming more violence -loving . And that is what explains the violence among school children recently , such as the violence we see in some shooting and murder games . Although these games are targeted at teenagers and adults , young children are increasingly wanting to play such games , because they are spread among their older siblings . I think parents need to be aware of the good types of video games to buy for their children and make sure these games do not contain violence or are targeted to the age of their children . 
