At my university , there are many students who live in a student house . But , there are also students who have preferred for different reasons to stay at their parents home . In my opinion , it is better for students to live in a student house for different reasons . In this essay , I will entail why I believe that a student house is a better choice than staying with your parents . Firstly , living on your own is better than living with your parents during your university time because students who live alone develop skills that they need for their foreseeable future . Living alone means that your have to cook yourself . Furthermore , living alone makes you notified what it means to live alone . You are also learning to take proper decisions , because you are aware of your responsibility . Therefore , you ponder before making paramount decisions . However , there are many aspects which impede students to live alone during their studies . The livelihood is in many western countries increasing considerably . Therefore , many students can afford to live in a student house . Furthermore , many universities are established in cities where the house supply is dramatically low . As a ramification , many students cannot find a student house and are coerced to stay with their parents . 
