I think television can not only entertain , but also educate . There are many TV programs all over the world . Some of them are dramas , movies , music , animation and so on . Those are entertainment . We can enjoy these programs with our family or friends . But there are other TV programs , such as news , documentaries and so on . These programs can teach us new knowledge and information . There are also online educational programs on TV . We can learn many things from TV programs . If we join an online university program , we can get the grade for university graduation . Recently , we can communicate with other people or organizations on TV , because we have high level technology for interactive communication . We can get direct education from school using this technology . I imagine that TV may have a big capacity to change our lives totally in the future . 
It could be seen that health and wealth are two of the most important things in our lives . Nevertheless , to my mind , there is not a more valuable thing than health . Even being rich is not as meaningful as being healthy . We need to always take care of our health . When we are healthy , we can do almost everything . The whole world is open to us . For that reason , when we are healthy , we can become rich people . Unfortunately , when we are rich , we have no certainty that we will be healthy our whole life . Actually , many people think that when they have a lot of money , they are protected from everything . However , they forget that the best things in life are worthless and they ca not buy them . I 'm aware that money can help in a healthy lifestyle , however there are many opportunities to take care of our health . All of these are dependent on our behavior and attitude . We should remember that we have only one health and we should care about it . Because of all of that , I honestly believe that there is no more important thing than our health . 
There are two sides about zoos , there is a good side and there is a bad side . When you think about the children , the families and the students that go every day to the zoo , they are learning about animals , they are starting to be interested in animals and the zoo is an opportunity to study many animals too . Moreover , in the zoo there are several species close to extinction , like pandas for instance . On the other hand , many people think that a zoo is like a prison for the animals and this is cruel . In my opinion , there are zoos and zoos . Many are reasonable for the animals , quite comfortable , with spaces similar to in nature . However , many are like terrible prisons , bad places where the animals suffer a lot . So I guess that a zoo is good for society and for the animals , but the zoos need to be verified if the conditions are good for the animals . 
These last years , and especially this year with the Coronavirus pandemic , we have seen the following problem : A majority of medical doctors want to work in cities where they will make a lot of money while there are not enough doctors in many rural areas . Thus one wonders , what are the reasons for this problem ? Firstly , a majority of medical doctors want to work in cities because they have their friends near them and they can do a lot of activities . In brief , the major advantage is human contact . Secondly , the wages are more attractive in cities than in rural areas . So now , we have identified the reasons for this problem , what could we do ? Firstly , we could increase the salary of medical doctors who accept to work in rural areas . We could also regroup all medical doctors who work in rural areas in the same competitiveness hub . 
