There no doubt that these days writing is becoming very popular . However , the question is , is it important to learn writing ? It is considerably controversial today . Nowadays , learning with technology is much easier than it was . There are many websites which provide many materials for learning , for example , some people can improve their writing skills with some online courses . From my experience , to improve my writing skills , I am using the Write & Improve website to practise writing in English . The Write & Improve website is a great innovation to help people who are not native speakers of English to learn to be able to write in English at a high level . This website has a perfect technique to correct the errors and provide some comments on the writing , to help the learners to know their mistakes and try to fix them . Finally , I recommend all people who need to enhance their writing skills to use the Write & Improve website . 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? This question is what some teachers may think . Well , of course , both of them have advantages and disadvantages . Of course , I think that idea is not correct . We need libraries , so that we can improve ourselves and it is beneficial for our health . Well firstly , the welfare of using computers and tablets . Using the internet is the easiest way to search . And it is also very agile ! But if you depend on it too much , you will get addicted to it . And if you get addicted to the internet , it is very difficult to get back to normal . Looking at the screen can also very bad for your eyes ! And if you look at the screen too much , it will affect your health . Secondly , the advantages of using books . Using books may be slow and hard to find , but it is the best way to learn ! You can improve your reading skills and your understanding skills . And of course , your eyes wo not get as bad as using computers or tablets . 
