Going to university is a big new step in everyone ´s life . And a lot of freshman students think that they are only students when they move out of their parents ´ house . But is it really so ? I think that nowadays it is common for young people to rent their own flat or room when they begin their education in university . And this often has a good reason : Not every city has universities and not every university has the same directions . For example , if you want to study biotechnology , you will have to go to a university which offers suitable courses . And if this university is in another city , your best option is to move to this place . Now , with mobility being more convenient , it is easier to get to another city and it is getting normal for everyone to move out to study . But on the other hand , if you have less than an hour to your study place by train or bus from your parents ´ house , I do not think that it is necessary for you to change your flat . Staying at your parents ´place , you can save a lot of money and it is very convenient to have your mum who does your laundry and cooks food for you . In summary , I think that you do not have to move out without good reasons , because not through changing your flat , you will become a real student . 
There is no doubt that these days all teachers have a positive effect in education and teaching students , but it is difficult to choose one answer to this question . However , the question is , is changing the teachers every year a good choice for students ? Actually , my personal opinion is if the students need a teacher to keep teaching them , that means they prefer to study with the teachers who they already know . Also , it depends on the students if they do not want the same teacher and they want to study with another teacher . Sometimes , if the teachers change every year , that makes the students worry about the subject and teacher and his / her character . That maybe will affect their understanding and their scores . As we can see , it is difficult to choose one answer depending on just one opinion . Also , we cannot deny the benefits of changing teachers every year , because definitely , every teacher has a different way to teach his students . 
Recently , surfing the Internet , I discovered Write and Improve , which is an online platform to improve English writing . Write and Improve is a very useful tool , because it offers the possibility to practise English for free . It is very inclusive because every English learner can use it , no matter what their level . There are exercises both for those who are beginning and for those who already speak Enlgish pretty well . In this way , everyone can follow a personal pattern and choose their own goals to achieve . In fact , there are areas with exercises to get several English Certifications , such as IELTS Academics or B2 First . Write and Improve is so useful because the writings can be checked in real time by the algorithm which it is based on . Mistakes and misspellings are immediately individuated so that the student can fix them in real time . Moreover , yellow highlights incorrect sentences using two different shades : the lighter one is for those sentences which have a few mistakes in their constructions , the darker one is for those sentences which are completely wrong . This part is probably the only one of Write and Improve which should really be improved : it would be very helpful if , after highlighting an incorrect sentence , it suggested a way to make it better and more fluid . Despite this little defect , Write and Improve is an optimal tool to improve English and I strongly recommend to use it to every English learner , from the beginners to the advanced ones . 
In fact , exercise is important for our health , but there are other things that are more important than only doing exercise . Our health is affected severely by external stimuli , such as stress , anxiety and depression , which we may encounter in our day -to -day life . Due to the increasing life demands , people are busier at work to meet these life demands . As a result , problems like stress , anxiety and depression may occur , making a poor work -life balance , which has very negative effects on our health . Exercise alone can never be the solution for a healthy body unless we find peace of mind . We need to do things that make us happy all day . In addition , our day should be full of various activities so that we do not get bored . For example , having time to go out with friends for fun is an interesting idea that boosts our peace of mind . Furthermore , taking up a new hobby , like singing or playing the guitar or piano , or doing yoga , are all nice activities that promote our mental and physical health . There are plenty of activities that everybody finds a part of him/her in them . Doing these activities along with exercise promotes our health . 
Hello my friend , I hope this email finds you well . I am writing to you to invite you on Saturday night to go to the cinema and watch the film ' James ' . It is my favourite film . It is a comedy film and it talks about three friends ; they are from different countries , but they met each other in the United States . They try to have many adventures and travel to many cities such as Atlanta , Florida , and New York . If you would like to come with me , tell me now to be able to reserve two tickets . 
There is no doubt that these days the Write&Improve website is becoming very popular . However , the question is : does this website really help the students to improve their writing or not ? It is considered one of the most controversial issues today . In this essay , I am going to examine this phenomenon from both viewpoints . On one side of this argument , there are people who are argue that the considerable benefits outweigh the disadvantages . To illustrate , the main reason for believing this is that the Write&Improve website has a lot of tools which are perfect to help students to write from the beginning because there are four levels for writing . The first level is for beginners and then for intermediate and finally for advanced and business . The first level , which is for beginners , includes some questions which make the students think about the answer and write it in easy way . Moreover , this website has some parts to prepare for the IELTS test . In the second point of this argument , some people argue that the website is profitable , and it provides some amount of writing and , after that , you have to pay to complete your progress in writing . Furthermore , they request a high fee to let the learner improve his or her writing . As we have seen . there is no one easy answer to this question . On balance , however , I tend to believe that this website is very good to help all students to improve their writing skills . 
The first aspect to point out is , all around the world , people are spending more and more time doing sedentary activities . During their leisure time , people like to sit on sofas watching TV , playing games or just socializing with others . The problem is that many children take their parents ' example and that can give them diseases . One solution for this problem is to force kids to do sports activities . To begin with , an extremely important place where you understand aspects about life and gain knowledge to help in materializing your future is school . But school should have to provide more physical activities for kids to take part in . For instance , children spend on average six hours in school every day while students can stay at school for eight hours . That is a lot of time just to sit on a chair and listen to someone . Children are getting bored as the time passes and they do not pay attention anymore to what the teacher is saying . Secondly , not only are physical activities good to increase attention , but they also reduce high cholesterol , high blood pressure , obesity and feelings of depression and anxiety . For example , one of my acquaintances had problems with anxiety and his therapist recommended him to do exercise and take walks . That worked for him and now he is really fond of sports activities . Because those activities made him one of the happiest people I have ever known . On the other hand , there are kids who feel uncomfortable when they are doing exercise in front of the other children . Some are often rude and make fun of others ' bodies and that can cause self -esteem problems . However , I believe that the results of doing exercise are worth it . To conclude , physical activities are a necessity in order to feel good , be healthy and look good . More people should do sport because it is wholesome and they will have many advantages after doing that . 
Some high schools have a requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate . I find this requirement absolutely appropriate because it highlights a problem which most of the times is too underestimated : that of social activism . We are habituated to do things in order to receive something back , but sometimes , things must be done just because they are right . In a society which wants to define itself , civil people must help the next one without asking for something back . Helping just to help , without any other purpose , is a wonderful way to make the personal cultural luggage of everyone grow . Volunteer work offers the possibility to meet people with different experiences , perhaps coming from other countries or from families with difficult conditions , or to care about animal which had unluckily been adopted by the wrong person . It offers also the possibility to understand different ways of living and to take conscience of the problems which the community has . It is possible to do a volunteer work cleaning the seaside from plastic or organizing beneficial events to collect money for the associations located in the territory . There are several possibilities to do something good for the community and this is a very relevant point because everyone can help according to their attitudes . Volunteer work also allows us to learn to be less selfish , which is not so obvious in our days , and that no one nor nothing have to be left behind . 
I have been learning English for more than 20 years , but I have never seen any website for learning English writing which has a feature as good as ' Write and Improve ' before . With this website , you can practise writing anywhere if you have a mobile phone or a tablet . There are tons of essay topics divided into 3 different levels that students can choose on their own . After finishing writing , this website provides the ability of text checking , therefore , the writings are evaluated and are given some feedback on in only a few seconds . If the students have corrected their writing , the graph will show the improvement compared with the previous one . However , there are some problems I found while I was using this website . First , the fonts are too small and the background colour is too bright . Second , I would suggest that the feedback should be more specific to each writing error because it is hard to find what the writers have done wrong by themselves without direct hints . After all , I would like to recommend this website to you , readers . You cannot find any other websites which give you the great opportunity to improve your English without any fee . I believe that this website will gradually be better and become a promising way to learn writing . 
I think it was not important to learn and speak a foreign language in the past , because it was not really important to get a job and money , and not a lot of jobs needed to speak other languages . But now I think it is important these days , because to get a job , you now have to speak another language , and if you want to be a flight attendant , you need to know more languages . When your work is to travel , you have to communicate with other people and you have to know the languages , to know what people from that country are saying to you . And also , you can be smarter knowing more languages . That is why I think it was not important to speak other languages in the past , but now , in the present , I think it 's more important to speak more languages to get a job . 
Learning English Hello . My name is Sam and I am 14 years old . I am from Myanmar and our traditional language is Myanmar ( Burmese ) . When we went to school , we learned English . I always wanted to study English because it is an international language and you can use it everywhere , like in every country . Also there are many benefits of English . The English language can be used in the business community , technology field , education and social life . In business , English can be very useful when a company builds cooperation with another international company from another country . In technology , every electronic device uses English , especially computing and the internet . In education , an international student should have the ability to speak , write and read in English . In social life , people will continuously interact with each other in various social situations . Also , English is important to me , because when I become an adult , I will build a company and community with other people . That 's all . 
Every invention comes with both pros and cons . If we are focusing only on one part of an invention , than will cause serious problems in the future . Video games were invented to provide fun to digital device users and if we go from the past to the present , the journey is quite remarkable and appreciable in the way video games developed . Now the video games market has grown so fast and vast , that they are making games in all genres and soon they are going to replace movies . They are providing us a real -life , but virtual reality experience . Now the cons part is that they are being used widely by teenagers and these video games are quite addictive and aggressive . Certain games are so violent , that they have a great impact on one 's mind very deeply . If I have to choose between the pros and cons of video games , I 'll go with supporting video games . Yes , there is no doubt that video games are impressive , but we cannot defy their pros too . Many teenagers take inspiration from video games and make their own video games at a very young age , which is very progressive for future generations . When Oppenheimer invented the nuclear weapon for the first time , he was very happy about the revolutionary invention , until it was misused by the USA and they used this nuclear bomb on Japan . But this does not mean the nuclear bomb was bad and it should have been banned at that time . A positive approach was taken and the nuclear concept was taken for clean energy creation . Thank you 
Yes , zoos are a great place for people to learn and see the true nature which we are missing from our lives today , since we moved towards technologies . A great place for animals to live is their own home , but this logic was true some decades ago . Today the scenario is totally different from what it was before and there is no home left for animals to live . Because of our so -called development , we cut down trees and we have made soil infertile . So there is no natural home left for animals to live . Even if they live in their home , they are fighting for their survival . So it is better to take these animal into zoos , so that they can be taken care of . Yes , it is true that they will become weak . As they are getting food from humans , they are not hunting . Many endangered species are kept in zoos so that they can be protected from hunters . People also get to know about these animals so that there can be an awareness about the extinction of animals . 
There is a trend among students for pursuing a higher degree in other countries , which is good , because one 's getting a chance to learn in a different education system . Since this trend is at its very peak , we need to know the advantages and disadvantages of going abroad for a higher degree . Some of the advantages of going abroad are a better education , more chances of getting job there , more opportunities , etc . Yes , it is true that most of the students who are going abroad , it is due to a better education system . More job opportunities is also a major reason for this migration . Some of the disadvantages of going abroad are cultural differences , feeling lonely , etc . The cultural difference between two countries is a major issue faced by students living there . There are less known people among them and in a time of emergency , it is difficult to get help , since it is not the native country a student comes from . There is also a lot news coming out about discrimination in recent times . The native people of that place feel insecure that their job opportunities are being divided and university seats grabbed by foreign students . 
