It is more important to be healthy than to be rich . No one can deny that health is wealth which cannot be bought with money . The ways of taking care of one 's health have sparked a great controversy among people of all walks of life . Some of them hold the view that being in a state of health is a treasure , but some of them believe that wealth is something more important than health , as money is the utmost vital thing for living . As Albert once said , " Happiness is nothing more than good health and a bad memory . " This quote really proves that being healthy is a happiness in our life . Thus , we should figure out the reason why being healthy is more significant than being rich . As far as I am concerned , the dominant reason why being healthy is more important can be proved through the old saying , " prevention is better than cure . " No doubt , one will suffer from a severe disease if they do not take good care of their health . Let 's say , they will pay a heavy price for not taking care of their health . For example , a billionaire will still get sick or ill , although they possess a lot of money and there is the moment when they cannot " buy health " as they wish . 
