Since globalisation , people have undergone many changes in their lives , and precisely in their speaking . Hitherto , individuals did not travel as much as we do currently . Travel is part of our life and increasingly people need to speak different languages merely to better understand the needs of outsiders . In fact , we are all connected and we need to start discussions and negotiations . If someone does not have the ability to fit in and speak at least one foreign language , it would be difficult to correctly negotiate and keep up with what is happening . It is important nowadays , because companies are becoming more global , and to succeed , employees must know how to speak another language than their native one . It is also important because at present we are doing international business with foreigners . Before , it was not mandatory to speak several languages , because we could still trade with local companies and therefore speak our native language . 
