Some parents worry about the negative impact . Video games have some positive effects on their children . Video games are very popular with children . They can make friends by talking about games and playing them . It is not different between playing ground and playing games among children . They can communicate with each other to share an experience . Children can get fulfillment when they complete the game . Mark , he is my cousin , likes to play games . He said that he could not concentrate enough without playing games in his childhood . " It might not be a good example , but the fulfillment of completing games gave me confidence , " he said . There are many types of games recently . some games need to use their head creatively . For example , online chess games are a little different from face to face games . Video games are just one approach to communicate with other worlds . Some games have a negative impact on children . However , there are some positive effects to play video games . If parents understand the contents and good points of the games , they can use it positively . 
