These days , the majority of university students prefer to live with their families when they study , and other students appel to move to live alone or with their friends . I completely agree with students who prefer to move and live on their own when they are students . First of all , it is often argued that moving to live away from their family is more advantageous to students who want to complete their studies for two main reasons . The first reason , these students will be more dependent on themselves , more than they were . The second reason , many studies and research show that students who live alone or on their own are more confident in themselves than students who live with their families . For instance , university students , who live away , will try new experiences and learn new things , which they will explore by themselves . That is why moving to live away from family is very important , especially when studying at university , which helps to be independent and confident in life . Secondly , living alone or away from families assists in many aspect for students to be successful in their lives . For that , the majority of parents encourage their children to pursue their goals even if their goals are in another area because they already know this way is very advantageous for their children in their future life . A good illustration here are the new studies which prove that students who move to live away from their families can afford the responsibilities in the future , especially in their jobs , and they are more successful in their lives . Thus , to live a successful life is dependent on your own choices . To conclude , I strongly believe that living an independent life is more useful for advancing in life . It is useful for people 's characteristics to be successful in the future . 
I use a computer every day and it is hard to imagine now life without a computer . At home I use my PC for writing emails , reading online news or ... improving my English . At my job I also need a computer for completing different tasks , for example , recording laboratory results . But what I enjoy doing most with my computer is writing stories and taking a break from the real world . 
Are video games good or bad for children ? People have asked this question for such a long time . Some people believe that they 're good , others believe the opposite . In my opinion , they have both positive and negative effects . Positive effects ? According to a Ted Talk , video games have many positive effects . Problem and logic solving . When a child plays games like Flappy Bird , he trains his brain to come up with creative ways to solve puzzles and other problems in short bursts . Accuracy . Action games train the brains of players to make fast decisions without losing accuracy . As you can see , video games give children positive effects . However , too much of anything is just too much . Video games could negatively impact your studies . This is the clearest effect that everyone knows . When you spend a lot of time playing video games , you start to feel tired and you do not want to do your exercises anymore . Next , it may cause insomnia . An adequate amount of sleep is essential for your brain and body to be productive during the day . However , excessive gaming , especially before sleep , can result in insomnia and sleep deprivation . That 's it . Everything has two sides . If you do it properly , it will give you positive effects . If not , you 'll have some problems . So be careful ! 
One of the most popular games in the world is the video game . Most children have experienced playing video games . By considering the negative impacts , I think playing video games is an exciting thing to do in our world . We can let our children experience them and keep our mind on their behavior too . One of the most positive effects on children would be improving their brain function . Video games would develop their skills and ways of thinking . In addition , living in a small flat could be boring for children . Playing video games gives them the chance to play and be with their parents . Also , some video games have been designed to nurture children and their potential . Parents could control their kids and also help them to use these games to learn something new . In conclusion , I think it is good for children to use video games . We can pay attention to their disadvantages and use them in the best way . 
Most medical doctors study this field because they would like to achieve good prestige and earn a lot of money . Rural regions are always suffering from a lack of health care and professionals . There are some specific reasons for this problem . First of all , there is not enough money in rural regions . Since most rural areas are located in the periphery and most of them live in poverty . So , they cannot afford the costs of a medical system . In addition , the government does not support these regions . Most rural areas are forgotten in the policies and public plans . As a result , the government does not know about the situation . In my opinion , the government must pay more attention to rural areas and prepare plans to improve their situation , especially in the health system . Also , it must make a compulsory rule for medical doctors to work in the peripheral regions for a couple of years . Moreover , support them to earn enough money to maintain their motivation . In conclusion , although working in rural areas is more difficult for medical doctors , there are some solutions to make them satisfied and develop in a rural life condition . 
In some countries , schools have a music course for all students . But , other countries may disagree with music or they could not be able to provide musical instruments . In my opinion , we need to consider music as a practical course for students . But , it would be better to give students a chance to choose it by themselves . The first reason is music can improve their mental and physical situation . For instance , music makes people feel peace and happiness . The whole history of the world is full of different kinds of music and musical instruments which have brought beauty to individuals . Another reason for using music courses is to develop students ' talents and potential . In other words , they could be able to find their skills in music and would follow it in the future as a career . In conclusion , it would be better to have a music course in our schools , but it should be an optional choice . Personally , I would always love to have a chance to try a specific musical instrument . 
Going to university could change people 's lifestyle . Most students would decide to move and start a new life in a different way . On the other hand , some prefer to stay with their family like the same past time . In my opinion , moving away and living on your own has some advantages . The first main reason is , by living alone , you can achieve independence . It means , you can make a decision on your own and control your life without any interference . The other one , living away would provide you for the future . You can start learning how you can earn money and manage your costs . Also , you have a chance to face tough situations and find solutions for them . On the other hand , some people believe students must stay with their family due to a lack of the security in society . But , from my point of view , students must learn earlier how to protect themselves . In conclusion , students could see life at university as an opportunity to learn how to live on their own . It helps them to live better in the future . 
Hi , It 's a little different . It 's not normal to go to a restaurant . Sometimes we go to a pizzeria and celebrate there , but , we usually have a party with a barbecue or we could eat junk food such as " coxinha , quibe , bolinho de queijo and so on . After that , we have a cake and we sing " Parabéns " and sometimes we sing another song . Then the party has some more songs and then the party is over . Bye , Igor 
Sleep is essential for our good health . We can see many advertisements for exercise on TV and in magazines , so the importance of exercise for our health is recognized commonly . However , there is one thing that is more important than exercise , but not treated seriously . It is sleep . A lack of sleep can have various negative effects on our health . Many studies show the bad influence of little sleep . For example , the report published by the national center of neurology and psychiatry clarified that a lack of sleep could make our mind sensitive to negative stress . Appetite and sleep are related closely . According to the research of Chicago University , less sleep stimulates the hormones that increase our appetite and diminish satiety . This study indicates that people with a lack of sleep might gain weight more easily than others . Many researchers show that little sleep is harmful to our health . However , people treat the risk of it as a trivial matter . Exercise is a good thing , but sleep is essential for our health . 
Dear Sara , I 'm so happy you invited me , but I could not go there . I do not know if you remember , but my mother had suffered an accident and , yesterday , I had to sit with my mother in hospital and it was my day . I 'd love to have been able to go because I 'm so exhausted and sad . So , did Jerry go to the party ? Did you say hello to him ? Tell me what happened there ! What do you think if we go to the park and we have a picnic ? Do you accept ? See you , Igor 
These days , students need to do some volunteer work before they graduate . This system is required in most high schools . I completely agree with this requirement to work as a volunteer . First of all , volunteer work teaches students anomalous things and information which they are not try it or know it before . When the student volunteers to work in charity places to help poor people or old people , all these works will change students ' thinking and beliefs for the better by making them be more cooperative because they spend their time and effort without any wage . Doctors , for example , are from the most people who provide volunteering not just their work as . To illustrate , poor people do not have enough money to pay for the hospital , and most old people cannot go to the hospital . So that is why volunteer work is important for students before they graduate , which makes them help other people . Secondly , in every major , volunteer work has advantages for both the students and the companies or the volunteering place . There are many institutions , companies , universities and shelters which need more from their employees but they cannot pay for them a high wage or their budgets cannot afford to pay for new employees . So the best solution here is volunteer work . . A good illustration here are shelters which need volunteer people to help the shelter 's center to provide enough services for poor people who come from other countries due to war or other reasons . Thus , volunteering is a good choice to complete the lack of needs . In conclusion , I strongly believe that volunteer work is very important for all students to learn and try new experiences . 
Are zoos good or cruel for animals ? A sensitive question , right ? When you ask someone , he may think they 're good . But then you ask another person the same question and he answers the opposite . So who is right ? In my opinion , I prefer the opposite , which means they 're not good for animals . First , animals should be free , not be jailed . Imagine that you 're an animal . You 're living in the wilderness and one day , you 're captured and put into a cage . You ca not do anything . You 're separated from your own fellows , you spend the whole day going around inside the cage . How would you feel about that ? Secondly , it 's about the zoos . Well , some zoos take care of the animals in a bad way . They do not feed them , even mistreat them . That 's the second reason why I do not like zoos . And you say that they 're good places to learn about animals ? If it were years ago , it may be true . But now , look around us . Smartphones and social media are everywhere . We can search for anything on the Internet . It describes in even more detail . So why do we need zoos ? For something else ? For no reasons , it wo not change my mind . 
I would like to talk about the most wonderful holiday that I have ever had . I went to Istanbol two years ago and stayed there for one week . It was a really memorable moment for me when I arrived there . First , I met one of my best friends at the airport . After seeing him , we went to a hotel and checked in . Then we started visiting the city . We visited a lot of monuments in Istanbol , which were really amazing . We also went to visit a famous mosque and I believe it was a beautiful ancient building . In addition , Istanbol is a gorgeous city and you can experience fascinating moments . I can remember when we were walking on the streets , we were delighted . Also , we did some good shopping there , because there were enormous shopping centers . In conclusion , if you want to have a different holiday , you should choose Istanbol . I guarantee you will like this city and you would certainly find a lot of wonderful adventures . I wish I could go there and stay for a while . 
One of the aspects of having a good job is its place . I think people need to feel convenient at work . In my opinion , it absolutely depends on the form of job . I will explain my reasons to provide a good answer . First of all , in the enormous companies , it is better to enclose the place . Because people who work in a huge building must deal with a lot of people . In addition , separate walls can increase disciplines and specify their duties . On the other hand , with an open design , they would lose their privacy . Also , in these kinds of companies , providing security is more difficult than in small offices . On the other hand , an open design is appropriate for small offices . By removing walls , people can feel sincerity with each other . In an open place , colleagues and their employees can work as a team and it helps them to increase their skills together . But , it can put their privacy in danger . In conclusion , each type of design has cons and pros . But , it is important to know which one is better for them . We can use both kinds in a specific situation . 
Nowadays , we face a world in which its countries are linked together . People in different countries need to have communication with each other . In my opinion , learning a new language is more important now than before . I will give some reasons for answering . First of all , relationships between people are increasing these days . There are some communication ways , such as social media , travelling in fewer hours , economic relationships , education , etc . To have a good relationship with foreign people , we must learn their language . The second reason is immigration . Most people like to go abroad and live in a foreign country . The first thing that they must learn is the language of the host country . As a result , learning a new language is really important today . In conclusion , there are some main reasons to learn a foreign language and I have tried to explain two of them . In these days , making connections and going abroad are increasing . So , people decide to study another language more than in the past . 
People always want to travel . It will not be different in the future , but the trip will be different . You should forget the line in the airport , the time on the train or on the bus . In the future , you will receive the ticket at home , by the internet , brought by a woman or man hologram . You are going to enter a machine in your city and you will be transported to any place you want to go to . The tele -transport will be very frequent , absolutely normal . Would it be dangerous ? Of course not . Your baggage would go in the same way . On a weekend , you could go to the other side of the world , visit a museum , a beach and return to your home quite , and go to work on Monday . In your life , you could visit all the countries of the world and each day that passes , it will be less expensive . You should prepare for the new world of travel and tourism . 
Study abroad ? Should you or should not you ? Some people say " you should , " others say " you should not . " So , which is right ? Everything has 2 sides , so it 's hard to answer which is correct . Let 's take a look at this . First , I 'll talk about its advantages . Studying abroad gives you many benefits . You can see the world , study in a better education system and experience a new culture . Your language skills will be extremely improved . You will have opportunities to get a great job as well . There are still more advantages of studying abroad , but I think this is enough . Now about its disadvantages . Homesickness . Being away from your family and friends can be a lonely experience . This can result in sadness and anxiety . I have seen an amount of students studying abroad who have to come back because they ca not stand the loneliness . Cost . An important thing that you have to be concerned about is the cost . The cost of studying abroad can be expensive , especially when you do not have a scholarship . Next is culture shock . This rarely happens , but who knows ? You will be faced with a new language , customs , food , dress styles , etc . This may make you feel frustrated , even if you have fully researched it . 
My topic is the difference between a city and a rural area . I would like to focus on medical doctors . There are in the cities many doctors , more than in the rural areas . Why is it a problem ? I 'll start with the second question . In my opinion , it may be a problem for the economic situation . Doctors want to be in the cities because they can be in the middle of cultural and social life . In the cities , there are more possibilities for education . On the other hand , the surrounding is anonymous . The health problems of patients are connected to their respiratory tract , for example , influenza , coronavirus . Other problems are connected to the immune system . The situation is different in rural areas . We can see advantages and disadvantages too . The doctor can be a part of the patient 's family . He knows his anamnesis and family genes . The health problems are about a surgery on legs or arms . 
Living a healthy life is not easy . A lot of people think that to live more , only two things are necessary : doing exercise and eating healthy food . However , in a greater understanding , there are several habits that may be considered to live better . For instance , taking care with our mental health . It 's normal for people to say that the body is linked with the mind . But only in a few cases , people give real importance to the mind 's care . Having a healthy mind is essential to be conscious about how our body is . If a person goes to the gym every day , but lives in a routine full of sadness , he is not completely healthy . Besides that , it 's important to understand what things make each person happy . If a person is happy traveling , he should invest more time and energy in planning his future trip . Or if a person misses his family a lot , he should stay close to his relatives . So , there are a lot of factors that must be considered to live better . But the most important thing is that each one is different and only that person can know what makes them happy . 
Learning English is one of the most important concerns in our world . There are an enormous amount of English classes and online sites in each country , which are working hard to teach English to people . In addition , like other people , English is really important to me . I will give you two main reasons to explain this concern . First of all , the English language is one of the top languages in the world . Actually , it has been accepted as the first language for international connection . People need to use English for travelling , studying abroad , having relationships , etc . So , I need to learn English like other people , to live more easily in this world . On the other hand , I really like to learn English , because it is a special language . I always enjoy reading English texts . Moreover , I also watch English movies and I prefer to know their language . It helps me to improve my knowledge and my brain function . In conclusion , there are some essential reasons to learn English . Having good communication with other people and learning your favorite language are good reasons to spend time on it . 
