My favourite season of the year Everybody loves one of the 4 seasons of the year . Most commonly it 's the season when we have a birthday or when an important event happened for us , like a wedding , vacation , Christmas or Easter . But I have other reasons . My favourite season is spring . I think it is unique . In winter we stay at home , use blankets and drink tea or cocoa . Outside it is peaceful and quiet . Nowadays in Poland , snow does not fall . In winter in Poland it is cold and wet . It is really pessimistic . But in spring everything changes . Grass starts to be green ( not brown or yellow like in winter ) . On the trees we can see buds , beautiful little buds . I like it when my neighbour 's forsythia is blooming . I feel happy when I look at it . In cities , people go out , meet with friends , organise parties and events . People become happier and start smiling . Everybody makes plans for summer . It 's really optimistic . I wonder how many people love spring ? 
