Studying abroad is a dream of most students that are in high school or university . The big reason , in my opinion , is to learn about a new culture and another language , but getting to know a new country has a big importance too . So if I have a chance to live abroad , honestly I will do it without thinking about it , because it is my big dream and I really hope that one day I will achieve it , but while this is not happening , I study here without a problem . By the way , I think the biggest disadvantage is living without the people that you love , like your family . In this case , it is so bad , but with the internet , nowadays it is easier talk with them when I miss them . Already , the advantages are so many to talk about , that I am a little lost , but some are meeting other people , making new friends , speaking another language , having experiences that you never thought about having . To tell the truth , this looks amazing and I hope to do this one day . 
