Medicine is an arduous job to do because doctors not only have to spend many hours on call , but also they have to study hard to become a good professional . That is the reason why a lot of doctors want to work in a good hospital in a city instead of rural areas . This problematic causes there to be not enough doctors there . Besides that , the lack of doctors in rural areas is because those doctors who have to go there have to leave their family or friends and life is difficult because there are no facilities that a city provides . Also , an important reason for doctors is the delay and lack of adequate equipment to work correctly and develop their job in a good way . These are some reasons why doctors do not want to do their practicum or work in those kinds of areas . A solution for this problematic situation that affects everyone could be to provide the rural doctor a better payment to be there . A different alternative if hospitals and rural areas ca not afford a higher salary . The rural community and the place where doctors go should make it as comfortable as they can . Rural communities should try to adapt good places for doctors not only for their stay but also to work correctly with adequate devices or an adequate work environment . having as a result more doctors ' work applications for those kinds of places . 
