A universal language Why does every school choose English as the second language to teach students ? Why do many parents want their kids to speak English perfectly ? The answer is that English has become a universal language . To cut down the differences Today , the world where we are living is composed of 193 countries . Each of them has a different culture , belief and people . However , language is the most crucial difference between them . That 's why it is so important to learn a common way of speaking . English is an ideal choice for everyone , because it is the most widespread language in the world . When two strangers meet , they could know more about each other if only they speak a common language . Essential for life Like every else , I started the study of English when I was at elementary school . Then , the more I grow up , the more I understand how essential English is . Travelling is my passion . If I had not learned English , I would never be able to go abroad . The majority of my friends are foreigners . Recommendation Taking learning English seriously is an intelligent choice . Even if you rarely have the possibility of meeting foreigners , do not give up and keep studying it . 
