Write and Improve is a website where you can improve your English so far . When I started with this website , I learnt a lot of English in roughly three months . Now , I 'm going to express my opinion about this astonishing website . It was a nice surprise to find that this website could correct all your mistakes when you are writing a text . As well as that , the texts of this place are similar to the texts of the Cambrige exam , so personally , I think that it is flawless and useful . However , I was disappointed with some texts because sometimes it could be misunderstood and , in spite of being that , you can use it only to improve your English , which causes you to not be able to improve other languages . It did not prevent me from enjoying this tool at all . Anyone who likes writing in English will really enjoy this website because it is a very systematic tool to practise your English and another advantage is that it is free , so you do not have to pay for it . If I were you , I would enter now because it would be useful to improve your English . Do not miss the opportunity ! ! ! 
There are plenty of useful online resources for English learners . Everything can be found online , from improving vocabulary to practising grammar , from interactive worksheets to printable worksheets . Sometimes , I find it too overwhelming and hard to focus on only one website . Besides , one website ca not satisfy what I am looking for . However , when it comes to the writing part , " Write and Improve " is the one and only tool for me . Why is it so great ? You can choose tasks according to your level . Once you write enough words for each task , your worksheet will be checked , and the score will be informed instantly . Moreover , you can see the feedback , for instance , what mistakes you have made , what words are misspelled . Then you have chances to change and improve your writing to reach a better level . I do not find it difficult to use this tool . It has a clear layout . It is easy to understand and follow . Other than that , you can be awarded when you accomplish some tasks , which encourages you to continue practising . It seems to me that I found the right and perfect tool for my writing skills . Whoever is still trying to upgrade their writing , either for fun or for a test , Write and Improve is the best tool that you should not miss out on . 
