Nowadays , video games are very popular in the world , especially with children . They were born during the 90 's , becoming more and more popular in the following years . The secret behind this success has different reasons . The first reason is the amount of different games that we currently have , starting from football games to war games . The second reason is about the graphics , in fact nowadays , video games are becoming very similar to real life in terms of characters and scenes . Their success has brought a problem in our life , especially for those of us who are a parent . In fact , they attract the attention of children more easily . I think that the right amount of these games could be good for children , because in this way they can stay away from some danger , like drugs for example , and at the same time , playing with them can teach children how to face life 's challenges . On the other hand , playing too much could be a danger for their health and for their mind , and besides , there are people that think war games make children more aggressive . I think that the ball is in the parents ' hands and it is them that have to check better in order to let them play , but not too much . 
