Nowadays it is becoming more and more popular to do exercise . Many studies have shown that a reasonable amount of exercise can improve your health , so more and more people have started to do it . I had a class discussion on the importance of exercise yesterday afternoon . There were a lot of different opinions about this topic , especially how to do it and if it is the most important thing in a life . This is always a tricky problem , because like everything in life , the important thing is balance . If you spend the whole day doing exercise , you will not have time for your family , for your girlfriend or boyfriend and for your friends . In fact , when you only dedicate your time in the gym or in your home doing exercise , probably you will always lose something in terms of friendship or love . On the other hand , if you do not dedicate a bit of your time for exercise , you may damage your health , in particular when you become older . For these reasons , as I said before , the secret in this tricky problem is balance , so in other words , you have to take time for yourself , but also for your effects . 
In my opinion , I think it is not good to have the same teacher for several years . The best option is changing every year , because I think every teacher has a different way to teach English . If you have the same teacher for several years , perhaps you wo not improve a lot , or wo not improve in all in your capacity and you will stay in your comfort zone . In my experience , I have had a lot of teachers . Every year I have a new teacher and I have improved a lot every year . Every teacher taught me in different ways and every year I practice with my new teacher the clues and methods of my old teacher . When you have bad teacher , you hope to finish the class and the English course , but when you have a good teacher , you do not want the class to finish . I would like to choose some old teachers again , but sometimes it 's impossible , because they do not have enough time . 
