We are living in a digital era in which video games are developing rapidly . How video games impact on children is an argument among their parents . In my point of view , playing video games will have both positive and negative impacts on children . The positive of playing video games is developing children ’s brains . It makes them more innovative . Besides , playing video games is a means of stress elimination . On the other hand , playing video games also has many negative impacts . The first is children waste time and money playing video games . The second is children ’s health problems , such as eye defects . Their sight is worsened because of the time sitting in front of a screen . Besides , addiction to video games makes children ruder and more aggressive in their behavior . The worst negative impact is game addiction . For example , children are likely to imitate the games they have played . Many teenage crimes are the result of game addiction . In conclusion , the children ’s playing video games have both positive and negative impact . How their parents control and face with those impacts are important . 
