Having different teachers is probably good for students with capabilities , such as being sociable , a good understanding , autodidactic , etc . because they can to adapt to the changes and challenges in class or the way of teaching of the new teacher . This is good , because each teacher has a different way to give the class , for example , class management , the development of the topics and the resolution of problems and answers , are very important to impart knowledge . However , for many students this is difficult , due to the fact that they are timid and they do not develop the abilities to interact with other people , although they take time to get used to a new teacher , and this is a problem for the teacher , because they not integrate with the class . Actually , these pupils need special focus and the compainers should be helped to have an enjoyable course . 
Video games are an excellent way for children to spend their free time , however this becomes a problem when the children do not want to do any other activities and the time in front of a video game console is too much . The video games could be alter their current mood . Sometimes , many children present with violent behavior , due to a lack of sleep , malnutrition because of not eating well and they could present with nightmares and sleep disorders . In my opinion , video games are not bad if the time is supervised by the parents and they are driven to develop other activities , such as sports , obligations of the home , caring for their pets , going out to the park and training , etc . In addition , the other activities can help them in their mental and physical health . It depends on the stability of the family nucleus and I believe that this measure must be taken to take care of children 's health . 
Zoos are incredible and excellent places for animals that are in danger of extinction and animals that were born in captive conditions , because there , the caregivers take care of their health . And these animals would not survive in a wild place , due to natural threats , such as food chain members and hunters . Some zoos have the conditions and the capabilities to maintain these animals and this is very good . However , other zoos have deplorable and precarious conditions for the species and their bad behavior towards the animals could provoke their death . In this case , keeping these animals in zoos is wrong because the animals should be treated with responsibility , amiability and specific care , and a good diet , as well as care by vets . If these animals do not return to the wild , they should be taken to other zoos where they are treated better . 
According to most trainers , exercise is very important for the maintenance of health . For adults it is necessary to do physical activity for at least thirty minutes , five days a week . These activities could improve the current mood too . However , other things , such as behaviors and customs , are important , such as a healthy diet . Due to a good diet , it interacts with the organism and gives it energy . Furthermore , it contains the requirements , like proteins , carbohydrates and bio -active compounds that we need . On the other hand , there are some activities , such as sleeping well to not have sleep disorders and not to be tired . It is important to keep in a good condition and to hydrate constantly , to take supplements , like vitamins and minerals . All sports are good for training , but to perform activities that are more likely to be healthy , do not forget the measures previously mentioned . 
