It seems that electronic devices have become essential things today . Living in the twenty first century , I am also familiar with those electronic devices . So , I use a computer for about two hours every single day . Being a student , I always use a computer for writing assignments , browsing the web and sending emails . I like typing up documents with a computer . It is very convenient for me . With a mobile phone , it takes me a long time to finish it . I also watch Netflix with a computer . I really enjoy it . 
Nowadays , more and more students decide to study in another country for a certain time . It is becoming a sort of fashion , but sometimes the students have strong reasons for doing it . Studying abroad can have both advantages and disadvantages . The advantages can be both for your career and for your culture . A positive aspect when you go to a foreign country is that you can learn another language , which can be useful in terms of your career when you find a job . Another positive aspect is the opportunity to find out about other cultures and traditions that can improve you as a person . The disadvantages are due to being away from your family and if you are very young , it can be a very difficult thing to put up with . However , in my opinion , the advantages are more than the disadvantages , because an experience like this can help you to grow faster and face life in the best way . 
In my opinion , it has always been important , but it depends on what language you would like to learn . For example , these days the English language is very important , but if you would like to learn a language that just a few people use , it will waste your time . So , in my opinion , you have to learn English . And if you would like to learn an extra language , at first you need to know how many people speak this language . And is it easy or not ? This is an important thing because if the language is hard , you will take a lot of time to learn it and this may not be good . So , in my opinion , if you would like to learn a new language , look at a famous language and an easier language than your mother language . I will explain , my mother language is Arabic , so for me , the English language is okay , not hard and not easy either . But if my mother language was Korean , for me , the English language would be so hard . 
To be honest , I basically do not like to exercise , but I have to do it for my health . I do exercise every day . I do not have a fixed schedule to take exercise , it depends on my free time . As a high school student , I ca not afford to exercise at a gym . Therefore , I do exercise outside . Jogging is my favourite exercise . I enjoy jogging every evening . My mom tends to suggest the skipping rope . But I always refuse to do it as I do not want to be covered in sweat . As I said before , strenuous exercise is not my thing . I only enjoy light exercise like jogging , dancing and yoga . 
I do not like my children playing video games . I think they never learn anything . They spend a lot of time playing video games that they could spend reading books , watching a documentary or playing with their friends . Some people think that playing video games has positive effects on children 's brains , because they improve their imagination and creativity . Perhaps some video games offer good effects on creativity and imagination , but only a bit . My children 's friends played a lot video games and they got bad results at school , they lost their friends and changed their behaviour . They have been spending a lot of time with a doctor , trying to recover their behaviour . Moreover , they are spending a lot of money . I prefer my children to spend time reading books , playing with friends and family and walking in the forest . When I have found an educational video game , I 'm going to let them play video games . Do you agree ? 
I heard about your accident . I am very sorry about that . In our class , everybody misses you so much . As you know , the first test is coming up in the next three weeks . Anyway , our class has a plan to help you do it well . We will come to your home at the weekend and share the lessons and our notebooks with you . 
I started my journey to improve my English writing 1 month ago . I made a decision that I should improve my English writing this year . I decided to improve my English writing because I want to pass the IELTS English test . The first thing I did was surf the net and search for a method and tips that can help me to work easily and efficiently without wasting my time with a bad start and then I feel disappointed . Due to what I found on You Tube , I started to practice . First I started with an easy task . Every day I wrote a simple word in my journal . Second , after two weeks , I truend to site named write & improve it 's an amazing site , He start withe from the beginner level to a site named write & improve . It 's an amazing site . It starts from the beginner level to advanced level , with several subjects it tests you to write about . Furthermore , I also started to read in English ( books , articles , blogs ... ) to increase my vocabulary . On this journey , I hate to write about subjects I do not like or weird subjects to what I know . Finally , I advise you to start improving your writing skills with something you enjoy when you write about it . Write about a topic which you love and that interests you . 
Having the same the teacher for several years is good for students . Some believe that . On the other hand , others think having new teachers each year is more beneficial . In my opinion , I think the best one is having a new teacher each year . The first reason is this is better for a student to learn from different methods of studying , to know what is the best way to learn from it and prepare themselves to fit in with changes , because in real life , they will be live in a world which is changing every day . There is nothing constant . Every day new things appear and things disappear . Second , this helps them to know more things , because maybe the teacher who teaches them does not tell them about a topic because he does not know . Third , it is good to change environment and the students do not see this teacher every day , or that this makes the students feel bored , because there is nothing new that will happen today . They start to know the routine and the next action of the teacher , even before he starts to do it . Maybe this method has some negatives , but in my opinion , it is still better than the other belief . 
Nowadays , it is very common that some students choose to study in another country during high school or university . It is very important when someone is learning a new language . He or she can have contact with not only the language , but also the culture and living abroad is a great experience for anyone who wants to learn about the language and the culture of another country . On the other hand , students who choose to study abroad can miss some opportunities in their country . Students can redo their school year , because the subjects in another country are totally different and perhaps a university student can miss a job opportunity in that year he is traveling . To sum up , it is a great chance when someone can study overseas . It is not an opportunity that all people can afford , because it is very expensive and even if students can stop their lives for one year or more , it will be a terrific experience and it will be very important for their resumé and personal experience . 
A month ago , I asked my English teacher , Mrs . Gomax , what I should do to improve my English writing skill . Then , she suggested that I should try the website named Write&Improve , which is sponsored by Cambridge University . So , I tried it and found it useful for me . Once you enter the website , you can choose the level you would like to join . There are three levels , which are beginner , intermediate and advanced . You can freely go for a suitable level for the ability of your English knowledge . You can also create an account . It already gives you the titles that you have to write about . For example , let us say you choose the beginner level , you can see the different titles with questions . If you are going to write , click the question , write the answer and then submit it when you are finished . It is really useful for me . I feel that my writing has improved within a month . And I like the way they motivate the students . When your writing is finished , it gives you some feedback and awards if you reach the goal they set . You can see your progress on the progress graph as well . That is my favourite part , as I can see my progress day by day . I like all the functions involved , it except one thing , that is it ca not correct each of your mistakes exactly . However , I would like to recommend this website to my classmates who wish to improve their writing . I am sure that you will all see good results . 
Nowadays , doctors are not as tempted to move into the country as they were back in the day . Cities are not dirty places anymore and instead physicians are greeted with a generous income and a wide offer of free -time activities . But essentially , there are more potential patients in a rather tight space , allowing doctors to abandon long trips to bedbound patients . As a result , you do not waste too much time driving around , which you could also use to cure even more patients in a day . You see : money is the cue . To solve the problem of doctor shortage in the country , you have to attract physicians by securing them extra help by the authorities . For instance , you could offer them special conditions for the building process of their doctor 's offices . Alternatively , they could be provided with lower running taxes or prices for their equipment . Another option would be to give more places at universities to aspiring students of medicine who consent to working for a certain period in rural areas . 
I like zoos very much . I think you can enjoy them a lot with your children , where they can learn a lot about wild animals . When I was a child , I enjoyed them a lot and I want my children to be able to enjoy them the same . There are people that do not like them , because they think that animals suffer a lot when they do not live in their natural environment . I do not agree with them . The animals grow in a good environment , they have fair treatment . They are born , grow up and die in the zoo . When you go to the zoo , you learn a lot of things about the lifestyle of animals and you learn to respect them . I think the damage to the animals is very low if you compare it with the benefits . There are many animals that are suffering because they live in a circus , and you cannot compare them . Animals in circuses have the wrong lifestyle and the animals ' defenders think they are the same . 
My best ever holiday was in Mallorca , when I was seventeen . I was with my family , my parents and my two brothers , and it was amazing ... I enjoyed it a lot . We were staying in a big house , with a beautiful garden , a huge swimming pool and 2 minutes from the beach . We spent a lot of time in the swimming pool , in the garden and at the beach . We met many people from different countries and different Spanish regions . We spent one month in Mallorca . Every morning , we had breakfast in the garden and every day we had a meal and dinner at different restaurants on the island . We went to Ibiza for two days , where we traveled around the island and enjoyed it a lot ... its beaches , its sun , its restaurants . I would like to repeat the same experience with my children and enjoy it as I did it . I have good memories about Mallorca and I do not want to lose them . 
Hi Fran , I hope you are well . I hope to write to you . Last weekend , I went to a concert . Can you imagine who ? The Rolling Stones . It was fantastic concert , with a spectacular performance on the stage , with a lot of lights and dancers . They sang twenty one songs , the concert lasted three hours . It was an amazing concert . I had a little problem . I broke my leg jumping . I do not know who it was , and now I have to rest for two months with my leg in plaster . I invite you to my home , would you like it ? I want to see you and talk . I hope you write soon . 
In this new school year , I will be very pleased to learn English Literature and grammar . Grammar is my favourite subject and I will really appreciate studying it , since it is a very difficult area of knowledge for many students and even some teachers have some difficulties with that . Besides that , I would like to improve my writing and my pronunciation in the English language . It is very hard for a foreign student to learn a second language and now , with this program , I have the opportunity to do that . To sum up , to achieve my goals , I will do my best and I will study hard as well . I would like to enjoy this opportunity and I am sure that it will be a long time to improve my skills , but I know that I can do it and with this help , definitely it will be easier and I will certainly develop my skills for sure . 
The best holiday that I ever had was in January in 2006 . My husband and I decided to get married in this month , because we wanted to celebrate our engagement in our parents ' town , since we had been living 6 hours away from them . Another reason to choose the date and the place was because we had a lot of friends in common that spent that holiday with their relatives . All our friends had gone to another city to work , so we could meet them on holidays and vacations . It was an amazing party , with all our family and most of our friends . I had a beautiful dress and we invited 400 people . After the party , we spent the night in a hotel and we had lunch with our family in the same place where the party happened , because a lot of people had lunch with us . After some days , we went back to our apartment and now , almost 15 years later , we live in a nice house , in another city , with two daughters and one fish . 
In our country , Myanmar , it takes time for the teachers to change from one school to another , because they have to serve at the same school for about four or five years to be promoted . So , I rarely experience being taught by different teachers . I do not know well the differences between having new teachers and the same teachers each year . I believe that both have positive and negative effects . For some students , they like having the same teacher for several years , because they are accustomed to his or her teaching method and they like it . But , to be honest , I really would like to be taught by new teachers each year . In my opinion , having new teachers will give us something new to learn . For example , supposing we do not like the teacher now teaching , then we can expect another one who is better next year and his or her teaching method may be way better or may be more fun . As I mentioned before , we could learn something different from her and she can attract us to be interested in the school lessons , I think . On the other hand , the new teacher might be worse at teaching . However , I like to have a new teacher each year , as I wish to be taught with different teaching methods by different teachers . 
Hello , First of all I would like to wish you ' happy birthday ' . Here in my country people sing " Happy Birthday " to the birthday person too . We usually have a party for that person . A party must have a beautiful iced cake with a lot of little candles , candies , soda and many colorful balloons . Stay in touch . Thiago 
There is no doubt that volunteer work nowadays has become a famous job due to the fact that people have become more sensitive and caring about the people around them . However , the question is : is it suitable to have volunteer work as a requirement for graduating from high school ? In this essay , I am going to discuss this phenomenon from both points of view . On the one hand , we have people who argue that forcing our children to volunteer is considerably a bad thing to do . People believe that the essence of volunteer work lies in our intention . For instance , some students might not be willing to volunteer , so when we make them work arbitrarily , they are going to hate it and , in this case , we lose what really is the meaning of this work , which is to give all you can unconditionally and with passion . Moreover , on the other hand , people argue that making our students work voluntarily could benefit many people and , at the same time , we teach our students to have loads of experience in such a field , which will benefit then in the long run . A good example here is that they will learn how to be patient and control their time , also to respect people and to learn these work skills would make their life easier . Eventually , we could say that forcing our students may not be the right decision . Instead , we could tell them the importance of this world and leave it alternative . 
Today 's subject ; Healthy living Hello everybody , I hope all are fine . Well , today 's subject is very important . Why ? Because this is the first thing you must focus on . I think our health helps in grow all the socials , and helps people to learn and education how we are daily routine . It 's correct . My opinion in this essay is that we cannot live without health together teaching and security and food . These are three important things in life . No countries can achieve any real growth without these points . All the world faces many pandemics for all time , but it ca not win because all viruses end time . Also , I think many poor communities have more illnesses because they do not have solutions to all the problems . I hope finally my essay will encourage all people in the whole world to live healthily . Kind regards . See you soon . 
Living in the twenty first century , the age of IT , all children play video games , except the poorest of the poor , because the poor cannot afford to buy video games facilities . Video games are frowned on by parents as time -wasters and worse , some education experts think that these games corrupt the brain . They can affect children 's development and health when played exceedingly . Some experts say that some young people become violent or commit extreme anti -social behaviour because of playing games . Some children spend their time playing games alone in their own room instead of hanging out with friends . It can affect their cognitive development unless they go out and socialize in the real world . This can also impair their eyesight . Contrary to the common view , video games have some positive effects when played moderately . There are many types of games made for varied purposes - some can be entertaining and relaxing , while others can be challenging and good for learning . Some games can improve children 's development , such as making decisions in a short period of time and critical thinking skills . It seems to me that parents should not forbid children from playing games . Instead they can help them enjoy video games properly and avoid problems . 
Dear Mayor , Dear Members of the Town Council , With this letter , I 'd like to express my opinion about your last decision regarding mobile phones . I do not think it 's up to you to decide those things . You ca not - and moreover you should not - stop people from using their mobile phones while they are on public transport or in shops and restaurants . They can use their mobiles because they do not disturb anyone . Of course , the volume has to be switched off , in order to respect everyone 's space . You should instead ban the use of mobile phones while people are walking on the streets or biking , to prevent and avoid accidents , and in places , like cinemas and theatres , where it is dark and even the littlest light can disturb who we have nearby . It makes no sense banning mobile phones from public transport if people can use them just out their doors , maybe crossing the street . Mobile phones are not the problem , people are . You should promote campaigns which encourage people to use less their mobiles and live more in real life , to teach them that the real world is outside their smartphones . People do not learn with denies , but with teachings , explanations and examples . I beg you to retrace your steps to find a better and effective solution . Best regards , A citizen 
The Future of Travel The covid -19 pandemic has changed travelling because it is restricted to travel for another country , so if you want to travel nowadays , you spend fourteen days of your trip in quarantine . Doing this is boring I know , but is necessary for our health . Thinking about the future of travel is complicated , because it is an uncertain future , yet we do not know what the world is gonna be like next year . If you do not have a vaccine , what the world will be like ? This is a good question that I am not prepared to answer . My thought about everything that is happening is confusing , but I 'll share with you . Maybe if all people travel now , things are gonna be so complicated because of this . In three years , we can travel without being scared of this disease , but now it is not necessary to travel because there are many more important things than this , like your life , so wait and be careful . 
It is very important to do some exercise for our health and a lot of people do not do that , because in their opinion , it is very boring and tiring . Some people prefer hanging out with friends or even watching TV to doing some kind of exercise . On the other hand , although exercise is not attractive for some people , others love it and they are obsessed with it in a certain way , so that they ca not control it and they forget everything in their lives because of that . There are a lot of competitions for those that like to show off their bodies and muscles . Also , there are a lot of products on the market that promise to improve your physical condition . To sum up , it is necessary to do some kind of exercise . Remember that it is not necessary to go to the gym . Maybe someone can find a fun activity such as dancing , doing a sport or swimming . There are a lot different activities , so that any person can do exercise without noticing it . 
Hello everyone , I think exercise is very important for our health , because that permits our body to keep its metabolism . If people do exercise to have beautiful skin , hair and nails , the muscles grow , the brain and the organs work properly . Otherwise , people who do not do exercise have health problems with time , the muscles atrophy and it 's more difficult to keep the metabolism healthy . However , it 's more important for our health to have good eating habits , so the body can work properly and keep the functions of all the organs . Even research has demonstrated that people with a healthy diet live for a lot of years and preserve their youth . No doubt , another important thing is to be calm , because stress causes issues to health , due to people not being able to rest properly . The brain is altered and the organs work inadequately . That causes nervous , heart , kidney , muscle and skin problems . It ´s important to know that doing exercise helps to relieve stress and to stay calm in different situations . In conclusion , doing exercise is important for our health , but it is the sum of several factors which allows us to have good health . 
The aim of my report is to describe my experience with my English writing that I 've been practicing on Write and Improve . The suggestion came at the right time , because I needed to improve my writing . I also had the need to learn other words and comprise my vocabulary and the Write and Improve site gave to me what I required , by making me practise different kinds of writing . This helpful tool obliges us to provoking thinking by having so many ways to write and learn more about the English language . In my experience , I 've started to understand how to write in diverse fields of knowledge . By doing exercises daily , I can improve how I express my thinking in another language . I really recommend this learning and practising tool that is Write and Improve to all my classmates . I think it helps us with the assessments for practicing various types of writing . 
Except the affluent countries like the US , students in poor countries wish to study abroad . They believe that their education system is much higher than theirs . Lagging behind the western countries , most students in Asian countries are trying to go abroad and study there . Not only undergraduates , but also graduates go abroad to get a job with a high salary , because they know that their government is not able to create a special post for them . But some students do not want to go abroad , as they are not accustomed to their culture and something like that . From my point of view , I want to study abroad and serve my country . As you know , studying abroad is not easy . You will experience culture shock certainly . You have to get used to their food , culture and weather . Worse than that , you might get bullied . To the best of my knowledge , it has been said that some western people discriminate against Asian people on the grounds of race or ethnicity . On the other hand , there are a lot of advantages to studying abroad . As you have to learn their language , you will become bilingual . And you get to know their culture and lifestyle . You begin to know the difference between your country and their country . You will get a ton of knowledge , since you can see and learn many different things from them . And with that knowledge , you can serve and strive for your native country 's development . 
Speaking for myself , it is more effective if the space is more or less open . In a perfect environment , there should not be any walls or things similar to them , which separate working spaces . One simple reason is that it makes it easier to communicate with other workers in the office , it helps to keep the information flow running smoothly . In addition , the open space will create a better atmosphere in general , which can increase moral and productivity . Every wall is a potential unused space that could be used for another coworker to do their work . Some people are afraid of having not enough space as result of a crowded area , those people are more likely to get sick . When workers are sick , the enterprise loses a lot of manpower and also money . Generally speaking , walls are just a waste of room and make people uncomfortable . Last but not least , it gives some employees the false feeling of privacy that can tempt people to feel at home and then start doing private stuff at work . Isolated people between walls are more likely to break rules because no one can see them there . 
Hi , Last week I went to an amazing concert , where my favorite band Queen was going to play . I went to the concert to buy a ticket . First , all the people wanted a ticket too . I waited 30 minutes and the ticket was 20 euros , so expensive . I entered the concert . The band came an hour late . Can you believe it ? The concert started and all the fans started singing all the songs , and with all of that noise I could not hear some songs . But , even though I could not hear all of the songs very well , I enjoyed it . 
The future of travel will be different than as we know it and that 's because technology is improving day by day . If we think about something basic , like how we move ourselves to travel , we use cars , planes , ships and trains , but in the future , this transport will be faster . Travelling around the world will be easy , cheap and efficient , due to technology . Right now , even if you do not know anything about a place , you only need to check your phone and you are going to have all the information , like places to visit , restaurants , hotels and things like that , and one of the most important problems that we have nowadays is the language problem . When we visit a country , maybe we do not know the language , but I think in the future we are going to be able to understand all languages , thanks to our phones , because we are only going to need to record our voice and automatically we 'll have the translation . 
In the future , with the development of technology , we wo not just go around the Earth , but will also fly into space . Now we can fly anywhere on the Earth within a day , enjoy a delicious meal , relax in a luxury hotel . But there are still a lot of people who dream of going beyond the sky , into dark space . Technology has been developing rapidly for a couple of decades . In a few more decades , we will see the cost to travel into space drop significantly . More and more people will be able to go into space , people may have a honeymoon on the moon . Instead of using a plane , we may use a rocket to go around . Check -ins in space may become a new trend . In spite of a new way of traveling , the core attributes of travelling will still remain the same . They are the curiosity of a person about a new place , the experience that travelers want to have , the desire to explore a new area . The future is unpredictable , who knows where we will be able to travel to , maybe a new solar system , I do not know , time will tell . 
Living being completely honest is the hardest thing in my life . Not because I want to lie to people , but because people do not want to hear what they do not expect to . I am one of those people who refuses to lie , but this shape of my personality caused me a lot of problems in all my life . I 've never been able to pretend to be a friend of someone , nor to support an idea I did not share , nor to adapt to something I totally disagreed with . But living in complete honesty , always telling the truth , it is very hard and sometimes it becomes impossible because the consequences of the truth would be a true disaster , not only for me , but also for other people . I ca not stand the idea of making someone suffer with my truth or honesty , nor to create serious problems . For example , I ca not tell my boss that one of my colleagues does not do his job correctly because he would be fired , and I do not want this responsibility on me . I ca not tell my mother - in - law that her daughter is growing up like a ful , because she would not let me enter her house never again . My choice is to avoid situations that do not make me feel comfortable , to preserve civil and pacific relationships with everyone , and to tell a half truth when it is impossible to stay quiet . When it is impossible to say a half truth , I always choose the truth . I do not believe in lies , they are just a way to escape from responsibilities . 
My favorite film is " Star Wars . " This film is exciting , eventful and very very good . This film is about the war between rebels and the empire and power . I think you would love this film . You wo not feel prejudiced . My second favorite film is " Harry Potter . " This film is magical . I think you would like this film too . 
Books and technology nowadays are at war . Both have a side which fights each other . The reasons are many , like the prices and quality of the products . Personally I do not think that computers and tablets should replace books in school , because it can be very expensive for the family to buy these technologies . Reading a book is 100 times better than reading something on a tablet for example . You cannot enjoy it like a real book . Also , giving a tablet to students would mean giving them the chance to play video games in school in sight of the teachers without any consequences . This already happens today with smartphones . Books are also useful to take notes , which are important in a student 's life , or you can underline important paragraphs in order to have a better understanding of the topic which you are going to study . Technologies are not useful for the teacher , because a lot of them do not know how to use the modern phone or PC . I personally think that using a book is the best way to teach in these and future days . 
Hello there , I 'm available to go to your house for supper tomorrow . I like to eat vegetable salad with pasta , I also like eating baked potatoes with olive oil . And I will bring a delicious full -bodied wheat beer . See you soon . 
Every student should have the possibility to choose where to study . Most of them ca not do it because going to study abroad is very expensive . Obtaining a room on university campuses is quite difficult because there is a limited number of available rooms . So , a lot of families do not have any other alternative but paying affit . A room can cost around 400.00 euros per month in normal cities , but in the most expensive ones , such as Milan , prices are around 700.00-800.00 euros per month . Moreover , despite being public , university has taxes to be paid , which are calculated based on the annual salary of the family . The problem is that the base under which people do not pay is very low and a normal family needs at least 2,000.00 euros per year to pay university taxes . In addition to that , there is material to be bought : a pen is always a pen , of course , but a book can even cost 60.00 euros . When I attended university , every exam took at least three books . Then there is the bus to move around the city . At the end , it is obvious that studying abroad is an economic choice : those who can do it , do it , those who ca not , do not . I chose to remain because luckily my city offered me the university course I wanted and because I did not want to leave my family , my boyfriend and my cat , whom I 'm very close to . Probably , in other conditions , I would have gone away to a foreign country to learn the language , to open my mind , to grow up . Certainly , studying abroad forces you to grow up because you 're alone , but it is necessary to be a responsible person , a condition too rare nowadays . Living alone does not mean living without rules , but it 's a chance to follow our own path . 
Workplace Design There is no doubt that one of the important places where people stay for a long period of their days is their workplace , therefore it should be designed in a way that makes you feel comfortable and ready to accomplish your duties . However , in this article , I am going to examine various types of office designs . Firstly , one famous design is known as the open design , where there are no walls to separate different desks , so all the workers work in one huge hall . Also , many employees say that this type of design has many disadvantages to them . One of which is that sometimes the workplace becomes very annoying because of the amount of people and the sounds will make you work insuffesintly . Moreover , these days , workplaces in different firms have considered their design to be like this one , which may affect several workers . Secondly , there are enclosed offices , where many workers feel comfortable and happy while working in such a design . These employees like this pattern for many reasons . For instance , it provides their own space where they feel free to work without any disturbing noises , therefore , their work would be done suffetintly and in a good time . Eventually , we could say that different types of places and their designs could massively affect the workers ' job . So we need to focus on this fact if we want to succeed in our business . 
Life Choice There is no doubt that we all wish to live a happy and long life . However , the question is : if you can make a choice , would you like to live a long calm life or an short intense one ? In this article , I am going to write my own opinion with examples . Firstly , my opinion is that I would like to live a short life , but one which is filled with excitement and different adventures . The main reason why I choose this option is simply because I want to try it , I believe it would be wonderful . As my life now is kind of calm , I think it would be good for me to change it . Besides , it is better to live and have a great life than to get old and have nothing to do . However , some people may have another opinion . Those people think that living a long calm life would be extremely greater than living a short one . Moreover , they argue that living a long life means having children of your own and raising them along side your husband and growing old with them . Those people believe that there is no other thing in this life which could be compared to this precious moment . Finally , we could say that people have varied personalities and whether you disagree with them or not , it does not matter because different individuals have different circumstances than yours . 
First of all , I discovered this useful tool while I was browsing on the internet , and I decided to try and see how it works . So , the first thing I watched was the tutorial video , about the benefits , how the program works , some recommendations and other functions . Then I clicked on the link and at the top of the screen a small message appeared with which I had to decide which level I am . After that , I had an activity in which the program gave me a topic and there was a space to write about it . Before I started writing , I noted that there are so many tools on the screen . For example , there ´s a timer which helps you to check the time that you take when you write an essay or report , also , there 's space for the feedback in which the program shows what is wrong in the text , it could be grammar , spelling or about connectors and so on , and finally a chart where you can see your progress graph after the revision . I really like this tool . For me it 's really useful to improve my writing skill in order to prepare myself for my next test . On top of that , it has a beautiful design and it 's easy to understand how it works . 
