English is an international language . Many people around the world speak English as a first or second language . It is vital to have a command of this language for communication with other nationalities . International companies use this language to make trade agreements with other countries . Therefore , it is an advantage for your resume if you can speak different languages . Besides , English students have another goal in learning , taking an international test such as TOEFL or IELTS . International certification is essential for entering college or starting studies abroad . It is one of the requirements . Another exciting aspect is that learning provides a high understanding of the world . Language is not separate from culture , on the contrary , it is a cultural element . You begin to understand the world from a different perspective . In the English view , you immerse in new social rules , new concepts and thoughts . 
In my opinion , travel will be very different in the future . People will be able to arrive at their destination faster than now . The accidents that kill a lot of people will decrease , because all drivers will be controlled by sophisticated computers , avoiding , in this way , mistakes . Traffic will be much better , because people will prefer to take public transportation to go to work . Trains and buses will be comfortable and cheap . On the other hand , some people will spend a lot of money on visiting the moon or even visiting another planet . People who live far away from their family will be able to visit them in their own cars , that will take only a few hours , because they will fly . To sum up , technology will help a lot of people in having fun , spending more time with their family and they will travel with safety and peace . A driver will be able to program a car and sleep until he arrives where he wants to go , because the automatic pilot will drive for him . 
