Being a volunteer is a good thing . However , if the volunteering is " required , " it may not be good . The goal of volunteers is " to help . " Whether helping humans , animals or the environment , people do it from the bottom of their hearts to make themselves feel great . Besides , helping others can give them a sense of accomplishment and self -worth . On the contrary , someone who is asked to be a volunteer , not aiding others by their own will , may not make an all -out effort . These volunteers just want to reach their goals as quickly as possible ; therefore , they wo not leave no stone unturned . The high schools which demand voluntary work from their students are well meaning , but that could distort the intent of being a volunteer . High schools should find some attractive ways , and guide students in the right direction . Only do things from the bottom of one 's heart could acquire the treasure of being a volunteer . 
