The education process is a result of interaction between students and a teacher . Then , the quality of the contact and how long this happens is important for the success of this action . In any situation , for a better following of the progress of a student . they should continue working with the same teacher , who can do it in the correct way , by planning tasks and exercises . This mode , where they do not have a break , is interesting for a specific situation , like when the students have a problem learning . But , for a normal situation , the contact in the process of teacher -learning with different teachers is interesting to prepare the students for life situations , like working with different people , adapting to explain subjects in other contexts and other ways . For each situation of learning , there is a different request for the action . to know it is happening . The class is a space for contact between people that have different requests , then learning can happen through different ways , like the same teacher for a long time or not . 
For me , health is more important than being rich . Of course , it is necessary to have enough money to be healthy too . In my opinion , you need to work enough to have a comfortable and healthy life . If you can get a lot of money , no problem , it is very nice . However , you should not spend all the time , all your life , worrying about money and about a lot of money . It is very important to spend your time with your family , with your friends , doing exercise , watching a good film , reading a book , etc . It is good to have a balance in your life . Sure , if it is possible , try to work with something that gives you some pleasure , because we are in the job for a long time . You must try to avoid being nervous , try to be calm , try to sleep well , try to smile and try to have a good life . 
First of all , I think it is a fantastic experience with so many advantages and some " disadvantages , " which I prefer to name as learning . By way of introduction , studying abroad is highly recommended in the majority of schools and universities , because of the opportunity that a student can have in order to improve another language . Apart from that , there are so many skills that a student can develop or improve during an exchange , such as communicative and social skills . Due to the student meeting new people from a different country and from a different culture , he has to find ways to interact and make friends . In addition , the student would learn to work with diverse teams , which is really significant for his or her resume for the long term . Moreover , an incredible advantage of having an exchange is to visit different tourist places , such as beaches , deserts , mountains , museums , lakes and archaeological places . Besides , the student can try new and diverse dishes , which are traditional or very popular in the resident country . On the other hand , the student will have the challenge of developing the capability to adapt to change , owing to the student going to live far from home in a new city , as well as far from friends and family . She has to face changes in her routine and start to visualize and plan new activities according to her circumstances . In spite of all the opportunities and advantages , there are also some disadvantages from having an exchange . One instance could be that it can take a lot more time to finish a degree , due to the university just allowing the students a certain number of subjects , which is not bad at all , because the universities do this in order to make your exchange more enjoyable and with a little bit less stress . However , when a student starts studying abroad , there are some difficulties in view of the new university having different rules and processes to assess the students . Nevertheless , another disadvantage of studying abroad is that it is an expensive experience that requires so much money . If a student wins a scholarship to do the exchange , which just covers part of the expenses , but on the contrary , she will have to pay the flight tickets , the housing , the food and costs of traveling and the payments to the university . Finally , speaking personally , I would recommend all students to do an exchange wherever they want and not only learn and enjoy , but also lose and find yourself again in that new country . 
