Video games are very popular nowadays , not just with children , but many adults also enjoy playing games on their video games console or on their computer . With the evolution of technology , games are become more realistic and it makes this kind of distraction very interesting to do for people that like it . You will find some specialists saying that video games are very bad for children , because they can cause some damage in their brain and besides that , they could cause social problems too . For them , if children start playing games at a young age , it can cause an addiction to playing games all the time and the children will lose interest in doing other tasks , like studying or doing some physical sports . However , many other specialists and parents agree that playing games can improve some abilities in children 's lives . Some specialists say that the games can help children to be more concentrated , calmer and playing games can improve their ability to think faster and it could help them to solve complex problems . Of course , it is a complex subject to discuss . I think it is necessary to do many studies to know if playing games is good or bad for children . Meanwhile , I guess the best thing to do is to be careful with the time your kids are spending playing games and besides that , we need to be very careful in what kind of games we are letting our children play , because some games are so violent and sometimes they contain sexual scenes or inappropriate language for kids . 
