It is really wonderful to see animals in the forest living their lives free , but it is not so common anymore . The natural environment is becoming smaller each day and the natural habitat for wild animals almost does not exist . An alternative that humans found to let people keep some contact with wild animals was to create a fake environment and put some species of animals there . It is not a perfect place for the animals , but it is a place where they can have food and medical care . To keep these places working normally , visitors have to pay for the visit and this money is used to manage the zoo . Is it the best way to keep animals ? No , of course not , and I think everyone agrees with that , but on other hand , sometimes it is the only way to keep some species alive , because their environment no longer exists . It is so sad to see animals in a cage , as if they are guilty of something , but they 're not ! They just do not have more space to live . I know many people like going to zoos , taking pictures and having fun with different species of animals . For me it is not fun . I would like to see them in a natural environment if I could . To be honest , I think it is so wrong to keep wild animals in a zoo , but I know that there are many zoos that keep ill animals that ca not live alone . In that case , I think it is great , because those animals would die and they have a chance to live , even if it is not a perfect life . I know that we humans need to think about what we could we do to give some better living conditions for animals . 
