Dear Betty , I am writing to tell you about the concert I went to last week . Firstly , when I heard that Green Day were going to have a concert in my city , I knew I must go to it , because it has been my favourite band for many years . The concert was absolutely wonderful . I had the opportunity to see my idol , Billie Joe Armstrong , in the flesh . Plus , I had a seat in the first row . Can you believe it ? Being looked at directly into my eyes . For me it was more than a concert , it was a real experience . It was amazing to turn up the phone lights and to sing along with the crowd their most underrated songs , such as " 22 guns " or " Holiday . " I had so much fun and I hope that one day we will go together to one of their concerts . I am looking forward to hearing from you . Love , Bianca . 
In every country , there are many problems that have not been able to be solved . Requiring doctors in rural areas is a common problem today . Most medical doctors want to work in cities where they can make a lot of money . Yet , in many rural areas , there are not enough doctors . I think it is not only because of money , but because of accommodation and food . And they probably do not like the environment . In cities , everything is great like the internet connection , food and so on . Rural areas are very poor in everything in comparison to cities . So , most of the doctors do not want to spend time in rural areas . Moreover , as I mentioned above , they ca not make a great deal of money when they are in rural areas . For example , in developing countries , doctors tend to open clinics on the basis of their respective field . They make extra money by doing so . To solve this problem , the government should give doctors an incentive to work in rural areas . For instance , giving a pay rise or giving elite privileges to the doctors who work in rural areas might help solve this problem , I think . 
Hi Jack , It 's nice to hear from you . I hope you are very well . I prefer to stay at home with my family and to invite my friends . Mi mom cooks a dinner , usually traditional Mexican food . We listen to music and dance . Afterwards , we break a Piñata in the backyard . It is a lot of fun . Well , it 's time to say goodbye . Best regards , Sylvia 
The best holiday ever Last summer I went to the beach of Mazatlan with my family , my husband and my son , George and Junior . The first day we took a little time for ourselves , because we were very tired because of the trip . The following morning we went to the aquarium . We could see many aquatic species , such as little sharks , turtles , shalls , fish and an octopus that was isolated in a huge container . I had never seen these animals , I was surprised . After , we went to the restaurant and we ate seafood . We ate a dessert too , a little coup of cake with wine , it was a flavor explosion ! My son only ate the cake with milk . In the evening . we went to the edge of the beach and we saw baby turtles being born . It was beautiful , I did not believe it . We stayed for four days and we returned to our house . It was a great experience in my life . 
