The purpose of television Nowadays , a television is a tool for families to reduce stress or for entertainment . So , most people have an electronic gadget of this type in their houses . But the questions is , is it really necessary ? In ancient times , TV was not essential , because the technology was not as advanced as now . However , in these days , with the pandemic of covid -19 , the government has implemented some strategies for primary and secondary education . For the students that do not have Internet access , the topics of each group and area are transmitted on TV programs . So , in this case , television was helped to impart the classes . On the other hand , television is very important for entertainment , but the time should be suitable . For example , I like to watch TV series , but I do it when I have some free time . 
