In terms of learning English , why we should learn English and what the target of doing that is , I will illustrate three important points of learning English . Firstly , if you good at languages , you can study abroad . Also , you will be a privileged candidate for getting job opportunities . Secondly , you can communicate with foreign people around the world and protect yourself from scam processes . Moreover , you can enhance your ability to learn another language and make your life easier . Lastly , you can make a business by teaching this language to children and adults . The English language is considered the mother tongue in the vast majority of nations and global companies who are dealing in English because it is the easiest language to learn and teach . Now , I wrote this essay to evaluate my ability on the Write and Improve application and to see what I need to adjust in my mistakes and to improve my sentences . 
