Is there anyone who likes the rainy season out there ? If you love the rainy season , this article is for you , because I want to share my feelings about the rainy season in this article . It is the season I like the most . Maybe it is because I was born in that season . Nothing can make me happy more than seeing rain while having a cup of coffee inside of the house . It is so amazing , that I could forget everything at that moment . You ca not deny that the rainy season is very helpful to agriculture . The luxuriant vegetation is likely to grow with the help of the rain . The verdant surroundings make everyone feel peaceful when they take a look at them . On the other hand , some areas are flooded because of the heavy rain . And , of course , mud is the most disgusting thing in this season . Moreover , there may be some difficulties in transportation . But I still love the rainy season , as I feel warm when it is raining . You may think it is ridiculous . The sound of the rain can heal my soul . Therefore , it will be the most special season for me no matter what other people say about it . 
Hello . My name is Sam and I am 14 years old . Today , I am going to review an English website called Write and Improve . This website is published by Cambridge and most of the students do not know how good this website is . On this website , there are many levels for your writing skills so you choose your writing skill . Also there are many essays , letters , reports and review in one level . So you choose what you like . The writing levels are Beginner , Intermediate , Advanced , Business and Just for fun . Also there is IELTS General Training . You can save your writing by making a Cambridge account . This website also checks out writing skills and the website shows our skills with a graph . On the graph , there are many levels . Those levels were the same as Cambridge English . Like A1 , A2 , B1 , etc . Also they check our writing essays , letters , etc . If there are mistakes , they show them with a red line and they are also words entered in every essay and others . If you are not on the word entered in essay , you ca not submit your essay and the website wo not check it either . I used this website for 4 months and my writing skills level were improved . In the first essay , I got A2 level and , after 4 months , my level went to B2 . I think this website is for students ' writing skills . I recommend this website to every student . I hope this website is helpful to every student . Bye . 
First of all , I think that exercise is not only important for our physical health , but also contributes to having a better quality of life , due to when we work out we have more energy for our daily activities , we feel more relaxed and reduce our stress levels . However , there are other things that we can consider as important as exercise , there are even others that we consider more important . One instance of this could be learning a new language , which could represent an opportunity to develop a new skill , have more knowledge and be able to communicate with other people in our work and personal life . Also , we often consider it indispensable to learn a new language , in order to visit other countries , meet new people and get to know other cultures and traditions . Besides , it means an opportunity to enjoy a wonderful trip , which is one of my personal goals . Apart from that , I think our studies are really important for us as students and sometimes we dedicate more time to studying for tests than exercise , owing to what we learned during our years in university would be essential to have a successful future career . In addition , I would say that dedicating time to our family is also more important than exercise , so in order to drive this home , I think not only are our families our foundation and our support when we are feeling down , but also they are those who we can share our achievements and happiness with . Finally , I would say that indeed there are other things that have more priority over exercise , but that does not mean that we should be careless in that aspect . It just means that we would often make decisions about what to do with our time and our lives according to our priorities and what we want to achieve in the long term . 
Hi friend , I watched an amazing movie last night . It was called The Warriors , you should watch it . This movie is about a gang called The Warriors . This gang lives in New York , like many other gangs . One day , the biggest gang of the city sends a message . They want to get together with the other gangs at midnight in Central Park . Nine members of The Warriors attend this meeting . Suddenly , the leader of the big gang is murdered and in the confusion , the killer blames The Warriors , then all the gangs begin to chase The Warriors through the city . It 's an amazing movie . I really recommend it to you . 
It is a tricky question , because I think both can be done . If I had to choose , I would go for a short intense life . I cannot picture myself doing nothing over my entire life . What is the meaning of life when the only thing you do is to live , and do nothing that you enjoy . I am a bold person , I am a daredevil , as a result , I like to take risks , It is in my genes . I like rock climbing , running , I intend to do skydiving in the near future . I am even mindful that these activities are risky , I am nothing but a coward who runs away when he encounters risks . Admittedly , I am more likely to die , but it is when I am close to death that I am overwhelmed with my emotions that I feel the most alive . People who are not risk -takers will never set out projects or activities that would lead to failure , despair and disappointment . These people need to get over it and to push themselves beyond the line . I am not of this kind , I perceived my dreams and projects whether they are risky , bold , mindless or not , as long as I will relish the process to get it . I think a shorter life has much more meaning than a long and dull life when you keep slumping on the sofa while looking at the world going forward through your window . 
Today I choose as the topic an opinion essay on health or wealth . In my opinion , everybody says that health is more important than wealth , of course . But the reality is different . There is compulsory health insurance in Europe . When we are children the compulsory health insurance is paid by the Czech Republic , when we are 18 years old , we have to pay it ourselves . We have healthcare in each moment in the system of insurance . If someone has no job , he has to give evidence of unemployment . He gets a dose each month and the compulsory payments are paid by the Czech Republic . The second situation is in the USA . It is opposite . Healthcare is not for everybody . I can pay for health insurance , but I do not have to pay for it . If I am ill and I have to go to the doctor , I have to pay for all the injections and pills . 
The Future of Travel Nowadays , we are facing a new era in which the coronavirus has brought changes in our ways of doing things and one of them is the way we travel . So I think travel will be different in the future , starting with the quantity of people allowed to enter some places , such as museums , stadiums and parks . Besides , it will be likely that people will prefer to go to close places rather than far countries . On the top of that , I believe that technology and artificial intelligence are going to play an important role in traveling . One instance of this could be that now , thanks to them , there are going to be offered simulations of different trips to different countries , in which people will be able to experience a trip , hence they will have the opportunity to make a better decision of which places to visit . Apart from that , I think the way we transport and travel is going to change in the future , in view of technology advancing so much . I think there will be other kinds of airplanes and cars , which are also going to be cheaper and more accessible . On the other hand , I think there are many ways of traveling which might still be the same in the future , such as the routes of journeys . These routes wo not change , because they have been determined taking into account the preservation of the tourist places . In addition , I think travelers are going to still make reservations in hotels or hostels before arriving in another country and people will still prefer to eat out in the future rather than stay at home and cook . 
Oh , it is good to talk about holidays . Although I have not had so many holidays in my life , I could say that the holidays I had were great . But how do I write about the most important holiday I ever had in my life ? I think the most important for me was when I went on a honeymoon holiday . That was great because I went with my wife and we were just starting our life together and it was so fantastic having that time with her . We went to a beach located in the north of the state of Sao Paulo . We had already been married and for us it was all new , it was new being together and sharing our life with another person . It was the first time we went on a holiday alone , yes because it was not our first holiday together . When we were dating , we went on a holiday , but on that occasion we went with other people , her mother and father , her daughter and my son . That definitely was not a romantic holiday . I cannot say it was a terrible holiday because it was not , it was good . My father -in -law is a very good person . 
