There are those who prefer to live their own while they are attending school , and there are those who choose to live with their parents while they are students . The difference depends on the choice of personal decision . It is up to their consideration ranging from their financial situation to personal matters . To me , I think moving away and living on their own is a better choice if a student is able to choose whether to stay with family or live on their own . The reason is simple . It is time for them to take care of themselves . As a student , besides pursing an academic road , learning and adapting to a new environment is another aspect that students have to learn themselves . It is a place where students acquire social and living skills in a school environment . It is better to acquire it at an early stage instead of at the adult stage when they face even harsher challenges . 
Nowadays , most medical doctors want to work in cities to make a lot of money and find all that they need , like shops and markets or even governmental interests . This problem is not easy to be solved but the government should solve it quickly because of the adults and children who are sick and ca not work as a reason for illness . This problem needs many changes for it to be solved , it 's easy to find the solution but it 's difficult to create it . One of them is building good hospitals for doctors to work in . That is very important because it makes the doctor feel like if he is working in the city . It will also be more accurate and easy in treating patients . Second , there should be compounds where doctors live . The most important thing in the compound or the place where the doctors live is it should contain the main services like water , light , internet or even food stores . Last but not least are the governmental interests and the police , they are very important because no one will leave a safe city and go to an unsafe place . There should be offices for both , police and governmental interests . All in all , there should be doctors in rural areas and they need to find all that they need . 
Hello Billal , How are you doing ? I would like to tell you about a trip I went on last week with my classmates from college . We went to an old beer factory . We saw old and rare bottles of beer and we tried a new beer . I had the opportunity to try this new beer three times , I was sure that it would be really good , and guess what ? It was ! So I tried it again . In resume I liked this trip because you did not go with us , so I will need to go again , but now with you . 
During the history of human life , we have seen upper class parents sending their children to boarding school , but most of them stayed at home because they do not have enough money to send their children to boarding school . But why do parents send children to boarding school ? Because they want their children learn how to live independently . Students , who go to university to continue their education , move away from their families , and live in independently , have advantages and disadvantages . The most important results are : they learn how to deal with problems and solve them alone , they face problems that they have not encountered before and are forced to a find a solution to them , and this is very useful for their future . Of course , every student could not live on their own . Another important case is they learn how to deal with other people . Conclusion : life for students on their own is important for their future life , they learn how to deal problems and deal with other people . Therefore I suggest that every student , if they can , live on their own . 
What is the best office to work in ? From parents , friends , films , books or other sources I know two general types of office . The first one is when everyone is sitting in the same room and can communicate without e -mails or phones , but just by shouting or going to their neighbour . Such offices are useful for workers who have a group project because they need to exchange permanently in order to stay at the same level . But in my opinion , the second office design is better . Here , every one or two people together have their own room . At first , they can create their rooms like they want in order to have a suitable atmosphere . Another positive point about working alone is that you are not distracted by other people . I knew from school that working with a lot of people simultaneously is very difficult , because people speak about every topic except the task to be done . In summary , I think that working in the same building , so you can spend your luncheon with colleague , is good , but sharing a big office with 10 people is not efficient for your work . 
Nowadays , a lot of young adults , teenagers and school children are struggling with obesity symptoms . This is because most of them are sitting inside for the whole day and do not do enough sports activities . Because of this , it can be questioned if it is appropriate to force all the mentioned young people to do exercise activities at least three times a week . The first advantage for forcing students to exercise three times a week is to make sure that they are not behind their laptops or tablets at these moments . When teenagers are the whole day inside behind their screens , they do not move enough . As a result , the children develop not as many motor movements as they should do for their personal development . The second advantage is that children improve their unhealthy lifestyle . Since students eat too much unhealthy food and exercise too little , a lot of teenagers are almost diabetic patients or they show more often obesity symptoms than approximately thirty years ago . A disadvantage to forcing students is that not all people have the ability to pay contribution because they do not earn enough money or go for a sports activity that is far away because their parents do not have a car . For those poor families , the government has to pay for the sports lessons of these students if the state wants to force them to go . In summary , it is a good idea to force students to exercise more often so that young people can improve their lifestyles . For poor families , it is a necessary gift from the government and after that , also the children from those families are able to exercise more often . 
We humans have to work for a living . We need food to live and we need shelter to live comfortably . Consequently , we need money to some extent . However , money ca not solve one problem ; it ca not buy us happiness . In order to live peacefully , health plays a vital role in our daily life . It seems to me that health is more important than wealth . Do you ever ask yourself if you live to work or work to live ? For me , I work to live . Being healthy is a blessing : you can do anything you want and go anywhere you want . In other words , you ca not do whatever you would like to if you are not good in health . For example , supposing you are ill , you ca not go to school or work . You would have to stay at home until you are well . Besides , your mother would go out of her way and make time to take care of you . There would be nothing good for you . That 's why you have to stay healthy physically and mentally . It is essential not to forget that you are enough . We do not need to try to be wealthy like others . I am not saying that being wealthy is not good at all . As I mentioned above , we need money to live properly . I mean that we should not work desperately without taking good care of our health , which can lead to disorders . In fact , we will not be able to make money if we are unhealthy . To sum up , I strongly believe the idea that " health is wealth " . For the reasons I mentioned above , I personally believe that health is definitely more important than wealth . 
