With the development of globalization , the number of students who study aboard is increasing dramatically . 20 years ago there were only three main destination countries for most Chinese students to study aboard : Japan , the UK and the USA . Now Chinese students are dispersed everywhere . Besides the previous popular countries like Japan , the UK and the USA , other European countries such as Germany , France and Italy are also becoming popular for them . . There are actually advantages and disadvantages of studying abroad . Firstly , students who study aboard can experience a different culture and life and broaden their knowledge . Secondly , most students also want to improve their foreign languages . For instance , most Chinese students do not really speak English in their daily life . However , good English skills are a must in almost all working fields . Therefore , many students choose to study in the USA to improve their spoken English and get a better understanding of the western culture . Besides the advantages , there are still some drawbacks that one cannot ignore . Firstly , the cost for studying aboard is relatively high . For example , especially in the USA , the students are paying around 50,000 dollars per year . It is quite expensive for most students . Secondly , many students who study aboard cannot really adapt themselves to the new environment , they do not have many friends there and they always feel lonely . Thirdly , as far as I know , for example , many Chinese students are far too shy and are not good at accommodating themselves to the new culture and environment . Therefore , they only try to get in touch with other Chinese students and have very little chance to speak English or other foreign languages . As a result , many of them still cannot speak English fluently even after studying aboard . In general , studying aboard is a good chance to boost foreign language skills and experience a different lifestyle and culture . However , how much one will benefit from it varies from person to person . 
