I think that it is more important to learn or speak a foreign language compared to the past . First of all , these days , we can travel easily all over the world . It means , even though we do not go to other countries , we will meet or see other countries ' people , because they will visit our country . They do not know our country , so it might be they will ask some questions on the street , in stations or buildings . As that time , we should answer the question and help them , to give a good experience or memory in our country . Secondly , recently our working style has been changing , which means another country 's boss comes to our company or we communicate with other countries ' people or companies . Unless we speak other countries ' languages , it is difficult to get a good job or raise our position . For these reasons , I really believe that we should learn or speak other countries ' languages , which is more important than in the past . 
