My best holiday for me is in 2017 when I went to Germany . From 19th June to 19th July , I practiced in a food safety laboratory in Munich city . That was my first time living far away from my home . For one month , I traveled around Munich city and I had a chance to travel to Austria and The Czech Republic . This was a very good experience to see a lot of architecture from the Middle Ages . There are many beautiful and fascinating buildings in Munich , even though some of them were destroyed in World War II . I am interested in the history of World War II , so seeing and going to the real places in the war 's history was like my dream fulfilled . German people faced with a tough time after the end of the war . Most of the important places and people 's faith were devastated . Not many years later , the German government restored places , public facilities , the economy and technology and turned into one of the top 5 of European trade . I am impressed with Germany 's effort and unity in order to reunite their nation . This summer was my best holiday forever . 
