Television has a big responsibility in the world . It makes our culture and has a huge effect on people 's behaviour , beliefs and how they fill their free time . Television has some roles that will change the opinion of society . The majority of its fans are children and old people , because adults are always at work and have no free time to watch its programs . So it is essential that governments take notice of the kind of program . Education is a key role for television . It is easy to connect with all of the world and use their programs . We can educate children , make their future , give them good ideas and help them to progress , but instead of good and useful programs they show dangerous films . Television can change our habits . If we have free time , with the use of television , it will be a good time or may be a bad time . 
In recent years , more and more people join universities or colleges after graduating from senior high schools . However , university life is totally different from senior high school life or before that . According to the concern of living at home or not , my opinion is as follows . As for me , moving away and living on their own while attending university or college is a better choice than living at home . of student life , living outside can learn and acquire more skills and knowledge which you may not acquire at home . Before entering the workforce , undergraduates not only have to learn professional skills but social skills and the ability of self -care . Undergraduates can learn or acquire these competences quicker if they move away and live on their own . They need to do everything by themselves , such as go to classes , mop the floor , wash clothing , and so on . Therefore , living outside may teach more than living at home . 
Healthy living Regarding the question : Exercise is important for our health , but are there things that are more important , opinions among people are quite different , since each one has their own preference . For instance , I would like to say that money is more important for me than exercise , even if regular exercise is necessary to stay healthy . However , it does not mean that I do not do any exercise at all and health does not matter to me . Due to a stressful financial situation and high living expenses , I have no choice but to work hard to get more money to finance it . Therefore , compared to exercise , I will prioritize work . Nevertheless I usually do a Zumba workout every week to keep me fit , since if I am not fit and always sick , then I also cannot finish my tasks as planned . However , some may disagree with me . For them , health has absolutely the highest priority . Therefore , there is nothing else that is more important than exercise . And such people usually have a very good work -life balance . 
