I do not see any problem with being as old as the whole century . Maybe your health condition will annoy you sometimes , but from my perspective , I wo not have got this old until the time when all cars will hover in the air like balloons . I mean , health and medical services are surely going to be not only more accessible , but also better , faster , more precise and less painful . Imagine being a centenarian , but feeling like you 're in your mid sixties . I 'm not afraid of that . When these demands are fulfilled , I am inclining towards the first option . I simply like my pace , and peace . Maybe I used to be a bit ferocious , but how many people in their teenage years were not , hm ? There is no need to live your life intensely , without any sleep , practically surviving from day to day . In my humble opinion , settling down , eventually not moving a house much , having a good wife , husband or any other partner , maybe making some kids , having a stable and prospering job , Doing a stable and prospering job , simply fighting with life normally . You may enjoy the rush , adrenalin and joy of your short life , but it 's important to realize that any one of us can hide a great potential . In your later life , some people can contribute to this society so much and although some geniuses have died relatively young , they ca not be the majority . So , a shorter life can be a waste . All of this is only my opinion . Note this . 
I had a very important holiday when I was in my twenties . I went with my friends to Acapulco and it was the first trip without my parents and more important because my other friends and I did not ask permission . I saw one friend happier than the other , because he had never seen the sea before . We called our parents when we arrived in Acapulco , It was the best holiday that I have ever had because it was so different . I could go with my friends and we went around of gallants conquering girls , we walked on the beach and enjoyed drinking some beers . We did not have enough money , but it was not important . When we came back to our house after the trip , it was funny and when we go out to talk about the old days , we always remember this holiday and it is a great story that we tell our partners and friends . 
