The computer games ' industry has experienced huge success over the past two decades . Only very young people played them twenty years ago , but now it is a common form of entertainment . It has to be mentioned that not only young people play computer games , but also middle -aged and even sometimes the elderly . However , is it really safe to let your children play video games ? In my opinion , parents should check if a particular game is suitable for their children . It is easy to find a game with a lot of violence or improper content that should not be displayed to children . On the other hand , some of the games may have a very positive impact on children . They develop creativity . I believe that playing games may be more beneficial than watching TV programmes . I think that games producers should clearly categorize their games , so it is not difficult to decide if it is proper for children . 
Zoos are places that have existed since a long time ago . However , new thinking and reflection about a lot of usual space of society asks questions that may change the relationship in this \ animal 's house \ . For a long time , the humans have seen themselves as the center of the ecosystem . New studies and other forms of reports on men and women 's equality as part of nature , but everybody thinks that was good for some animals to stay in jail for someone 's entertainment . When we look in more depth at conditions for animals in zoos , it is possible to see that the majority of animals are badly treated . The reflection changes the financial structure and makes more claims for places that decided to continue as zoos . Then , it improved , in general , for animals ' conditions , in animal life and usually the spaces are created to gather more information and care for animals that had some accident . It ' s possible to say that , if they have good management where animals ' better conditions is the priority interest , keeping the animals is good for the society and me too . 
There seems to be a divide between school having students not take any music class and schools forcing students to study and learn to play a musical instrument . Given such a division , it seems plausible that we should let students choose depending on whether he or she likes music . Surely , there is a scientific fact that music can develop students ' ability in the aspect of imagination and perception . Besides focusing on academic studies , music can relieve students ' pressure and have a fair judgement . However , it is not always true that every student has the interest in studying and learning music . Involving music as a must requirement at school could increase students ' burden in studying , and therefore , it could affect his or her academic performance in other subjects . Whether he or she likes music or not , the choice should be up to student 's preference instead of forcing them to choose what to study or what to learn . Otherwise , it could have a negative impact on students ' development . 
The video game is , perhaps , the most famous electronic toy for the new generations . They started the trajectory of controversy among the millennials , people that were born between 1980 and 1993 , but the first results of the after -effects can be seen and interpreted in the following . There are not any questions about the importance of contact like games for the development of human intelligence . There are more questions about when this could happen . Usually , kids get in contact with video games very early , between one or two years old , which has been delaying the learning of skills , like communication and interaction . However , it is possible to see there has been a development in skills for the new electronic life , like the ease of use of a cellphone and other electronic devices , beyond the English language for children that live with other languages . There are two questions to answer : " When is the best moment or correct time to start the use ? " and " How many hours is good for less negative consequences ? " Unfortunately , there are not exact answers . The recommendation is a general balance between a lot of skills that children need to develop in the use of technology , like videos games , and the ability to work in a group , write , movement , etc . 
I think " The Future of Travel " should be Eco -Tourism . A tourist produces a carbon footprint which affects the environment every year , so people must be concerned about this effect . The carbon footprint comes from travelling and waste , so Eco -Tourism is one of the options that any tourist can choose in order to preserve any place they have been to . Wherever you go , you should help and keep those places clean , you should help and keep those places be clean like the same . For example , a lot of litter from tourism causes problems in local areas . Moreover , animals , native people and the surroundings are affected by the smell and sore sights . For this reason , travellers have to look after the things around them and support the local people to cultivate a consciousness of loving their hometowns . If other people pay attention to tourist attractions , the inhabitants will love and cherish their habitats . It is good for everyone who wants to travel to any place and have a valuable attitude about saving the environment . Sustainability of the surroundings is the sustainability of travel too . 
What places do you usually go to for a holiday ? My family usually go to a nearby forest for a holiday . I cannot understand why they always go to forests for a holiday . But the holiday we went on last week was amazing . We went to a forest as usual . But this forest was very different from the previous ones we had been to . It was the best holiday I have ever had . There were loads of lakes for us to swim in and they even had horses . I love horse riding , but my favourite thing about the holiday was the cabins we stayed in . It was like being in a tree house and we got to stay up late and eat chocolate and drink soda . There were some kinds of animals in the forest . I saw a rabbit , peacock , monkey and some kinds of birds . Some people took their dogs and played with them around their tents . The moment I looked at them playing with the dogs , I thought to myself that I should have a dog , because they are so cute . And at night , we played truth or dare . I love this game , because it is so funny , especially the dares . I always choose dares whenever I play this game , as I do not want anyone to know my secrets . While we were playing , some people in the next cabin joined us . And the game was much more fun than before . We got to know each other and I made new friends . That 's why it was the best holiday I have ever had . In conclusion , this holiday amazingly raised my spirit . I hope I can go on such a holiday again . 
