When I was younger , I loved to have the same teacher for several years . I believe that it helped me to get better when I had to answer some questions , so I got more confident . But I believe that changing teachers for the following years could help to build our perspective about life . Further , we 're able to develop our connections between people , we 're able to feel what other people feel too . I 'm trying to look for words to express my mind , but knowing what other people feel is really important to the development of a society . So , creating new connections between people can change the world . Sometimes I got upset or uncomfortable with the new teacher , but it 's an important thing that has to happen or exist in somebody 's life . Further , it develops our abilities of communication and it supports in the development of our point of view . Every person has their personality and working with different personalities can solve our problems with each other . If I had not changed teachers , maybe I would not have been able to work on my abilities with other people . 
My personal opinion is that you should save your body from diseases and nourish your mind by reading , and eating some particular food , for example , blueberries , nuts . And we should move our body and eat healthy food . The important thing is to maintain relationships with people in order to maintain psychological health . Then , for my personal exercise , I am eager to walk and sniff the air . Additionally , I believe we should follow a specfic system to save our body , spirit and mind . Plus the important thing is not to forget to earn money in order to help your parents because it is your duty to your parents . Plus , travel and meditation on nature and different circumstances with people like this thing make you more mature , in addition to arranging your priorities . And an important thing is to sit with your children and play with them . Do not give up your hobbies . For instance , shooting , swimming and horse riding . 
In my free time , I watch TV , I read books , I work out , I walk , I cook and sometimes , I do nothing . But , I do not often have time to enjoy my free time . In fact , as I work , my free time is short . I try to find some once a day , but it 's difficult . I like feeling relaxed , without thinking about daily life , only thinking about myself . I guess free time is a necessity for everyone . It allows us to rest and my mind to escape . So , the last time when I enjoyed some free time was yesterday . 
My favorite movie is The Notebook . It 's a story about a young girl and boy who fall in love during spring break . The girl is from a rich family and the boy lives in the countryside . They have an amazing summer together and despite their differences , they make it work . When she goes back home , they promise to write each other letters . The story is being told by the man in his eighties . She has dementia . He reads their story to her every day . In the end , they die together . The movie is a bit cheesy , but it 's a great love story . You can feel their emotions . It will bring you some tears , but also a lot of happiness . 
Music surrounds human life . Besides , music is a magic thing because listening to music and playing musical instruments can change our mind . However , is everyone familiar with music or does everyone need to know about it ? My answer is yes . In Taiwan , we have music classes during the basic education period , so everyone has basic knowledge about music . But why should we study music ? Like I said , music is a magic thing . Although there are many kinds of music , such as classical , pop , jazz , bossa nova , and so on , it can always lead us to a different mood . In my mind , " music " is one of the greatest ways to release pressure . Through singing songs , listening to music , we may feel happier and immerse ourselves in relaxed atmosphere . Besides , there is a saying in Chinese -- Children who study music wo not go bad . The study proved that the kids who study music have higher stable emotions , concentration and lower nervousness . Studying music has a lot of benefits and without any cons . Let 's everyone get to know more about music . People may find changes in themselves . 
Learning a foreign language is more important now than ever . This is because the world is now more connected . Everywhere you go , online or physically , you can meet someone who does not speak your language . Learning English can help you a lot . Almost everywhere there is someone who speaks English . This way , you can communicate everywhere you go . However , there are some places where people refuse to learn English . These are countries like France and Spain . Both languages are being spoken in other countries . So it also can be quite handy to learn French or Spanish . Besides those three languages , another upcoming language in Mandarin . Mandarin is one of the most spoken languages in the world . The reason for this is because there are billions of Chinese people in the world . They travel around the world , but you also see them a lot in the Business World . So my advice is to certainly learn English and choose French , Spanish or Mandarin as an extra language . 
I do not think there is a better choice whenether you go live or your own of live with your family while being a student . I think it depends on your needs and satisfactions . Currently , I am a student . I still live at my parents . However , if it were possible , I would like on my own . Unfortunately , living on your own can be quite expensive . This is the reason why I still live at my parents ' , it is way cheaper than living on my own . Some students prefer living on their own and choose to borrow money . However , they do not only have to borrow money to pay their rent , but also for grocery , gas , water , electricity , etcetera . When you live on your own , you have more freedom . You do not have to think about somebody else . You can eat whenever you like , listen to music whenever you want or watch a Netflix show you like . You ca not do all these things when you still live with your parents . However , I do not want to have a debt . So my preference is to still live with my parents and move out as soon as I have a job . 
Some people think that it is better to live a long and stable life while others prefer to have a short and happening life . I believe that it is important to be peaceful and friendly because it allows you to pass your traditions on to the next generation and also stay close to your family members . To begin with , although people prefer to live short and intense life , I believe a long calm life has many advantages . One of them is that it allows you to have spare time , which can be spent with your family members . In other words , they can take care of their loved ones and help them to become successful and healthy people . This means if they spend more time with family members , they get so close that they start enjoying their life to the maximum . For example , in 2002 , Oxford University conducted a survey among people who live with family members and separate , and they found that individuals who have with their families are much happier than the other people . 
When we want to describe a person , we use some words like honest , loyal , kind , aggressive , liar and so on , some of them are positive and some of them are negative . In my opinion , the worth of each person can be explained by his/her behaviour . I hate lying people and think everybody has to be honest . We had a lesson in school whose name was cry wolf . I liked that lesson because we could see some people in our society who are not honest and they say that our lie is a white lie . I could not accept this word . A lie is a lie and it does not change with its size . I would rather say truth and punish because when we say one lie , we have to say other lies to bring reasons for our works . Some people think that the goal can justify the facility and means , but I disagree with this sentence . In the world , from the north to the south and the east to the west , a lie is a lie and lying people are not acceptable among other people . Parents are a symbol for their children . A lying parent could not demand an honest child . Sometimes , the leaders and politicians do not say truth but do not tell a lie . Imagine a bad condition like a war or . 
I 've used this program since last year . I 'm grateful for this program existing and coming into in my life . I love Write & Improve because it has specific subjects and specific levels . For example , I 'm an English Beginner student and I 'm able to develop my writing abilities in this program . I may see my mistakes and errors and this program shows me where I am wrong and what 's wrong with my text . Furthermore , I have used this program to evaluate my development on Inamara 's English course and so far I have been able to improve my English level . So far I 've kept up a level B1 in English . It has kept me up at the top of the class . I think it 's fantastic . I 'm so thankful for this program . By the way , I have recommended this program to my colleagues from the English course and I gave it as a suggestion for improving the English course . I 'm so excited about this program existing in my life . It has changed my life and my English lessons . 
