I have several reasons why it 's important for me to learn English . First , after I graduate , I want to study further . I want to follow a Master 's in Marketing Management which is completely in English . One of the requirements is to have an advanced level in English and prove this with a certificate . Therefore I will do an English exam on December third . Not only is it important to learn English in order to succeed in my test , it 's also important during my master 's . During the master 's you have to write essays , so therefore my English also has to be good . Besides my reasons for learning English for my master 's , I also want to travel a lot around the world . Therefore , it would be very useful if I spoke English fluently . I am worried that I will be in a strange country . If I can communicate well , I am reassured that it will be fine . 
Nowadays , there are a lot of ways to learn on the internet , such as Cake , etc . Many of them are fake , but there are good applications and websites that help you learn in an academic way . I usually search for good ones that I could recommend to young or advanced learners . One of the most helpful websites that I found is Write&Improve . This is a page which you can visit from Google . To start writing on it , first , click sign in , then create an account and , then start writing the tasks that you like to know your accurate level . One of the rare advantages that you could rarely find is that it gives you the mistake and lets you correct it by yourself . Write&Improve has many things , such as a level for beginner , intermediate or advanced people , and it can also train people who are preparing for the IELTS exam in the two kinds of writing . It also has an section called " Just For Fun , " this section has story tasks like this one : if you found a box that does not belong to you but it has your name on it , what would you do with it ? All in all , Write&Improve is a spectacular website to practise on , furthermore you will have a great future in writing essays and paragraphs . 
There are many means of transport which have been used for generations , but they are becoming obsolete and being replaced by technological advances . I strongly believe that public transport and more environmentally friendly vehicles will be used poluparly in the future , because these new technologies help mankind to cope with problems related to the environment , climate change and the growth of the population . Firstly , using public transport is beneficial for both the environment and the economic situation of people . For example , buses can carry a large group of people at the same time , which reduces the number of vehicles on the street . This will also decrease the carbon emissions significantly . Also , bus tickets are quite cheap compared to gasoline prices . In addition , this means of transport also helps resolve traffic congestion , which will save time for many people . Secondly , the development of technology also affects how people travel . Batteries are now more efficient than in the past . There are many cars which use electricity instead of fossil fuel . People have realized how severe climate change is , so they will use electric vehicles to travel rather than classic ones to protect the environment . 
