Most countries all over the world use television . It has a lot of uses in many different types of work , such as education , public health , economics and entertainment . Television can be for education or entertainment . For example , in schools , teachers use television to show educational programs to students . Also , in cinemas , they use television to show movies . People have a choice to pick what they want from a wide range of uses . It makes many complicated things easier than in the past . For example , children can teach themselves with television . Teachers use television to show difficult experiments to students instead of applying them . However , parents can also use television to show entertaining programs to their sons and daughters to make them silent , so that allows the parents to accomplish many tasks . In my view , all of us need television these days because it has more benefits or uses , so it depends on our choices with it . 
Thinking about how to live is one of the most interesting subjects for human beings . While some desire to have a long life span , in my opinion , it is more exciting to live an adventurous life . The main reason to choose a short but intense life is that living in a severe situation can motivate people to live more productively . It means having a calm condition can be boring after a while and you will stop making a plan for the future . For example , for a few years , I experienced a situation which was without any problems , but after a while , I realized that I did not any any useful work for my future . What is more , facing challenges and new things can open our horizon and improve our way of thinking . According to a survey from Oxford University , living in a tough condition can develop the creativity of people . For instance , there are some examples of famous individuals in the world who have had worse conditions in their early life , but could pass that life and become popular . Having said that , human beings like trying immortality to see the future . As a result , some prefer living calm and long to face unknown events . I think , this excuse cannot be enough to forget about endeavouring new changes . In conclusion , although some prefer having a long life without any troubles , from my view , a short life but full of new experiences is more enthusiastic for people . 
