It 's unfortunate that some doctors will only work in hospitals where they earn a lot of money . I think I know the reason why . A lot of young people want to become a doctor . When they have good grades , they go to medical school and study for years . The workload during their studies is high , which is the reason why most medical students does not have a side job . Because of this reason , students will borrow money from the government . Because medical school is a long trial , it takes years before they can pay back their loan . I think there is a way how this problem can be solved . During medical school , there are some internships . Currently , students do not get paid during their internship . If hospitals pay these young doctors , they wo not have to borrow from the government anymore . This way , when they 're studying , they do not have to work hard to get their loan paid of . 
