In this techno -savvy world , everything is possible , whether it is education on television or entertainment . However , education plays a crucial role in this modern era , and the media has a lot of influence in people 's lives . For the last two decades , people 's way of watching television has been changing . They prefer to watch television to acquire knowledge . First , grabbing knowledge through television would be a good way , which helps those people who have no time to go to school or live in a suburban area . In order to popularize education on television , more and more programmes about learning are presented . For instance , when I was a child , I used to watch more television and there were many phonetic songs from which I learned many basic things and also good manners . Moreover , television is preferred by every age group . It provides us with a lot of information . There are many channels , such as National Geographic and Discovery Channel , through which we get to know about nature more specifically and can know how to survive in the wild . There are many cookery shows from which I learned to cook delicious meals at home . I believe television has the potential to educate us , furthermore the internet is an excellent way to reach education . We get to control when and what to learn about . 
I think all students should have to study music because of all the advantages and benefits it brings about . Besides studying music is a great opportunity to develop skills and qualities in students . First of all , I want to bring home some of the benefits of learning to play a musical instrument . The first one is the development of creativity and the use of the left hemisphere of the brain of students , for which , as a consequence , they can have success in other activities at school . Besides , another benefit of studying music is that it can make people feel relaxed and focused . According to some studies , people who play or study music can reduce the rate of stress in their lives and can release good hormones , like serotonin and dopamine , which makes them feel happier and have a better wellness . Apart from that , music is a way to express ideas , feelings and thoughts , hence it contributes to improve emotional intelligence in students , which means an amazing advantage for the students ' future in their relationships , self -esteem , empathy as well as self -control . Furthermore , when students learn about music , they can communicate with other people no matter where they are from , because music is a universal language . On the other side , there are so many people who do not have the opportunity to study music or learn to play musical instrument , like the piano , guitar , violin or ukelele , even when they desire it and they dream with it , so if schools can teach them about music and how to play a musical instrument , this can be a chance for the students to dedicate their lives to music and , in the future , they could likely be excellent and renowned artists . Finally , I would like to say that learning to play a musical instrument and studying music are not only two ways to promote creativity and art in the students , but also music is a way to share feelings and thoughts , a way to connect with many people from different places with different languages . 
What will your school become in the year 2100 ? At that time , perhaps I will be so old , but my school will be newer and more modern than now . I think it will have many big buildings replacing the little and old structure at the moment . The gate will be so impressive , with the school 's name , which will be written in red . And I guess that the trees in the school 's garden will be so tall and with more branches than today , so the atmosphere will probably be more comfortable and cool . But I think there are things that wo not change , such as my school 's uniform , which includes a white T -shirt , a blue skirt for girls or blue trousers for boys and especially there is a red tie for everyone . And another thing that I think will be retained is the studiousness of the students and the dedication of the teachers in my school . I also think that the school will become the best school in my city at that time . I am certain of that and I am proud of it . 
My favorite film is The Lord of the Rings . The main story is about the journey of Frodo . A young Hobbit , known as Frodo , has been thrown into an amazing adventure , when he is appointed the job of destroying the One Ring , which was created by the Dark Lord Sauron . He is assigned three warriors , including Gandalf , Aragorn and Boromir . But it 's not going to be an easy journey for the fellowship of the ring , on the ultimate quest to rid Middle -Earth of all evil . The story is so amazing and so is the film . If someone wants to watch a nice fantasy adventure movie , I would like to recommend it . 
A few weeks ago , I started to use Write and Improve . This is a website where you can practice your English writing skills . The main feature is that it checks your writing immediately . The computer gives feedback about how much you wrote about the topic , how your sentences are and corrects some incorrect words . With yellow marks , it says where you need to improve . For me , the usage of this website is very helpful . I started two weeks ago and have already improved my writing skills . Within each essay you write , it says at what level you are . So you can track your own growth . I need to achieve a level of Advanced English , so for me , the notification of which level your are at is the thing I like the most . However , I also like the diverse subjects you can choose to write about . On the other hand , there is one thing I 'm not so positive about . Sometimes , the computer says you need to improve a sentence . But , it does not says where or how . I found this very difficult . Overall , I do like the website and it does help you improve your English writing skills . Therefore , I would recommend this website to everyone who wants to achieve an English Certificate . Recommendation . 
Studying abroad has became very popular among students in Europe . The results of a survey conducted by Cambridge University show that the experience of most of the students who went abroad was positive . But , are there really no disadvantages ? Firstly , I will discuss the pros of studying abroad . For sure , students who decide to study in another country are able to experience living in a different culture . It may open them to other points of view . Secondly , students who are usually not wealthy can visit new places and not pay a huge amount of money for that . They can also make new friends with people with whom they would not normally meet . But , for some students , it may be very difficult to find in new environment . For example , it would be hard to adapt for an Iranian citizen in some of Western Europe 's big cities . Another thing is that the level of education is very different among European countries . So , for some students , it is better to stay in their country where this level is comparably high . To summarize , I believe that studying abroad is beneficial for students . They should apply to go abroad if they only have a chance . 
To start with , most of the time , it 's not a good idea to tell a lie . However , there are some cases where telling a lie is fine . In the Netherlands , we have a holiday called Sinterklaas . Each year , on December 5th , an old man visits the country . He gives presents to children and spreads candy . However , the old man does not really exist . It 's the parents who hire a man in a costume and buy the presents . The things the children believe are a lie . However , in this case , the lie brings happiness with it . It makes people believe in something , something exciting . On occasions like Sinterklaas , it 's okay to tell a lie . However , in most other scenarios , it 's not okay . It 's not okay when young adults lie to their parents about where they 're going . In addition , it 's also not fair to lie to your partner . When people tell a lie , they do not consider the consequences . When people find the truth , most of the time , the lie will upset them . It is not a nice feeling knowing someone is lying to you . For example , when your partner is secretly texting with another woman . You often find him texting on his phone . You confront him , ask the question why he is on his phone that much . Do you want him to tell the truth or do you want to live in a lie and find out later ? I think you know the answer . So my advice , when telling a lie , think about the other 's feelings . Would they become happy not knowing or is it better to tell them ? 
Hi Jack , I am grateful to you for taking care of my house while I am on holiday . Do not forget the house keys in the exterior door because in our area there are many thieves walking around . You should water my plants every other day and give meat and water to the dogs every day . And lastly , you should control the mail box once a week . Thanks for everything . 
Thank you for recommending this awesome Write and Improve website . I have been using Write and Improve to practice writing English for two weeks and it is amazing . It helps me to improve not only my writing skill , but also other skills , such as reading and critical thinking . I can see that my English writing skill has improved within the two weeks . I like using Write and Improve because it is an interactive website and I can see all the mistakes after submitting the tasks . But there are cons as well , such as this website has a limited grammar and sentence structure . It is a problem for me sometimes . It would be very nice if they created something to practice speaking as well . I will recommend all my classmates to try this Write and Improve . I am confident that they would love it . 
I strongly believe that having several teachers is better than having one teacher for several years . In ancient times , a lot of people went to one rector to learn so many subjects . That was good enough for them , because there were not many subjects . However there are cons to that , because one person could not be an expert in all subjects . There are a lot of limitations to that , as those people would only learn what their rector knew . Nowadays , most of the universities have more than one rector to teach and train the students . Students would learn different experiences and knowledge if they have many teachers . Some universities have even more than one teacher for single subject , so that they can concentrate on a specific part to be more proficient in that area . In conclusion , students nowadays can be better than their teachers , because they could learn different skills from their respective teachers . 
Hi Ana , I am an academician . I read many scientific articles which are written in the English language . In addition , English is the most common language in the world . If you can speak English , you can go anywhere you want in the world because everywhere you can find a person who can speak English and they can help you . 
My home city is Konya . Konya is a Turkish city near Ankara , which is the capital of Turkey . Konya is a historical city . It has a lot of historical mosques , museums and churches . It has several big malls . In addition , it has a historical bazaar which is named " Bedesten " and which is also nice . 
I absolutely agree with this decision . Around the world , young people are making their future and their health is one of the most important problems . I mentioned the health of young people but what I mean is not just their physical health but also their mental health . For that reason , I emphasize sport . The majority of students at universities are 18-25 . This circle is the most important time of everyone 's life . Students at universities are teaching , but I think studying is one of the parts of their responsibilities . They have to improve other abilities because , in real life , when they graduate , they will enter the real world and probably they will have to face some problems . So I emphasize on sport because sport makes a person strong and it can decrease her/his stress . When universities force to do sport , it is just for students because the lifestyle of most of them is inactive . They spend most of their time back of the computers . Their movement and activity is at minimal degree . Unfortunately , technology and science have prepared a comfortable life for us , but they come down our activities . Some people need to force them to do something . In my opinion , sport can act like a inspiring thing and it can reassure students that there are some difficulties in their life . Today 's metropolises have complex huge difficulties that directly effect their lifestyle . Modern life is not good in all aspects . It warns people about the bad affects of the wavy sea . I think we can see the reflection of sport when facing hazardous positions . Athletes are stronger and anxious . At the end , I believe that sport for young people is like water for trees . 
There are pros and cons when it comes to having the same teacher for a longer time or a different teacher . Most of all , the most significant thing is to find a good teacher with an appropriate approach and effective teaching methods which work in our case . If you find someone like that , you should stick with this person , because it does not happen very often . All of us have a mixture of traits and our personalities mainly differ from each other . This is what , in a special way , makes us feel good or bad when interacting with others . Instructors with whom we cooperate during the learning process are also those who can attract or repulse others . So when you run into someone who does not posses the qualities which are compatible with your own , it can be a disaster . It is not the main factor which can discourage you from the subject , but also make you discontent with your life overall . So dealing with a variety of instructors gives you a chance to come across the right person for you . 
Some people claim that exercise and staying fit is the most important thing in our lives . Is this really true ? Or maybe we are exaggerating its importance . I will try to answer these questions in the essay below . There are plenty of benefits of exercising . First of all , staying fit improves both your mental and physical health . The results of some research conducted by Cambridge University clearly show that even twenty minutes of walking can prevent some serious diseases . Secondly , sport may become your new hobby . It 's always better than staying at home and playing computer games . Moreover , you can meet new people if you start doing a team sport like football or basketball . Are there more important matters in our lives than exercising ? Of course there are . I can easily think of several , for example providing money for your family , finding true love or staying in touch with your friends . However , in my opinion , finding 30 minutes a day to run or exercise with a You Tube video is not a big problem and the benefits are undeniable . 
My favorite film is Central İntelligence . Why do I advise this movie for you ? Because this film is very funny and cheerful . The leading roles are Dwayne Johnson and Kevin Hart . The subject of the movie is , there are two friends in high school , Jack and Robby . One is very successful but the other is unsuccessful . They meet 20 years after finishing school . And they get into trouble . After they have many adventures and more . You should watch it , you will not regret it . I have watched it a lot of times . When I watch again , I am really happy . After watching it , send me a message about your comments . 
Today , our modern world comes face to face with a hazard . What is it ? Video games . Are video games a danger or not ? What is my opinion ? What do l think ? I believe that this is not just my opinion , moreover it is a problem for the whole world . Why ? Why are video games a problem ? Video games are trouble because children are playing games for approximately five to ten hours each day . Sometimes children fall asleep in front of the game . They fight with their families to play video games . Moreover they hold to the behaviour . They do not go to school or eat something . Yes , video games are detrimental for children . However , they have some upsides when children check themselves . For example , video games improve our perceptions and develop our minds . But we must take heed of them . Consequently , as much as video games have some advantages , we can lose command of our children , therefore we must be careful . 
Music is considered in several ways by people . There are different considerations about it . Some believe that music is important in our life and , in addition to that , it has a healthy effect on our body . Some scientific studies stated that music may be a useful strategy and therapy , from the medical point of view . It is helpful in surgeries and more . By the way , just some weeks ago , this experiment was made by a surgeon in a famous American hospital . He played a piano while he was getting surgery ! What an incredible experience ! Probably , this medical approach will be adopted by several hospitals in the world . Music is very often associated to something done during leisure time . However , there are many schools in which music lessons are taught . In particular , students learn to play musical instruments and not only that . In fact , they study the history of music , its origins and the most relevant musicians of the past . It is very important because whatever is known up to now is basically related to these artists . However , there are some who believe that music and music schools are not so important for our society . In this sense , many schools prefer to not teach music like other subjects as well . Furthermore , music is defined as a simple pastime , useless . In my personal opinion , I believe that music is important and it should be taught in every school . Music is a universal language , which links to each other . Thanks to it , the world is ' coloured ' , cheerful and beautiful . Otherwise , we would live in a grey and sad world . 
Nowadays , most of the population lives in cities , either small or big ones , and due to that , villages and towns are starting to disappear , which leads to several problems such as the lack of medical service . Firstly , it has been asserted that medicine is one of the most elected and best rewarded jobs , and it is important to take into consideration that this degree can only be studied in a city , so that is the prime reason why most medical doctors choose to live in a city rather than a town . Furthermore , salaries are a crucial issue to have in mind when talking about that problem , since it is well -known that city jobs are way better paid than small town jobs . Although it is a severe problem , it seems that no solutions are given by governments or town councils , when for some of them , it could be as simple as raising salaries and offering more advantages to people specialised in medicine , so they can find convenient it moving from a city to a town . Besides , if that problem was more shown and stressed by governments or social media , it would spread more , and more people would know about it , instead of ignoring it like most of them do . In conclusion , the lack of medical services in towns is an important problem to tackle since people in towns need medical assistance as much as people from cities do , and with a little concern and solidarity , it could be very easy to solve . 
Hi Josh , Thank you for your last letter . How are you ? I hope you 're well . As you know , last year we could not attend any music events because of the global pandemic . Fortunately , we were all vaccinated in January and everything has been going back to normal . That 's why yesterday I decided to go to a Madonna concert . I am a big fan of hers and I had always wanted to see her live . The tickets were absurdly expensive , but it was good value for money - she was brilliant . Unfortunately . during the concert , some guy insulted my girlfriend and I had to fight with him . Please do not worry - I 'm all right . The doctor said that I will be able to leave the hospital in a few weeks . So , we 'll see each other at your birthday party ! See you soon , Kenny 
Being a doctor is an extremely prestigious and recognizable career , but there is not an easy way to achieve this . One , who is really interested in a subject , needs to be ready to sacrifice a part of one 's youth to study and memorize difficult definitions . So after graduation and a couple years of placement , a new doctor would like to find a place to thrive and to gain vast experience and sufficient training so as to have a high opinion and obtain the needed knowledge and necessary expertise for his job . It is known that small hospitals in little towns are not as well subsidised as in big cities . Cities give far better opportunities to achieve a remarkable success in your job in healthcare . A huge hospital with highly qualified staff and modern , even ground -breaking , tools and advanced devices gives a chance for improving your skills and broadening your horizons as a professional doctor . Among experienced adroit colleagues , you can improve your medical abilities . 
Office designs play a huge role in company culture . The type of layout can dictate your employees ' satisfaction level , attitude and organisation . Although , open offices are believed to encourage better communication and teamwork , offices with cubicles have their own individual working areas , which provide privacy to the employees . I think closed offices are better in the workplace rather than open offices . NA , . usually employees work in the same room , often beside each other , while seated along a huge desk or on workstations positioned close together . Firstly , open offices are cost -friendly when it comes to financial aspects , it is without a doubt that an open office layout is much cheaper and practical compared to a closed office . For instance , companies do not need to buy a lot of furniture . Moreover , an open office keeps people accountable and productive , as there is a motivating force in knowing that anyone can see what you 're doing . Open office naysayers argue that with all eyes on you , you are less likely to interact with your colleagues . On the other hand , segmented private offices are the best if you want privacy among your employees . are better for working productively because they prevent too much noise . For instance , if you have employees working on tasks that require concentration and a quiet space , then private panels are the best option . Furthermore , employees can also personalize their cubicles by hanging family photos or memorabilia that will inspire them to work better . Closed cabin offices are better used for companies with jobs that require quiet working areas , such as law firms , accounting agencies and other businesses in the financial sector . To conclude , I believe the best solution is to create cubicles . Unlike open offices , closed offices help minimise distraction allowing employees to work better and produce quality results . 
Although there are many doctors who serve in rural areas , most doctors prefer working in cities for some reasons . I will explore some of them , which deserve some comments here , and make some suggestions . First and foremost , doctors ' choices concerning work places depend on certain criteria , such as financial and social ones . Thus , to select where to work is a normal process not only for doctors but also for other professionals . Needless to say that everybody has a right to make a choice in order to have a better life . Secondly , based on the recent statistics , almost all people would rather have jobs at which they can make good money . For instance , I was introduced to a girl who had not earned well . And then , she decided to change her life and jumped to another well -paid job . Now she smiles and enjoys life much more than in the past . Money is not everything but something which is important . Thirdly , job vacancies at medical services in rural areas should be controlled by the government . That 's to say , national authorities cannot disregard the situation of health services there . Being healthy has a vital importance . In a nutshell , provided that the problem of unfound doctors in rural areas can be solved by authorities , citizens who fall there have an opportunity to go to doctors when in need . 
Hi my teacher , I want to study Arabic alongside English . I am a Muslim and I want to understand The Holy Quran . I would like to begin immediately . I have spare time recently and I want to use it beneficially . Would you like to help me with Arabic ? I am delighted with your teaching of English . 
My favorite season of the year is spring . Summer is too hot for me and autumn is too cold and windy . I would like winter - even though it is cold - if there was at least some snow . Spring is cold at the beginning , but it changes to warm and sunny days . Some years it rains a lot , but I like the rain too . It is great . Everything wakes and starts to grow - nature turns green again . Everything is fresh and new . I think the weather is perfect and it is special to me , because it is a great change after the cold winter and the hot summer . It is the perfect time for long walks in the forest . I also like to look at the flowers that have started to grow or the new leaves or needles in the case of the larch . 
Getting a high quality education is important for every child , because education is the only key to get out of poverty and to build a strong nation and country . For those reasons , people like to study in a good university to get the best jobs after graduating from the university . There is no high quality university in my country , because our country is poor . For those reasons , studying abroad is common in our country for rich people . There are advantages and disadvantages in studying abroad . It will cost around 3000 dollars per year to study abroad . You will feel homesick sometimes . But after graduating from a foreign university , your life is almost secure , because the demand for foreign degree holders is very high in our country . You can also expect a high salary and high position as well . However , there are also a lot of people in a high position who graduated locally . That 's why getting a high quality education is important for students , whether they study locally or at a foreign school . 
Hello teacher ! The schools are opening soon . We are excited to meet you . We had a great year and I am excited about the coming year . I am interested in Geography , Biography , Math and Physics . I love learning those subjects . I have always got high scores in those subjects because I am good at those . I am not interested in learning Chemistry and English , but I need to get high scores for those subjects as well . I will pass the matriculation exam only if I pass all those subjects . That 's why I need to improve in those subjects . I believe you can help me , because you are the best teacher I know . I also have a plan to improve those subjects . I will take extra classes for those subjects . I will do homework every day and study harder in those subjects . I believe that I will pass the exam with the highest score . 
Banning the use of mobile phones is a good idea , but it is not a good idea in every place . The council is thinking about three places , but each of them must be considered separately . The most important to use mobile phones is in times of need , so banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants can not be a comprehensive law ; because sometimes we need to use the mobile phone , sometimes people call us so we must answer them and sometimes , vice versa , we must call other people . Therefore , this ban is not a good idea , it can be changed in such a way that there is a limited time for the use of mobile phones in these places . The ban , for example , could be for one minute , not more . But this time may vary from place to place . On public transport , because people are crowded together , the ban could be for one minute . In shops , the ban may be less than 3 minutes and , in restaurants , the ban may be less than 5 minutes . Of course , you have to ask the opinion of those who are responsible in these cases . A poll from people who use transport public . After that , consider the result of poll and make the decision which is the best approach to do that . 
Personally , I think the best choice for students is to move away and live on their own while they are attending university because this has so many benefits and a student can learn about life even more . One advantage of living on their own is that they have the opportunity to be more independent and develop their time management and organization skills , due to them having to be in charge of the payments of the rent , doing their laundry , making time to prepare their food and doing all the other stuff at the same time they do well in university . Apart from that , some students can live in a house or apartment with other students so they can make good friends and develop their social skills . Owing to living with other people , there would be good and not really great moments , which implies that it is necessary to respect , to learn how to solve conflicts , how to express differences but without damaging someone . On the other hand , moving away from home sometimes is the best decision owing to many students living away from the university , which means they have to commute long distances in order to arrive on time to class , which can be tiresome after a certain period of time . So bearing this in mind , living near the university can be perfect for these students and it represents an opportunity to have more time for their subjects . Nonetheless , this choice can bring out the best in the students , it can also bring out the worst in them , because living in your own requires effort and compromise to take care of yourself and accomplish your goals . To sum up , living on your own has benefits , learnings and challenges , but it is a great experience and opportunity to prepare yourself for the near future . Finally , I would say that I support this decision , but everyone has the right to decide and evaluate which is the best option for them . 
We can find both advantages and disadvantages of studying aboard . If we talk about advantages , we can find experiencing new things , being in a foreign country expands your horizons and makes you a more interesting person . Also , it looks good on your resume , because it tells your employers that you are open to different cultures and have the ability to be independent . Studying aboard takes you out of your comfort zone , gives you the opportunity to create a social network around the world and also learn a new language ( and that is always something positive ) . As a disadvantage , you can feel nostalgia for home and if you are close to your family , they will miss you . Also you can experience cultural barriers with the language for domestic things , like opening a bank account or going to the doctor . And what about if you dislike your course or because of personal issues you have to return early and have spent a lot of money ? Studying aboard is a high risk . 
Dear Maia , Last week I went to a concert of Coldplay . I decided to go to this concert because it 's a band that I really like and I was told it was worth going . So I went . The concert was really good . I had a great time . Coldplay is really a great band . There were a lot of nice surprises during the concert . The surprises at the concert were that they invited people to come on stage and you could win either a sweater , a CD or a signed band flag . And you want to know , I won and went on stage and I got a sweater . I was really happy and I 'm still happy . 
It depends . If you study a foreign language , you should travel to a country where you can practise this language . For example , you may travel to Ireland to improve your English level . You will work as an a upper or as a waitress in a restaurant . You will be able to live in a house with native people and you would talk in English every day . However , this way to practise supposes you must go out of your house . You need to find an exchange house . You do not know anything about this family and you may find staying there so bad . If I decide to study abroad , I would prefer to live in a rented house . I can rent a bedroom to another partner and we will pay all the things together . Another disadvantage is if you have a wife and some children , you will need to find a house for your family and for you . In my opinion , in this option , it would be more difficult . 
From my perspective , health is more important than wealth . As we all know , we can buy anything and enjoy everything we like with wealth , but I think that health is more imperative than wealth . Do you know why ? This is because in order to have fun or to enjoy our happiness , the first thing we need to have is a healthy body . When we are sick , we do not have energy to carry out activities in our daily life . Consequently , we will not feel happy , even if we are rich . A person with a healthy body can live a longer life compared to a person who is rich , but not healthy . Honestly , money cannot buy us a new life , cannot buy us time and it also cannot buy us a healthy body ! On the other hand , a healthy body enables us to have a longer life and it enables us to spend more time with our beloved family and friends . If we are healthy , we will feel happier and more cheerful . As we all know , there is nobody who likes to get sick and no one likes to suffer from different kinds of illnesses , for example , coughing , fever and getting a cold . We all know that getting sick makes us feel uncomfortable and we have no energy to carry out our daily activities . Thus , why are we rich , as we cannot do anything if we are sick ? In conclusion , I totally agree that health is more essential than wealth . 
Last week , I went to Da Nang city , which is one of the most livable cities in Vietnam . Da Nang is located in the centre of Vietnam . It was the first time I had ever been there . My first impression of the city was that it was so peaceful . The population is far less than Saigon , so that the streets are not crowded and people are not in a hurry like people in Saigon . The atmosphere is so comfortable , as there are not many carbon emissions and the temperature is approximately 20 degrees Celcius . This atmosphere reminded me of Dalat city , which is also my favorite destination . The scenery of Da Nang is so beautiful , because it is a coastal city . Visitors can enjoy a sea view and mountain view at the same time . On the first morning at Da Nang , I walked outdoors along the beach and enjoyed the breath -taking view there . It was a once -in -a -lifetime experience . Around Dang Nang city , there are many tourist attractions , which are famous not only in the nation , but also well -known worldwide . I spent one day visiting Ba Na Hill , one of the most popular tourist destinations in Da Nang . I really enjoyed the spectacular scenery there and took a lot of pictures . I wish I could have stayed there longer . 
Today , medical doctors want to stay in cities not just for the money they can get , essential facilities and medicines are not available in rural areas , it can be stressful saving lives if you do not have the basic elements to do it . Another reason is because of their families , in cities , they can provide a better standard of life , access to a better education system for their kids and for themselves . It is important for a medical doctor to update their knowledge constantly and , in rural areas , that 's hard . Some doctors claim they do not get a salary regularly in rural hospitals and do not have proper accommodation to stay . Now , how can we solve this problem ? Well , making rural hospitals more attractive for medical doctors . Reserve post -graduate seats in medical colleges for doctors serving in the public sector , for at least two years . Improve medical infrastructure in rural hospitals and provide the necessary stock of medicines and supplies , so they can work without problems . 
Health is an important aspect of our life . There is a popular saying that " Health is wealth . " For a joyful life , it 's necessary to be healthy . In today 's world , everyone is busy in a virtual reality that never ends . There are social media apps , games , dating apps and all these virtual things rapidly replacing physical connection . Before this technological revolution , people met each other or they talked for hours and spent some quality time , but now , social apps have replaced that completely . People are more interested in virtual meetings instead of physical meetings and , due to this , the emotional connection between people is not developing . There are many side effects of this in the long term , people feel alone and , at the end , depression is the thing that they get . People are more interested in playing on mobiles or PC gaming instead of playing actual games on the ground . With the growing technological era , companies create fantasy games that people ca not play in their actual life , but due to this , they lose their physical activity . Sitting hours on the table is not a good thing for our body . Everyone 's body needs some physical activity . But in the absence of physical activity , people get fat or gain weight , and after that , they face problems in their daily lives . So it 's a good idea to force students into physical activity . A man who is more physically active lives a longer and healthier life instead of those who avoid it . In today 's sick world , there are plenty of diseases that are ready to catch you if you compromise your health . Due to an unhealthy life , you will have to go to hospital and , due to this , you lose your money and time . So try to do some physical activity wherever you want . It will increase your life a span and make you attractive . 
Throughout the year , we experience four seasons : fall , winter , spring and summer . Each season has its own taste and feelings and different people prefer one season over the others . Like others , I have my favorite seasons and they are spring and fall . If I had to choose one , I would pick the fall season . This season always amazes me every year and I have had good experiences in it . First of all , fall 's weather is unique and differs from any other season . As it comes after the hot summer , the temperature starts dropping and it becomes enjoyable to go outdoors during the day without worrying about protection from the sun . Also , during fall , all the trees change their color to beautiful shades of red , and the leaves fall on the sidewalks and streets , creating a distinctive look that always comes to my mind when thinking about this season . In fact , it is a great opportunity to go for a hike and explore nature at that time of the year . Another thing that makes fall my favorite period is that I can meet my friends and family after being away for a while . In the summer , people usually travel to different locations . However , they come back at the beginning of fall to start their new semester , which is a great opportunity to get together and hear about what they have done on their travels . 
I would like to talk about a holiday that was really important to me . Two years ago , I went to visit my home town with my family . That was the best holiday I have ever had . I left my home town years ago . All my relatives were happy to see me , because I am their only nephew . During my holiday , I visited so many places , such as the central monastery , school and farms . I plowed on my grandfather 's farm and cleared the grass from the fields . I felt so good to be with my grandparents and siblings , because they love me , take care of me and keep me happy all the time . When I was there , I learned how to be kind to the people around you , value them and take care of them when we can , because we cannot substitute them with anything in the world . That is why that holiday was an exceptional one for me . 
I would like to study Applied Physics too . I need to study Applied Physics , because I have to choose that subject in a university exam . I want to start that subject from next month . Could you tell me which textbook is better ? I am a beginner , so I need to know what the easiest book is . 
Exercise is important for our health . Our body needs to do exercise daily to be healthy , especially for office workers , because they sit on chairs most of the time . But it might not necessary for manual workers . Apart from doing exercise , there are other factors to live healthily , such as having a good sleep , eating nutritious foods , avoiding eating too many calories and so on . Consuming the right food is very important for our body , because our body is like a machine that uses fuel . Our machine will last if we use clean and the right fuel for our machine . Otherwise the machine will break into pieces and will not last long . Likewise , we should consume only what is good for our body to live happily and healthily . In conclusion , we should eat what is good for our body , not consume alcohol , do physical exercise and rest , then we should live healthily . 
It is the start of a new school year at school . There are new skills to improve in different subjects . The first day , we had the show of the teachers and the schedule and syllabus for the first term . I think I must study for lots of hours . I 'm pleased with Spanish , the English language and Maths . I do not like science , music and PE so much . I want to improve my English level to achieve better goals than last year . I need to study at least two hours per day to improve my English level . I am going to go to an English Academy to help me make a big effort . I 'm good in Maths . However I do not trust myself . Although I do not like some subjects , I will try to have the best goals I can . This is my last year at school and I would like to achieve good marks . 
University students are considered to be adults . They can be in charge of their own lives nearly like adults , however , their main goal is full -time studying , not yet a full -time job . Choosing places to live during their studies is one of the crucial decisions for them to make . For students who choose to stay at home . One of the reasons might be finances . Staying home can save a lot of money on accommodation , food , bills , etc . Moreover , staying home can guarantee the safety of students and put their parents ' worry at ease by knowing that their children are in the safe place and in their most comfort . On the contrary , students who choose to stay on their own during their studies at university can be more confident and be able to handle any obstacles that might be thrown at them during this time , money shortage , juggling studying and a part -time job , take care of their own basic needs , such as food and clean clothes , to name a few . In conclusion , I would prefer to stay on my own while studying at university . Because being on your own can teach you to be strong , ready for good and bad situations in the future once you enter the work cycle . 
