As technologies have improved over the last century , the world has changed . All the relationships involving countries have become closer and some changes were important to do that , such as determining a universal language to make connections wherever you are . Once English was chosen to be the universal language , learning it became more popular year by year . Then , finally we arrive at nowadays , a time when knowing English is an important skill to get a job or just to make new friends on websites . If most people ask their parents what the importance of learning a new language is and later ask this same question to a friend who is the same age , probably they will find a big difference comparing these answers . However , nowadays , learning English ( or another language ) has become a essential skill for living better . Even if the second language were just to be used in a job , it will always be important to personal improvement to know more about our planet and the different cultures on it . 
