Many young people believe that migrating for studying at university may benefit them while some of them like to be with their family for support and help in their education . In my opinion , families are the supporting pillar for every student to achieve their goals and offer them a good environment to be successful in their life . , . adolescents nowadays prefer to go far from their home because they think that it could lead them to a better career . They choose this way because they want to become independent and gain some experience facing difficulties throughout the process . However , they can suffer from homesickness . Furthermore , being away from family might result in following sexual or porno sites , which destroy their life at the beginning . For instance , some students who do not have family to keep an eye on them have no fear of doing dreadful things . Their friends mislead them to commit some crime for their own benefit , such as consuming drugs , or theft for the greed of luxurious things . On the other hand , students who prefer to live with their family because they feel relaxed that their family is here with them whenever they need their support , whether it is financially or psychologically . Families also protects their children to stay away from misdeeds . They not only provide educational support but also teach them good manners and how to interact with people , help others , be aware of awful activities to be successful in life . Although , being alone throughout their studies can make students mature enough to face life 's troubles , being with family makes them feel that no one will help them in crises or with risks . To sum up , staying away from family provides the happiness of being independent ; however staying with family gives a great pleasure to relax and follow family advice to deal with any problems . 
In the research of motion and time control , we have a section that determines the importance of time and how we design our office to get the best results . The kind of design that you choose is related with your work . For example , if you work as a secretary , it is better for you work in solitary and your employees have a separate but if you need to have more relationship with other colleagues , you should have a more open design with no walls . I personally agree with an open design since all co -workers can see each other and I believe eye contact is a good motivation in the office . Imagine a manager or a banker . In an open design , they can see their workers ' manners and operations and it is easy to judge their abilities and confidence . I think an open design is like a mirror that reflects your actions and you have to be so strong to work in front of others . Another benefit of an open space is that you use better your spaces . 
I agree with the type of requirement that students must complete some volunteer work in order to graduate . I have three reasons to support my opinion . Firstly , students get a chance to communicate with many people by volunteer work whom they have less opportunity to . By cleaning work , they can communicate with local people and , by devoting work , they can communicate with weak people . This is beneficial for students because they can understand many perspectives as well as broaden them . Secondly , students get a chance to improve their action by volunteer work . It needs spontaneity . Students have to be active for others by themselves . This is beneficial for students because action is necessary to promote in the future . Lastly , students get a chance to gain their self -confidence by volunteer work as they are appreciated . This is beneficial for students because self -confidence leads to actions . In conclusion , I agree with the requirement that students must complete some volunteer work in order to graduate for those three reasons . 
If I need to choose one of them , I will select opinion No . 2 . Why ? Because life is changing every day , so you need to adapt to that . The main issue here is the quality of the teacher , not the change . That means if you have a good teacher and they 're a mirror that you can learn from and develop , then there is no need to change the following year . The problem I should mention here is the student has a right to choose the teacher who will teach and support her/him during learning period . On the other hand , the student is like a customer in that they pay for the course , so they have their own power to choose any input that can impact on them . that decided creates the pressure that is put on shoulders of the teacher , so to help them to improve , they need to have more positive feedback from their students . Hence , the quality of education and learning can improve . 
As we know , English as second language is known as across word where it is not as first the language . As a language , English is crucial to learn to live well in this world . There are a lot of issues which could be solved by knowing only the English language . Every English learner searches the way to learn English while nowadays most learners search an online method . There is a lot of content available on the internet while not every material is useful . As we know , to learn any language , there are four parts , reading , writing , listening and speaking . Most of the websites arrange matters for consuming not for practice and even do not provide a service to check your content but Write and Improve provides a writing workbook where you can practice writing and explore your creation , as well as it corrects your written content . Further to this , I would like to say that everyone says that practice makes the man perfect . Write and Improve provides a lot of writing topics which cover all areas of the writing practice where one can practice well his creation and also check his written content . In addition , On this platform , you can get ideas from other writers by seeing their writing and learn also with their content . These advanced features on this website attracted me to join it . 
