These days , studying in another country has become common , so some people are not convinced about emigrating , while others believe that for science . . This article will discuss both sides and I will draw my personal opinion . From the characteristics of travelling abroad for education , for example , when you want to travel , you have to learn the language of the region by talking to people . Then you can understand their customs and traditions . In addition , you have to depend on yourself . For instance , you become someone who manages your money and learns something about economics . This is beneficial for you in the future . On the other hand , there are some drawbacks of emigrating to a different area . To illustrate , when you travel to any country , you do not know how to protect yourself from thieves , especially if you are a girl . In conclusion , after careful analysis of both points of view , I believe that in life you have to struggle for your dreams . 
Currently , it is a big issue in the health sector that most doctors do not want to continue their job in rural areas . There are two main reasons which I would like to explore in this writeup . Firstly , the lack of basic needs , which are primary requirements for a doctor , like education , availability of resources and infrastructure . If any person is a doctor , then he thinks that he offers a better education to their kids and a healthy competitive environment for the upbringing of their child , meanwhile rural areas fail to provide these basic services . Further to this , a doctor wants to live a luxurious life in cities , which is not possible in villages . In the wake of automobile services or road transport , these services are not good in rural areas . Secondly , I would like to say a medical practitioners has to always learn for the betterment of skills , which he could get in cities well . In cities , the number of doctors is higher and surrounding is comptetive where he could get more . In my opinion , to sort this burning issue , firstly , the government should increase the basic amenities in rural areas and provide all the facilities which are required to do well in villages . 
My favourite season of the year is winter , due to the cold weather and holidays . Moreover , I like the feeling that I have when I finish my duties from school , that feeling of relief because I know some free days are coming and that means I 'm going to relax and think about other things . Even though I 'm not into Christmas and those kinds of celebrations , I like it and that is because I eat a lot of food . I even receive some gifts from my family . Sometimes , I go to visit my family in Poland . My cousins and I usually go to camp next to a famous lake . I really like visiting Poland , despite the bad cold that you feel there . The main reason that I 'd say winter is my favourite season is the weather . I hate hot weather , that means I hate summer . 
My favourite season of the year is winter . My favourite sport is football and basketball and these two sports require an outdoor field . So , in winter there is no rain or sun and it is the best to do sport . In winter , I can also wear my lovely hoodie . It is very warm and comfortable when you wear a hoodie in a freezing cold season . I can also drink a sweet cup of hot chocolate , my favourite drink for winter . In winter , my country does not have snow , so this is a chance for me to ask my parents for a trip to Europe , where it snows a lot . Also , in winter , when Christmas will take place and also people around the world will be ready to welcome the new year , I will be receiving some money for the Chinese New Year . 
You spend more than half of your life at your work place . Hence the environment of the work place is very important which effects affects your daily life and working efficiency . Everyone has their own mindset , some are cooperative and a few are self -centred . Due to this condition , I believe an enclosed workstation is more useful . If you are doing work in an enclosed chamber , you could do your work more confidently because there is no chance of disturbance and failing from losing your work secrecy by a colleague . You could also make your personal time zone when you have no office work during this time . If you have to stay in the office , you could spend your time learning as well as improving your skill . If you do work in an open design and any your data or ideas are open without your consent , then you will feel unhappy and also not only the person who did this ill act but also other colleagues of yours suspect , which changes the working environment sound to unease , un pleaseant and it take a sufficient time to away from this situations . 
I like going with my family on holiday , on an enjoyable trip , once a year . The best holiday we had was four years ago . My wife 's grandfather decided to invite us on a Mediterranean cruise . My wife prepared all that we needed . She went to a travel agency , she gave us the different options , we decided which was the best and she booked the wonderful trip . We went from Pamplona to Barcelona by train . We joined my wife 's grandfather there . We travelled from Barcelona to Venice by plane . The cruise was from Venice to Venice . We visited cities of Italy , Croatia and France . We met local people and we ate local food . We walked a lot to see lots of monuments and landscapes . Although we were very tired , we were so happy . We enjoyed ourselves a lot . The best place we visited was Druvobnik . There was a marvellous castle . The Game of Thrones series was recorded there . I will never forget that experience . It was the best in my life . 
The environment of work has changed a lot since this half of century . The model of design for our desks was highly developed towards combining comfort as well as efficiency . Many companies are adopting the new open design . It 's generally open spaces that permit a huge interactivity between employees and allow everyone to work in efficient conditions . I prefer to work in an open space . There are many reasons behind this choice . First of all , it permits me to feel free and cool . It also allows me to be close to my colleagues . As I mentioned before , an open space not only seems to be very relevant but also it leads users to become creative and productive . In addition to these arguments , I believe deeply that an open space will remain an efficient means in the way to follow the requirements of respect for the environment and energy efficiency . Currently , even if it 's weird , due to the coronavirus pandemic , we are obliged to adopt teleworking . 
First , we need more and more use of computers and tablets , either in our lives or in school . A change has come and the old way of learning and teaching is over . We certainly approve of the new way of learning . It 's easier and faster than yesterday . Knowledge is in the hands of everyone . But is it enough ? Second , computers and tablets cannot take the place of books . However , you would be better closing all the libraries around the world . Reading a book is different to surfing on the Internet . You look up a word in a dictionary . You have a good time with a book . You seem to be concentrating with a book . So , is it the end of books ? To conclude , it feels you can either take a book or take your tablet . It depends on you . You do not have to choose and can use both of them . 
To keep students occupied with useful activities is usually a great challenge for teachers . In the past , reading a book or doing some ordinary activities were enough for children to enjoy it , but now , it 's very difficult to satisfy them . Studying music has become through the years a relevant and innovative activity leading students to increase their skills and capacities . In some rare cases , some " ignorant " schools do not allow children to follow a musical learning session . It is , in my modest opinion , a huge mistake considering the importance of music . Doing music gives students many faculties that they need like an open mind , connection with other friends or the feeling of self - esteem . Many schools are not aware about the importance of music in enhancing a student ’s behavior and therefore giving them solid protection against violence or drugs . I continue to believe strongly that music is very important for students not only in schools but also in life . 
I 'm going to give you my opinion about if it is important to do exercise or not . On the one hand , I think exercise is so important . If you eat healthy food and you do exercise every day , you could be healthy . This question is , is it the most important reason to be fit ? People who do exercise and eat well have better health than people who do not do it . On the other hand , I think there are things which are as important as health . In my opinion it is very important to have a family and have good friends . If you live alone and you do not meet with other people , you may be so sad and you will have health problems . If you do not have any person who loves you , I 'm sure you wo not be happy . Finally , I try to do exercise in my free time . After that , I usually feel more relaxed . 
In my opinion , music is part of life . It is scientifically proved the role of music and sound , not only in human beings but also in animals and plants . As we know , nowadays , sound therapy is used to heal many diseases , like Parkinson 's , depression , mood disorder and anxiety . Most clinicians and personality developers say that you should know how to play at least one musical instrument to improve your personality . Further to this , the boy who knows how to play musical instruments , everyone attracted to him soon or he has magnetic personality . Earlier in Indian culture , there were lot of music systems and rag tal and Sur , which are used on different occasions and different parts of day for happiness and joy of life . Like Bheem plasi rag is used to heal your tiredness at night and , during daytime , rag bhiarvi . Besides this a lot of use of sounds and music , hence I would like to recommend a musical system in the school course and also an extracurricular activity . 
Television is very famous and common at the present time . This technological device is in all homes and it 's very useful . Thanks to television , we can follow the news and agenda , also we can watch a lot of series . Actually , the problem is television entertains , but it 's stealing our time . It seems very innocent , but it ca not educate . We must read books for education . I think we are using television just for fun . For example , when I turn on the TV , there is always war or love on the television . We ca not improve in this way . If we want to do research , we can use a computer and we can use books . But television can only give us entertainment . In fact , if we talk about children , we have two options for this subject . First , television has educational channels . If our kids watch these channels , they will improve . Second , if they watch absurd cartoons , they will be worse and they will lose their learning capability . Finally , I want to say television is fun , but it is not able to educate us . 
Schools are very important places for educating students in every city . Schools are developing people . Schools were not modern in the past , but now there are many new things . In the future , the teaching will become better and the buildings will become modern and bigger . School will be extremely different in the future . The ways of teaching are going to be more technological than these days . Students will not be able to take bags with a lot of books to school , they will carry a tablet instead of bags with books , because a tablet can download and use electronic books . It might have robot teachers instead of people . The education will be harder than now . Teachers may take students diving in the sea to learn about kinds of fish , or to the jungle to see animals in their habitat . Finally , I am looking for better methods to teach in a fun way . 
I think all students should study music and learn to play a musical instrument . I have three reasons to support my opinions . Firstly , we have a sense of hearing , which is one of our five senses . Why do not we improve this potential skill ? Hearing much music , we can improve it easily and understand this world more . Secondly , we can broaden our world playing a musical instrument at school . It is difficult to touch or play many kinds of them in our daily life because of fewer opportunities . But there are many and we play them for free ! Why do not we take the precious chance to play musical instruments ? We may start our career as professional musicians with the opportunity . Thirdly , this world is full of music . Music is everywhere . There is much seasonal music or event related with music and so on . Even if we know little about music , we can enjoy more our life . With these three reasons , I agree that students should study music and musical instruments . 
I think nothing will be the same in the future . Probably , people will like travelling the same as nowadays , but we 'll use different means of transport . Yesterday , I read some news about when we will start to travel to the moon . A few years ago , nobody thought we could do a trip there . Although it is possible at this moment , it is so expensive . I 'm sure that my children will watch the first trip to the moon before they die . Today , people are buying electric cars . In 2050 , cars will be able to fly without wheels . Planes will fly faster than planes that are flying today . In my opinion , transport will be faster and with less pollution . I think maybe we will have a problem : Will we have enough money to do a trip ? Perhaps people wo not travel because there will be more poverty around the world . In fact , that is an important question for globalization in the next fifty years . 
