Dear English teacher , Thank you for your question . I really like learning through hearing English stories and through speaking . After , I learn enough grammar . It means , I ca not stand writing or speaking falsely . More than that , I like being qualified to understand fast speakers . I would love to improve speaking , using the best words in the best context . In addition to that , I would be able to increase my knowledge , so that I can teach what I know . If I can translate between my mother tongue and English , I will be such a happy guy . I would also be able to write an disquistion and documentation about new research to interpret the information with examples . I have a lot of learning methodologies . An example of one , I use online tools to practice writing skills . I try to translate some poetry from my mother language into English . Some of the translation applications are constantly being used to dive in synonyms and antonyms of the new words ( vocabulary ) . I think one day I will be able to use English better than English people . Thank you for your efforts . Ahmad . 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? The government can take action on reducing the weight of a school bag . The majority of adults hate carrying books . Books are best - the weight is only the problem . Computers and tablets make tasks easier . A combination is the best . Lastly , it depends upon the standard at which student studies . It has been studied that most adults own a mobile and the majority of them waste time on a mobile or tablet , so by providing more digital material for adults , we could enhance the productivity of the adults . 
Yes , it is very important to learn a foreign language and I learnt that a foreign language could provide exponential growth in the following areas , like personal development , social development , competitive edge and bilateral advantages . For negotiations with other countries , it is very important to learn their language , so that smooth communication will be carried out . Many companies expect their new employees to speak at least two foreign languages , to increase the company 's availability across the world . 
Leading an inactive lifestyle has many negative effects on health . That is the reason why a proposal has been put forth : obliging all university students and school children to do sports activities at least three times a week . Is this really a good idea ? On the one hand , forcing something like this upon people is very authoritarian . Such a law infringes on personal freedoms and bodily autonomy . It would give the state more control over our youths ' personal lives and diminish their sense of personal responsibility . With freedom comes responsibility , and both of them are very important to have and properly make us of in life . If from a young age the child has great personal autonomy , they will better at learning to make use of it than if the state were to interfere . The proposal above , were it made law , would stunt our children 's ability to administer their own lives . On the other hand , the benefits of sports activities are so great and many that the sacrifice of some freedom may be justified . Physical activity improves both physical and mental health , as well as cognitive abilities . And in the context of schooling , where children are forced to do tasks anyway , it would make sense to make use of the advantages of sport . Moreover , there are generalised benefits for the whole of society . Healthier people get sick less and live longer , putting overall less strain on the public healthcare system . This saves costs , since treatment is very expensive , a lot more than prevention in the form of sports activities . This saves taxpayers and the government loads of money . All in all , the benefits of forcing our youth to do sport outweigh any possible objections . They are already obligated to a variety of tasks in school , and adding sport to that would only have benefits . 
In my opinion , if the group feels comfortable with a specific teacher and the results are satisfactory , then the best option is to keep the teacher with the same students . However , it 's known that in almost all schools the students have a different teacher for each subject . This shows us that students are used to taking classes with different teachers . As for my experience in my life as a student in a high school , some of my teachers changed every semester , but my group kept the same Math teacher for 2 years . He was the best math teacher that I 've ever known . The way that he taught made me love math . On the other hand , we had a different English teacher every year . That was inefficient for us , because we could not get used to the way of teaching of each teacher . In consequence , we were not able to learn English . When I finished high school , my level of English was really poor , so I had to learn it in another school . I think every student has different ways of learning and every teacher has different ways of teaching , so it 's difficult to know what is better for the students , because what works for some on occasions does not work for others . 
I have had a lot of ' best holidays ' throughout my life . So , choosing just one of them is a big task for me . I have been thinking and I decided to choose one when I travelled to the beach to work on an internship in Ubatuba . In that city , I met people who are still close to me now . Every day that I spent over there was full of knowledge , fun and reflection . I miss so much when I got off work and I went to the beach to swim and drink some beers with my new friends . Besides that , my co -workers and I shared the same house for one whole month ! It was fun when we cooked together or helped each other to get up to go to work . This time was amazing ! When I returned to my city , I thought a lot about what I wanted for my life and what my goals were . Certainly , this holiday changed my life and I 'm grateful for having all this . 
What is life ? Life is very complicated . It depends on the person . Some people 's life is full of happiness , some people 's life is full of surprise , some people 's life is full of sadness and even some people 's life is full of hardships . We must choose our own life , we have the right to choose the life we want to live . I saw many people 's lives were tied up by their parents . Their parents did not let them have the opportunity to choose their own life . I feel quite pity for them . As for me , I wo not let others lay a single finger on my own life , I insist on choosing my own life no matter how . If I was given the choice to live a long , calm life until 100 years old or a shorter life but much more intense , I think I would choose to have a shorter life but much more intense . Do you know why ? This is because living a shorter life , you do not need to suffer from many different kinds of illnesses like diabetes , heart attacks and hypertension . When we are getting old , various illnesses and diseases will start to come towards us . This is because when we are old , our body starts to deteriorate and our immune system will start to decline . After hearing this , do you still want to live a long , calm but suffer from sickness ? Of course not ! Everyone gets ill when they are old because this is one of the parts of life . This is why I would rather choose a shorter life but much more intense instead of living a long , calm life . Plus , we feel very lonely and sad when seeing our own friends and family members passing away one by one . Sadness and loneliness bottles up in our heart little by little when we lose our loved ones . If I live a short but much more intense life , most of my friends and family will still stay by my side and I will be able to confront the most brutal setbacks and hardships with their help . I am sure that they will seek solace in me if I am defeated by failure . Hence , these are the reasons why I would choose to live a short but much more intense life . In addition , do you want to see yourself getting old ? As for me , I do not want to see those wrinkles keep on appearing on my face , my hair turning from black to white and my back getting more and more hunched . These are the signs of getting old and this reminds me that I am getting old and need to get more help from others . I do not like to depend on others because this might be a burden to the one who takes care of you . Furthermore , a short but yet intense life can make us to live in a good shape and full of different colours . In conclusion , a long , calm life will not only makes us feel very lonely but also sad . Therefore , I choose to live a short but intense life over a long , calm life . 
Some people believe that nowadays it is not necessary to learn languages . The question is why . At present , the mobile phone has apps that translate in the moment . For this reason , many people think that it is not vital . From my point of view , I consider that it is very important to learn a language . My reasons are : First , when you are reading a book in English , it is different reading an English book than a Spanish book . The meaning of the phrases changes from one language to another . Second , when you learn a language , your mind changes . That is , there are studies that have demonstrated that if you learn another language ( different to your mother tongue ) , you will improve your cerebral cortex . Your brain secretes substances which help to avoid degenerative illnesses , like Alzheimer 's . To sum up , I consider that it is very important to learn languages and discover other cultures . 
In Taiwan , there are a lot of people who want to learn and improve their English . English is the worldwide language , and we have to use it in many situations of our daily life , such as business , traveling , and so on . Recently , I have discovered a helpful tool , Write and Improve , for English learners to practice their English writing skills . Write and Improve is a free website . You just need to register as a member or sign in with your Facebook account , and then you can use it for free . On the website , you can choose the level which is suitable for you or which you want to challenge . When you decide the level , you will notice that there are plenty of questions in each level . It provides different kinds of conditions for you to practice . In addition , in the task , there is a timer for you to clock your writing time . After finishing the writing , you can click on " Check " and see the feedback of your writing . Moreover , you can revise your writing in accordance with the feedback , and check it again . According to my experience , Write and Improve is a useful tool for people who want to learn English writing skills . Practice makes perfect . Please do the exercises everyday if you would really like to improve your English . You will find out the effect . 
Write and Improve is an app by Cambridge University , made for students in order to improve their writing . Having used it for almost a month , I am going to summarise my experiences with this app in the following paragraphs . Firstly , I would like to write about the biggest advantage Write and Improve has , namely the check function . This means you can write a text and after completing the task , the programme checks it for you . This has helped me not only improve my grammar and vocabulary , but also my style of writing . Next , the app is helpful because there are many different levels of language . Therefore , Write and Improve enables its users to improve and move on to the tasks that best fit their needs . Lastly , I have to mention an aspect of this website I have not found helpful , which is the cost . Although the first tasks are for free , most of the workbooks have to be bought . This is a border for learners who do not have the money to pay for the app . In conclusion , I can highly recommend this app , since it has helped me and many other users improve our English skills . 
I started thinking about this question when I was a child because , when I was eight years old , I saw the film " Troy " for the first time in my life . Our history teacher gave us homework to watch that movie because we were studying the Greek history of that period . I was so impressed by Achilleus 's character because he could have anything he wanted : a long life , a wife , health and a family , but he chose , being aware of the consequences , to leave for Troy , knowing that he would not ever come back home . I could not explain why , it was totally unobvious for the little girl I was . But then , going on watching the movie , I got it clearly : he was doing it for glory and immortality . Living a long and calm and boring life would have made him upset , which is the point of living 100 years if your life is not worth being lived ? Emotions , feelings , experiences are what keep us alive , so I would prefer to live a shorter life , but full , lived and not wasted , instead of spending my time doing nothing because everything is dangerous . If you stop a moment and think about the risks , you will understand that everything is risky , so you would not do anything . I 'm not talking about having mad experiences , I 'm just talking of living freely and fully , tasting every single moment that life has to offer to us . Besides , we have just one life , it 's pretty inconvenient to waste it . 
Hello everyone , Thank you for giving me this opportunity to answer this issue . I have to imagine an answer , because I have never been to any necessary holiday . The most important holiday I have ever been on was when I went to a country where the people could not read and write . I had to go and try to teach them , how they will be able to read without being able to read , if only they will read . The idea might seem too complex at the beginning , but it is not . The word reading is usually mixed with the word reciting . What I mean is that I tried to teach people reciting . Why did I want to tell them about this idea ? Because the time was too short to help them to be able to read and I have read in history that some knowledgeable people were not able to read . It is so , not being able to read does not mean being stupid at all . That is why I taught them , how they can hear something important and interesting and repeat it many times till they can recite it without any difficulties , so they can teach each other , that some teachers cannot teach their own students . I was happy to help them break the rock of ignorance . 
The question I will discuss in this essay is the following : should university students and school children be forced to do sports activities at least three times per week ? Sport is very important for a healthy lifestyle , but should we force people to do so ? Playing any kind of sport certainly has an effect on your lifestyle . It is good to exercise your body , it needs to be exercised . You can just hang out on the couch and expect to have a healthy lifestyle . Making people play sport is a good idea , it is often included in the curriculum in primary and secondary school . So even if there are people who do not do sport outside of school , at least , they exercise once or twice a week . However , the question is whether you want to force people into doing sports activities . People do not like to be forced , especially when they do not like the thing they are forced to do . However , with sport , it is a bit different . There are so many sports nowadays , that it is almost impossible to not like any sport . Each person has their own preference when it comes to exercising . Besides , it is very easy to , for example , for young children , hide any kind of sports activity in some fun game . Those high energy games should be considered sports activities . So you either really have to force people into sports , or somebody should come up with an alternative plan to get people into sports . I think that we should not force people to do sports activities . That is because I think that there really are people who just struggle with getting themselves to do some sort of exercise . However , I do think that playing sports should be more encouraged . Sports clubs can organise fun recruitment days to promote their sport . 
I completely agree with that opinion . If you have lost your health , you can be rich , nevertheless you ca not be happy in your life . Imagine that , you have so much money , cars and homes , however you have cancer . What is their worth if you do not have your health ? So , we need to attach importance to our health . We should do this . What can we do to take care of our health ? We should eat healthy food in terms of vitamins , protein and oil . We need some healthy oil , like peanut and avocado . We should eat the necessary amount of vitamins and protein . Secondly , we should do exercise four times a week . Exercise is a significant thing to stay healthy . We can do walking , running and fitness . If we do these things , we can stay healthy . As a result , in my opinion , being healthy is more significant than being rich . Money may not bring you health . 
In the era of technology , everything is changing rapidly , among which , education is the most affected . Dating back , books are one of the most essential and crucial tools for education . Replacing the existence of books , computers are now generally used for the sake of learning . On the one hand , some declare that books are an existence that cannot be replaced . On the other hand , some counter by comparing the convenience and flexibility between books and computers . In my opinion , the latter one is more preferable than the former . Nowadays , from college to senior high school , numerous teachers use technology in their courses . With a computer on hand , teachers can easily have access to the abundant resources online . Moreover , learning the lessons through the internet , students can ask questions without the restriction of needing to be at school . In light of the above , I think computers and tablets definitely have the potential to completely replace books in the realm of education . 
Hello everyone , I thank you for this opportunity . I will tell you about some important things , which will help you to keep yourselves healthy . Doing sport is necessary for your body , but there are really many more necessary measures that protect your health . The most important measure is eating healthy food . The body has limited power and unhealthy food affects badly on your health . Unhealthy drinks also affect so badly on your health . I guess sleeping early and waking up early are also truly healthy actions to assist your immune system . Too much sleeping might also have bad effects on your health . An additional bad thing is also arguing with people . Working for a long time will cause health and psychological problems , especially if one works five days a week . Do not think about the past bad events , which had unexciting consequences . Do not care a lot about the future . Thank you . Ahmad . 
Hi Billal , I went on a trip to Yangon with my classmates last week . This was my first time going on a trip without my parents . I was entirely nervous throughout this trip . We put up a temporary tent to live and sleep in there for one day . In the morning , we went out looking for firewood to cook rice and meat . We had our lunch in the afternoon , which was so delicious , I had ever eaten . We were very happy there because we cooked the rice ourselves and saw the beauty of nature . 
Given the fact that traditional businesses tend to establish enclosed stations in which workers are separated from their employers , while several modern offices are designed with an open space , meaning there is no barrier amid co -workers . In my opinion , working in an open space offers workers creativity and better conversation among them . To begin with , a growing number of companies have been switching old cubicles to a spacious design due to its efficient results on the workflow . Nowadays , a great number of graduates are not confident enough to show their abilities and desire to stay focused on doing private things in their spare time rather than having a meeting with their co -workers . As a result , most of them find struck in communication and teamwork which leads to the downfall a the whole company results . There is no visible barrier between co -workers , which allows them to have more face -to -face interactions related to work and afterward the workflow might run effectively and smoothly thanks to approachable space among them . A well -known software corporation called Google has been setting up an open design since its establishment , which helps workers more easily exchange information and take a deep breath during work . In conclusion , I reaffirm that an open design offers an effective environment in the workplace because the workers find it more convenient for exchanging ideas and information revolving around the work . 
I want to start by saying that the school of the future will be different . That is to say , I consider that high school will be different in how they will teach the classes . I strongly believe that it will be online . It will only be for children under 10 years old . To begin with , I want to say that today school is changing . It is more practical and more technological . The use of tablets is more common . In addition , with COVID , it has taught us that online classes exist and work . Students have learned to organize themselves with online classes . I believe that the way of learning and teaching has improved . I consider that academic performances will be better in the future than now . But it is possible , like the never -ending story , that politicians do not realize it . 
In my view , I think all students need to change teachers over the years , because it is important for students to see opinions and ways of living their lives . All the teachers have their style of explaining something , and during the classes , sometimes the teachers give examples from their life to try to explain the matter . This act helps students understand more about everything . It is a benefit to students . If students have the same teacher all the years , it is boring , because it is the same every year , week , day , and it is a necessary change , because in real life , students will be professionals in the area they will work , and in their company , they will always change colleagues and boss , etc . Changing teachers is a lesson for all our lives , things always change for us , at school , at the supermarket , at a bank , with the police , with the government . Nothing is forever , it is good to change and grow up with these changes . 
The theme of this essay is " Television entertains , but can it also educate ? " I agree with argument that watching TV conditions our well -being . I have been trying to prove the thesis that television seldom educates . Firstly , modern television provides a lot of programmes , In the first place are breakfast programmes and serials . The impact of these programmes on our behaviour is enormous , we only waste our time . Secondly , many people watch the news on TV , They wait for information , shocking information especially . This can be seen primarily among young people . Is this healthy ? Of course not , because that could change their way of thinking and understanding reality . We should teach teenagers positive thinking . Thirdly , all over the world there are changes . Television is being replaced by the internet and new technology . We turn on the television less and less . Young people spend more time using Internet websites , mobile phones and a lot of communication platforms . Obviously , many people like watching TV , but the purpose is not education , only entertainment and fun . Furthermore , today , a lot of televisions are controlled by governments and businesses , so that shapes our political views and our worldview . This is not okay . It has been demonstrated that television entertains , but it does not educate . We could watch TV only for fun , but if we want to learn something , we should read a book or use a computer and various educational websites . 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? When there are more and more computers and tablets , some people ask themselves something like that . To my way of thinking , computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities . Firstly , computers and tablets are much better than books , because they can hold a million times more information than the average 400-800 pages of a book . If you want to find something , it will take you 15 , 20 even 30 minutes to get information from books . But with a computer or a tablet , it would take less than 5 minutes to get it . Secondly , computers and tablets hold many more types of data than a book . If you are carrying a computer or a tablet , that also means you are carrying a thousand books . Finally , they are more convenient . An e -book is much cheaper than a traditional book . The information in a digital format can be edited and shared easily . This makes them overall more convenient for students who might not be able to afford one copy of a book each . In a nutshell , computers and tablets are much more convenient than traditional books . They should completely replace books in schools and universities . 
Travel in the future Travelling is moving from place A to place B with public vehicles , trains , buses , airplanes , ships , private cars , etc . I think there will be big changes in the duration of the journeys . They will be much shorter than current journeys . It will be also more comfortable . The capacity of the vehicles will be bigger . The available joy tools will be more . The time of departure and the time of arrival will be more punctual . The appearance of the booking applications and web pages will be programmed more amazingly . Internet access will be free on every means of transport . The noise which is produced by the vehicles ' engines will be quieter . of those engines will become milder . That means the CO2 and the co2 and the pad gases fumes will be produced less by the engines . The engines might become electric and wo not produce any fumes . It will be better for the people who like travelling and at the same time , they wo not affect the environment badly . Finally , the prognoses might be totally different from the reality . But one is allowed to imagine new possible innovations . Thank you . 
New technologies have been developed . Researchers from the most famous universities of the world are still studying , focusing on new solutions and technological strategies . These are referring especially to the future of travel , not only on the Earth , but also in space . During the last two centuries , the way of travelling from one place to another one has drastically changed . The first industrial revolution provided new transport means and tools . Ships , trains and so on were the beginning of the Modern Age . Nowadays , cars , trains , planes and so forth are enhanced by using new smart materials and technological processes . The aim of the most important factories of the world and aerospace companies , such as NASA and ESA , are represented by succeeding in taking man to Mars . Concerning travelling on the Earth , many tests have been done in these years . A very interesting one is the design of a ' flying car ' , which is able to carry passengers in the air , among the skyscrapers of the cities . By 2024 , the first prototype is likely to be available to buy . This is proof that travelling is bound to be really different in the future , becoming better and better . 
My reasons for learning English are for business life and other things . English is an extensive language in this century . It is a common language . It 's a beneficial thing that there is a common language , because if I learn English , I can talk to other countries ' people who know English . Nearly every establishment wants you to know English to admit you into their establishment . If I want to good job , I should learn English . A good job gives a good income and this leads to a happy life . On the other hand , it is the best way to communicate with foreign people . You have different languages , but you know English . That 's a point . If two foreign people know English , they can communicate with each other . Another reason , I like learning languages . Learning a language is a long process , but amusing . I want to learn different languages in the future , like Spanish and German . 
