New school year , new goals The purpose of this report is to show the subjects which I have been comfortable with and the subjects which have been difficult for me , and furthermore explain what I am going to do to achieve my goals . In general , few students enjoy mathematics and physics . It is not the case with the arts , because almost all love them . They think that they are difficult , however , mathematics and physics are easier than you think . You only need to know the rules and the formulas and that is it . Most students seem to enjoy learning a new language , the classes are fun and interactive . Last year , the English class was taught by an excellent teacher , but the problem has always been listening and speaking . It 's difficult because an hour is not enough to practice them . The best solution seems to be to have classes with a private teacher or take an extra English course in a language school . Also I suggest practicing by yourself , listening to music , watching movies , finding a native English speaker and practicing every day . Remember that practice makes perfect . 
Compared with television broadcasters in other countries , like the United Kingdom or the USA , Italian television is very young . During its first decade , Italian television had , as its first aim , an educational role . Indeed , in the 50s , more than half of the Italian population was not educated and they did not speak Italian , they spoke dialects . The national television broadcaster , RAI , had some programs with the aim of helping schools in teaching the Italian language , history , civics , etc . RAI had this educational role until the 80s , when it changed its aim to better compete with the private broadcasters . Since then , entertainment overtook the educational role , to the point that , on the contrary , it began to have a bad effect on the audience . In the last few decades , the national broadcaster has tried to go back in its educational role , even with just little projects . Now we can watch new television channels with cultural and educational aims . 
In my opinion , learning a new language is always significant . If you learn a new language , you can have some opportunities . For instance , some companies work with different countries ' establishments , and they need an intermediary to communicate with them . They can pay a good amount of money for that . There are so many chances if you learn a language . You can teach students in a language course establishment if you know the language you teach well . So , when we learn a language , we can communicate with foreign people or we can find a job . On the other hand , we could visit a country for a different purpose . When we do this action , we should learn the language of the country we will go to . If we go to study , like a master 's or doctorate , we should learn academic language . As a result , learning a language takes time , however it 's significant no matter when . 
When you are young , you do not mind doing exercise , because you think that it is not important for your life , but most young people are wrong about that . Exercise is so important for our health , because it helps us with anything in our body . Beyond that , it is good for our mind . Usually , when you have a problem or you are so stressed with something that has happened and you do some exercise , your mood changes at the same time . Therefore it is so important for our life to do exercise every single day . But there are other things that are good for our health , like eating health foods and drinking a lot of water , because when we have a good diet , our body feels happier and more willing to do new things , like going out with our friends or doing a hike . So these two things are so important for our health . I would like to say that maybe these things work better together . 
The best holiday ever One of the best places that you could visit is without doubt Queretaro . There are many beautiful natural places . Moreover , you can go with your family , friends and also you could take your pets with you . For this reason , for our holidays , we chose the Sierra Gorda Queretana and San Luis . All the way to these places is awesome and the villages too , where you can eat traditional dishes and buy handicrafts . However , the most awesome places I ’ve ever visited were “ The half moon and Bridge of god ” , where you can swim , camp and take walks . There 's a long walk to get to the bridge . It was taken by my family and me . I took lots of pictures , but I could not swim because the weather was cold . I have good memories about that holiday , because I was with my grandparents and my best friend , who hated the walk by the river , but loved spending time with me . In conclusion , the places gave a special touch to my holiday , because I learned the most important was spending time with people that I loved . I ’m excited about the next place where we could have a terrific time again . 
In my opinion , the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants should have limited access because of it disturbing the public 's concentration and also the dealing person of particular person . I have two main reasons to support my view , which I wish to explore in this essay . Firstly , nowadays , mobile use is very much generalised and most people do not know the proper way of mobile handling and it is a big issue , not only for the mobile user but also the people who are surrounding the user . As we know , nowadays , public life is very busy , hence people have limited time or we can say not sufficient time for their public work . And , in that case , if he spends extra time because of one 's disturbance or due to another person who is talking on the mobile at the time of payment or at the time of negotiating , in that case , only extra time is consumed by the customer because of his mobile call . Safety is the main concern in a public place . Sometimes , people get into accidents at the time of entering the bus because he is busy on a phone call not seeing the proper foot rest and it is very a common type of bus accident due to unaware use of mobiles . Further to this , on long journeys , people usually read on public transport and , in that case , if someone is busy on a mobile call and talking loudly , that person is just disturbing his co -rider . 
