May I present you a new website I recently discovered ? It is Write&improve . This website provides a tool for improving your writing on your own . It is even useful for beginners , like people just starting to learn English , as much as for some more advanced English speakers . The site offers plenty of topics and forms to write about , you can choose freely what you would like to or can write about . Then you can start to write . As soon as you finish , the really great thing starts , you can get instant feedback on your writing , which points out all your mistakes and marks them as well . But that is not all , it also shows you your current language level , and lets you improve your written texts . You can check after every change if it makes your text better , so you can slowly increase your skills by thinking of ways to improve your writing even further . The only downside is that it does not provide suggestions to replace the wrong parts of your writing , which makes it kind of hard for not so experienced writers , because they can think of another way to express themselves . So this would be a huge upgrade for the future . 
