Dear Billal , Thank you for your email yesterday . I 'm happy that you passed your last exam and that you could fly with friends to Africa to your aunt . I ca not wait for you to show me your photos and films from the trip . How long are you planning to stay there ? Write to me , please , when you have landed . I was with my school friends on a trip to Warsaw . We started from Radomsko about 7 a.m . and three hours later we were already in our capital . We parked near the old city so we could go sightseeing in the Kings ' Castle and the Column Zygmunt III Waza . From the old city we could see some amazing views , especially of the National Stadium . In the old city we spent about three hours . Our teacher prepared creative trial games and we had to search many places and talk with other people . What is your favourite place in the old city in our capital , Billal ? At 12.00 we heard the Warsaw anthem from the clock tower in the Kings ' Castle . I recorded it , and if you want , I can send you this incredible video . I heard almost anthem in Cracov when we visited this city last year . It sounds great ! At 2 p.m . our teacher organized an appointment with a non government organization - Polish Foundation of Schuman . The volunteers told us about many projects , events and happenings , for example , the Schuman Parade . I love this event ! I have been in the Schuman Parade a lot of times , and I met many pro -European young people . We discussed the future of the European Union , and the Polish place and position in the EU . What do you think about the future of the EU , Billal ? Are you thinking that the EU should be more united and should new countries have access or not ? Returning to my trip to Warsaw . After the appointment with the NGO 's , we had lunch . Two hours later we went for a walk in the King 's Bathrooms . You wo not believe me , Billal ! We met here the President of Warsaw ! We took photos with him and taught him about the important matters of our country . I have recorded when he greeted our school ! You should see it ! We were back in Radomsko by 9 p.m . , tired , on our last legs , but we were happy ! Billal , I 'm happy and enjoying from my trip . Every activity was amazing . It was a great time ! Write to me quickly , please ! Warm regards , Elizabeth 
