School is one of the most important steps of people 's lives and it must be good for everyone . For this reason , I think that changing teachers every year is one of the worst things about school . In fact , with the same teacher , students can follow a complete educational path that also includes a straight school program . When a new teacher arrives , he has to check the knowledge of the class and , in general , he must repeat a lot of things , because he does not know what the students have studied or what the previous teacher 's method was . It 's also true that changing teachers could be good to avoid bad teachers , but with an efficient school system and prepared teachers , students can really benefit from it , with a consequent increase in their preparation and general knowledge and establishing a great empathy with one who could be one of the most influential people in a student 's life . 
