In my opinion , video games represent a great hobby for children , but they must be limited . Like everything , they have good and bad things . In fact , they are not a useless thing , because , according to some studies , they can help children improve their skills and intelligence . But they are also instructive for them , because specific types of games , such as games with a storyline or a plot based on mythology or history , can help children increase their knowledge and their interests and educate them about important values , like love , respect or bravery too . Obviously they also have negative things , such as inadact games for people under eighteen years or easy access to the community . The latter can be a good thing , but for children it can be also dangerous , especially without a parent 's supervision , which could avoid any type of cyber -bullying . So , I think video games are a great instrument for children . but they must be used wisely . 
The future of travel Do you ever wonder about the future of travel ? I ’ve always imagined how technology could change the ways to travel all over the world . It ’s why I did some research about the current progress . To begin with , the ways in which we can travel have changed notoriously . Transport is faster and cheaper , such as airplanes and boats . Another thing is the fact that if you want to get to know new places , you could do it through virtual tours , we could even do space travel . On the other hand , the attractions will be the same . Throughout the years , people always want to visit the same places , pyramids , museums , archaeological sites and so on . Another thing to consider is that unexpected trip cancellations , delays and emergencies will continue to occur . In conclusion , people think that in the future it will be easier to travel , almost everyone will be able to pay for a trip and space travel will be a possibility . But we have to be conscious that there will be situations in travelling that wo not change and we wo not be able to avoid , like bad weather or technical problems . 
In my view , keeping animals in nature is the best thing to do , because all animals need to breathe and feel nature , it is their nature , they need to live in their natural habitat to survive . The natural habitat of humans is together with a family or some other human . We survive having conversations and interactions with other humans and exchanging experiences . It is necessary for us to have a good life with everyone . Although it is a good idea to keep animals in zoos , because they always will have food and a good place to sleep , and puppies too , it is wrong leave they arrested . The best way is if we just keep animals that got hurt and were rescued . In this case , I think it is safe and healthy for animals stay for some time in zoos and after release them into nature and never keep them broken in a cage . If kids and teens want to learn about animals , they can search on the internet . 
First of all , music is a wonderful thing that a lot of people around the world love . In a lot of schools , there are music sessions , but in other many schools , there are not any music sessions , these differences are not good . I love listening to music but not playing it , so a student like me does not need the music session , so now , we have to find a solution . Now , we could give every student a paper that asks him if he wants to take the music session or no . The students who need it could take it , but the others would have a free session with the metron or they could practice any subject they want . Another solution is changing the form of the music session , for example , we could separate it into two halves . The first one will be for listening and singing if the students want to . The second halve will be for playing music , but the students who do not want to can go to their class . All in all , there should not be differences in music sessions a long diverse and many schools or making students do what they do not like . 
