In my opinion , over time , zoos are becoming dangerous for the environment . In fact , in the last century , the environment has been damaged so much by pollution and by the elimination of green areas . For this reason , zoos represent a dangerous way of altering the natural habitats of animals , which have become , during recent years , much less . I think animals must be free of any type of artificial jail , that brings only the destruction of their normal natural life . I think that in our digital era , animals can be studied and people can also learn from documentaries and innovative ways , such as videos or through virtual reality . Maybe somebody can say that zoos are useful to preserve the animals that risk extinction , but I think that they are wrong , because zoos were only made for humans ' fun , without any consideration of the animals ' needs . So , animals at risk can be supervised into a specific area that is limited , but which preserves their natural habitat . In conclusion , I can say that a world without zoos could be a better world . 
In my opinion , studying abroad is one of the best features of school . In fact , in our world that is very globalized , international experiences are really important for students that will be the future society . Through this possibility , they also have the possibility to visit new countries and meet people all around the world , also getting to know different cultures and different ideas , which , for me , can open their minds to the entire world . Under a didactic aspect , these projects are useful to accelerate language study or improve students ' skills . But I can say that these projects could be very difficult for shy people or people that are not fit for this type of experience , that could be one of the most difficult parts of their life . On the other hand , this experience can be also helpful for them , because it can give the possibility to go beyond these limits and become a better person . In conclusion , I think that studying abroad is a great experience that can only bring benefits to the people that could enjoy it . 
The reason is simple working in cities will make them earn a lot of money . This is because government 's concern is centralized in cities , development in cities is more engaging . Systematically , this will make medical facilities in rural area hard to be accessed by the community . And the impact is medical treatment will not be on demand in rural areas . This causes no balance between the salary for working in cities and in rural areas . This can be solved by the government themselves with the community 's support . We have to raise the voice of rural area people to remind the government that they exist . , . we hope the government can be more concerned about facilities and medical development so their economy will also develop . And medical facilities will be more accessible for the rural community , and then medical doctors will be in demand and will create a balance of salary between working in cities and in rural areas . Despite this problem , medical doctors should not choose their workplace based on salary . Yet , they should consider being the hero in places that need medical treatment , but are hardly accessible . 
