There are fewer and fewer places for animals to live on the earth now . It 's a natural trend when the population rises . Unless we can control our population and resources well , it will be really hard to reserve many places for animals . Under this condition , I think zoos are good places for people to learn about animals , although it might be cruel for these animals since they have lost their freedom . But if zoos can provide proper care for these animals , they might not feel so bad in the zoo . At least , like people , some like to work hard and some like to take a rest . I think it should be similar for animals . Without zoos , many animals might disappear from the earth in a few years . On the contrary , zoos can help to keep some animals from disappearing , due to the population , farming and deforestation destroying natural habitats . One day , when most people learn to respect nature and can live with animals , we can free these animals into the wild . 
