My reasons for learning English Nowadays , more and more non -native speakers have learned and mastered English due to different reasons . Most of them have done it for their studies or work . On average , most of them learned English in their childhood . When I was a child , I also learned English in school . However , English learning in Chinese schools primarily focuses on passing the exam , not on mastering the language in daily life or work . Therefore , I still need to improve my spoken and written English . And there are several reasons for it . Firstly , I need to master English for my master 's program , since all my finance courses are in English . And in two months , I must write my master 's thesis in English as well . Secondly , I need it for job seeking . Since the finance sector is very international , even in Germany , job seekers must speak and write English and German very well . Thirdly , according to my experience , if I have mastered English , I will be able to communicate with my children in English and help them to learn English at an early age . So they will not have the same problems that I suffer now . 
