There is no doubt that earning money is crucial in our life , to grant our life 's necessities , as well as being healthy is crucial to do your daily jobs and chores . Sometimes you fall in a difficult puzzle about which is more important , being healthy or rich . Being healthy can help you to be rich , since a healthy body can do its own work efficiently , without complaining of any diseases . To achieve the goal which may be a dream of being wealthy , you need to have a healthy body and healthy brain , since an ill person ca not do anything , even if he is rich . The second reason why health is more important is that a healthy person can enjoy his time with his friends and family , and eat any kind of food he likes , while only being rich will not mean that you will enjoy your time if you are not healthy and have some diseases . Not having any diseases is a reasonable reason to tend to care about health more than wealth , since having a disease may cause permanent pain , which will be an obstacle many times to eat freely , or go to some places , or do hobbies , or even move , while a healthy person does not have to care about any of these eventualities . 
I do not agree with the opinion that computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities . I have two reasons to support the idea . First , there is a lot of information in books which are held in school libraries . Indeed , you can access what you want to know immediately with your computer in these days . You can find the information online with ease . However , the quantity and quality of information in books is greater than on the internet . In addition , most online information has not been reviewed by any other person . Thus , the precision of the information is not guaranteed . If you are a university student , it is good for you to find the information in the library . You can open a new world through many books . Secondly , there is an advantage that you can write down anything and save it in your book . If you find some information online , you cannot write anything on the website . To understand what you want to know , writing is a crucial factor , because the movement of the fingers accelerates your working memory in the brain . Writing something in books lets you understand something more deeply . For your studies in university life , it is important to recognize things in depth , because researching activities needs a lot of knowledge . To sum up , books are required in universities to make students understand things in depth . 
