In my opinion , the workspace configuration is significantly important to increase efficiency in work . When the offices have a more open design , it can distract more the employees . On the other hand , office partitions provide privacy and sophistication , besides improving the workspace organization . In spite of the fact that an open design office is known as a more modern concept , some American research stated that many employees have difficulties to concentrate on work , therefore it 's essential to reduce distractions in the workspace in order to increase efficiency . Moreover , there are other things which can similarly improve efficiency in work , such as lighting , temperature , table heigh , chair comfort and many other characteristics of the office . In conclusion , enclosed workstations are the most effective type of arrangement , because there are less distractions and , consequently , less wasted work time . In addition , some other improvements in the office can be made to increase efficiency , as exemplified previously . 
Most people are pursuing their dreams of being rich , but not many people are taking care of their health . You can say money is what our lives are all about , however , I think it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . First of all , having physical or mental diseases easily prevents you from being happy , even though you are rich . Our goals and dreams are built on a foundation of being happy . If you had a million dollars but also a serious disease , your money would lose its value , because you might not have enough time to spend all of it , and even more , you would want to spend it on curing your disease . That means health is more valuable than money . Whether you are rich or not , you can still be happy , having a loved one or successful career . But without being healthy , you end up being unhappy . 
