As far as I am concerned , health is the most significant and exceptional thing in the world . You cannot be capable of doing anything unless you are healthy . In this brief essay , I will attempt to explain my reasons . First of all , I would like to start with wealth , in other words , money . Indeed , you can manage to do loads of things , such as buying expensive cars or having a spectacular phone . Even though you can afford to buy something essential , you cannot buy affection and health . Have you ever considered what will happen to your tremendous fortune after you die ? Your facilities or the extent of your fortune wo not be important . Besides , you will marry someone devoid of affection , enthusiasm and sympathy , a person who wo not appreciate you . Accordingly , you wo not be happy unless you find someone who loves you . Consequently , your money wo not be valuable unless you have a soul mate and health , because you cannot manage to do some things without these crucial things . My recommendation is for you to be aware of your treasure . 
In my opinion , this is a paradoxical statement . In general , I think that health is surely the most important thing in people 's lives , because without it we would not be able to do anything . On the other hand , in countries like the USA , healthcare is not free , and poor people could be discriminated against for health treatment . It is also true that middle class people can live healthily without enormous wealth , but it 's also true that there are rare illness that require specific operations and treatment , and they could be too expensive for them . On the other hand , I think that everyone should have access to all health treatment , but it is actually an utopian idea , due to the economic problems that are involving the world . For this reason , I think that the two things are truly connected much more than people expect , because without health , wealth could not exist , but without wealth , nowadays , health is not guaranteed for everyone . 
