I study at the dance conservatory so I have to study music in my school . We study theory of music , history of music and also to play the piano . I do not mind it , but lot of people do not like studying these things . I think it is not necessary to study music hardly in some other school , because people do not need this knowledge for life . But on the other hand , students have to study , for example , physics or chemistry and it is also not important for life , so why do people have to study physics or chemistry and music they do not have to ? Many people cannot understand music , they cannot feel the rhythm , they cannot learn to play a musical instrument or they cannot sing . That is because they are not musically talented and these people usually do not like the music classes at school . But I still think that every student should have some elementary knowledge of music . It is unnecessary to study to play a musical instrument , but they should study a little bit of musical theory or , at least , the history of this beautiful art . 
