I 've already visited some zoos , one in Brazil and another in Germany . But , afterwards , thinking for a while , I concluded that zoos are not good places for animals , because they are not in their habitat and keeping them in a fenced -in place is stressful for them . Once I watched a movie called Blackfish on Netflix , which talked about a whale named Tillikum . It was captured from the ocean where it was living , taking care of its group and humans took it from there to cloister it in one of the most famous aquariums in the world , called Sea World . There it was taught to jump out of the water and to do funny tricks to entertain the public . However , in the background it was cloistered and stressed out . But humans did not take that into account , and one day , during a presentation , the whale freaked out and killed a presenter in front of the public . That said , I believe that humans must live with animals in harmony , as in the highest level possible . 
Changing teacher every year is not good for students , because when students are comfortable talking with their teacher , it 's good for the students and the teacher who wants to help and advise the students . So if we change a teacher every year , students have to start a relationship with a new teacher and it takes time . In contrast , if students have the same teacher for several years , when they have problems , they will be comfortable talking with the teacher . I even read an article named " The Impact of Teacher -Student Interaction on Student Motivation and Achievement . " It said the interaction between a teacher and students is an important thing . On the other hand , when a good relationship has been constructed , a teacher and students enjoy each other and the class , and feel more inspired to do well . In conclusion , a good relationship can improve social skills for a teacher and also students . 
I saw a request for articles in a magazine : We invite you to write about : The Future of Travel . I think I will write my article about this . The Future of Travel is an excellent question . Actually , I do not travel very much , at least until now . I think I have only been on about eleven trips since I was born . So I think I do not have much experience about the future of travel , but I am going to try my best to imagine the way that we will travel in the future . Nowadays , people usually travel all over the world by plane , train and by boat , and those are the only ways that people can travel to anywhere they want nowadays . I think in the future we will still travel by plane , but on a modern plane that can go faster and more safely than now . I also think in the future we could travel by train , but on a modern train that can go really fast . Traveling by trains and by planes in the future will be really different from today , Traveling in the future could be faster . In the future we could travel all over the world in just a few minutes . 
Dear Katie , How are things ? I went to an amazing concert last week . I decided to go to the concert because it was organised in my neighbourhood , close to the park . The price was also quite low , so I was able to afford the tickets . I did not know the performing band before . They are called " Red Guitars . " My mom said they were famous when she was young . Even though I usually listen to another type of music , it was enjoyable . There was a little surprise for the audience - everyone got drinks and snacks . The staff were also really polite and gave us directions where to go . What about you ? Have you been to a concert recently ? Write back soon , Julie 
I use a computer a lot , it 's usually on for the whole duration of the day . However , I use it for work for about 8 hours a day . I use my computer for studying , listening to music and browsing the internet . The most enjoyable task would be writing and improving with the Cambridge English application . In the evenings , I like to watch crime and action movies with my spouse . 
There are over a hundred languages in the world and some of them have already been forgotten . So the language may differ from country to country . When you go somewhere , if you do not know their language , you cannot communicate with people . Sometimes you cannot communicate with your business associates , etc . But there are dragoman out there nowadays . You can hire them too or you can just use a translator on your phone . But knowing a language still has opportunities . Firstly , if you know a language other than your main language , you may learn that language 's culture . You can visit the countries which use that language and you can mingle with them . You may feel free and successful . Secondly , if you want to study or work abroad , you must learn the language which is used in the country where you want to live . Other than this , if your business associates are foreign , you must communicate with them somehow . If you know their language , it will please them . They will feel considered . In conclusion , knowing extra languages does not do any harm . Moreover , when you learn a new language , a new world is opened up to you . You also learn a new culture and a different perspective . Knowing a foreign language in today 's global world is important . 
The expansion and the increase of metropolitan cities has influenced several professional figures . Concerning medical doctors , who are the main topic of this brief essay , they are involved in this evolving phenomenon . In fact , most of them are moving into big cities , where the amount of patients and , more in general , people is larger than in the country . Of course , money is another important reason . As a result , the number of medical doctors has strongly decreased in rural areas , becoming an important issue which has to be fixed as soon as possible . Therefore , what would the solution be ? We would try to answer this hard question . First of all , some procedures for the employment of new doctors should be modified . For instance , ten thousand young doctors are waiting for a job in Italy and , at the same time , some regions do not have enough doctors . Hospitals must be renewed in order to be more efficient and safer than in the past , so that doctors can do their work properly . Because of the pandemic emergency , doctors and any medical figure represents an important resource for fighting this bad enemy , which is everywhere , not only in the big cities . Little towns , rural areas and poor people must not be left alone . 
Dear Sir or Madam , My name is Jules Cool and I am writing this letter concerning the discussion about banning phones from public transport , shops and restaurants , and wanted to let you know what my opinions are on this matter . I want to start with the aspect I am most concerned about , namely banning phones from public transport . The devices are , indeed , necessary for the commuters , since they are being used to buy tickets and to inform themselves about delays . As I strongly believe that our transport system is one of the best in our country , I am worried people will stop using it when there are no phones allowed anymore . Furthermore , I disagree with the council wanting to ban cell phones from shops , because they are not only used to compare prices online , but also to pay for the goods . Therefore , phones are helpful devices when people want to go shopping and must not be prohibited in shops . On the other side , I strongly support the idea of not allowing phones in restaurants , as it is a place where food and connecting with other people should be the focal point . Sadly , it is becoming more and more common to take pictures of the food and post it on social media , instead of enjoying the meal with a friend or family member . Additionally , most customers have stopped communicating with the person sitting in front of them and instead are texting their friends constantly . In brief , I hope you take my elaborations into consideration when deciding upon this matter . Yours faithfully , Jules Cool 
I used Write and Improve for my preparation for the STANAG exams . It was really useful for me , but it is not as good as practising with a real teacher . The problem is that the feedback is not specific enough . It helped me to improve in spelling , but I still have a problem with the composition of sentences . However , it is for free and I can practise whenever I want and that is great . I think that I should recommend it to my colleagues at work , because they need to practise too and they also do not have a real teacher like me . It is still much more useful than just some applications you can download to your phone . The point is that if nothing else , it can help you to be able to think in English . 
My favourite season of the year Phuc When it comes to a favourite season , most people will say it 's spring or summer . But for me , winter is my favourite season . Winter weather is cool and pleasant . In my country , the temperature of air shifts to a completely acceptable range and the water is a pleasant 27 degrees Celsius ( not freezing like some other countries ) . Evenings may be dedicated to wandering and gastronomic experiences and numerous cozy restaurants . Winter is special for me , because during winter there are 2 holidays : one is Christmas and the other is New Year . Those are 2 holidays I like the most . They are the times when everyone can go out and have fun . It makes the city where I live crowded and bustling . In conclusion , winter is my favourite season for 2 reasons : one , it has cool and pleasant weather and two , there are 2 holidays which I like the most that happen during that time : Christmas and New Year . 
Nowadays , studying abroad is the best option and popular , however , it 's hard for some students who have little or no budget , because they compete for scholarships to study abroad . So we can see that there is a disparity between the high -class family and the low -class family . The advantages of studying abroad are improving your language skills and discovering career opportunities abroad . These advantages are more attractive for students who are from a low -class family from other countries . It 's because of the difference between economics and socialities . In developing countries , there are a lot of students who want to study abroad for their future , because most of them are from a low -class family . In contrast , the students from a high -class family can study abroad with their parents ' budget and they do not need to compete for scholarships . However , there are also disadvantages , such as high costs , language and cultural barriers and higher risks . These disadvantages affect all foreign students , by the way , but studying abroad is still a golden opportunity for everyone . 
Video games are the same as movies , but the difference between video games and movies is the experience . I think video games give you more experience , because you feel like it 's you in the game . I feel OK with the children who play video games , but the parents should teach them the difference between video games and real life . Parents should not ban video games , because it can cause a bad relationship between you and your children . The best way is trying to understand the children and if it 's possible , parents should play a video game with the children . It can make your relationship stronger and better , because the children will feel comfortable and happy with their parents who are interested in the same thing . When you play a video game with them , you can teach them about the behavior in the video game and real life . In conclusion , parents should allow their children to play video games and teach them about the difference between video games and real life . 
Hi Paul , Without any doubt , I love to see ' Dancing with Wolves ' . It 's my favorite film . Would you like to see it with me ? It could be fun . Why do I appreciate the film ? In my point of view , it represents the wild part of a human being . It is a road movie . I adore the photography of the film , where you see the huge American landscapes . I 'm sure you are going to adore the film too . 
In my point of view , I think that both could be a good way to learn English . On the one hand , if you have only one teacher for many years , you can create bonds with him and he can see your weak points and focus on them . However , if you are always with the same teacher and he always teaches you in the same way , you can get bored or maybe his teaching method is not the most suitable for you . On the other hand , if you have more than one teacher , you can learn different learning methods , because each teacher has different teaching methods and personal characteristics . Besides , it can be more interesting for you , because every year you 'll get to know new people . To sum up , both have good things , but if I had to pick one , I would pick having more than one teacher , because I think that it might be more fun and probably better for my learning . 
Healthy living is the most popular topic every year . People believe that it can help you live a longer life . If you read articles or health magazines , they 're all about exercise , healthy eating , sleeping and nutritious food . So we ca not say that exercise is not the most important thing , but there are also other things . Some people may have time for exercise , but not everyone can do that , especially the working -age population . Working people are always busy and exhausted with their work , so it 's difficult to organize their time for working and also exercise . On the other hand , there are also alternative options for being healthy , such as healthy eating and getting enough sleep . It 's simpler than exercise and everyone can do it . Although healthy eating is easier than exercise , in some countries , healthy foods are more expensive than fast foods . To solve this problem , people can choose nutritious foods that they can find in articles . A healthy lifestyle is not only about exercise , so we can choose alternative options , such as healthy eating , getting enough sleep and choosing nutritious foods . It 's not easy to be healthy , but it 's important for your body . 
Today I am going to talk about food . Food is anything we eat when we feel hungry , but be careful when you choose your food and also be smart . One of my best dishes is spinach , I can eat it all day at any time . It is green leaves and my mother cooks it with some water beside the meat . I like this food because it is a plant , and it is healthy and does not have any oil , starches or a lot of calories , and as I told you before , be smart when you choose your own food . 
I like sleeping ! I like sleeping in a tall bed , in a quiet bedroom . I need three pillows , fresh bed sheets , and a light blanket . The room must be in the dark , without any light entering into the room . When I am going to sleep , I have to be pretty tired . Just before switching off the light , I take a little time to read . This reading permits me to fall asleep . I think I move very much during my sleep . Why can I say that ? Because when I see my face , especially my hair , I know I have had an eventful sleep . 
I like sleeping in a dark and quiet room . I believe that sleeping with a light on , even a small light , and with noise , can disturb the quality of the sleep . Speaking on a biological level , our body needs a dark and quiet place to rest and stay completely relaxed . The human being has evolved in this way . Since the beginning of time we have done it , sleeping in a dark place . The light on and noise are strange for our rest . This situation can affect our circadian cycle and as a result of sleeping in this way , we can feel tired all day long . 
There is a question that television entertains , but can it also educate ? That is an amazing question for us . And to answer the question , we have to think carefully . In my opinion , I think television is a good way to entertain , but also an amazing way to educate our children and ourselves . We can see television played an important part in our childhood . It made our childhood happier and more interesting and it also teaches us a lot of useful things . I think television is the best way to educate our children and teach us a lot of things that we do not know . It can also have a lot of information for us to know about the world . But to make television able to educate our children and ourselves effectively is a very hard thing and it takes time to do it . But it is not impossible . I believe that we have a lot of people who have a passion for educating all over the world who can do it and it is the meanest thing for all of us . Then we wo not need much money to learn anything . 
I prefer sleeping in a dark and quiet room to sleeping with a small light on because I can feel calm in the dark and get a better sleep . I could also sleep in a noisy environment , but I would not like to do so . If it 's bright outside at my bed time , it would not be dark , it could even be noisy . Then , I would be able to sleep in those conditions . I would not care about the situation at that time . 
Hello , I like sushi , it 's Japanese traditional food . Have you ever tried it ? I usually eat it at weekends . It 's delicious , and healthy because it 's made of fish and rice . I recommend it to you especially " salmon . " Although it 's not a traditional dish , it tastes great . If you have not had it before , then why do not you give it a try ? 
I like to sleep in the dark . I also like to listen to music to fall asleep . I recognize that I can sleep everywhere . Moreover , I can sleep at weddings or birthday parties . I can sleep while we are driving for our holidays . I fall asleep when we have been driving for more than 10 minutes . Sometimes I sleep with the door opened , and that is not a problem for me . I can sleep everywhere and this is very practical . 
Hi Sam , Here in Germany we eat a lot of potatoes . I like to eat potatoes as well . I eat them with a lot of things . For example , I eat potatoes with vegetables . I like potatoes because they are changeable . You can eat potatoes in various creations . 
I prefer to sleep in a dark room , with as little noise as possible . Sometimes I like to watch TV before I sleep in the room too . For me it is important to lie down when I am so tired , and want to sleep . I never go to bed without the desire to sleep . I do not sleep for a long time , so I need to spend that time to sleep very well . I wake up very early every day , and I love to sleep for a short time after lunch . 
I appreciate meat a lot , many kinds of meat . In Brazil , we often eat meat , by many people every day , in diverse forms . I like meat very much . I love to make a barbecue on the weekend with my relatives and friends , for example . 
In the beginning , it was a habit that you used to do . I used to sleep in a dark room , to feel more comfortable and more relaxed . As to it being quiet , it 's something you ca not always control , because in many countries we have noisy neighbors who are still awake after midnight , and you ca not handle them . Doctors always say that to get all the benefits of sleeping you need to sleep in a dark and quiet room . So always try to make your sleep as good as you can to get a great day . 
Television used to be the most popular audio -visual medium . There are many TV programs that can entertain and also educate , such as documentaries . But nowadays , this is an era of technology , so there are many audio -visual presentation devices . These devices are more convenient and fascinating than television . However , television is still the most popular platform for news , but in the new generation , people access social media by using their smartphones . On the other hand , television is the best device for a family . Watching television as a family can build strong family relationships , such as making conversation and having fun together . Parents may worry that while kids can become addicted to their cell phones , it 's a golden opportunity . I even read an article named " Watching TV can be good for kids . " It said TV shows can inspire kids to try new activities and engage in " unplugged " learning . In conclusion , television is still very useful for kids and it 's the best device for accessing the news . 
Thanks to the extension of the communication network and the promotion of the Internet over the last two decades , a new way of being able to learn has appeared . Online learning is a system that is much more flexible and adapts to different ways of living . Thanks to being able to study online , the different resources and materials available have greatly increased , as well as adapted to people 's different schedules and lives . Now , it is easier to find information about what you want to learn and you have less rigid schedules , being able to adapt . On the other hand , the individual 's demands must be higher . Now , it is up to each person to find the motivation and to follow up , trying to find areas without distraction and to take advantage of the moments available . So , I recently discovered a new website to improve your writing , it 's called Write&Improve , where I can write and rewrite my own composition at some levels ( Beginner , Intermediate and Advanced ) forcing me to improve my grammar and write about some subjects and topics . Although this way of learning sometimes is not easy to follow up and continue working because you have to do homework yourself , but if you plan well and motivate yourself , you can improve every day . The Write & Improve method is helping me to adapt and incorporate new grammar into my English level . 
In my opinion , there is no doubt that being healthy is much more important than being rich . However , it is important to realise what being healthy actually is . The fact is that to be healthy you have to take care not just of your body , but your mind too . The body is quite easy . You have to eat the right food and work out every single day and you will be fine . But what about your mind ? For example , I do not need money to be happy , but I need to work hard and do my job as well as I can , otherwise I feel useless . So , I would rather sleep less and be more stressed to be good at my job , rather than taking a day off . I could have a day off , but I would feel like afterwards . And if your mind is not set properly , the body will follow . 
I would like to recommend all of the readers a website called " Write and Improve . " I 've been using this resource since September and definitely can say it 's helping me a lot ! Thanks to W&I , I improved my vocabulary and sense of grammar a lot . Writing is easy and enjoyable for everyone , so the idea of doing it in another language and then seeing some feedback and my progress is incredibly smart ! I like how you can observe the changes you make over the months and even be told what language level you 're currently at . I also enjoy the feedback I get every time - when I combine it with Grammarly , I start to see mistakes more clearly and - more importantly - understand what I did and why I did it wrong ! The only difficulty I had to face was with the online connection . It 'd be amazing if I could use this tool everywhere , no matter if there 's a stable Internet connection . One of the last negative things I can think about is that you have to know basic English - both grammar and vocabulary . Of course , the section " for beginners " is helpful , but it 's all about writing without any clues expect a topic . All and all , as I said earlier , I really recommend this site . I have seen changes in my grammar after a few days of everyday usage . My friends seem satisfied too . I hope you will try it out ! 
I like to sleep in a quiet room where there is not any noise , I do not like it if there is a TV in the room , because if there is a TV in the room , I cannot sleep well as it 's a distraction and the body ca not rest . But also , I can sleep with noise , I do not have a problem with noise , I just need to concentrate to be able to sleep . A way to be able to sleep is by reading a boring book or use a slow breathing for the body to relax and then it can rest well . 
The mode of sleeping is different for each person . Light and noise are elements that work to help or interfere in this moment . I do not have any problems going to bed . Usually , I sleep in other situations with light and noise , but I prefer to sleep in a dark room where there is not any noise or any song . I need only a place on which to put my head and I can fall sleep very fast . A long time ago , I was working in the country city and I had to take a bus every day from the bus station . When I sat down , immediately I took a nap . Then , sleeping for me does not need to have special conditions for it to happen , I can take a nap really easily and fast . 
Choosing where to live as a university student is an important decision to make . In my opinion , when university students have their own places , they can have many benefits compared to living with their families . First , by living away from their families , those students learn to be independent and not rely on others ' help . It pushes them to be serious and responsible since they now need to perform many things that they previously had not even thought about . For example , they need to find and evaluate a living space which is suitable for their situation . In addition , they need do everyday tasks , such as buying groceries , regularly cleaning the place , etc . Second , living on their own , students can have freedom and full control of their time . They could utilize their time for activities that enable them to achieve their goals . For instance , they might need to spend more time at night to study for a hard subject or find a work opportunity to complement their studies . This is possible because they are free from their family responsibilities and schedules . In the end , when students live on their own , they learn to take care of their life matters and focus their time and effort on things that interests them and provides a chance for rapid growth . This choice puts them on the road of success both as professionals and members of society . 
I love pizza . It is a special food I like to eat . I eat pizza on the weekends , but sometimes I eat it even during the week days . I like pizza because the flavor is delicious . If you order pizza from a good pizzeria , I 'm sure they use the best ingredients and the sauce can be the best too . Some pizzerias use a special tomato sauce , made with fresh ingredients . They are the best ! 
It is more important to be healthy than to be rich . This is a statement that my teacher asked me to write an essay about . In my opinion , I think health is the most important thing in life . And of course , health is more important than wealth , because if you do not have good health , you ca not do anything well . We can earn money in different ways and we can earn money whenever we want , but we ca not earn health and , when we lose health , we ca not do anything we want or need , so that is why to be healthy is more important than to be rich . But you can see that there are a lot of people who are trying to earn money , but they do not take care of their health and that is really bad . That is a serious problem nowadays . They just care about making money , but they do not take care of their health , and it is awful for them . When they get old , they wo not have enough health , then they will have to spend the money that they tried to make when they were young to take care of their health in a hospital . 
My preferences are , sleeping in a relaxed and silent bedroom , without too much noise and light . However , I am used to sleeping in any condition . In my life I have traveled a lot , therefore I have slept in amazing hotels and really nasty rooms . Due to my lived experiences , I could sleep in almost any situation . The past summer , I slept in a campsite , and I could bear it without any problem . I usually listen to a podcast when I go to bed . In conclusion , any place for me is good to sleep in . 
What ? - I love Chinese food . I am not sure if you know it . Maybe in your country you do not have this type of food . I do not enjoy going to restaurants , so I have decided to prepare my own food . I did a Chinese food course ten years ago . Nowadays , I eat this kind of food almost every day . I relish Chinese food , because it is tasty , healthy and colourful . There are many types of dishes , however I revel in the vegetable ones . In my opinion , these vegetables are the best choice because you have all the energy , nutrients and flavour in one spoonful . In conclusion , try it if you can . 
Nowadays , we hear very often about how young people underestimating the importance of doing sports . Many do not understand or do not want to comprehend the fact that sitting in front of our computers is not the best activity to do all day long . We need to do some sort of physical activity in order to stay healthy . However , because if it , is it crucial to force students to do sport at least 3 times a week ? Does everyone have to attend PE classes at their school and should we even have PE classes at school ? In my opinion , there are some exceptions , which we should take into consideration . Firstly , as I have already pointed out in the first paragraph , sports activities are valid for achieving a healthy lifestyle . This is why I think every student , starting from the first grade of primary school and ending in the second grade of secondary school , should have obligatory PE classes at school 3 or 2 times a week . The third graders should have the possibility to do sport at school , but I think it should be an extra -curricular activity , since the third grade ends with A levels and young people , who face this exam , must focus on studying . Another issue that I want to write about is that some students may do sports outside of school . In that case , school should take that fact into account because then , those students should be forced to exercise at school . If they do enough sports activities after lessons , then why should they take PE classes at school ? They only waste their time by doing that . Overall , I believe that sports activities are very important , especially for young people to avoid , for example , obesity . It is good that schools care about their students in that matter , however , they should consider making PE classes not obligatory if a student does sports during their free time . 
Dear friend , How is it going ? I 'm spending my free time watching movies and TV series . Regarding movies , I watched a movie which amazed me . Its title is " Taxi Driver . " Directed by Martin Scorsese , it talks about a man , Travis Buckle , who applies for a job as a taxi driver . We are in the 70 's and the USA has just concluded the Vietnam War , remembered as a disastrous event . The isolation and madness are relevant in the protagonist 's behaviour . This is the reason why I love it . The evolution of his mind is the interpretation key of the movie . I recommend it to you . I believe you will appreciate it . Let me know what you think about it . Lots of love , Jerry . 
Hello Jim , How are you ? Some days ago , you sent me an email in which you asked me if I had been to that music concert . Well , this is the reason why I 'm writing this email . As you know , I went to the concert of my favourite rock band , the Red Hot Chili Peppers . What an amazing experience ! Listening to own favourite music band at a concert was a totally different experience . In addition , there were many people , crowded and attached to each other like sandwiches . But it seemed not to be important with respect to the band . They were fantastic , performing not only the last released album , but also their greatest hits , such as ' Callfornication ' , ' Give it away ' and so on . The whole audience jumped with Flea the bassist and Anthony the frontman of the rock band . The concert lasted three and a half hours , more or less . The time passed very fast ! It seemed to have lasted just some minutes . Actually , this was the only drawback . Anyway , I 'm going to see them again . Next time , you have to go with me ! See you , lots of love Jack 
