I 'm 34 years old , and live with my husband and my cat . We are quiet people , we love the calm places , and we always sleep together in a dark room and with no loud sounds . That permits us to rest , talk , think , share and sleep , so we prefer the first option . NA , . we have an inconsiderate neighbor , she has a party every week with loud music , many people , alcohol , and cigarettes ; they do not permit us to relax and rest . We think she is a real problem . Honestly , it 's difficult to keep calm and rest when she has a party because the sound is strong and we ca not sleep . 
What are the reasons for this problem ? The reasons are diverse for this reason , so then we will analyze some situations and factors which force medical doctors to work in some cities instead of a rural areas . - Notoriety to work in a famous hospital : most of the important hospitals are in big cities , for instance , Memorial Hospital is in NY City and you can get more resources to enter into some research & development projects . - Experience working on specific specialities : most of the medical doctors want to specialize in specific medical areas like traumatology , cardiology , oncology and hematology . These specialities cannot be practised in small hospitals or rural areas , so then , physicians would prefer to work at these hospitals which are in big cities . - Better salary : this factor is the consequence of the last 2 factors commented before . If you have experience and notoriety , you will earn more money because you will treat more patients , you will receive some offers from private hospitals and you can combine your practise in public and private health care , having two salaries is quite comment in a health care environment . Understanding these 3 key factors , that 's why they want to work in big hospitals . I will just try to answer your second question " How can it be solved ? " It will be solved if we can build some big hospitals which connect some rural areas and meet notoriety , experience and salary . This concept is called Reference Hospital and you can attract some medical doctors to these rural areas and , of course , ensure a salary which will be competitive against the medical doctors working in big cities . To sum up , if you want to have good medical doctors in a rural area , you should get notoriety , experience and salary , but also , a work -life balance which they you can find in most of the rural areas , such as fresh air , inner peace , not rushing , less stress and living close to the mountains or coast . 
I like to sleep with a small light on and in a quiet room , but it sometimes is difficult when you are married with two daughters and a dog . My wife is always snoring and I need to move to our living room , so then , when my partner is not snoring , there appears like a fairy , my little sunflower Olivia who would like to sleep with her mother and again I have to move to our sofa , even though our sofa is so big and comfortable . To sum -up , my best option is to sleep with my family at home , even though , I cannot sleep . 
Zoos are good places for adults and children to see animals , to build a relationship between humans and animals . Nowadays , people in the western world have little or no contact with animals . Because of industrialization and urbanisation , there is no place or only bad conditions for animals . People are used to going to a zoo and it is a part of their life . No one asks themselves why animals have to be in a cage . And what about the animals , are they really happy to live in a cage ? Animals cannot speak to us and they cannot tell us their feelings . My opinion is animals do not belong in the city . You must not keep animals in town , but rather send humans into the wild . The living space of animals is not the town . Animals do not have to adapt to our city life . That is not natural . NA , . we have to show consideration towards animals . We must ask ourselves if that way of thinking and acting fits with our values and imaginations . 
