Today is the day . Today will be the start of a new chapter of my life and I hope that this year will be a good year for me and for my friends . I would like to learn more about history and philosophy . Math would be so nice , but in fact , I would like to learn more about life . That is why I said history and philosophy . Without math , it would be lacking , because I believe that experiences and knowledge make us strong . I was going to say we should be strong when we are in trouble , but suddenly I realized , even if we are not in trouble we need that . It would be more tasteful if we knew what kind of history there is where we travel or what kind of places have more possibilities to enjoy more . And if I have a chance to do it , I would like to learn a new language . There is not enough time to learn a new language for one year , but actually it could be a good starter for it . German would nice . By doing it , I could end up on my German mission . I have to keep my passions and work hard for them . 
We live in an age when many of us are more interested in getting lots of money rather than taking care of ourselves and having a healthy life . However , I do not totally agree with this way of living . If you 're searching for how to be happy , being rich is not the best option . In my opinion , being healthy is more important than being rich . Why ? Because there is no point in having a lot of money if you 're seriously sick , then you cannot enjoy that money . Furthermore , life gives us pleasures for which you do not need to spend money and on the other hand , being rich only implicates having a stressful life . Despite this , currently people are only interested in making a lot of money , they work so hard and spend their lives trying to have lots of money . To sum up , we have to be focused on taking care of our health . We need to learn that money does not buy happiness , real love and tranquillity . The happiness that money gives us is momentary , like our lives . 
Music and studying music is a really interesting subject to discuss together . In my opinion , I think music is really complicated and also a very subtle thing that people invented . I think music is the language of feelings , that language can touch our soul . Studying music is not easy , on the other hand , it is very difficult to be good at music . So let me answer the question , do you have to learn an instrument , you must not learn an instrument but I encourage you to learn how to play an instrument you love . Then you will see that it is an amazing thing you have not done , I promise that you will not regret it . Learning how to play an instrument at a basic level maybe is a simple thing , but if you want to be master at the instrument you are playing , then it is a different story . Being a master in the instrument you are playing is a really hard journey , it will not be easy at all . If you want to be a master in the instrument you are playing , you have to practice playing it regularly for a long time , but it is worth it . I think learning how to play an instrument is a good thing to do when you have free time , and learning to play an instrument can teach you how to be patient , and it also teaches you a lot of things that are very good for you and your life . Do you think music is the best way to touch someone 's feelings ? I think music is the language of feelings . When I listen to a piano piece , I feel so peaceful and lightly , it makes me remember my childhood , is not it beautiful ? I ca not imagine what we would have been like without music . 
Write and Improve is a really useful program . I like it very much . It evaluates my writing skill , so I can see how my writing level is . Basically , it gives me all kinds of tasks and then I write sentences based on them . Afterwards , the program will evaluate my sentences respectively . If I have made mistakes in my sentences , it will point them out to me . Thanks to that , I can easily practise my writing in English . Although there is no specific explanation about the wrong points , I feel some improvement in my writing . It would be better if I had a tutor for my writing . It 's okay with this program for now . Anyway , I 'm going to use this from now on , so I can improve my writing skill in English every day . I think the important thing is consistency . If we want to be fluent in English , we have to be persistent and consistent . The more I write in English , the better I will write in English . I would recommend my classmates to try Write and Improve , absolutely . 
I do not disagree with the fact of children playing video games . I believe there are pros and cons . Video games can help children develop many cognitive and physical abilities , such as motor coordination , critical thinking , self control , the ability to think fast and so on . It is good , because currently these abilities are becoming a need for the next generations . Currently , video games can be highly advantageous . There are so many competitions and the teams that participate in them are composed of its are composed with proof video game players . Therefore , if your children like playing video games , you can show them this activity as a professional job . But there some cons too . Children need limits , they cannot play video games all day long . Children need to work on their other abilities , the so -called soft skills . Children need to know how to handle other people and how to solve problems . Children have to be responsible and video games ca not help with that . 
Getting information and exercises on paper , having a plethora of books to carry and writing with a pen : That is what an ordinary school nowadays looks like . However , this could change a lot , even soon . According to many IT experts , the school system of today is very out of date and needed to be modified a long time ago . In times of digitalisation , industrial countries such as Germany have implemented digitalisation in almost every area , except school . Nonetheless , the measures to start digitalisation in school are there and it is not a big deal for western countries to do so . Specialists have explained what a modern school in the future could look like : Instead of carrying dozens of books , a simple tablet or laptop will set and end the severe burden of students . Every book and exercise will be contained in one thing . But there is even more . Writing on a white - or blackboard will not be necessary anymore since the writing of the teacher is directly sent to the students . And why are we even talking about teachers ? Even today there are online platforms galore , which provide thousands of students with video lessons and exercises for free . 
I would like to tell you about my favourite dish . It 's a Polish speciality that we mostly eat once a year on a Fat -Thursday . I like it because of its delicate and crunchy texture . It 's also really sweet . 
The space where we work is one of the most important aspects that can help you to be more productive and creative . Thinking about it , many companies around the world have been studying many different types of offices that could better fit with their employees . They have invested much money and time to find the balance between what is the best for the people who work for them , so this can be good for the company because people that are working happy can produce more and better . Some giant companies , like Facebook and Google , are in the top of mind when we think about the modern relationship between employer and employee . More than offices with open concept , there you will find offices which have no tables and desks how we were used to seeing in traditional offices a few years ago . The changes are not just when we talk about the physical space being much bigger . People who work for Google , for example , have no specific timetable to work , they just need to do what they have to do , so that way , they can make their own time to work . When we talk about how the way to work in offices has changed in the last few years , it can cause some confusion or perhaps we have the impression that every company in the world has changed and every office is now open concept and you will have great flexibility to work in your own way . But it is not exactly true even you work in one of these companies that was told in the last paragraph , probably you will hardly find some others that work in the same way . 
Hello everyone , It is a pleasure to talk to you , today . I want to tell you about my favourite food . The truth is it is a simple food , but I love it . My favourite food is sushi , I do not prepare it so when I look forward to eating it , it is necessary to ask for a domicile . I have two places to ask for it , one is economical and it has a good taste and another is expensive , but it has a lot of options and its taste is excellent , I love it . My husband thinks that it carries a little bit and he feels hungry soon afterwards , so he eats sushi with a little rice and a drink . 
I am learning English for lots of reasons . One of them is that I had to have a certain level to graduate from university and I need proper English skills because of my level now . And I will probably use English in my future career . However , there is something more about learning English . The most important aspect for me is books . I love reading and I read a lot , but most of the books I am reading are in English only . I ca not imagine that I would not be able read those great pieces . And the other important thing is , for example , the Jocko podcast . I have been listening to it for about five hundred hours with no subtitles . The thing is that no one will translate so many hours of the podcast , so the only way is to translate it on your own . 
English language learners need to practice English on a daily basis . Therefore , they should find resources and tools to help them do so . One tool that could potentially help learners develop their writing skills is a service called Write and Improve . Although it has its limitations , I believe that this service will help the students write better . The website offers the student various writing prompts which are classified by students ' writing abilities : beginner , intermediate , and advanced . These prompts are about many topics , such as education , art , technology , etc . In addition to the variety of topics , the website has various types of writing , such as narrative , opinion , and argument . The students are guaranteed to find writing tasks that match their need and interest . Moreover , the service provides feedback to the learners about every piece they write . After the student finishes writing the text according to the task instruction , they can submit it for evaluation , and after the evaluation , the student sees a score ranging from A1 to C2 and the sentences that could be improved highlighted using a varying degree of yellow . The darker the color , the more problems the sentence has . The students then use the feedback given to make changes and repeat the process until a sufficient quality has been achieved . Additionally , every evaluation is recorded in the system so that the user can see past task attempts and compare it with the most recent ones . Finally , I think Write and Improve is a very good service for those who are aiming to improve their written communication . The large number of tasks along with their diversity in topics and purposes ensures that there are always suitable for every writer . In addition , the feedback gives the writer guidance regarding where improvements could be made and an indication of their writing level . Nevertheless , the feedback is sometimes ambiguous and frustrating for some learners . For instance , erroneous sentences are highlighted , but there is no information about what the error is . Those who do not have full mastery of English grammar and mechanics will have difficulty determining possible ways to improve the sentences without relying on the help of teachers or other services . What 's more , the feedback often is not accurate because it is fully automated using artificial intelligence . For example , it fails to mark basic spelling mistakes . Despite the issues mentioned , it is the best option available for students that do not have access to qualified teachers and , hopefully it will improve in the near future . 
There are two types of accommodation which students have to choose when they go to university . The first one is to stay with their families and the second one is to move away from them and live independently . It 's hard to say which is better because both of them have their pros and cons . But to my way of thinking , I prefer the second . Firstly , it helps them grow up . Moving away from family and living independently also means that they have to do most things by themselves . For example , when they stay at home , their mothers make lunch , dinner for them . But when they live alone , they have to do it by themselves . They also learn how to spend money in a smart way . Secondly , they have a chance to relax and convenience to study and follow their educational life . If students live separately from their families , they will focus more on their studies and could achieve more achievements . On the contrary , living at home can lead to many bad results . Without preparation for life 's struggles , students can suffer from a deficiency of practical experiences . The family 's overprotective process usually solves almost all their troubles , which results in the elimination of endeavors when they have to face problems alone . Of course , this way of living has some of its downsides as well . But , I believe it is still a better choice for students . 
I think that having new teachers each year is better than having the same teacher for several years . The teachers have their own ways of teaching respectively , we cannot receive all techniques just from one teacher . So , I prefer to have a lot of teachers . But if I find my favourite teacher , I could possibly stick with that teacher . In any case , I have to take many lessons from many teachers . I do not think that having only one teacher is a bad idea . He or she would have more personal information about us . Because of that , they could teach us more suitable techniques . It is definitely a good thing . However , there is a limit what one person can teach to their students . I assume it is inevitable . Having a lot of teachers could be better , because there are more aspects of studies . We may find more suitable study methods for ourselves . This is why I think students benefit more from having new teachers each year . 
We live in a world that is changing very fast . What was considered trendy a decade ago is now old -fashioned . Do we really still need to learn foreign languages in times of artificial intelligence ? Maybe we should just trust our robots to do this job . I will try to answer this question in the essay below . Some futurologists claim that learning languages will become obsolete in the next few years . Tools like Google translator keep improving and people who do not know English can easily communicate with English speakers . Future developments in this area are highly possible . A group of scientists has been working on a special chip which will be located in the brain . This chip will allow us to translate from all of the languages . Although all this sounds promising , there are still some serious doubts . First of all , Google translator is still not perfect . In the case of English , it is effective , but not so much regarding other languages . The language brain chip will initially be very expensive and people will be afraid to use it . In my opinion , this kind of tool will not be commonly used before 2050 . 
In contemporary society , we are told to always seek truth . It does not matter how hurtful this truth may be - most people would advise you to never lie , even when it would make a situation better . Is this really applicable to real , everyday life ? Let 's find out . I would like to recall one specific example - you are a nurse helping an old couple , one of them is laying on their death bed , even though they are not really aware of it . What is the best to tell their significant other ? They are already in pain and agony , why would you make the situation even worse ? In this situation , and situations similar to the described , I think the best decision is to tell a partial truth . You should not pull them down by saying there is no hope , but convincing everything will be fine would not be ethical either . But what about other examples ? Because , for sure , there are a lot of circumstances when it would be the best to just tell the truth ( such as cheating or playing truant ) . My opinion is you should rethink everything and then decide alone , but remember , no lie can live forever . All things considered , the truth can be valuable and most of the times is , but you have to observe the whole situation and then calculate how much good for both sides there is . 
The vast majority of the world thinks death is terrible . They are afraid of the post -death process and leaving their loved ones behind . They do not think it through , but actually , resisting death is an instinctive act . The way I see it , both samples have their own advantages and people 's choices may change according to their personality . To begin with , a short but intense life is perfect for people who just live in the moment and do not care or are ambitious people . We can view this issue from different angles . From the ambitious part , we can say that a short but filled with achievements life is perfect for them . Such people do not have to live long , they will be the happiest in the world when they achieve their goals . If they live long and they cannot achieve anything after a while , they can be frustrated , devastated and angry . This kind of life will be a torture for them and they can tug their loved ones into misery with them . NA , . people who just live in the moment and do not care about other things do not waste their lives on responsibilities , jobs or anything that would interfere with what they want . They just need to fulfill their daily needs , and concurrently with having fun . Such people do not want to live long but calmly , the majority of them do not want to get old . On the other hand , I think most people want to live long and calmly . They want steady jobs , happy wedlock and above all peace . Such people know how to be happy with the little things and do not seek adventure in daily life . They prefer spending quiet days with loved ones and things and doing different things occasionally to intense lives . All in all , I will not prefer either . The way I see it , we should mix these two lifestyles . We must live our youth to the fullest and live a quiet life after a certain age . We have to go where our hearts take us when we are young and be open to different things , try everything we can try . When we get older and our responsibilities increase , we must lead a quieter lifestyle . Of course , this does not mean leaving all our wishes behind , we should not give up on things that will make us happy . This is my point of view on this subject . Everyone chooses a lifestyle according to their character . 
I was practicing on a speaking website whose name is free4talk . com . And there was a teacher and I asked him for help with my writing skills . After that , he wanted me to send an example of my writing . He said that I have way to go to progress in writing skills . That was the day I met with Write and Improve . Since then , this website has become the first choice for my writing training . It is my favourite because of its features . I can set a timer and I do not think about any topics . They are so helpful and they save time for me . Because it takes so much time to find a topic . I believe that they do in order to new learners . Initially , I did not understand the checking system . It was colouring the lines yellow and it was rating my skills between A1 to C2 . Then I searched and found it dictates that some problem could be in that sentence . I was making so many mistakes , but thanks to this application , I realized my mistakes and I decreased them . After you check your mistakes , then you correct them , you can check with the menu . Actually , I have not seen any difficulties but page orientation . When you check your text , the checked text order is not on the same line as the original text . I ca not always match the lines between two screen . Maybe it could be better if it were synchronised with the original one . I recommend it for everyone , especially for intermediates . 
Nowadays technology has advanced so fast , we are able to get a lot of information wherever we are and whenever we want . This easy access to information has benefited many students and schools . However , some people think this technology will replace the traditional ways of learning . Firstly , students do not need to spend a lot of time in libraries , or schools do not need to get lots of books for the school population . You can get electronic books on the internet and check them with tablets , computers and even with cellphones . Nevertheless , these kinds of devices wo not replace traditional books . Some reasons for this are the fact that not all electronic books have a good transcription , good books cost a lot of money and others are not available in electronic format . To sum up , having electronic books has advantages , such as you can access your favorite books from your computer , but even with the advantages , electronic books should not replace traditional books . Many students and teachers prefer this kind of reading , because many times the information is more reliable . 
I 've got to say that I really love books and I 've got my own little library . I buy my books and I am not into reading Kindle books . However , in universities it is something different . During my studies , it was necessary to have some books from our library , although I rarely used them . I think that it is much more practical to have all the materials on the computer , so you can find anything by a quick search and you can copy the most important information and make your own tools for studying . The problem is that you rarely need to study just one book . You have to switch between them and it is much faster on your computer screen . There is so much information that you have to process these days and everything is constantly changing . And that is the other important aspect . You can update your online documents , but you ca not print all the books every time there is something new . 
Indeed , some video games can have a negative impact on children . But , in general , video games are not necessarily bad for children . There are a lot of educational games in the world , for example . Children may learn lots of vocabulary through video games . They could learn social skills in some cases . Moreover , playing video games is safe in terms of children 's bodies . Playing outside can be dangerous , especially for children . Besides , I think that forbidding children from playing video games can rather have a negative impact if the children want to play video games . They could feel pressure because of the strict rules . Of course , playing video games all the time is bad for their health . There is a problem that children do not play outside nowadays . They should sometimes play outside , so they can do exercise . In conclusion , we should not forbid our children from playing video games . The thing is , we should watch out for the video games that our children are playing . If the game is not suitable for our children , then we must tell our children not to play it . When it 's not the case , we should let the children play freely . 
Hello , My favorite food is pizza , even though I do not usually eat it very often because it is not good for my health . I used to eat it every other weekend , on the other hand , now I do not eat anything because it is bad for my health . I like pizza more than other foods because it is really fancy and thus it is easy to get and it is cheap . 
This is a real problem that we have to solve . As city people , we ca not close our eyes on rural areas . On the other hand , we ca not close our for on doctors . Nobody has to work where they do not want to . It is a two -sided problem . Rural folk want to get treated well and the doctors want good living standards . In my opinion , this ca not be solved between rural folk and doctors . It is a matter for the government and health department . If the wages depend on where you work , it has to be changed . A country has to be one body . From villages to city centers . Some people do not want only money . They want to wander around , visit a museum , go shopping . And they also want to feel safe when they walk . This all interests the government . If you want doctors to go where the mission is , you should provide them these standards . If you decided to do it , it will take time . That is for sure . One life could be wasted while you are developing the rural areas . So you have to assign enough doctors when you are in the process . This could be provided incentives . If you say , I will give more money for rural doctors for a while , someone could utilize it . It could be a chance for newly graduated students . And I wonder if the health department announces that they will assign new doctors to rural areas if it can also help to develop . For instance , in my country , if you work in the government , you have to work on the east side , which is rural , for five years minimum . And if you provide good living standards , it will become a chance to save money , especially for youngsters . I hope that every member of a country feels equal . 
Hello everyone , Today , I want to write about the advantages and disadvantages of studying abroad , I will mention my opinion . Studying abroad has a lot of advantages , such as : 1 . People get to know other cultures and features about food , languages , buildings , nature , laws , clothes , weather , devices , drinks , money , animals , plants , history , etcetera . 2 . People can travel to other cities nearby , because they can use buses , the underground , cars , motorcycle , bikes or walk , due to it not being expensive and find tourist plans to go between cities . 3 . People study and know the different levels of grades , if they search for a degree , it is good for them in their country of origin . 4 . People can study and learn other languages , because they need to speak to other people . 5 . People can enjoy the seasons , because in many countries there are not four seasons . However , it is important to mention that there is a big disadvantage , that is people are generally alone in a country , so far away from their house , so they can feel sad , afraid , discrimination , poverty , hunger , etcetera . In conclusion , I think studying abroad is a big opportunity and it is necessary to try it . Unfortunately , I cannot travel to another country , because I am poor and my family does not have the money to pay for my tickets and to stay there . Now , I am thirty -four and have a good job , so I can think about travelling , but only on holiday . I hope to do it this year or very soon . 
Dear mr . Council I am writing to you because of your last proposal . I am glad that you care and that you can identify the current problem . The proposal about banning the use of mobile phones would be a cure to our digital dementia , and it ca not be sooner . In my opinion , it is maybe a little bit too radical . Mobile phones in restaurants are destroying our culture and our ability to communicate with each other . We do not talk any more . Although we sit at one table , it is like there is a mile long gap between us . On the other hand , nothing is black and white . Phones protect customers from exaggerated prices . You can easily find the recommended price of a product and you can compare the price . And public transport is another area where it can be useful to use a mobile phone . It is true that some people disturb and they act like selfish immature people with their loudspeakers blazing . But you can find important information about your trip on the internet and , most importantly , the trip can be very long and you can use that time or waste it . You can do both with your phone . You can work on it or you can read or , at least , play some music . But on the other hand , you can waste that time on social media and it leads to another degeneration of your mind . I appreciate your work and I believe that you know what are you doing . Best regards , Kuba 
One of my favourite films is " Manhattan " by Woody Allen . I think this movie is well written and the story is enthralling . Allen 's sarcasm is at its best . You can find a love story and a consideration about friendship , but you find a picture of the 80s as well . The soundtrack is really great , and a very good example of this is in the movie 's intro , when the images are perfectly synchronized with " Rhapsody in Blue " by Gershwin . The movie is in black and white and this is because the main character said , " New York City is a city in black and white . " I agree completely with this . 
Why do I want to learn English ? For several reasons . English is so important for every job . Even though you do not need to communicate with foreign people , now all firms want you to know English . I agree with this , but not completely and not always . But this is it and I try to adapt myself . English is also the first international language and it is indispensable if and when you travel abroad . And I like to travel abroad , so I need to speak English . English is important to buy flight tickets , to reserve a hotel , to order at a restaurant , etc . Furthermore , I like to read a lot , and so many books are not translated into Italian , above all , many essays about Technology and Science . So I need to understand and read in English to read all those books . English is important to do almost everything today . 
Sports should play an important part in everyone 's lives , but unfortunately , they do not . Physical activity keeps both the body and the mind healthy and positively impacts one 's life . The negative effects of an inactive lifestyle should not be ignored because they affect more than we are led to believe . Besides the obvious effects , obesity and the health problems it causes , the lack of physical activity also affects the mind , leading to unhappiness and unproductivity . First of all , doing sports activities at least three times per week is enough to make a change in one 's life . These activities would provide the most benefits , especially if they were between classes at school . Taking a physical activity break between chemistry and maths , for example , gives you a break from mental activities that require you to focus and gives you some time to clear your mind and prepare for the next class . An active lifestyle leads to an active mind . This has also been proven by scientists . When doing sports , the body releases endorphins that trigger a positive feeling . So , there are no disadvantages to increasing students ' and school children 's physical activity . Second of all , it is vitally important to make everyone understand the dangers of an unhealthy lifestyle . The way we live our lives is the root of all of our problems . An inactive lifestyle will never allow anyone to become the best version of herself or himself and it might actually cause more serious problems , like depression or physical illnesses . Young people are the most impressionable and that is why it is strongly recommended to teach students and school children about the importance of an active life as soon as possible . All things considered , there is no doubt that sports activities are as important as mental activities and they should be mandatory in school . 
I agree with the people who believe zoos are good places for people to learn about animals . The knowledge of animals is very important to people . People can respect animals more because of this knowledge . Moreover , animals in a zoo are not in such bad conditions . Usually , they are treated really carefully so that they do not feel stressed out . On the other hand , animals in nature are in very brutal conditions . Some animals cannot survive in such an environment . Thus , I think animals do not have to belong in nature and it is not necessarily wrong to keep them in zoos . The important thing is to respect those animals and nature , but not let them be free without thinking . We are the same as them in terms of living thing on the earth . Let us not ban zoos and let us keep them comfortable . And then , let people learn more about them . 
I think that studying abroad is a really great thing in the main . The students who go to study abroad could learn various things from it . For example , they could be independent , because they have to live on their own . Not to mention , they have to speak in another language , so they could improve their language skills . Moreover , they could learn about the cultures of the country where they are studying . They could even make friends in those countries . Those experiences would be precious without doubt . However , I think that there are some problems . The cost for studying abroad would be very expensive . Some students could not afford to go and live abroad . They would have to borrow some money because of that . What is more , they might suffer from loneliness . They could not meet their family and friends back in their country . I do not know if they could persevere with it . In conclusion , I guess that studying in another country for a time during high school or university is a great idea . Despite there being some problems , the experience in another country outweighs the problems . The experience in another country would be lifelong treasure . 
I believe that zoos could be good places to learn more about animals . However , the current model used to explore this business is not effective . There are few zoos that are good examples of how to conduct this business . Exploring the image and visiting the animals are important to generate profit , and these profits must be used to generate research to protect and preserve the animals . Also it is necessary to study how to improve the methods of reproduction of these animals in captivity . If these studies are effective , maybe the new animals could be introduced into safe areas , such as rainforests or other natural areas . The main idea is to try to recover and preserve these safe areas , so the animals could live in a free space . As a result of this effort and studies , people could visit these safe areas and observe the animals in their natural habitat . Consequently , the conservation would help the humans reach the aim of preserving many animal species . 
I believe that working with a group makes me productive . For this reason , I would say open design offices are more effective than closed offices . But I also value research about human thinking styles . There must be some research about it because productivity is one of the most important things in the business area . Productivity and efficiency are the keys of manufacturing and mass production . If we downgraded to a human not a machine , it would help us to create a more comfortable zone . If a human is not in their comfort zone , they ca not think properly . If flexibility for thinking is not provided , workers ca not work with high efficiency . A professional worker does not want to work in those areas . While you are losing your workers , you can also lose the time . We all know that time ca not be taken back . If we value our workers and co -workers , we can gain more than we gave . As I declared , I would create an open design office for more efficiency and a more comfortable zone . It came from the research that I read . It is actually called herd psychology . We feed from what we eat . That is certain . And I believe that our readings , our listening and our watchings shape our mind . If we see a group of hardworking people , we try hard not to be the black sheep in the herd . It happens subconsciously . But on the other hand , being a single white sheep in the herd also harasses us . So we should mission workers decently . We should warn the black sheep and we should appreciate the white sheep . As a summary of my thoughts , we should utilize academic resources about human thinking systems . After that , we should organize our offices in suitable forms . Giving awards to hard workers also could provide an example to be good worker . 
Cristina , I am so sorry to hear that . I am going to miss your funny jokes and chatting together , as you are my close friend . If you need anything , just call me and do not be shy , I will be of help at any time . I need to come and see you . Could you tell me what time I can come ? Take care , stay safe , see you later . 
Obviously , to be healthy is more important than to be rich , but in all countries and in all societies , wealth helps to be healthy . This is a problem not only in countries like the US , without a welfare state , but in countries like the UK or EU members . People with a good job and a good wage could eat more healthily and have better treatment . This is not a matter of access to a private and better structure , but if you pay well , you have a faster and better service also in public health structures . And this is not a matter of corruption . Health has a cost , and the public can not afford it as well as it can ever . The same problem is for healthy food . The poor can buy cheap food and cheap food is dangerous , unhealthy , fatty , full of preservatives and sugars . By contrast , rich people can buy organic and safer and healthier food , because this food is often very expensive . 
Studying medicine , these days , has become commonplace and necessary , so some doctors study medicine in order to obtain a fortune . While others believe that being a doctor is a humanitarian job . This essay will discuss both sides and will draw my personal opinion . On the one hand , when you want to study medicine and get a lot of money , this is your right , but the first purpose is helping poor people . To illustrate , human nature favors collecting money , so you can obtain some money through your job in also volunteer . In addition , volunteering is a great occupation , especially when treating people 's diseases , for instance , all doctors have three days a week so they can help people and visit rural areas . Because in the countryside , there are elderly people . So that 's will was a big benefit to mankind , such as philanthropic organization . On the other hand , most of nation suffers from hospital distance being very far because the government builds the institutions according to population density . Usually , rural areas are on the borders of the state and do not have population density . In conclusion , after a careful analysis of both point views , I believe in the importance of the medicine occupation , but must of the all people not to neglect the humanitrain sides . 
My short answer would be , yes . Nowadays , we do not have any incentive for children to learn musical instruments , however , this is really important for them mentally and , at the same time , physically . Back in time , schools were used to teaching music to their students . Sadly , in our time , this is not true anymore , but in some places , this is still a requirement and , at least for me , this is really good . Recently , I have started to learn to play the violin and I need to confess it is really amazing how we can develop new skills even though we are ' old ' . After this new experience , I have discovered that I am able to learn anything I want to and that that story about children 's learning processes being better than adults ' processes is a lie and I am saying this after experiencing this on my own . So please , give you a chance to learn how to play any kind of instrument , it will be more than rewarding . 
Hi Matt , How are you ? This year I want to be able to speak English , so I 'll focus on it . I am good at writing , listening and reading , but I 'm not very good at speaking . return to my country because my native language is Arabic and naturally all the people in my country speak Arabic . I am not sad about that because I 'm trying to learn a language that is not my first one and it makes me happy . Always the best one , is not the achievement , but the journey of achievement . The most important thing is the plan and how to apply it . 
Interest in the design of work stations has become commonplace , so some people care about wher he employe , because they believe that impacts their psychological state . While others believe that the place is not very important or the type of decoration because what they see first is money more than the work . This essay will discuss both sides and will draw my personal opinion . On the one hand , most employees prefer working in new places which contain entertainment , for example , the evolution of the technical world during to high norms human . In addition , the work environment has become more care about than the work . For instance , in the past , in But now the situation has become different . To illustrate , in the past was the employers intersted about the customer more and eager to comfort to them , entertainment such as coffee devices or a well - ventilated place , and especially a place to relax . So that 's why some think that psychological health for them is important because they can have creativity in the job . On the other hand is the arrangement side . A must for business owners balancing between the number of employees and distance of the place , and increase the salary of workers outside the institution . In conclusion , after a careful analysis of both points of view , I believe that a healthy environment work positively effects the workers in it . 
Languages represent a form of communication between people . They are part of the history and traditions of a country . We could not define ourselves as human unless languages existed . Learning to speak a foreign language is a bridge which links two or more populations . It is as important as speaking one 's own language . However , there are some important differences with respect to the past . In fact , people were not used to travelling as much as today . Basically , this is the reason why a person did not need to learn a foreign language . Moreover , schools did not hold a sufficient number of language lectures , so people did not have solid language skills . Thus , learning a foreign language was not an important matter in the past . Nowadays , a foreign language must be learned , not only when we are going to travel abroad , but also when we are applying for a job . Indeed , more and more national and international companies are requiring proficient speaking skills in one foreign language at least . For instance , English and French are the most relevant languages . The more languages you know , the more possibilities you might have . This is the future ! 
Studying abroad is a great opportunity to improve several skills , such as language , educational , professional and personal as well . Depending in which country the person will study , he or she can study in a high level institution . And it can make all the difference to the training and preparation of this person . Certainly this person will be better prepared to apply for the best jobs in the future . Studying abroad is the best way to improve and get the confidence to explore a new language at a high level . Being exposed to a different environment obliges the person to make a great effort to improve their abilities . Sometimes studying abroad could be a better way to get well -paid jobs , so the person can build a new style of life . For this reason , improving their quality of life is feasible . On the other hand , some people have problems adapting to a new country and to a new culture . These problems are due to a lack of self confidence and a necessity to stay close to parents and friends . Despite the fact that living abroad can awaken some difficulties , I believe that the effort is worth it . 
There is no doubt that these days people watch television a lot . The question is , what do they use it for ? In this essay , I am going to talk about the purpose of television and how to make TV helpful to you . In terms of the problems , watching TV all day will damage your eyes and you might have mental problems . However , watching TV can also educate you and help you learn new things . In other words , do not only watch something that entertains you , watch something that can educate and help you with your life . In conclusion , after a careful analysis of both viewpoints , I believe that watching TV for one hour a day might not damage your eyes . If you 're watching TV , do not only watch it to entertain yourself , watch something useful to help you with your life and educate you . 
Some students choose to study in another country for a time during high school or university . Why do they make this choice ? I think that it is easier to learn a new language . When students go into a new country , they have to learn the new language to understand the native students and courses in the university . 
I really apreciate eating pizza . It 's my favourite food . I usually eat pizza once a month and I like it because I can choose the ingredients . For me , cheese is the best thing and for this reason this kind of food is so delicious . 
Write and Improve is a wonderful website for those who want to learn and improve their writing skills . It is also a great tool for beginners to learn how to write correctly in English . In my opinion , Write and Improve is really helpful for everyone who wants to learn how to write in English or who wants to improve their writing skills . I think about everyone who wants to learn how to write in English or who wants to improve their writing skills . The reason why I think Write and Improve is really helpful for people to learn and to improve the writing skills is that Write and Improve provides us with a wide variety of topics for us to practice with . On Write and Improve , you do not have to worry about what topic you are going to write , sometimes it takes you hours to think what topics you are going to write about and it really wastes your time , but on Write and Improve , you do not have to spend your time thinking what topic you are going to write about because Write and Improve will provide us with a wide variety of topics for us . So on Write and Improve , you just choose what topic you want to write about and you just spend your time thinking of ways to write about your chosen topic . Write and Improve also saves your article and rates your article for you to see your mistakes , so you can improve your writing easily and effectively . 
Everyone has a favourite thing from when they were a child . A colour , an animal , a book , a season . In particular , the favourite season of the year is said to be an expression of our behaviour . In this article , I am going to explain to you what my favourite season of the year is and why . The season that better represents me is winter . I love winter because I like to listen to the blowing wind through the window , looking at the snowy land on the coldest days . It makes me feel relaxed . It is very special for me . I have many happy memories of my childhood in that season . When I was a child , I used to go out with my younger sister to play with the snow , rolling on the snowy ground , for example . Winter is very often associated with Christmas time , one of the best moments of the year . In fact , I love opening Christmas gifts with my sister and my parents on Christmas morning . I remember how exciting that moment was . I was looking forward to discovering what present I had received . Winter is this for me . Memories . 
I truly hope that each parent has the right to raise their children the way they find appropriate . However , feelings and beliefs are not only difficult to articulate , but also very individualistic . Therefore , looking at what the data tells us is crucial . Like any other tool , video games can be put to good or bad use . For example , if young children play a game designed for teenagers , it will harm their psyche . That 's because games can evoke strong emotions , and confronting a defenseless child with them is a bad idea . It can lead to anxiety or aggression in the long term . Another harmful way is to allow our children to play for an unlimited amount of time . If there are no restrictions in place , the child will play for the whole day and sometimes even the night . In contrast , educational games are very useful and desirable . We play video games because they are fun and if we can make learning fun , success is inevitable . To summarise my short answer , I 'm for a reasonable and controlled use of video games , not only for educational purposes , but also for pleasure . 
Zoos are a very good place to learn about animals . Imagine a family of six going to the jungle to see a gorilla , giraffe , or a lion . This task would be both logistically and financially challenging . And for most people it can only remain an unfulfilled desire . Zoos provide a taste of such an experience at a lower cost and with greater convenience , not to mention safety . You say that people believe that animals belong in nature and this is true . However , there are people who believe that animals can be kept in captivity with no harm done to them . Some even say that it is better for them , because they do not have to struggle just to get by , as everything is provided for them , including safety , which is impossible in the wild . Yet again we are discussing people 's beliefs . How we can actually decide whose beliefs are right and whose are wrong ? 
I went to Paris , France ten years ago . It was the most significant holiday to me . Before that time , I had never been abroad . I remember that I was very excited at the time . I love French culture , especially the art and cuisine . Also , I got on an airplane for the first time at that time . By the way , I went there with my family and friends . My friends were excited about the holiday as well . In Paris , firstly , I went to the hotel that I was staying at during the holiday . The hotel was really beautiful , classy and magnificent . I was really exhausted right after arriving there , because of the jet lag . The next day , I went to Disneyland and really enjoyed myself there . There were a lot of attractions . On another day , I went to the Louvre , the famous museum . I saw many famous pictures and sculptures . Besides , I ate a number of delicious meals . I love French cuisine very much . Definitely , I wo not forget these precious experiences . I would love to visit France again . 
I certainly think exercise is important for our health . It is a fact that is proven by scientific research . However , are there things that are more important ? Yes , I guess that there are indeed more important things than exercise . For example , there is the food which we eat in our everyday life . There is a famous proverb , " You are what you eat . " I think it is true . If you do not get sufficient nutrients , you are going to be sick . I assume people tend to have unhealthy food these days , for instance , they eat a lot of junk food . They should eat more healthy food . Another important thing for our health is sleep . I believe that sleeping is underestimated by most people . But actually , it could be the most important thing for our health . We can get refreshed by enough sleep . It is also beneficial to our brain as well . If we feel stressed out , it will affect our health . But sleeping can take it out of our mind . We have to get more sleep , absolutely . Although , as I have written as above , exercise is also important for our health without doubt , we have to think about them all . 
Dear Anna , Thank you for your letters . I hope you and your family are well . I am writing to tell you about my favourite film . The film is Miracle In Cell No 7 , and it tells the story of a mentally disabled man who has a daughter that he adores . He wrongly imprisoned for murdering and raping a seven -year -old girl , but he was a very kind man who had been misunderstood by his cellmates . It is the most emotional and lovely film I have ever seen . I wish you watch and enjoy it . Write soon . Yours , Mariam 
Nowadays , it is true that many people think that living a shorter life is much more intense and they are going to live the rest of their lives in this sad way , but I consider that living until 100 years old will bring many good things to human lives and I can tell you how . On the one hand , the vast majority of people are wasting their time doing nothing , just working , and there is not any kind of pleasure in this . For example , they can risk their lives and the time will be shorter than for people who live 100 years . On the other hand , it will have you in hysterics when you always hear : " I like my life like this , going to parties , watching movies all the time , exploring new places and meeting new people , so I 'm living my best life , " but in my humble opinion , I can say that only God can gives us all the time we need . In addition to this , and from my personal experience , I can say that I prefer to choose the first choice : living a long , calm life until 100 years old ( if God lets us ) because you can go from this life until you did all it was for your life and familie 's too . So keep it simple , be healthy , brave and also be proud of yourself always ! 
I have realized that on this website , you generally want me to say some certain declaring . I do not like it all . If I am not a person capable of analysing the topic , I hesitate to say something absolute . But I have another option too . If we come to the topic , all we know , music affects our brain . It makes our brain 's different parts work . They say the brain has muscles in it . So if we do not practice it , it could get lazy very easily . But on the other hand , forcing is not an eligible thing to do . If I want to be an engineer , I may not want to learn something about music . I do not have to listen to music either . School principals should decide it for their own students ' nature . If you ask my opinion , I would say if it is optional , not like an obligation , I would want it as an option . Actually , I am an engineering student . I do not even need to know something about classical music , but actually , I would like to know small things about it . It would help me in conversation with some people . It could help outside of my major . But I value personal interaction with others . It could be good to maintain a conversation . Nobody can say music is an unnecessary thing . Some say it is nutrition for our soul . But I would not stand it if it were an obligation . Students ca not be forced to do something they do not want to do . It could create some barriers for students . 
Hello everyone , I am Andrea Peralta and I am thirty -four years old . This year is a different year , due to the coronavirus pandemic . Most people are in the house and receiving virtual classes . That changes the way I want to make my plans . First goal : My husband has obtained a new and important job . He is going to start it on Wednesday next week . I hope he has an excellent experience and in the future , we can go and stay in another country . Second goal : My eternal paint is English . I think I have a medium level in writing and reading , a low level in listening and a terrible level in speaking . This happens because I freak out when I need to talk to someone in English . I do not have confidence . That brings me many problems and does not allow me to achieve my goal to be a fluent speaker . I hope to find a way of talking in English . Third goal : I need to start learning about security cisco , because I have to pass the exam to achieve the next level and renew my CCNA degree . This is very important for me . I do not want to let myself down and get discouraged . Fourth goal : I am interested in taking care of my health . For this reason , I am going to go to the dermatologist . I hope to have healthy and beautiful skin . I am anxious about my appointment . 
Our favorite film is an interesting topic to discuss together . In my opinion , there are a lot of movies all over the world , so it is very difficult to tell you what my favorite film is . I think I do not have a favorite film , because I think I ca not choose what movie I like the most . I have watched so many movies since I was born , and I think maybe the cartoon genre is my favorite movie genre . The reason why the cartoon genre is my favorite movie genre is that I have watched cartoons since I was a kid and they make me remember my childhood . 
It is always an adventure to travel to another country . Studying abroad is especially relevant , because you get to stay in one place for longer . That gives you the opportunity not only to taste , but also get to know the local people and their culture . Furthermore , you make friends while studying . And some friendships are very precious and may last for years . And there is also a chance of a romance , and maybe something even more serious . Another benefit of studying abroad is learning the language . First -hand experience cannot possibly be replaced by even the best regular lessons . When you are exposed to a language most of the time , you learn it the best . On the other hand , you will be far away from your home . That means not seeing your family and friends for an extended period of time . That may be even harder if you leave your boyfriend or girlfriend behind . The new environment and culture may not be to your liking as well . There may be those little things that you 'll miss , like standing in a queue , hugging and kissing your colleagues , or even the products you might not be able to buy abroad . 
Schools in a new reality Is it only me , or have you had the same complaints about your school ? Imagining the future of school takes place on every level . We used to dream of more colorful buildings , better teachers , less homework , diversity in subjects . Now it 's coming true . School has been getting closer to the futuristic vision of it . For instance , the first difference will be the use of technology . Tablets , computers and robots will not be only used by teachers , but mainly by students . Paper notebooks will be long gone . Another point will be creating smaller classes . Psychological studies show that a human is not able to focus in a group of 30 people . Taking that into consideration , schools will be reducing the number of students in a group . In addition , societies will realize how great a role nature plays in our life . Classes will be organised outdoors in order to show children the beauty of the world . However , there will definitely be no changes in grouping kids by age . Governments like it . It is easier to control people . The teacher will probably stay as a head of the class . 
Dear members of the town council , I am writing to express my strong dissatisfaction with your idea of making restrictions connected to mobile phones and their usage in public places . First and foremost , you do not specifically have any reasons for these regulations . As much as I am informed , there has not been a single problem with individuals using their mobile phones outside . It does not bother anybody in particular or cause any major conflicts . You also claimed in your previous press conferences that you will not implement any restrictive measures that would significantly limit the freedom of your citizens . That turns out to be an absolute lie from what I see now . Last but not least , I decided to carry out an online survey on my personal website to find out what citizens think . What they think is what matters the most . Following the survey among the citizens of this town carried out online , 90 percent of teenagers showed a full disagreement with the idea of not being able to use mobile phones in public . About 75 percent adults think that it is not necessarily needed and it would only cause arguments and chaos . When it comes to seniors , only 25 percent answered that they are against the idea , as they usually do not use mobile phones much and do not care much . As it was shown in the survey , not only I , but a majority of citizens , do not agree with banning mobile phones in public . I hope this matter receives your immediate attention . Yours sincerely , Dana 
In this new school year , I want to improve my English skills and I would like to achieve some goals . About these goals , I will list them in the following lines . First , I have to say I am pleased with the progress I have made so far . From last year to now , I have improved all my English skills , but I know it is not enough and I have to work hard on it . Second , I want to improve mainly the writing skill , this area is my weakness . I need to make some effort to improve my ability to talk more fluently with other people . I mean , sometimes when I am talking , I have to stop and think about what I will say , and it does not sound natural , or like a native English speaker . To achieve my goals I have planned to read more news from relevant newspapers , listen to podcasts in English and broadcasts on the radio and watch TV series with the subtitles in English as well . I believe having conversations with native English speakers can help too . 
We are now living in a global and international world . In the past , traveling was a more difficult thing . But now , we can travel to almost any other countries , wherever we want to go . This is definitely fantastic . So , what about travel in the future ? I think that it is going to be easier and more affordable . We might not even need passports . There could be no borders in the future . I fancy that it would be great for everyone in the world . It would help us all in many ways , too . For example , we could easily meet our family and friends in other countries . Let 's look at public transport . There would probably be far faster ones . I guess that there could be space rockets in the future . We could go to the moon at that time . There will definitely be no borders , no countries . We are all just humans . Traveling is just traveling . Despite what I have written above , I actually suppose that there will be no difference in the future of travel . Dreams are just dreams . We have to live in more realistic ways . 
My name is Michael and when I go to sleep I prefer to sleep with the lights off , any kind of light , no matter the color , does not allow me to sleep . When I want to sleep , I like a quiet place , and I do not have any problems because I live alone , and my neighbors are very respectful people . When I sleep at my mother 's house it is a big problem for me , my siblings are noisy and they do not allow anyone to sleep . 
Hello Charlie , Remember me , John ? We used to email each other monthly when we were teenagers , it 's been a long time . I would like to tell you about my favorite food , and that is pizza , I love pizza . I eat pizza every weekend , it 's my favorite food because I like all the ingredients : cheese , ham , pineapple , eggs , tomato sauce and oregano . It 's wonderful to go out with some friends and eat a delicious slice of pizza with them . 
Hello everyone , Here , today , I am thinking about what the means of travelling in the future could be like . Well , let 's begin . First , I should mention I am 34 years old and all my life I have been in Colombia , an underdeveloped country , where all people only use a bus , car , airplane , bike , motorcycle and boat . It depends on the place where they live and their economic situation . For example , in Bogota , the capital city of Colombia , most people use a bus and Transmilenio ( this is an articulated bus , it works with some special conditions this allow faster movement within the city , but it is more expensive ) . Other people use cars and motorcycles and finally there are people who use bikes . The government says it is important to find other ways to travel within the city . The project is to make a train line that crosses the whole city . This proposal has not had a good reception with the population , because we think it is a bad project , where the government is going to spend a lot of money and the city will not be better . Also , this will bring more social problems , such as unsafe , dirty , structural problems with the buildings , over -costs , etcetera . In conclusion , I think about the future of travelling in my city . It is not going to have other means of transport , because the infrastructure is pretty deficient . 
First and foremost , I would like to thank you for assisting me for the whole past year . It really helped me to understand the key concepts that we discussed . I 'm especially happy about my progress with writing . However , I do not feel confident enough to write captivating paragraphs just yet . I would like to continue improving my English and writing skills . These skills will be ultra important to my personal and professional development . Especially relevant , I want to undertake work in Great Britain and hopefully , turn it into a career . A successful career will assuage my sense of inferiority . To achieve my objectives , I will work earnestly , because improvement in my speaking and writing skills is my priority . Furthermore , I will set aside a specific amount of time a day to learn and study under your gracious supervision . You know that I 'm a downright person and I believe that what I have just written encapsulates my desires and observations . 
Books are an instrument for learning . Books give you a lot of knowledge . You can touch a book and feel its texture . On the one hand , I think books are very necessary in schools and universities , because they are the essence of education . When I was a child , I preferred reading physical books rather than ebooks or on computers or tablets . I was born in the age of technology , but I still prefer to read a book than other things . On the other hand , I think computers and tablets have helped society . Computers teach each minute . Education is better with them . Children learn better because they learn visually . They learn by watching videos , singing songs and doing exercises on platforms . Nowadays , everything has changed . In the universities , they also learn and study with computers and I think it is more interesting than searching in books . They can take notes on computers or tablets . I think it is faster than writing by hand . In conclusion , I think computers and tablets are very necessary for society , but books must never disappear . 
The special food I like to eat is pizza . I usually eat pizza twice a year . I do not eat pizza very often because the yeast makes me feel bad . I like pizza because I enjoy the cheese , sauce and ham flavors mixed . My favorite pizzeria is Pizza Hut where I always ask for a Cheese Bites Pizza . 
Some people want to sleep in a dark and quiet room . Other people sleep with a small light on and do not mind noise . In my opinion , I prefer to sleep in a dark and quiet room because our brain will be completely relaxed if we sleep without any light . Furthermore , a quiet space will help us easily to pleasant and sleep . So , we will have a deep sleep . To me , noise or light will make us have a good sleep and also nice relax . 
Travel may be a field that will not disappear in the world . In other way to say it , travel will develop more and more in the future . Have you thought about the future of travel ? Indeed , in what ways do you believe travel will be different in the future and in what ways might it still be the same ? In this essay , these topics are discussed . Regarding things that will be changed , I believe that humans tend to visit places which are close to nature . It can be clearly seen that people care about the environment and nature . That 's why they will choose to enjoy a natural landscape instead of commercial places . In addition , technology 4.0 is being developed and customers will book , set up , pay for ... in a manual way with high -tech solutions . Many things will be combined , marketing , storage , booking ... will managed digitally . Everything will be solved quickly and immediately . Regarding things that will be not different , I think that way to serve customers will be the same as before . Clearly , meals , spa services , transport ... will still be the same . I see that service now is OK for visitors . 
How do I Iike to sleep ? It is a difficult question , because it depends on the occasion . Firstly , I like to travel , I sleep in hotels , motels and private houses . For me after all day , my priority is silence and I prefer to sleep in a dark and quiet room . But , if I choose multiple person room , when I want to spare some money , it is not possible , because everyone likes going to sleep at other times . Secondly , I 'm a teacher and twice a year I organize a trip for my students . We are together for four or five days and we sleep in a youth hostel . Then I ca not sleep in a dark and quiet room , but only in a small light room . Thirdly , in my own house I definitely prefer a dark , quiet room , without any light at night . Then I fall asleep fast and I sleep for seven to eight hours . Additionally , the window in my bedroom has a view of the street , and sometimes my neighbours turn on the lights and wake up me , so I must buy some window blinds . In conclusion , I prefer to sleep in a dark and quiet room , it is healthy for me and I can rest after all day . But it depends on the occasion , what I showed on the free example . 
I think it 's important to learn English . I have reasons why it is important to me . 1 ) When I 'm older , I 'm going to go on holidays to other countries and most of the countries speak English . 2 ) For me it is a fascinating language and easy to learn . 3 ) I have to learn it because my parents ca not speak English and I see how hard that is when we go on holiday to other countries . 4 ) England is really nice ! I want to go to England when I 'm older with my husband . English is a world language . If you go to other countries and you want to communicate with the people who live there , then it 's definitely important to speak English . I have English classes , so I do not have a choice . I need to learn English , otherwise I will fail . I hope more people think like this . English is really important . 
I remember one of my first holidays and I remember how good it was . My holiday was in Switzerland . I went to Switzerland in 2014 for the Christmas holidays . I went to Catania airport on 24 December and I landed at Milan Malpensa airport the same day . It was Christmas Eve , Me and my family were alone and we decided to go to Turin , because we have cousins that live there and we celebrated Christmas Eve and Christmas Day all together . On 26 December , we finally started our trip to Switzerland . We left Turin and went through the San Gottrdo tunnel . In the evening , we finally arrived at my cousin 's home . I met my uncle Yurg and his other friends . I was very happy . He gave me a gift and when I opened it , I was very amazed , because there were two games for Nintendo 3DS , which I loved . In the next days , we did a lot of things , but surely the most beautiful was when we went to the waterfalls . I was really amazed . This was my best trip 
I think zoos are good to see the animals . Of course it is not so nice for the animals when they have to live in small enclosures . You can learn a lot in a zoo , for example how the animals look or how they behave . Moreover , you can see a lot of different animals for little money . When there were no zoos , you had to travel to various countries to see the animals . That would not be good for your ecological footprint . In addition , a zoo is very nice for kids . They like to see the different animals . I think it would be best if the animals had large enclosures and their normal conditions to live . Moreover , it is important that someone who knows the animals cares for them . So it would be better for the animals . I think for school classes , which are learning something about exotic animals , it is very good to see the animals in real life . I know it is something different to in the open wilderness , but it is a good compromise . 
Most people fall in love with travelling . They spend a lot of time aspiring to relaxing moments , really enjoyable , alone or together with the family . The problem it is that in jam , some situations happen and the trip does not happen like they hope . A trip can have a lot of menace that can compel them to manage , or the opportunity for everything to go wrong . A good trip means choosing the correct means of transport , accommodation , a good guide agent who is lenient with short questions , like the weather , culture and behavior of the place that is to be visited . Every variable has to be noticed in the contract , for security and everything should be overt . Current society has the internet , with a way for relationships and this opens opportunities for news about every area . For a lot of questions that there are on a trip , it ' s possible administer with software and a program on a computer . The access to a lot of information about the place that is to be visited is very close , only one click away . Like this , a lot of problems can be minimized . The future of travel is more use of technology at all levels to organize a wonderful trip . 
Hi Rie , I can come Rie , you know in the food I do not joke . I do not want to be nosy , you can make whatever you want , except fish , because I do not like it . See you later . 
My favourite season of the year is definitely summer . I have a lot of reasons for that . 1 ) My mood is so much better in the summer because it 's hot . 2 ) We always go on holiday in the summer and I love holidays . We wanted to go to Turkey . Unfortunately we could not go because of COVID -19 . 3 ) I can swim in the sea and become brown in the sun . Summer is so special for me . It gets dark late you can walk outside at 10 pm . It 's never cold , so I love to walk with the dog . 4 ) Summer clothes are so much better than winter clothes . In the winter I 'm always grumpy and angry . That 's also a reason why I love the summer . I do not even understand why people love the winter . It 's so cold and it 's dark in one minute . 
Dear people , I think school will be different in the future in these ways . 1 ) Technology . I think a lot of people will have better laptops and I think the teachers will have more choices to teach . 2 ) I think the way of teaching will change . I think it will be less strict than now . 3 ) I think there will be more subjects than now . I think school will be the same in the future in these ways . 1 ) Homework . I definitely think it will be the same , we 'll still have to do homework . 2 ) Tests . I think that the tests are not going to be different than now , because there are a lot of ways to cheat . Beyond this , I think a lot will be different , but some things ca not be , because 20 years ago we had tests . Maybe we will have more options with levels . 
There is no doubt these days that technology is spreading to every place in the world . The question is , will they use computers and tablets over books ? in this essay , I am going to talk about the reasons why books cannot be replaced by computers and tablets . I think because of this pandemic , they should replace books with computers and tablets until the pandemic is over and they should go back to books again . The main reason given to support this claim is that to stop the spread of COVID -19 and save lives by staying at home . Too many have died in this pandemic . Hopefully it will end soon . In conclusion , using lots of technology might damage your eyes . Therefore , I believe that using books is better and healthier for people . I advise all people not to use computers and tablets more than books after this pandemic . 
Hi Jack , How are you doing ? I am glad to hear from you . What type of restaurant did you go to ? Spanish birthdays are quite similar to those in England . We share this day with our family . However , we normally celebrate at home , we do not go outside . We eat a cake as a dessert . 
I like to spend my free time on outdoor activities . My daughters and I love walking in the mountains . In addition , we go every weekend to the countryside . Besides , I adore running . I run almost every day . My teammates and I run every Saturday and Sunday morning . 
Dear Anton , Thank you for your last e -mail . Nice to hear from you , and that you liked cooking and tasting new meals . What is your favourite new food ? Could you write to me with some recipes , please ? I will experience cooking new meals and maybe in the future I will stay a cook ? Who knows ! For me , absolutely number one is Italian food . I love pasta , with various sauces . Every weekend I prepare dinner for my family , and pasta is their favourite meal . I like baked pizza , especially with tomatoes , mushrooms , sausages , cucumber and additionally a lot of cheese . Once a month , I like to eat out of town with my friends and we go to an Italian restaurant . But I prefer to eat at home , I like talking with my family , friends and tasting my own and my mum 's recipes . We eat together on Friday evenings and often on Saturdays at midday , rarely during the week when both of us work . I like Italian food for three reasons : First , Italian food is healthy and delicious , and it is cooked using some vegetables . Second , I like traveling to Italy , so if I ca not fly and smell the pasta and pizza in Rome , Mediolan or Venice , I will try to eat Italian food at home or in a restaurant . Third , Italian food has enormous power , integration people , encouraging conversation and works for de - stressing . Moreover , Anton do you know anyone who does not like Italian food ? I do not think so . I ca not wait to receive your response , Anton . Maybe one day you will visit me in Poland and taste my meals . I will invite you whenever you want ! Yours faithfully , Kristina 
Schools are set to educate the students . Traditionally , there are teachers and students in school . They must go to school almost every day until they graduate or move to another school . They must get up in the morning in most cases . Some students have their lunch at school . Others have their lunch elsewhere . They should not to go home until after school . Almost every person in the world experienced such stuff . I always doubt whether or not students should go to school physically . I think schools ' duty is to teach their students themselves . They do not have to attend schools in reality , as long as they study what their school teaches them . There are online study courses everywhere nowadays . I assume students in the world do not have to go to school unless they study somewhere else . They could study without schools and it is enough for them . In those ways , they do not have to waste time too . I do not want you to get me wrong . There are certainly some good points that schools exist physically . However , it is not necessary . 
I think television could educate people in general . In fact , there are a lot of educational TV programmes in many countries . Of course , we would be able to learn many things from books or something else . However , television can give us stuff in action . For example , we can watch various wild animals on TV , their life , food , shape and so forth . It is very important that something is moving in reality . Sound is also important , because we can watch various things with sounds . It is not necessarily only TV programmes that are educational . For instance , there are a number of educational videos on the internet . The thing is , television is a thing which lives in our everyday life , because it is everywhere in our life . We can watch something we did not know about until we see it . I think that it is really fun . And sometimes we could discover something educational on TV . This is why I would say that television can not only entertain us , but can also educate us . 
Hi Peter , I ’m writing to you in order to tell you a couple of things . But first of all , let me tell you that I hope you and your family are doing well . To begin with , I would like you to know that I do not have a favourite film , but if I were to choose one , I would go for " Beauty and the Beast " without doubt whatsoever . With regard to my decision for that specific film , I also want you to be informed that I love it because of its message , which is that beauty is found within . Besides , I consider that film quite a good mix between fantasy and adventure . Last but not least , I would like to mention that I really recommend you to watch it , because it is a powerful classic story which never gets old . Let me know your opinion about it . I ’m looking forward to hearing from you soon . Best regards , 
Learning to speak a foreign language today is more important than ever . Speaking a foreign language is important because we can access to a lot of information from abroad , we can contact foreign people and we travel abroad more than in the past . English is the main language we have to study , because it dominates the world of work , affairs and communication . However , Chinese and Spanish and Arabic are important too . Today , the Internet is the main media where we can find information or communicate with other people , and English is the first international language people use on it . Speaking a foreign language improves and increases our knowledge , it connects us with other cultures , it broadens our diversification skills and so it can reduce conflicts and misunderstandings among people . There are studies that confirm that learning a foreign language keeps the mind young and healthy . 
We have only one life and therefore we have to keep it healthy . I think that a healthy lifestyle is more important than exercise , for example , less stress , more vegetables and fruit and more breaks during work . We would be more alive and with more enthusiasm . The key for a happy life is doing more activities , not only one . I played squash , but unfortunately my knee got hurt . Now I am trying to do a lot of activities . Our mind is half of our success . I am going to plan a new lifestyle balance , because it is very important for us . Some fruit and vegetables for breakfast , lunch and dinner are normal at this time . I do not know anyone who does not eat these things . In the Czech Republic , we have tried some spots on TV for a healthy life and I thought it was good for citizens , but many people have not seen them . All of us want to be healthy and have a good body . 
It is more important to be healthy than to be rich . So now , in the modern lifestyle , we are all busy day by day , so forget what is happening . We also use all our time for work , we eat fast food , do not do any exercise many times in a week , drink coffee instead of having breakfast . Usually this will make you sick , which means we should take care of ourselves if we do not want to be sick . A healthy body is a sign of a healthy mind . Finally , health is always more important than wealth . If you do not have health , how do you make money ? 
My best holiday happened over twenty years ago . As far as I remember , it was summer 1998 . It was just before my 18th birthday , which in Poland marks your age of achieving adulthood , at least in a legal sense . We went to my friend 's plot located just by a beautiful lake . He only had a little shed there , so it was a proper camping experience , including tents and outdoor cooking . Some of us went there by car , while others rode on bikes . I remember my little Fiat was quite a sensation there . We wrote some funny sentences on it and decorated it with empty bottles , a reminder of the previous night . We used it to drive to the local village to buy some bread and canned meat . We ate cheaply to have more money for alcohol . During the day , we spent most of our time on the lake shore . We were swimming , sun -bathing , playing cards , drinking and having a lot of fun . The best part of all was being there without any worries , because as a teenager , during the holiday , our only worry was having something to drink . 
There is a lot to say about working . It is the most important thing to do because it allows you to survive in this world . If we have to work to survive , we need to be together . Personally , if I have to decide in which way workers should work , I definitely choose to let them work with their co -workers . Sure , it could be a dangerous move because you are allowing your employees to talk to each other and it is not good at all . On the other hand , you are giving them a nice way to work . Being closed in a cubicle could make an employee feel bad or , in an extreme case , depressed with their job . The size of an office can really make a difference , just imagine an employee works in a small office . Surely , he would feel sad , or feel in a cage like an animal , and we know that someone who grows in captivity does not do their job nicely , but if you let people have touch among them , it could be a good compromise , workers can help each other when they need it . In conclusion , to be a good boss , you have to help your team with their job . 
In this essay , I am going to talk about music in schools and why it is a good subject to study . First of all , music is something that I think everyone should understand . It can give you too many feelings , there are different songs , one for every mood . I have always been jealous of the schools which own music classes . I have really liked music since I was young , it can make you free , happy or make you feel stronger . Of course , it could be difficult to understand how to play an instrument , but when you succeed in something , you are so proud of yourself . For example , after nineteen years , I decided to play the guitar , I am at the beginning of this journey so I still have much to learn . It is hard because I am studying it by myself . I think that Italian schools should add music as a subject because there are so many teenagers that would like to play an instrument , but they cannot . I strongly recommend to add in every school a music class , it will help students to avoid problems related to school , homework and exams . As I said before , it can make you free and go away in your mind . 
The School of the Future will be totally different from today . Nowadays , we are living in an information and technology era . In the future there will be no need to have a place to go to school . School will be virtual . Students will attend classes from home or even while travelling . They will only need an internet access and a laptop . They can interact with teachers and submit assignments online . In the future students will have a right to enroll on their courses without school interfering . Those who like math can take it this semester and so on . School in the future will have no exams . School will apply continuous assessment . It will be a learning process with no need to have exams to evaluate the understanding of the course . In the future , school will have overseas ' teachers , which will be good for the students to get knowledge from teachers with different backgrounds and cultures . The School of the Future will definitely be different from today 's school . 
Hello everyone one , nice to meet you . How easy was your day ? What special thing happened to you today ? If you would like to share , feel free to contact me . I will always listen to you . So , turning to today 's topic , we have a normal subject , but I think it is one that is very close to us . It is sleep . As you know , some people sleep in a dark and quiet room . Other people sleep with a small light on and do not mind noise . How do you like to sleep ? Honestly , I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room , it makes me feel comfortable and safe . I also want to sleep alone , because for me sleeping is very important . I can sleep for a long time if nothing do not mind mine . I do not like anyone or any noise making me wake up . I also sleep in the dark , because light makes me unfocused and I easily wake up suddenly . It 's really terrible if you wake up and cannot sleep well again . A good night 's sleep will give you in a good condition in which to work and study . So what about you ? Do you sleep in a dark and quiet room or with a light on and noise ? Tell me your opinion . Thank you and see you later . 
This year , I want to improve my English skills . Actually I 'm pleased with my listening and also with my reading skills . Indeed now I can understand a lot of things , like podcasts , TV series and You Tube videos and also , when I 'm reading a book , I do not need to translate , because I understand a great part of the words that are written . This year I want to improve my writing and also my speaking skills . I want to improve these two skills because they are very important for me . Especially at this moment , I 'm really interested in writing skills and also grammar rules . For these reasons I 'm actually using some online platforms to improve these skills , like Speak and Improve and especially Write and Improve . But I will also use some grammar books to review and learn other grammar rules . To improve speaking , I 'm actually searching for a native English partner to start a programme of speaking improvement . These are my goals for 2021 . 
