Hi , John ! How are you ! I hope this email finds you safe and sound . Last week , I went to a music concert held in the magnificent music hall of Suzhou . I had been waiting for this concert for a long time and I even booked the ticket three months in advance . The primary reason I chose this particular concert is because Lang Lang , an internationally renowned pianist , would perform in the concert . I got to know Lang Lang when I was just six . You probably know that I have been playing piano for 10 years and the key motive for my persistence is because of Lang Lang , my spiritual tutor . The concert was very well organized . Lang Lang played at least 10 pieces of music on the stage . You cannot imagine that all the audience stood up and applauded for Lang Lang after each piano piece . Nobody went out for a break during the concert . Lang Lang was so polite , that he went back onto the stage three times after the final piece and he played two more pieces to return his thankfulness . I had a wonderful night that day and my interest in piano has been sparkled once more . Therefore , I cannot help writing to you and I wish to share my happiness and excitement with you . Best wishes , Michael . 
Hello everyone , Today , I have the opportunity to write about my opinion that television can educate . Now , it is time for writing , let 's begin : Television is an extremely useful or harmful device . It depends on the person who is using it , because if the person is disciplined , is interested in knowledge , watching educational programs , taking advantage of cultural programs , these actions permit people to be educated . Otherwise , if the person is not disciplined , is not interested in knowledge , watching movies , series , novels , comedies and other entertaining programs , it means not taking advantage of their time , this person cannot be educated . I think television is very useful or is very harmful , the same as the Internet . Smart people learn languages , do courses , download programs , exchange knowledge with other people , other cultures , other countries , while foolish people misspend their time only looking at jokes , memes and spam information . They do not want to learn anything , their interest is nothing . This upsets the world . There are a lot of lazy people that do not take advantage of useful things . It is the difference with people that make an effort and have success . 
As I see it , it 's more important these days than in the past , owing to the fact that today we have a more globalized world , where you can fly and do tourism or live anywhere and besides , we 're communicating throughout the world by the internet , therefore each day we can speak with people from other countries and learn from them . Right now , the most common international language is English , hence I believe in the present moment it is very important to learn it . Nevertheless , it is true that in the past it was harder to acquire a new language , due to the lack of options they had to study . For instance , they did not have all the apps , courses , language schools and so on , that we currently have . To summarize , from my point of view , today it 's more important for the reason that we are living in a more globalized world , where we can speak with people from other countries each day , although learning a new language has been always very useful and interesting and I recommend everyone to do it . 
It is true that we 're all taught to always tell the truth . But , in fact , sometimes , we do not follow that lesson . We do the opposite , but the interesting thing is it 's somehow accepted . So , did our teachers teach us wrongly ? No , they did not . Being honest is important . That 's not erroneous at all . But , in some circumstances , lying is more preferred . First of all , telling a lie can sometimes motivate the people we care about to excel . Humans are very competitive and always want to be the best at every task they have been assigned . Whether they are taking part in an athletic event or taking an examination , they feel more motivated if they think it is possible to archive the best result . You may know the fact that it 's an unthinkable thing for some them . Nevertheless , instead of telling the truth and completely destroying their hope , being a liar in those cases is better . Secondly , being honest all time may lead you to high levels of anxiety . Not all truths are good to be revealed . Some of them can make people unpleasant . For example , last week , my friend asked me what I thought about her new hairstyle . Well , I said frankly it looked terrible . Although she did not express any anger mark , I knew she was very upset inside . She has not talked to me since that day . Therefore , be careful with what you are going to say . In a nutshell , telling the truth is crucial . Well , no doubt about it . But , sometimes , you should do the opposite . If not , you may regard about what you said . 
Since the dawn of time , man has travelled from place to place at the expense of the most precious and irretrievable currency , time . We can now travel at speeds that were beyond the imagination of commuters just a hundred years ago . I do not want to sound disparaging of inventions like the Hyperloop , but it seems like we are touching the limits . Therefore , the future of travel wo not be much about time , but about comfort and safety . Even now , when I 'm writing this article , some long distance planes are equipped with the latest comforts and luxuries . You can travel across the Atlantic in your very own cabin , which is like a one -night stay in a five -star hotel . When you arrive , you will be rested , almost like the struggle of the trip never happened . I believe that sooner or later we will be flying a mini version of a town , where not only can you have a meal , but also visit a hairdresser or a doctor . 
Write and Improve is a very useful tool to learn English . I think writing is an important skill , because when we write , we are forced to think in English , to use our mind and it also needs creativity , so I have two sessions of writing in my weekly routine . Write and Improve has more levels of difficulty . Beginner , Intermediate , Advanced or Business , and there is a section Just for fun . Other parts are related to the IELTS and B2 exams , but I do not know how they work . After having selected your level , you can select one of many exercises . The text tells you how many words you have to write . After writing , you check and you have some feedback . I think this is a very helpful tool . Above all , for people like me that are studying on their own and they do not have a check . It 's more difficult to improve without someone that tells you if you write wrong or right . I think that this tool works very well , but it 's always a robot . Maybe sometimes , you write correctly , but not in real English . I do not know if there are some more pertinent phrases . Certainly , I recommend this tool to everyone because it 's well made , and especially for people alone or without control . 
Exercise is so important to us otherwise for health , power and activity . We have a lot of stress , depression , dissatisfaction , and madness in our lives , and doing exercise is the best solution for all of these problems . All of those things are going to make you think about killing yourself , but if you go to the gym or just do some exercise at home , that will be good for you and your negative energy . Yes , there are things that are as important as exercise , like food . Whenever you want to start a diet or some habit in your life , the most important thing you have to think about is to reschedule your food list . You have to avoid eating fast food or food that has a lot of calories , like ice cream , chocolate , chips , etc . This food going to kill you slowly and increase your weight that will make you feel depressed or angry . So the thing we all have to do is exercise four times a week . The second thing is to have a food list and avoid unhealthy food . Do these things not for a week or a month , but your whole life . Remember to make them a habit , not a period . 
I think it is true that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich , because you cannot take any money to heaven . It could be a waste if you died when you had a lot of money in your hand . But you will not have to worry about your money if you are healthy . Since you are healthy , you can do anything to earn money . You could even gain more knowledge in your life if you are able to live longer . I think that knowledge is the most important thing in our life . This is why I think that to be healthy is more important than to be rich . What is more , there are a lot of things to do which cannot be bought by money . The thing which is the most important to you is in your mind . I am sure that you also have something that cannot be bought by money . It could be a family , friends and so on . We have to take care of our health to become happier . Although it takes some money to buy healthy food , we can do it , definitely . 
