It is the best type of requirement . Volunteer work is important to improve human ability , to become better . Nowadays , young people do not give the right importance to volunteer work because , for them , it 's boring and it does not give a salary . In our days , working is the means to make money , hence volunteer work is not a real job for quite a lot of youngsters . It is true , volunteer work does not give a salary back , but I think it gives a more important thing than the money , the opportunity to help the others , to become a man . It 's a job with an aim and I completely agree with the requirement of some high school to involve students in doing volunteer work in order to graduate . It 's better for the others , but also for the students , because it is maybe the first job in their life . In the end , I hope that , in future , more and more schools give the opportunity to their students to do volunteer work in order to graduate . It is the best requirement that a school can have for their students . 
Zoos represent a new entertainment for all people , from children to adults . The number of them is increasing more and more every day . This is the reason why non -profit organizations like Greenpeace do not agree with that phenomenon . In fact , they believe animals belong in nature and zoos seem to be prisons rather than peaceful and fun places . In my opinion , there is no point in keeping wild animals chained in zoos . They must be free , like we are . There are many ways and alternative solutions to see them . For example , safaris and other tours do not require any restrictions for animals . You can go with a guide and visit these stunning natural parks , admiring the beauty of the local wildlife . I know that the staff of every zoo treat animals well . Moreover , incorrect behaviour and bad treatment is not allowed . Laws are clear and it is a value . Even though animals are imprisoned in zoos , they are safe and well treated . Anyway , from my point of view , I would prefer to see all animals free in their habitat and in general , in the wild , in their right place ! 
