Exercise and practice are very important to improve our skills . For our body , they are quite relevant in order to always keep it fit . However , it seems that exercise is in the first position and all the other things are less important . In my opinion , taking care of our health is important , but that 's not the only relevant thing : several things make our life colourful . There is no point in making our body more and more stressed by doing exercises for many hours . In fact , recent research states that it is sufficient to work out from 30 to 45 minutes . An excessive session might cause problems . Obviously , we want to avoid them . Not only is physical exercise important , but also mental . Our brain is essential for the whole human body , as well as our heart . For example , reading books or doing creative activities such as painting or drawing , are very helpful . The latest studies in some famous institutes have confirmed how powerful these activities are . What 's more , they can be done in our leisure time . During the week , it could be a good idea to alternate them with physical training . 
