My favorite season of the year is spring . For me it is special because it is not so hot as the summer and it is not so cold as the winter . The spring begins with the end of the winter , so after a long period of cold , some are sad , so everybody likes it when this season begins . I like to look at nature when it is spring . The flowers , the sun , they are different in this season . In this season , the animals are more active , the green of the plants is more intense . In this season , the schools are returning , so we meet our friends again . We start to do sports again too . I like to do sports outside , on the street , in the square , but it is impossible in the winter , so the new season , the spring , brings these activities . 
Are you one of these who ca not live without traveling ? If your answer is yes , then this article is for you ! We used to travel a lot these last years , however with the lockdowns for COVID 19 , now we ca not travel like in the past . From my point of view we will have to travel differently from now . For example , some countries have suggested creating a digital passport so that everyone knows who has been vaccinated . Also , I think that traveling will be more expensive from now on , for the reason that many airlines have lost so much money and only the strongest companies will survive , therefore we will have fewer offers of airplanes and hence the prices could be higher . For this reason I believe that probably local tourism will gain prominence from now on . Have you ever thought about the wonderful places that your country has and you have not visited yet ? However , I hope this current situation has a happy ending and we can travel again like we used to . 
Nowadays , it is well known that exercise is very important for our mental and physical health . Firstly , it is undeniable that doing exercise consistently can give a boost to our mood , release us from stress and more . As a result , currently , a lot of people , especially youngsters , do exercise every day . Nevertheless , in my point of view we should take care and not overwhelm ourselves with too much exercise . I have seen people who are always injured for the reason that they do all kinds of sports for a long time and they never take a rest . In conclusion , from my point of view , I believe that we should do exercise , because it has so many benefits for us . However , we also have to be aware that there are more important things we should do in order to have a well balanced life . For instance , one important thing which I suggest is doing meditation , for the reason that it is a great way to relax our body and mind . 
Schools have been involved in many evolutions in the last decades . Now they are still changing because of the pandemic emergency . New tools and a new approach are being tested in order to cope with this hard period . Are they effective or not ? What might schools be like in the future , when the emergency has ended ? These are hard questions to be answered , but we will try to do it in this article . The covid emergency has led everybody to stay indoors , changing our routine drastically . Students are getting used to doing online lectures , from primary school to university . The goal is to keep teaching as well as possible . However , many problems occur in this way . For example , children and teenagers do not receive the same feedback as in live lessons . As a result , they cannot learn the new topics well and their preparation level gets lower and lower . On the other hand , most university students are experiencing these kinds of activities with good results . Therefore , it seems that universities are going to keep this approach even when the emergency finishes . Will it be so ? 
