In my opinion , I think that computers and tablets are able to help students a lot , but should never replace books . Books are necessary , you have a guide and it 's where you learn things , a lot of things . I do not recommend students to study on tablets and computers , because our eyes suffer a lot and in the future we will have a lot of problems and diseases in our eyes and perhaps somebody could lose their sight . Technological devices are very important and necessary for students . They can a lot of knowledge in a click , they can learn all they need and it 's very easy to work with other students , do teamwork online , search for information , share homework , etc ... If I have to take an option , I will choose both , but I have a preference for books . 
I think that learning a new language in this moment of history is more important than in the past . Learning languages is really important for us for many reasons . Speaking a foreign language can help us in many ways and in different situations . For example , if I know Spanish , I can travel and speak with other people in a great number of countries like Brazil , Spain , Perù and Mexico . Speaking one or more foreign languages can also help you at work , because a great number of companies search for people who speak many languages , because it is important for commerce . I think that speaking a foreign language in the world of today is very important , because you can speak with people that come from other countries , you can travel the whole world and you can know more about a culture . 
There is no doubt these days , so many people have been speaking different languages beside their mother tongue from centuries ago until now . The question is , is it necessary to have knowledge about other languages like before ? In this essay , I am going to discuss both views and draw my own opinion . In terms of the positive side , some studies have said it is necessary to speak important languages , especially English and Spanish . The main reason given to support this claim is eighty percent of scientific language it written in English and 20 % in other languages . To illustrate that , if you wish to be proficient in your specialization . you have to be fluent in English . In other words . most of the Universities around the world are teaching in English . On the other side , some people are against this and strongly believe that learning any foreign language has a lot of disadvantages . Firstly , while learning any language , you will get their culture as a part of your studies and this knowledge would affect your beliefs and thoughts about your own faith . Secondly , a lot of books and information have been translated into the national language . Finally , Google translate could help anyone to change any document in any language to any other language for free . In conclusion , I believe that it is really important to learn the most famous of them , as English which is mandatory to complete a high degree . 
