My favourite season of the year is the summer , because we are on holiday . Summer has 3 months , June , July and August . My favourite month is August because it 's cooler than in July . I love summer because it 's hot and we can wear shorts and t -shirts . Summer is the best season to do your favourite sports , for example like football every day during summer . During summer is the best time to eat ice cream , drink cool soda and swim . During August is the best time to go out because it 's cooler than in July . During summer , I like going to the swimming pool and spending all day long there , because I meet with a bunch of friends . The summer is special for me because I can do whatever I like during the holiday . 
I am learning English because it 's the most spoken language worldwide . If you know the most spoken language , you can speak with lots of people . I learnt it in school , at the British Council and from video games . I also learn English because it 's good to know a foreign language , for example I am studying English along with Spanish and French . I am learning English because I would like to study abroad . I might study to the USA or to the UK . Another reason for which I am learning English is to get good marks in the English exams , such as TOEFL , IELTS or PET . I learn English because I want to improve my speaking and writing in a foreign language . Although some people do not want to learn English , it 's the most spoken language worldwide . 
