My reasons for learning English : Being able to speak a foreign language can be very advantageous . There are plenty of reasons for learning a new language and find one 's passion . In this essay , I will focus on the English language and explain my reasons for learning it . First of all , being able to speak English , there are almost no boundaries of communication . Since English is an international language or lingua franca , the majority of the world 's population has English knowledge . Thus , one can have conversations with people all over the world . Moreover , the English language , especially the British accent , is very charming in my taste . I adore listening to it and therefore would love to speak so . Furthermore , I love to listen to modern music . The fact that nearly every song is in English incites me to learn English more . Accordingly , I am able to understand all the lyrics . 
We , unfortunately , live in a capitalist society , where people prioritise money instead of social services . Of course , a doctor who has studied for almost ten years to obtain his degree must earn a reasonable salary to compensate the time invested in his profession . But in my opinion , one chooses to study medicine because one has the desire to help people . Most doctors prefer to work in big centers because of the money and because it provides better conditions to practice their work . I have visited a city where the hospitals were collapsed because of an outbreak , I had visited a city where the hospitals where in collapse because of an outbreak , there were no conditions to help people because there was not any medicine and not even equipment to protect themselves . Based on my knowledge , there are ways to solve this problems , the authorities should invest more money in infrastructure in rural areas and pay some extra money as an incentive to doctors who work in rural areas . In my country , the federal government hired immigrants from Cuba to work in rural areas . 
As you all know , sleeping is really important for our health . Therefore I would like to talk to all of you about how I usually like to sleep . I strongly believe that sleeping in the dark is better than sleeping with a small light on . However , when I was a kid , I used to sleep with a small light on . Nowadays I prefer sleeping in a dark and in a quiet room , because the silence is really necessary to be able to sleep and rest well . 
I prefer to sleep in a quite dark room , and for many reasons people usually prefer this . One of these reasons is that it 's scientifically proven that it 's healthier . And I do not know how to justify my answer as it 's just how am I . People who do not mind the noise are lucky , but they should be careful though , as this can affect the quality of sleep they get and can affect their health sometimes , as some scientific papers suggest . 
It is a common belief that it is good for students to have the same teacher for several years . However , I am against that idea for some reasons . First , when students have the same teacher for several years , they tend to become familiar with the teaching method of that teacher and find it hard to change . That leads them to be passive and inflexible in studying . Besides , working with many teachers as much as possible will make students change their attitude and their studying methods as well . Therefore , they can gain a lot of experience and precious knowledge in their daily life . Secondly , I think it must be boring and dull when I have the same teacher for many years . Students usually want to try something new and interesting . So , many teachers can bring many emotions for them . Whatever it is , it may change their life in some ways . Another reason is that a new teacher is a new opportunity . Not all students have their favorite teacher at the beginning . Hence , if the first teacher is not suitable for them , it 's okay . They will have the second , the third , the fourth ... teacher until they have suitable one . For those reasons , I believe that it is better when students have new teachers each year . 
A child born today is predicted to live up to at least ninety years on , an age 20 years older than just fifty years ago . Furthermore , statistics assure us that , in the twenty -first century , when almost every day a groundbreaking new medical treatment is discovered , life expectancy will increase each year about six months . But is it actually good that lives last so long or should short but intense lives be preferred ? The answer is clear , when keeping in mind that long lives are unnecessary when having lived a short but intense life where everything wanted was achieved . Having experienced everything longed for , a long life would conversely be boring and depressing as nothing new can be discovered . Therefore , shorter but exciting lives should certainly be preferred . Additionally , what is clearly more appealing when having a shorter life is that there are usually no health issues . Having an active and fun life is accordingly achieved more easily when being young . As a result , having a happy time on earth is made much simpler than when being older . The last and most important argument supporting the thesis that living a shorter life but more intensely is better than having a long life , is that dying at an old age is often connected to pain . By this , not only physical pain , caused by diseases and the aging process is meant , but also emotional pain . As a long life is lived , deaths and losses of loved ones will be experienced , which can cause tremendous emotional distress . As a result , a long life is not as appealing as before when experienced without friends and family . In conclusion , it becomes very clear that growing old and living a calm life should be seen more negatively than a short but intense life for the various reasons explained above . 
My favourite hobby to do in my free time is watching movies . I usually watch movies at home , but when I have time , I like going to the cinema with my friends . I think the best place to watch a movie is at the cinema , because the screen is huge and the sound is really good . 
