Do you have a favorite season like me ? Over the year we can feel and see the changes of the beautiful seasons , however , all year round , I look forward to the arrival of winter . The weather is so comfortable and the clothes are so fashionable . One thing to consider is the fact that I live in a semi desert area and almost all year the temperatures are so high . But in October , we can start to enjoy the winter season . That means that there are not any mosquitoes , you do not sweat , you can wear beautiful clothes and the best thing is that you 're able to sleep so well because the weather is so comfortable . In conclusion , in winter , the sun does not burn your skin , which means that you can go out to take walks or go camping . Simply , the weather is pretty comfortable . 
