HEALTHY LIVING According to statistics , doing exercise is really important and useful for our health . It is a fact that people who do exercise frequently have better health than people who do not do any exercise . Therefore , there is no doubt that exercise could help you to have a healthy life , but on the other hand , I strongly believe that there are other more important things . For example , I think that eating and sleeping well are as important as exercise . Food is one of the main causes for why people have bad health . Once , somebody said to me , what we eat is what we are . So you have to include in your diet food like some vegetables and fruit . How we sleep is really important as well . You have to rest in a comfortable bed in order to have good mental health . To sum up , there are three things to help you to have good health : doing exercise frequently , eating more vegetables and fruit and , last but not least , sleeping well . 
