LEARNING A NEW LANGUAGE I strongly believe that it is really necessary and useful to know how to communicate fluently with other foreign speakers . It is a fact that nowadays it ´s more important than it was in the past , due to globalization . We live in an increasingly connected world . This is the reason why many people choose to study a new language in another country . As you all know , living in another country helps you to improve faster . You can meet other foreign speakers in order to practice speaking with native people . Furthermore , you can see and learn the culture of the country . Without doubt it is a great experience . On the other hand , being able to speak a new language helps you to look for a job . In accordance with statistics , for many jobs , you need to have language skills , such an English or Spanish . To sum up , due to globalization , it is really useful and important to learn a new language . 
