' It drives me up the wall ! ' , said one student early this morning when he , sitting next to a computer screen , learned that all university students are advised to exercise thrice a week . This notification was immediately understood as abrasive and nosey by many students , but not so surprisingly , there is a good reason for embedding this rule . Research shows that university students in general and computer nerds in particular are activity -deprived individuals with fitness levels so poor they raise a red flag for their physicians . Not only have some students stopped any exercising , but they substantially minimized their exposure to sun , fresh air , and shockingly , some of them even do not leave their dormitories any more . Although the lockdown and curfew exacerbates the situation further , the real problem is mostly the inherent laziness of the students . Therefore , the college council suggested mandatory sports activities at least three times a week for everyone . Albeit justifiable , the decision triggers a question of personal freedom . Can the council indeed force students to engage in sports activities ? Some argue this is simply illegal , and thus , impossible to do so . But , this coin has another side as well . The council is a body fully responsible for the well -being of students and as such , it is entitled to take care of their mental and physical health . Therefore , the above mentioned statement is conceivable . Clearly , this non -trivial affair will ignite a fierce dispute in the next student assembly . But , given the usual bland and boring discussions , it is a great achievement as well . Our colleague Bend -Over shrewdly commented that this situation is a lose -lose situation : students are mad at the council , therefore they will hesitate to exercise . He gingerly suggested to encourage students ' sports activities by providing them free access to the gym and the swimming pool . 
I would like to write about my favourite season of the year . I would definitely like to say that it is winter . Some people say that they like spring , autumn or summer . But I would just like to say that spring and summer are damp and hot . Additionally , in these seasons , there are a lot of insects around wherever you are . So , there is also a lot of noise of chirps , inevitably . You cannot quietly sleep at night in those seasons . On the other hand , winter is quiet , calm and fresh . You could be in warm and comfortable clothes as well . Indeed , it could also be freezing and therefore stressful . However , that is what it is . In winter , you are able to enjoy a lot of warm food and soup . What is more , you are able to sleep in a warm blanket comfortably . In any case , I am sure that all people are going to agree that winter is tranquil . I like such a quiet time very much . The days on which it snows all day long would be much better too . 
Why do some people sleep in the dark ? Why do some people sleep with a small light on ? There are a lot of reasons for different sleeping behaviours . I like sleeping in the dark and without any light on . Also l do not want any noise when l am sleeping . I cannot sleep with a light on because it disturbs me . Therefore l close every window with a veil . Noise is important to me as I do not like it . Yeah l know some people like it , but l do not . Thus l close every window when l sleep . No TV and no music . It is really important to me . By the way , if l sleep with any noise , l have a headache . Also l think that not only noise but also a light on is so hazardous for people 's health when they sleep . 
In my opinion , knowing English is fundamental for students who want to communicate with the rest of the world . As we all know , English is a common language in the world . Therefore , the language is significant to be learned and when one has the ability to speak English , one can work , live and easily communicate with the people who one lives with . The importance of learning English for me goes back to my childhood . During my childhood years , I listened to English songs virtually every day and I recognized that it was a relief when I was listening to the language and it caught my attention to understand English . Also , I have a dream to travel the world , so I decided to learn English . I have been studying by reading articles and books , watching the news and listening to songs and sometimes I just turn on the TV and watch some English movies or a stand -up event . 
The best holiday I had was in 2019 , because I did my first trip with my mother travelling in the plane . It was so nice . I had already travelled in a plane , but when I was a kid . Now I am 19 years old , and on the day of the trip I was 18 years old . This holiday was close to Christmas Eve . When I went back with her , my cousin and my grandmother were waiting for us in my house . After so many years , finally I met my grandmother again , after 10 years . The first time I saw her , I was 8 years old , now I have other head and etc . This holiday was special to me , because I realized my dream , because I met my favorite singer . She was in my room on the same day with my grandmother . Besides that , everyone needs to have a special moment in their life . I had my moment when I met my favorite singer . She gave me a gift and I started freaking out , it was so insane and wonderful . I 'm so grateful for this special moment and this was the best holiday ever in my life . 
I use a computer to do a lot of things , so I use it every day . When I come home , I watch You Tube videos for entertainment . When I am learning about something , I use it to do research . Then I can play video games with my friend . The game is called Free Fire and we kill each other . 
Sometimes people want to find something brand new and almost their priority is going abroad . I realized that the same thing is happening to students : some of them choose to study in another country for a time during high school or university . Of course , it always has both advantages and drawbacks . I want to start with the advantages first . Studying abroad is an opportunity for students to have access to a different study environment . There , they can work with foreigners as much as possible . That leads them to learn other languages quickly and effectively . Moreover , the amount of knowledge they gain is significant . Students will be familiar with modern study equipment , scientific teaching methods and the working styles of foreigners . Therefore , it is easy for them when they have a chance to work in an international company or embassy . So , they will make a contribution to developing their mother country . Besides , when students study abroad , they will gain more experience . Because they have to live far away from their family , they have no choice but to take care of themselves . They will know how to prepare a meal and manage their money . Another advantage is that students can make more friends and enjoy the feeling of a traveller while they are studying . On the other hand , there are some drawbacks of studying abroad . The noticeable thing I want to say is the homesickness feeling . Students will miss their family and their classmates very much and feel alone sometimes . Besides , in the beginning , they may get some culture shocks and not be able to adapt to other customs . My friend studied aboard in China and she had not eaten any Chinese dishes until then . Moreover , people can be racist when they study abroad , because of their skin colors or their cultures . Sometimes there are annoying people who enjoy playing a trick on others . In conclusion , studying abroad has its own advantages and drawbacks . However , " one day of travel will bring you a wealth of wisdom . " 
How will we travel in the future ? It is an interesting question . I am trying reply to it . Currently , new cars are being invented . These new cars work with an electric motor , without petrol . Others can drive without drivers ! These cars have a computer as a driver . Maybe , in twenty fifty , motorcycles , cars , lorries and trains could transport everyone without product pollution , but not yet for planes . The traffic will be less noisy than today . Then , there will be less car accidents . Unfortunately , the driver 's licence will not exist , which will make people less independent . 
I think that Write and Improve is a greatly useful program for English language learners , especially people who want to practise their writing . Owing to this program , I am sure that I have gotten used to writing English sentences . I assume that getting used to writing is very important for English language learners . It actually benefits you , because you are going to find some kind of useful impression . I was lucky enough to find Write and Improve . I think that every learner who wants to improve their writing skills should use Write and Improve . This program is actually similar to writing a diary . I suppose that most people would agree that writing a diary is going to improve their English . However , there is a problem . There is not always something to write in your diary , although , most people have it . This program allow us to write something in English if we do not have anything to write . So , people who use Write and Improve are able to improve their skills in any case . Last but not least , this program gives you feedback . You are able to recognise your mistakes in your sentences , easily . This is very useful and important for learners of English . Although it is a shame that sometimes I cannot understand why my sentence is not good , it is useful , anyway . I am going to use this for a long time as well . 
This time , I would like to write about the problem with medical doctors . It is that most medical doctors want to work in cities where they will make a lot of money . Yet , in many rural areas , there are not enough doctors . I think that the reason for this problem is about money . So , if doctors in rural areas get as much money as other doctors who work in cities , the problem would be solved . Because the doctors who work in cities do not need to work in cities for their money . Then , how could this be done ? I think that the governments should control it . They should distribute money to doctors in their countries , fairly . Therefore , there will not be any inequalities in the salary of doctors . Thus the doctors in rural areas are not going to need to think about their money . I think that I have to read more English sentences so that I would be able to improve my writing skills . The sentences , which I have written above , are horrible . 
It is very tricky to answer the question " are there things that are more important than exercise for our health ? " To be honest , I think that exercise is the most effective way to improve our health . First , exercise keeps your body fit and flexible . When you do yoga , karate or just simple morning exercise , you must move and use many of your muscles . That leads to releasing energy and reducing unnecessary lipids . At the same time , your limbs will be familiar with that intense training , then your movements can be flexible and you can do many things more easily than before . As a result , your strength gradually improves . Apart from the physical benefits , you will gain pleasant mental health . According to an article written by a group of scientists at Oxford , exercise can reduce stress and help you to have better sleep . As far as I 'm concerned , a person who frequently does exercise has positive energy and is more carefree than somebody who does not . Moreover , exercise is a cheap way to improve our health compared to other ways , like going to the health centre or hiring a private doctor . Besides , it can enhance our patience and self -management . In conclusion , exercise is important for our health in special ways that no other method has . 
Telling the truth is an interesting subject to discuss together . In my opinion , it is important to speak the truth , but everything always has two sides , the good side , and the bad side . Why I think telling the truth is good or not depends on you and also depends on the situation . If you want to make others happy , but you know the truth will hurt them and you do not want it to happen , then it is acceptable to tell a lie . As I think , a lie with a good purpose is better than telling the truth , but it 's going to hurt others . I think it is difficult to figure out if telling the truth or a lie is a good thing . As I said , if it is good or not depends on you and also depends on the situation , so there will not be a specific formula for us to apply . As I know , people tell a lie every single day and , when they tell a lie , they are not even thinking about it . So humans always tell a lie , but it is a harmless lie . In some situations , you have to tell the truth because if you tell a lie , it is going to affect other people in a bad way . Telling the truth is very important at work because when you tell the truth , everyone at work can know the bad things in their job and they can improve them . In some situations , telling a lie is better than telling the truth , such as a friend you just met . 
There is no doubt that schools nowadays change faster than ever , as we see the differences year by year . I imagine if I traveled to space and came back to earth 10 years from now , I would be too old to catch up with the new systems that would have been developed but why ? I think that in the future , schools will have more classes and each class will include only 10 to 15 kids , so that the teacher can make sure they all understand . I imagine self -learning will be implemented on a regular basis , since self -learning will be a thing , so technology will be required as well . I think moving forward , exams with open books will be normal for kids and teachers will be more creative , coming up with their exam questions , since they will evaluate students ' understanding rather than memorizing the information . I imagine that mental health education will be included . What will stay in future is the need for teachers . Technology will stay as well , I believe sports will be done more often , since these classes encourage creativity and play a big role in mental health . 
Schools ' areas will be different from now . In the coronavirus time , we can see a lot of changes in schools . It is online teaching , online education , online homework , etcetera . I think the old times wo not come again in the same ways . Learning at home is better for many students , because they do not wake up early . The same will be only grades and the specifics of grades . Children might know what they want to do more than other people . In big cities , there are many possibilities for them . We had a good education and we could go to school without masks . We knew everything in our mind . There are more difficulties than before . Children will be better and they will be working alone with online courses . The school of the future is present and I am looking forward to learning a new thing . 
To be honest , I use a computer almost every day . I usually use the computer for several important things such to look for information , to study , to talk with my family when I am not at home and to revise my emails as well . On the other hand , I sometimes use the computer in order to play video games . This is the activity that I enjoy the most with a computer . In conclusion , a computer is really useful for a lot of important things as well as to enjoy playing on it . 
Hi Rie , How are you doing ? It 's always good to hear from you . Thank you for your invitation , sounds good ! I 'd love to go ! We could eat some Italian food , such pizza or pasta . As you know , I really love this type of food . What do you think about it ? Drop me a line when you have time and let me know if you 'd like to eat Italian food as well . Ca not wait to see you ! Lots of love , Jane 
AUTUMN : THE MOST COLORFUL SEASON OF THE YEAR If someone asked me which is my favourite season , surely I 'm going to say Autumn . Autumn is a wonderful season for many reasons : 1 ) It is the season when the leaves start to fall and the ground become colorful , like an artist 's painting . 2 ) In Autumn , there are a great number of celebrations , like Bonfire Night and Halloween , that are celebrated in many countries . 3 ) Autumn is the season when school starts in many countries and this can be really enjoyable ( especially for parents ) . Personally I love Autumn because it is a warm season and it makes me feel comfortable , and also because I love the color and the food of this season . Furthermore , I like Autumn because in my country , which is Italy , we have a lot of celebrations and festivals that are linked with this time of the year . Autumn is the best season 
During our life , especially when studying , we face some difficulties . One of them is being a student far away from our family . Actually , this has both advantages and disadvantages . According to me , studying away from family has more advantages than disadvantages . While studying far from home , first , will set some challenges to students . Throughout these difficulties , students will have a chance to struggle with them and it will be a lesson to them on how to live alone , so that how to overcome those problems . For example , a student during their education in another city , moreover , in another country , has a chance of him or her taking control using and saving money , this will help their life in future . Whereas , studying with their family might be easier , but for the rest of their life , they might face some challenges which they must struggle alone with . So as I mentioned in the above paragraph , for students , it is more beneficial being far away from their family during their education , as a result , they could manage their budget or how to settle their life without the assistance of their family . These simple samples could help with the rest of their life . 
It is more important to be healthy than to be rich , because health is the most basic thing of men . Living healthily is more vital than being rich . Health and wealth are expendable things , but there is a difference between them . If health is lost , it can be so difficult to regain it , whereas money could be regained in the case of losing it . Therefore , humans must care for their health , human must care of their healty upon this they can easily work and earn money . Not having a healthy life has no meaning , despite how much money he or she has . As a result of this , our primary aim must be being healthy , not being rich , because caring for their health , a human can continue their life . Thus , in my opinion , being healthy is crucial for people . Despite earning money , health can sometimes be lost forever . But it does not mean money is nothing . Sometimes , people need money to regain their health to work and enjoy life . 
My favorite indoor activity is playing video games on my PS3 or the computer . I like to play video games because I feel comfortable and pleased when I play a game that has a compelling story . To play video games is like walking in my thoughts and encouraging my creativity and reasoning . The last time I played a video game was in 2017 when I sold my PS3 . 
I think that enclosed workstations or cubicles are more favorable than open designs . It is undoubtedly true that some employees want to be in a private space . It is not necessarily true that an open atmosphere has an advantage over a closed one . Moreover , the employees who do not want to be in an open space would feel stressed if they were in such an open area . On the other hand , the other employees who want to be in a more open space can go to more open areas . For example , there should be meeting rooms or lobbies . When they want to communicate with other employees , they are able to do it in such open spaces . Therefore , the employees who are introvert do not have to feel pressured . If anything , the employees who are extrovert should go out to open places . This is why I think that enclosed workstations or cubicles are more preferable for a lot of people . 
I think that the requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate is a good idea because the students could get good experience from such volunteer work . For instance , they are able to know that doing things , which are helpful to people , is very rewarding . What is more , to do so , they are able to feel that , they are a member of society . It would be a very good thing for their mentality . People should think about their society , even if when they are young , so that they are sure that they have to help each other to live in the world . This is why I think that having the requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate is a good idea . It would be better if it were done before they graduate high school , because they are about to be adults . 
Let 's be clear . My favourite season of the year is the spring , by far . To tell you the truth , the main reason is because I can wear all of my clothes , no matter what the weather is like . During the spring , it 's not as cold as it could be in autumn or in winter . However , the weather is not as warm as in the summer . It allows several things . The first one is to be able to go out without worrying about the temperatures outside . On the other hand , the vegetation is growing during this period . So having a walk , either in parks or in gardens , becomes a real privilege . Finally , here , usually the season of the big events of the year come , like festivals and so on . I could also say that in France , you have a lot of holidays in this period , so you 're really free to rest and enjoy the season . 
Watching television is horrible , because it is a waste of our time . Always . I would like to say that we can see a lot of people that watch serials and other spots . A lot of time goes unneccessary away . One way is only programmes with educational videos . For example National Geographic etcetera . Entertainment is around us a lot . We had a television when I was younger . I watched only fairy tales and some news . This time our children are watching television nonstop without breaks . Televisions and computers are capital devices They are still going to continue . I have to set some rules . I will have to change the time for entertainment and for education . Separate the time into two halves . We will see whether it is OK for them . They will watch TV only in the morning and the other time he will be without this equipment . I think that that will be good for both . That is all that I can say for this topic . I hope that it was necessary to say . We will see . Thank you . 
Many people claim that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . Personally speaking , I agree with this statement . Firstly , owing to the fact that if we do not have a good health condition , we ca not enjoy our life , therefore it does not matter if we have a lot of money , because we wo not be able to benefit from it . Secondly , for the reason that if we are healthy , we can do sports or spend time with our family and we do not need to be rich to do these things . However , for me , the most important thing is to have a well -balanced life . Consequently , I believe that we should take care of our habits in order to have a healthy life and at the same time , have enough money to be financially free . In conclusion , being healthy is by far more important than being rich . Nevertheless , we must be careful with our money , due to the fact that it is relevant for our life . 
My favorite meal is Mandi . It 's a famous local meal that consists of grilled chicken with rice and a lot of pepper and a lot of spices . I usually prepare and eat it with friends as we gather together to have fun every week or so . I think there are two reasons I like Mandi : the first reason is how we prepare it , where we light a fire and prepare it for the Mandi together and the second is that it 's delicious . 
My reasons for learning English : There are plenty of reasons for learning English , do not you think ? Here I will show you some of the benefits of learning English . Firstly , if you speak English , you will be able to communicate with people from almost everywhere , due to the fact that it is the most spoken international language . Secondly , for the reason that it can help you to find better jobs or improve your CV . Thirdly , because if you understand English , you will have more sources of information and entertainment . For instance , you will be able to watch the You Tube channels of English -speaking people . Last but not least , I believe that acquiring a new language can be fairly enjoyable . Besides , you can make new friends while you are studying . In conclusion , as I see it , learning English is extremely useful . Besides it can be quite fun and interesting . So , my question is ... why are you waiting to learn English ? 
Although I feel that students should not be required to have any compulsory lectures , I also support that they should take some particular ones or responsibilities for graduation . The most famous responsibility type given at schools is volunteer work . I base my idea on two reasons . First and foremost , working as a volunteer gives students the responsibility of a task . With the aim of completing their tasks , they try to finish their work and this experience will most probably help them not only graduate but also to land a job in the future . Secondly , volunteers contribute to the workforce in marketplace while doing their tasks and needless people benefit from these volunteers ' contributions very much . Thanks to their efforts , according to statistics , volunteering has become much more important than before . In a nutshell , volunteering is very beneficial to both students and people who need help . In this way , students can get good grades , graduate and find a good job . 
Dear Sam , It is really important nowadays to learn at least one foreign language . The reason why is because the world has become very small with the internet . In these days , people can meet , speak and work in a different country only if they speak the language that the country has . For example , learning English is something that is necessary , because English is an international language . In jobs and businesses , if you know a foreign language you will know how to deal with difficult situations , such as customer service issues or communicating with people . In studying and education , if you would like to apply for a master 's degree or Ph . D , you need to learn a foreign language . It also applies if you would like to study aboard . You need to be able to speak a foreign language , it depends on the country . Finally , I highly recommend that you start learning from now on . Think about it and let me know . With love , Sara 
Dear Sarah , It is a really important thing to learn a language nowadays . In the past , people usually spoke only one language , but now we need to learn many languages for many reasons , like studying , working , traveling and the educational part , like if you want to apply to study abroad , in the UK you have to prepare for an IELTS exam by reviewing some past papers and using websites to help to improve your language skills . In addition , also , for people who love traveling , they have to learn lots of languages , English , French , Spanish and Japanese . It is best to have knowledge for things in life , especially learning languages and technological things . In my opinion , if you want to learn languages , firstly write your goals , why you want to learn this language . Secondly , you need to make sure to have an excellent outfit . 
In spite of the countless examples and benefits of working in offices without having walls , like the ones at Google , I strongly hold the belief that it is much more efficient to work in enclosed workplaces . I based my choice on two reasons . First and foremost , I personally cannot concentrate on my work while I am in open area where other people , even if they are my co -workers , can easily gaze at me . Provided that I have a personal area , I can burn the midnight oil unhesitatingly . Without listening to conversations , music and unnecessary and unimportant trivial sayings , I most probably manage to do my best . For instance , last week , I worked in a cubical for a project . Unfortunately , other peoples ' voices disturbed me so much that our company lost getting the government financial aid for the project since I failed to submit a well -prepared draft . Secondly , time goes too fast . There are many innovations and developments , not only in technology but also in other fields . Thus , it should be ready to be open to new things . Even though it seems to be a new , modern approach to work in open areas , independent , home office working is a newer recent step taken by employers . In a nutshell , it is better to work in a personal space for me to be able to roll up my sleeves . Through this way of working , I can focus on my tasks much more efficiently . What 's more , working individually and independently is the new working style of today 's world . 
I use a computer almost all day , usually eight hours actively per day , between eight a.m . and eleven p.m . Usually , I use a computer for studying , web research , watching You Tube videos , surfing the social media , and playing games on it . What I most like to do with a computer is study English , Data Analysis and Entrepreneurship , and also do research on the internet . 
Dear members of the town council , I agree with your idea , banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants is great , but we must think carefully about it . First , can we punish everybody that uses mobile phones ? Do we have enough laws ? Do we have staff to check and punish in all these places ? It is very important to consider this because the law needs to be obeyed . You should remember how the mobile phone is part of life nowadays . Everybody , in all places , uses this equipment all the time , so it will not be easy to change it . It will be so hard to change it . What can we do ? We can only prepare it for this , be persistent , make a lot of effort , and we must prepare for a strong reaction against this law . It is very important to raise awareness in our population , we live in a small town , so if we conquest their minds and hearts , we will have success with the law . We need to show that the law is important to the integration of the population , here everybody knows each other , but currently , nobody talks in public spaces , what is the reason ? The addiction to the mobile phone , many people use it in the public spaces , in the restaurants looking at this device . They could understand that the law is crucial for society . 
In my opinion , learning music and playing an instrument must be given as a lecture because music will help students to relax after a long and tiring school day . Most students have some lectures they do not like , like math or literature . During some lectures like these , some of them get bored and want to play with something . Upon this , to learn and enjoy some music could be an option for them and studying music and playing instruments should be chosen by students and it can be more effective and faster for their learning . Also students should be educated about everything and should know at least some information about those things , and music and playing instruments is one of them . Some students may have capability to play instruments very well than math or literature lectures . Upon this , a student will have a chance to improve his facilities instead of studying a lecture which he or she does not like or has no passion to learn it . 
Last autumn , my best friend and I decided to take a trip to Nan Jing , China after a hard semester at university . And I must say that it is the most memorable trip I 've had . It was a windy day , when loads of yellow leaves were falling off the trees . My best friend and I walked slowly in XYZ boulevard and enjoyed the autumn breath . We took a lot of photos and visited some attractive places , like the fairs , the square ... We felt like all our pressures had disappeared . There were also many cafes and restaurants . We went to one of them just to be chill in the lofi music . Moreover , because of the love for the Chinese culture , we bought 2 traditional costumes as meaningful souvenirs . To be honest , rarely did we have time to do things like that . Every moment there was priceless . The special thing is that my friend and I saved up for 4 years for this trip and finally it came true ! The feeling when achieving the goal was extremely cheerful . I will never forget about this trip . If I have other chances , I will go back with my best friend . 
In my opinion , books are the most important things in our life , because books teach us " What is life ? " and " How can we live fairly ? " There are so many factors which books teach us . So , I am against computers and tablets replacing books in life . They should not replace them completely at least . We know technology is improving and extensive , but I say like before , they should not replace them completely . We need to touch books ' paper and we need to feel them . Books are beautiful and valuable for this . Hence , we should take possession of them and protect them against who wants to destroy them . As a result , there are so many things which we learn from books . We should not permit them to be replaced by any technological development instead of books . On the other hand , we must read more and more and improve ourselves . I admire everything about books . 
Here , in Brazil , we just have the normal classes and this is not good because we do not have a distraction from all the classes . I think studying music is a good thing because it is helpful to stimulate discipline in students , and learning how to play some instrument can be good for the student how activities extracurricular . In the USA , it is so common that all the schools teach music in their classes and , in my opinion , it is so good . A song is so helpful with feelings and with the mood . There the youngsters always listen to music . Learning music is a good form of forgetting the problems with other disciplines and it is helpful too for making friends . Furthermore , it is always good to learn new things . So maybe if all schools have music classes , the students are gonna be so much more excited to go to school instead of staying home watching something on TV . So if you are thinking about adding some music classes in your school , I say that it is a good thing to do now . 
I really like sleeping in a dark and quiet room because I feel that I can relax and I fall asleep faster . I prefer a comfortable bed and a small lamp next to the bed for a lecture before sleeping . I cannot sleep well in a light room , the light is annoying and I fall sleep later and awake with a headache . But I do not have any problems with a noisy room or external sounds . 
Hello Michael , Have you ever tasted a cemita ? A cemita is like a burger but with totally different contents , it 's made with a piece of meat named ' milanesa ' . This ' milanesa ' is a chicken , beef or pork breaded bisteek . A cemita also contains avocado , onion , beans , mayo , and papalo , which is a herb with a hot taste , and a very , very hot sauce . The bread is special too . There are cemitas of different sizes , but the most common one is huge , and it is served in two halves because it is impossible to eat it complete . I usually eat cemitas when I go to the downtown , as there is a place with a variety of local food and their special dish is a cemita . They sell cemitas close to my house and I buy one when I do not have any food at home . I really like the combination of all the ingredients and the taste of the meat and the size is perfect to makes you feel full . The taste of the avocado and the meat produces a perfect combination . I am sure you will enjoy one when you know it . 
In my opinion , all students in school should study music in their classes . In general , people love music . They have to know about music to some extent . So , at least , they should play musical instruments for some time . For example , I think that the piano would be a good example for students to play a musical instrument . And then , hopefully , it would be preferable if there were some kinds of studies which were related to music . What is more , learning to play a musical instrument with the other students would help the student work with their classmates . Playing music as a part of the band would be a good experience for the students as well . I do not think that playing music has to be obligatory , but it should be studied to some degree . This is why I think that all students in school should study music in their classes . 
I think that university students should move away and live on their own while they are attending school . Thus , they are able to nurture their independence . When they are adults , they have to live by themselves . I suppose that university students are half adults and half children . Therefore , when they are at university , they should also get used to living on their own . Hopefully , they are able to get their parents ' help . Of course , they should not completely depend on their parents , but they should depend on their parents to some extent . For example , their parents should pay school expenses . What is more , students should not work for money . They do not forget that they are at university for studying . However , I agree that working for experience is good for a student 's experience . On the other hand , there are some students who live at home with their family while they are students . I do no think that that is a bad thing . Living with their family would benefit their finances . In most cases , they do not have to do housework on their own . Consequently , they are able to have more time to study . It is definitely a good thing . On balance , moving away and living at home , both of them are not bad at all . 
I like playing video games in my free time . I usually play a video game at the weekend , especially at night between six o 'clock and midnight . I like to do this activity because it de -stresses me , gives me pleasure , cheers me up , and fascinates me . It happened why playing a video game is an activity that holds my attention and stimulates my critical thinking . The last time I played a video game was four years ago . 
Well , I believe that sometimes it is acceptable to tell a lie . First , it is very difficult , maybe impossible , to tell the truth all the time . It would be hard , and so disagreeable to tell the truth all the time . Imagine if you tell the truth to your wife all the time . You stopped to talk with a friend in the street , nothing wrong , but your wife needed you quickly , so you said that the traffic was bad , because of this , you were late , end of the history , no fight , no problem . There are many examples to show how it is reasonable to lie sometimes . For instance , if a person asks you about her clothes , or about her new hair colour , or about the results of her plastic surgery , and you consider it ugly , or a disaster . What should you say ? The truth ? NA ? Of course not . It 's better to lie , perhaps not all lie , it is not necessary to say , it is beautiful , but you can say it is not bad ( the truth is bad ) , but what is the value of making the person sad ? A little lie is better . Sometimes , a little lie is important too about the perspectives of the life too . For example , about someone 's health , about the economic situation , about reality . It is not necessary to be crude . 
In my opinion , both points have their advantages and disadvantages . I will start with living at the university with other students . The first advantage that comes to my mind is that the experience can be amusing and you will remember it for the rest of your life . Another advantage , which I think is quite interesting , is the fact that you 'll be forced to leave your comfort zone . Therefore , you 'll have to buy your own groceries , prepare your meals , do the washing and so on . However , there are some disadvantages too . For instance , your mates can lead you to an unhealthy life and you can lose your focus and , as a result , get bad marks in your exams . Besides , if you live away , you will probably spend more money . Let 's talk now about living with your family while you 're studying . Firstly , if you are living with your parents , you 'll be able to save more money . Secondly , you have more chances to be more focused on your exams for the reason that you wo not have bad influences . In conclusion , both options are pretty good , but if I had to choose between one of the two , I would choose to live at the university with other students , due to the fact that it 's a more enjoyable experience . 
Yesterday , my children argued about the purpose of television . One said that it could entertain in many ways and played a vital role in the modern era . However , the other insisted that it also educated people in many areas . And I finished their argument by combining both options . First of all , television can entertain people . With the large number of films , game shows and news , people can relax after a hard day . Almost all TV programs are recreational and amusing , which makes you laugh immediately . In that way , television is an ideal means for you to kill time . Moreover , TV manufacturers have created some kinds of smart televisions that you even play video games on and sing karaoke with others . They also allow you to connect to the Internet and access social media . Therefore , television is an ideal means of entertainment . Besides , television can educate people in different areas . Many educational programs for kids have been broadcast , like ' Wildlife ' and ' Spell with Mrs . Jenny . " Moreover , there are some game shows that provide viewers with life skills . I learned a lot of ways to cook on ' ABC 's kitchen ' . In conclusion , television not only entertains but also educates . 
It is often said that it is important to always tell the truth , but is it ever acceptable to tell a lie ? Firstly , I want to state that I agree with this phrase . As I see it , if you want to be someone who can be trusted by other people and have their confidence , you have to be honest with them and , no matter what , tell the truth . Besides , if you are someone who normally tells lies , then you have a big chance of forgetting the lies you had told and , therefore , people will notice it and , as a consequence , you will lose your credibility . Although , in some cases , you can be allowed to tell a lie in order to relieve others ' pain . For instance , imagine that your dog is sick and , sadly , he dies , so now , you have to explain it to your children . Do not you think that instead of explaining to them that your dog has died , you could tell them that your dog has found his mother and he has gone to live with her ? In conclusion , I 'm one of those who tries to be honest and always tell the truth , owing to the fact that , in the end , you know what is real and what is not , and for this reason , I believe that there is no point in telling lies to other people . 
There is not a home that does not have a television . That is one of the important inventions in last one hundred years . Television has two very useful sides , but I think it is referring to the channels you put on it . The other side is that it gives you bad things , like habits , clothes , sexual things , I see that this side as a bad one and the worst around the world . People always watch television . The mass media and governments play on this thing to give their citizens what they want to give . The governments dominate people by mass media and have the authority of their brains . The same thing , social media always does the same , that is dominate your brain . People waste around half their life on silly things that never help them in life . Surely there are a lot of sites and channels that help you to learn things . 
