Health and wealth are both crucial points in the lives of people . Health is an essential part of our lives . Indeed , without it there could be some issues associated with our body and our mind . Health is crucial for everyone and every person should take care of their own health . However , for many people , wealth is more important than being healthy , due to being a wealthy person allows you to do a huge number of things and it permits you to live a better life . Personally , I do not agree with this idea , as I think that being healthy is more important and more essential than being rich . Indeed , good health is important in the life of all people and without it we cannot live . Health and wealth are both crucial for everyone , but having good health is surely the main thing that we could have in our life . 
