uld be so hard for these people who must learn and act as volunteers and it must start at schools . 
The W&I website is a tool that I 've been using for some time and , as an experienced user , I have some thoughts and tips to help other users . On the platform , we have access to different task levels plus a space for tests . The work done is stored so we can check and try to improve a past activity at any time , being a good way to verify our improvement over time . As we 're dealing with an AI resource - there is no teacher checking the activities , only artificial intelligence - it 's essential to keep in mind that some things can look a little odd in the feedback , with moments when we 're sure everything is alright but the website keeps indicating some changes to be made . My overall opinion is that W&I is a good resource for those who want to improve their writing abilities in English with instant feedback , but we have to consider that the tool uses AI , so some errors can occur with the feedback . Nonetheless , the tool can be a good learning resource as long as complemented with the habit of reading and listening to current English content , so when there 's a doubt about the feedback , you have enough baggage to deal and decide what 's right or not . 
I do not like exercise , but I have the PT in our school class . So , I usually do exercise four times a week . And I like doing exercise outside . There are many reasons for it . For example , I can get some fresh air , I can communicate with neighbors , relatives and anyone else , and so on . Exercise has a lot of variety , but I like running . While I 'm running , I can see the view near my house and I can change my house . and feel good . People 's feelings are influenced by exercise . Exercise gives us many good things . 
I have discovered " Write and Improve " randomly . It was kind of suggested to me . Anyway " Write and Improve " is a really good opportunity to put your thoughts into words and to get feedback instantly . To learn a language , it is important to write and to structure your thoughts . The site is structured in different levels , so you can choose the levels that suit you best . You can choose the topic about what you want to write and a requirement for word sets . After entering your text , you get an assessment and classification of your language ability . In addition , you get notes on suspected errors , which is really helpful . Furthermore , you have a run chart and an overview of your language level , which helps you to follow your development and makes your language education transparency . I can recommend this site and this kind of learning . In our school days , we had the task to write and summarize a story . I think it is a great way to learn a language . It is not enough to learn vocabulary or to watch movies in your goal language . As I mentioned , you have to put your thoughts into words and to use the new vocabulary . 
Hello classmate . My name is Xinh and I hope you are having a nice day . Today , we have an interesting topic . This is about your opinions about taking care of yourself . It is more important to be healthy than to be rich . And I agree with this opinion . I think health is very important for everyone . If you do not have good health , there are many things you ca not do it . Also , maybe you will miss many good opportunities in your life . If you have good health , you can easily travel everywhere , you can easily work on everything and some things . As you know , there is a lot of work to do in your life and if you are wealthy , I ca not compete with other people around you . You are always fighting with many things in your life and of course , good health is needed . Trust me , if you are healthier than many people around here , you can go faster and be rich if you try your best . If you are rich but have bad health , it will take a lot of money and time to heal , and there are even diseases that cannot be cured , like cancer . I know there are many people who worked a lot without taking care of themselves . They earned a lot of money . But when they recognized any health problems , it was late . Of course , money is very important , but you should enhance the time , money and work . You need to work to make money , but do not let it rule you . 
Well , for me , I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room , because this is my style and I always sleep when the night is quiet . However , I can also sleep when there is noise , sometimes I am tired and I ca not feel anything close to me . Finally , I think 8 hours is a good amount of time for our mental health , but some people like to sleep for just 6 hours . In my opinion , the best time to sleep is between 10pm to 5am . 
Sleeping is one of the necessary things for humans . And the sleeping place is an important factor that is directly related to your quality of sleep . For me , I would choose to sleep in a dark and quiet room for some reasons . According to an ABC article , light will make you find it hard to sleep . You will have the feeling as if it was daytime outdoors and your biological clock will make you conscious and active . So , it may take you a long time to sleep . Another element for a nice sleep is sound . The atmosphere around you should be peaceful and quiet . Therefore , you wo not be distracted by other stuff and feel comfortable enough to be relaxed after a hard day . I recommend that you should play some instrumental music or ballad songs . They have been studied and shown to have positive effects on the quality of a humans 's sleep . In a nutshell , I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room . 
I like to sleep by being in a quiet room , but having a small light in the corner of the room because , I 'm still a bit scared of the dark . When I sleep in a dark quiet place it relaxes my mind from any problems or stress that I might have during the day . When you sleep in a dark place , your mind is more likely to sleep because of the lack of light , so I can have a good night 's rest for the next day . That is how I like to sleep . 
Having gone through a tragic and full -of -challenges 2020 with the COVID 19 pandemic , we eventually started a new year 2021 with many hopes and promised things . I listed loads of stuff I wanted to work on . Currently , I major in English teaching at Hanoi National University of Education and I 'm really pleased with the area that I decided to pursue from scratch . There are lots of memorable experiences , as well as challenges , that I have learned a lot from . I learned how to plan lessons , designed many detailed slides for presenting in front of a bunch of people and did teamwork effectively . Besides , I still find that I have a dearth of many important skills , such as outdoor activities and communication skills . They are also my weakness and the reason why I did not win any scholarships in my first semester . But I will make an effort to improve them day by day . I will participate in one of the clubs at school and be more active when doing outside activities . At the same time , I plan to have a part -time job as a private teacher . So , I will gain more experience in my area and my communication skills will be enhanced . I always believe that one day I will be able to store enough knowledge to be an expert in my area . Then , I will use all the things I have learned at university to help my students on their study route . 
I guess that is a problem . Nobody wants to live in the back country . After finishing such a tough degree , like in this case , medicine , that is not easy . For a lot of students , it is difficult to have access to a degree because of their financial situation . Many students have to take on debt , to pay the fee , rents and other bills . Then should those people be sent somewhere in the back country , it does not seem fair to me . After their degree , they have to invest also a lot of money in the practice , devices and equipment . There is no end of debt in sight . In addition , what is also very important is social life . For singles , it would be very difficult to live in the back country without a partner maybe . There might be people , maybe with family , who would like to live there and to enjoy the life out of the city . On the other hand , there are families for whom it is really important to have access to the things which an urban city offers . A fair and right distribution , I guess is very difficult . It depends on needs , social situations , preferences and lifestyles , where people decide to live . We , as patients , require a good treatment when we go to the doctor and , therefore , the doctor has to be satisfied . 
Telling the truth is not always easy . However , there are situations in which lying may be the most efficient decision . Many people argue that lying is one of the worst things one can do and always telling the truth is very important . Whether I believe so as well will be discussed in the following . First of all , it has to be mentioned that the legitimacy of a lie depends on the situation . If the lyer and , moreover , the person that is being lied to was not offended in any way , I consider a lie legit . However , those situations occur rarely and one has to carefully analyse the importance of the situation . For instance , when only once arriving delayed at school the importance of that situation would not be crucial and no involved would be violated physically or mentally . Nevertheless , the danger of analysing a certain unsuitable situation still exists . Furthermore , I do not recommend lying in decisive cases in life . In crucial cases of life , a lie can destroy relationships and worsen situations rather than heal them . Moreover , the lying person themself may not endure the burdens of distortion and may suffer even more than the person who is being lied to . For example , when hiding a fraud from one 's partner , the matter would be turn out better telling the truth than veiling it for a certain margin of time . When confessing a lie , the opposite person may recognise the guilt and forgive it . On the contrary , hiding the truth could cause and horribly effect a person . 
Dear I would like to write you about the new rule that is to ban the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants . I am sure that the rule is absolutely outrageous . You should not accept that suggestion . As you know , mobile phones are indispensable in our everyday life . We could not even spend just one day without it in this modernised world . I know that it annoys people when someone speaks on their phone in a public space . However , that is because they need to do it at the time . Besides , people sometimes need to use the phone in case they are in an emergency situation . In those cases , their life and death would depend on their phone . I must say that you could not decide whether or not a person has to die . As I have written above , it is a bad idea to ban the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and so forth . Instead , you should just call on people to refrain from the use of mobile phones in some public spaces . Definitely , you should not ban it as that is too much . I hope that the other people who think about the ban would understand my opinion . I am strongly wishing it . Best regards , A citizen 
I would like to say that it is basically the right thing to always tell the truth . It is very important , too . People must tell the truth all the time . However , I think that there could be a moment when it is acceptable to tell a lie . For example , the time to tell a joke to friends . It would be funny , and people like funny things . It makes a relationship better . Likewise , there is a time in which the truth should not be told . We have to think about the result before we say something . If we could be offensive or rude when we tell the truth , then we should refrain from telling the truth . Thus , we are able to be socially acceptable . By the way , how about telling a lie without any reason ? I suppose that that could not be right in any situation . Telling a lie is heinous . I am sure that most people agree with me about it . I would be terrified if all people lied all the time in a callous way . I think that it is very important not to tell any lies . What is more , it is also important to trust people around you every time you see them . This is my opinion , but I would like to say that people should hate someone who has no qualm about telling a lie . 
