Sleeping well is an essential aspect of a healthy lifestyle . I myself like to sleep in a large room , preferably with the window open . The room itself should be rather dark because I am woken up easily by the bright sunlight . With regard to the sounds , I prefer the bedroom to be a bit quiet , although the sound of formula one races puts me to sleep in just a minute . Somehow I cannot stand that roaring sound of the motors . 
When people have the same teacher for several years , they benefit from the fact that the teacher knows the student inside out and is able to see the study progress the student is making . In other words , the teacher is able to monitor the student 's growth for a longer period . Also , the teacher may relate to the students on a more personal level , enabling the teacher to understand the students more in -depth . Aspects of the student 's private life can be more easily understood by the teacher , whereto he or she can empathize more with the consequences and help the student to overcome difficulties during their studies . On the other hand , a fresh pair of eyes will help the student to grow further . So new teachers could highlight more easily aspects where the student needs to focus on improvements . Each teacher brings along his or her special educational qualifications . All those aspects together will facilitate progress . 
In my opinion , all students should be able to study music since this requires many skills and competences which will help them in their lives . First of all , studying music is a great example of improving the creativity skills of students . Students will have to be creative while playing music . Creativity is one of those competences that will take them further in life while pursuing a career . This competence will help them to successfully anticipate different situations under various circumstances . One other positive aspect of studying music is that it provides a way to express themselves in other ways than with words . As long as lecturers provide a safe environment in the classroom , students will be able to use music to show other students how they feel . Music can be used as a means to vent emotions . Furthermore , playing music binds people together . Whether it is during a jam session or whether it is when studying a musical play . It is very fulfilling to jointly accomplish an enormous task , such as a difficult music piece . This teamwork skill will have an added value in the future . Therefore , I believe that all students should have access to musical studies . 
