Most medical doctors in order to earn more money prefer to work in cities than work in small rural places or small cities , and because of that , rural areas are faced with medical problems and a lack of doctors . To solve this problem , governments should make some statutes as to give much more to those doctors who work in a rural area that might encourage them , and governments can decrease the taxes in their salary . Moreover , giving them some privileges in the country , like traveling cheaper than other citizens , that might be a nice privilege for those doctors , because many rural areas or villages are away from cities and traveling might have a high cost . Besides this , rural areas should be developed by governments to appeal to doctors to live there , for example , founding some sport stuff like swimming pools , tennis and football fields . These solutions could be helpful for doctors who have no claim to work in a village or a rural place . So if doctors desire more money to work , increasing their salaries might be a solution besides other privileges . 
