Languages are the skills with which people can communicate with each other . Learning is the thing that everybody has to do and always be up -to -date with their knowledge . Learning new languages , besides being beneficial , is one of the important things on earth , because it is never old -fashioned , it will always have its position . If you learn a new language , you will be proud of yourself and break new ground . The more you learn , the more you keep digging into your knowledge . So it will never be old , Language dies when all of the people who speak it die . There is a wonderful quote by Nelson Mandela , that said , “ If you talk to a man in a language he understands , that goes to his head . If you talk to him in his language , that goes to his heart . ” I think everybody has to learn at least one new language besides his native language . That opens a lot of new opportunities for him . He also can travel to the country where people speak it . 
