I think that it is a better to live on their own when they are attending school . Generally , most students live at home with their family and depend on them for living things . It is not bad for students , however , living by themselves will give them advantages in the future . I have two points about my idea . First of all , living by ourselves develops our living skills . There are many things to live like washing , cooking , cleaning and so on . Then , at home , we probably rely on our families , especially our mothers . But , if we live by ourselves , no one does them without us . And , most students will leave their home and live alone when they begin working in society . So , living by themselves while they are students will be preparation for their future lives . Secondly , students can make time to do something efficiently better than living at home with their families . For example , at home , when we want to go to the bathroom , if another family member already has been doing it , we have to wait to finish it . This may be a little thing in daily life , but it also breaks our plan during the day . If we live alone , we can decide when we go to the bathroom and it makes it easier to make a plan during a day . While we are students , there many things to do such as studying , working in a part -time job and so on . So , in order to use time flexibly , living alone is very effective for students . All in all , I described two points about preparation for the future and using time effectively . Living by ourselves while we are students is very difficult and hard . But , it will give us a good effect definitely . 
My experience with Write and Improve . I started using it 1 month ago , more or less , and I have to say that I believe that it is a quite useful tool to improve my writing skills . One of my favourite things about this page is that it has many different types of writing to choose from , for instance you can write an informal letter and then a formal essay . Besides , I find the huge variety of levels that the website provides quite helpful . You can find levels for beginners , intermediate and advanced . However , I 'm not so happy with the automatic corrector , for the reason that sometimes it can misunderstand some of your words . In conclusion , as I see it , Write and Improve is a wonderful tool if you want to train your writing skills and therefore I would recommend it to everyone who wants to acquire better English . 
After having done some body exercises with my class , I am getting used to the idea that this is one of the best ways to keep our body in shape and in good health . Even with the time you spend doing body exercises , you are supposed to improve not only your physical health , but also your mental one . Some of them are aimed at strengthening your upper limbs , others are perfect for your legs or back . The variety of exercises is quite large and most of them come from the U . S . , however some American research has shown that a body exercise -based lifestyle is not the only way to take care of our health . What the statistics suggest to us is that we should keep track of our food habits . All of us should eat a great deal of fruit and vegetables as a way to avoid breathing difficulties or blood pressure problems . Some rubbish food we are used to eating is nowhere near as genuine as what we are recommend to eat . Just let me to be a little ironic : every rubbish food restaurant should be cordoned off , no car should pull over to them . 
I would like to live a long , calm life , definitely . It would be better rather than having a shorter life , even though that would be much more intense . I would like to explain the reasons . First of all , I like a calm environment very much . I always tend to avoid noisy places because of that . Generally , I do not like to talk to people . If anything , I would prefer to read books or something like that . Although I like to listen to people who are talking . Besides , a long life would give me more opportunities to get various experiences . I have a lot of things that I would like to do . To do so , I must live for as a much time as possible . If you do not have much time to live , then what could you achieve in such a short time ? However , in spite of what I wrote above , I agree that intensity is important to some extent . Even if I could live for a long time , it would be boring when I could not do anything . It is reasonable that some people do not hesitate to do dangerous things because they want to do so . On balance , I could not say which is better . But I would just choose a long life . 
That is an interesting question . Personally , I can sleep in any situation . For instance , before becoming a mother , I was sleeping in a dark and quiet room , but when I became a mother , I could not sleep in a dark room because sometimes my daughter wakes up during the night and she cries because she is scared . As a result of that , I turn on a small light in the room because that helps my daughter to be more reassured . 
Some people argued that students should not have to study music in school . However , I 'm against that idea for some reasons . First of all , it is undeniable that music is an effective entertaining way . As far as I 'm concerned , nowadays , students have to learn a huge amount of knowledge with loads of academic subjects . That leads to their high studying pressure and being overwhelmed by trillions of theories in many areas . Therefore , if there are music classes on their schedule , it will reduce students 's stress and make their brain less tense . Music is proved to have some health benefits including enhancing the memory and ability to concentrate . Moreover , the soft melody created by musical instruments can help them to calm down , soothe their mind . It tends to decrease the risk of conflicts between irritated students . Music also develops students 's artistic talents . By learning to play musical instruments , their sense of art is more subtle and delicate . In coincidence , it improves the right brain of learners . As a result , students can become more creative and be interested in the art area . For students that have talent in music at the beginning , they will maybe gain some useful experience and soon be experts in their pursuit of a musical career . For the rest , it 's likely some of them will find their passion for music . Then , they direct their action to become musicians , instrumentalists or even singers . From the above benefits of music , I think that this subject should be taught at school . It can make a significant change in students 's life . 
I like reading in my free time . I used to have free time after lunch but now I read less frequently . I love finding out new stories and new authors , I like it because it is so much fun and useful for learning many things . I usually read every day before dinner or before I go to bed . 
In many less populated areas , there is a lack of doctors as a huge number of them are moving to cities . Most medical doctors want to move to a town because there are more opportunities to find a stable job , such as nurse and other hospital workplaces . Indeed , in urban areas , there are more places to work , due to health centres in metropolis being bigger than the countryside 's health centres . Furthermore , in populated zones , for some kinds of specialists , such as physicians , psychologists and dentists , it is easier to find clients due to them working in areas that are more populated and where there is more density of people . For instance , a dentist who works in the city has more possibility to have a regular client rather then a rural medic . To resolve these problems , small towns and counties should try to search for more volunteers , like medical students , to work in their infirmary . Being a clinician in a big town is easier , but it is important to have more doctors in rural areas . 
