There is no doubt that these days , taking a rest from our job and daily work is very important for our bodies . There is some important information almost all people need to know before going on a holiday , such as the place , location , activities and residence . All of these things are important to have a good holiday . However , in this essay , I am going to write about my experience in the United States . When I got my scholarship from my government , I decided to go to the United States , for three main reasons . The first reason is that there are many states and we can try many things at the same time when we study . Moreover , the weather there is different from state to state , so you have many choices to decide which place you want to go on your holiday . Additionally to the place that we chose to visit , we saw many beautiful places that I had never seen . For example , I visited Georgia , Florida and Washington DC . In these states I went to many cities , such as Athens , Atlanta and Helin . Moreover , in Florida I went to Gainsaville , Tampa and Orlando . In conclusion , I had a great holiday in the United States . 
In my point of view , I think exercise is important to everyone , but just not exercise is important , it is important to eat healthy food , always drink water , eat fruit and the most important , do exercise every day . Nowadays , there are fat people , but if you are fat , it does not mean you are not healthy . Beauty is not thin people . Independent of your body , you need to feel good about yourself . Do not care about other opinions about your body or what kind of clothes you use , think just about you and your health . However , some people do not do exercise , but just eat healthy foods and feel very healthy . It is about that , feeling healthy and not following a standard of beauty imposed by society . Always be yourself . The best thing is to take care of yourself and doing exercise does not need to be boring . It can be fun , riding bicycle , using rollerblades , skating or swimming , etc . 
Health is more important than wealth It is well known proverb " health is wealth . " And we know human progress has been changing for years and it will continue to develop further . But sayings and proverbs do not change and we have similar proverbs in most languages . So , health is real wealth . In other words , we can enjoy our money and property when we are healthy . A sick person cannot be happy with his wealth , he needs a healthy body to be happy . We have wealthy and poor countries around the world . When we see the " happy index , " it says that only wealthy countries are happier . In fact , a poor country like Bhutan is the number one place where its people are happier than all countries and their people . Bhutan does not even have a proper democratic government , but a kind of kingdom running the country . Similarly , we can notice in rural and urban areas of a country in general , we find that people in the villages are healthier than those who are living in cities . And we know cities provide many more facilities and employment . The above information says that health is more important than wealth . 
Nowadays , people argue about the importance of good health compared to that of being rich . In my view , I suppose that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . Firstly , good health is considered as the most valuable treasure of each person . When you are healthy , you have loads of energy to do anything you want . You can climb up the steep mountains , run fast in the windy hills and do some extreme sports without being limited . Moreover , with good health , you will work productively . A strong farmer can do twice as much as a weak one . Similarly , a white -collar worker who exercises every day is able to work overtime and is usually active in their work . Sadly , some people are too self -confident about their strength and make full use of it to earn for living . They maybe become a millionaire , but in the long run , they will pay a heavy toll with their health . The money you earned will be used for pay the hospital bill instead of travelling all around the world and spending time with family members . In conclusion , I put health first and invest in my health for further benefits in the future . 
Computers and tablets should not fully take the place of books in schools and universities . Books are soul of education and knowledge . In particular , schools and university are colourless without books . We cannot imagine students without books . Books are original sources of classics and literature . Those classics gave us what we have now . Books are as important as computers and tablets are for us . We can use them for different places and purposes , neither can completely replace the other . It is like someone can manage his work with one hand and he should delete with the other hand . Just like we need various types of vehicles to travel , everything has its importance in life . Books are possible to produce at less amount in many numbers . And books can be bought and replaced , simply spending a few dollars . We cannot expect the same for computers and tablets . They are costly and many people cannot afford them . We have many countries at present that can not provide books to their people in a proper way and how we should talk about the replacement of books with computers and tablets . 
