I use my computer every day . I work for an overseas business department in a food manufacturing company in Japan . To communicate with our customers and partners , I usually write e -mails to them , and sometimes I have a meeting with them through a web meeting system . So almost every day I use my computer , I like the time when I am not using computers . 
The statement for today is : It is more important to be healthy than to be rich . And I think that is definitely true . Your health is very important . You ca not be rich if you have not got good health , unless you have a rich dad and he gives you everything you want . But most people have not got a rich dad . They have to work to become rich . And if you want to work so you can become rich , you have to have good health . Otherwise your boss wo not accept you . I think that when you are healthy , you are also happier . At least I am and I hope you are to . Money is not important when you are healthy and you have friends and family . And you ca not buy these things . A person who is not rich can be happy too , because for most people , their health and their family and friends are the most important things they have ! 
