I think that students having the same teacher is better than having a new teacher each year . I 'll explain my opinion with xx reasons . First of all , I can become familiar with the teachers . So , I can ask questions more easily . I can speak without being nervous . I think it is good for students . Second , the teacher not moving is good for the feelings of the teacher . The teacher can easily become familiar with the school . Then , the teacher can relax at the school . Therefore , the teacher can teach the students better . It 's linked with making the students feel better . The teacher 's feelings influence the students ' feelings . So , caring for the teacher is an important part of caring for the students . Last , if I do not know the teachers , I have to begin the class with introductions . But If I know the teachers , I can begin the lesson without introductions . That means I can study each subject a few days before . Studying from the first day makes a student more genius . Having the same teacher gives good benefits to the students and the teacher . I may realize that changing teacher has a better point too . But because of these reasons , I think having the same teacher is better . 
I like sleeping in a warm and quiet room , I do not like the noise , like people that are speaking or children that are playing in the garden near my house . I sleep , more or less , for 10 hours a night , from nine o 'clock in the evening to seven o 'clock in the morning . Before going to bed , I usually drink a cup of milk after brushing my teeth and putting my pyjamas ( nightdress ) on . 
As my conclusion , depending on the situation , telling a lie is acceptable instead of forbidding to lie for an entire life . The reason why I think so comes from my personal experience . When I was 18 years old , I bumped into a robbery in a doom street . I was threatened with a knife and asked whether I had enough money or not . On the spot , I suddenly told a lie not to be captured and harmed . I pretended to be a jobless guy wandering to find some food and some clothing . I told him to give me ten dollars as I picked it up from the street today as a mercy . Fortunately , I was safe because of my white lie coming across my mind . If I were to be persistent in a principle not to tell a lie to others or be less flexible , I may have got injured or captured . Of course , on daily occasions , on the daily occasions , keep telling a lie to others diminishes your trust in the end . Hence , it should be better to refrain from a lie even on a tiny matter as a habit . Yet , if you are in a crisis , I would strongly recommend you to be agile and tell lies if needed for your safety . My experience might be extreme , but the intent of quoting this example is to stress that telling a lie justifies your end depending on the situation . 
I prefer choosing to have a more intense life as long as nobody lives forever . Everybody knows about it , it can be more interesting and fun . Imagine you can live good and dramatic romances . I would have moments of deception and joy . It is incredible to have a life like a roller coaster , up and down all the time . If I choose to live a long life until 100 years old , I think could not be so happy . I believe that everyone needs to enjoy all the moments of their life until their last second , because we do not know about what happens after death , probably paradise or resting forever . The best reason is to have intense moments in our lives , it is so boring to have a calm life , but sometimes , I think about not having problems . It is normal to have problems , everyone has them , rich people or poor people and I cannot forget to mention deceptions in our lives are normal too . Depending on the point of view about how calm your life will be , if it 's a life with emotions , sometimes , it can be good , but just living a calm all the time , all the time , all the decades , all the time is so boring . Intense moments in our lives make us more mature , sometimes it is so bad to go through a bad moment , but this moment can be necessary for you to grow in your life and for you to become a good man or woman . Thinking about all my trajectory , I think that I am a winner . 
I do not want to have a shorter and intense life . I do not know what there will be after the life , so I want to stay here for a long time , as long as possible . I saw many friends that died young , from car accidents , for example . I always thought they were very young , they could spend their lives , they could enjoy the family , they could build a career , but they are not here . For me , it is very sad . I prefer to spend my life which is quiet , calm , but in a productive way , I want to stay with my family , with my friends . I would like to enjoy my time , watch good films and programs on TV , read books , magazines and newspapers . I will travel a lot , as much as possible . I would like to know many places in the world , from traditional to touristic , but the exotic too . I would like an old age for this , travel , have culture , meet new friends in the world . I want to spend my long years aging writing . I would like to write articles , many articles , about many topics . I would like to write books too , I have many ideas , but today , I do not have the time for this . In the future , after my retirement , I will spend my time on this . 
I do not like to do exercise very much but I have begun last Sunday . I practice sport every two days and I prefer exercising outside because I can keep my own timing . There are many activities such as running , push -ups and sit -ups . Also sometimes my friends and I get together to play basketball or soccer . 
Do you like to exercise ? Yes , I do . How often do you exercise ? Well , I do exercise five days a week . When you exercise , do you prefer exercising at a gym or outside ? Because of the pandemic , I prefer to do exercise indoors in my house . Why ? Because this way the probability of infection is reduced . When I do exercise , I like to watch on my cellphone or listen to music . 
