For me , the best holiday ever was staying in Hawaii for a week . In February 2015 , me and my family went to Hawaii . At that time , I was so busy at my work . I was a member of the investment team in our division . And from April to January 2015 , I had to work very hard , I sometimes worked till midnight twice a week . After our project was completed in January 2015 , we went to Hawaii . When we were in Hawaii , we could see a very beautiful seaside landscape every day . It made me so relaxed and I felt that my stress on the job had gone . My family also felt relaxed and enjoyed Hawaii 's nature . But it was a little bit expensive to go to Hawaii . I have tried to save money . So if I have enough funds to go , I would like to visit Hawaii with my family again . 
I think that exercise is very important for my health . It is more important to keep my health . What I would like to stress is that exercise is one of the methods to keep my health . To keep my health , I think I have to take care of my meals and I have to take care of the quality of sleep . If I only exercise every day , eat junk foods and do not sleep well , can I keep my health ? I think it is very difficult . So I think that apart from exercise , I have to take care of what I eat and the quality of sleep . 
As to the future of travel , I think that the biggest difference will be the way of travelling . At present , we travel by car , train , airplane and ship all over the world . If we travel all over the world in the future , along with the improvement of technology , except for the above mentioned travelling methods , I think we will use a large drone or a flying car . I have heard that some companies are already trying to develop new technologies for drones and flying cars . It is possible they will be commercialized in the near future . Furthermore , in the near future , I think we will be able to travel into space . Along with the improving technology , not just astronauts , but we will be able to travel to the Moon or into space . But I think the food that we enjoy might be the same on a journey in the future . I think eating is one of the most important factors on a journey . 
