My favourite film is called The Giver . The story of the film is about a group of people who live in specific place and each one has a specific job . The leaders chose it for them when they became teenagers . The houner of the film is called Jounas and his job is to learn all the memories from the old men , because all people take some type of anesthetic to make them not feel any feelings , because the old people in the area believe feelings are not important and not good for people . For instance , all people take the same thing . However , Jounas could change that by breaking the rules and going out to the border of the area . When he arrives there , all people can feel again . 
The school of the future will be different in many ways from a standard educational model . The teachers will not occupy the center of the class , but will become mere facilitators . However , the importance of their role will persevere . It is the profile of the job that will evolve . The teachers of the future will cherish the pupils and hold them in the center of their attention , a center that has been taken by the curriculum . All of the teachers will be emotionally trained to maintain a high level of communication with the students . They will have a positive attitude and soft voice so students can feel that they are welcomed at all times . Students will decide upon their schooling programme , which will be immensely elastic . They will need to know a little about everything and everything about one chosen discipline . There will be no grading system , just the feedback pointing to strengths upon which the students can build their knowledge . However , the teachers will always be available for the students if they only wish to expand and amend some of their work . 
The new school year is coming and it ' s always a lot of expect together . In the last year , I was able to learn a lot about chemistry . I achieved more knowledge about laboratory techniques , chemical analysis and information , where more equipment was used to achieve results and send for process engineer . The other interesting thing that I could see was about how I could develop my abilities for the job market . I saw that subjects like leadership , communication and the ability to work in a team matter to achieve good positions in companies . I hope this year to continue learning more about this analysis and soft skills . My expectation with new disciplines is big too . I will get more information to apply what I have learned and feel more comfortable deciding what my area for professional action is . My goal is to achieve a 9 in all the tests for the disciplines , make more friends and network . So , I hope I have a wonderful year in this school . 
A holiday is always an important moment for people , because it 's a relaxing time that can help lower the stress level , load energy for the daily routine and contribute to the person 's reconnection with the family . My best holiday ever was when I went with my mother , father and brother , by car , to the south of Bahia for 5 days . We enjoyed travelling to beautiful places . We visited three cities where there was a lot of nature . We saw animals , lakes , seas , ate good food and slept in very comfortable hotels . The moment was very pleasant , because it was possible to be together as a family , a nice atmosphere and rest in a reconnection between all these things . That was the first trip that we did . And maybe the choice of the best holiday ever is because of this . Although the other trips that done as a family , there were not a lot of expectations and we just wanted stay close far way the problem . 
The purpose of this report is to give all the general information about a site suggested to us by our teacher to practise and improve our English . Our teacher suggested a site to improve our writing English skills , and honestly I thought my progresses would have been quicker and more radical . However , there are some sides I really appreciate , but others disappointed me . I do not like the fact that I have to subscribe to a contract and pay a fee in order to practice with some tasks . This kind of resource should be free and all of us should be given the opportunity to practice , even if our English level is not so high . Only when you practise with it for several weeks can you see some radical and persistent breakthroughs . What I really appreciate is the large number of tasks you can choose from . What is more , they are classified in groups depending on your English level . This means you can adjust the tasks to how you feel more comfortable . The percentage of new users is increasing . This is the reason why I think the site should be recommended . 
