Hi Jack , In my country , the birthdays are celebrated just like your birthday . Most of the people celebrate their birthday with family and friends , usually at home , and they have a cake with soft drinks and afterwards they all sing " Happy Birthday . " Also it 's common for people to celebrate their birthday in a restaurant or a pizzeria , where the people eat and drink through a process of buying called " all -you -can -eat . " 
Working in enclosed workstations or in offices with a more open design is a hotly -debated topic that often divides opinions . Companies have different ways to work , including the way of organizing their work areas . However , employees must be aware of giving a comfortable work area . Personally speaking , an arrangement without walls is the best way to offer a friendly atmosphere to your employees . People need to have constant contact with others , regarding work areas , to have the freedom to interact with their co -workers , avoid stress problems and it allows your staff to work in a team . Due to the company giving a good working atmosphere , the tasks will be done as well as possible , thus benefiting both sides , the company and the workers . To sum up , it does not matter if it is a big or small company , the best way to maintain to your employees in your company will be to give them good working conditions and an excellent working atmosphere . 
As to the school of the future in Japan , I think it will become more flexible . At present , basically we have to go to school physically and have to study in a classroom face -to -face . But after the COVID -19 pandemic in Japan , the Japanese government had to lock down the cities . And a lot of schools were closed for several months , so many children could not go to school . As the result of this , it was very hard for the children and teachers to catch up on the curriculum . Through this experience , the Japanese government decided to change the way of education . The government gave PC tablets to all students and started to use the tablets for the lessons . I think this is the first step for a new style of school . In the near future , we will be able to study online . It will be not necessary to go to school physically . To be honest , I think there are many problems to solve for online school . But it will be changed to be a better way . 
In our town you can find a shopping center with all the biggest shops in the country . For the accommodation you have a lot of cheap but good hostels . You also have a big park , a science museum and several big restaurants . 
Every person has the right to equally benefit from the health sector , or that is what is written in the law , because most people do not have access to doctors or medications . There are some countries that do not have hospitals , and even in the same country , some regions have large health institutions , while others lack doctors . These areas which lack doctors are mostly rural areas because most doctors want to live in urban areas and earn much money . We cannot say that they are wrong , maybe it is not very moral , especially for a doctor , but earning money is essential for life . It is up to the government to solve this problem , as some governments have their own way of solving the doctor shortage . One of them is to distribute newly graduated doctors around the country by lot , so that enough doctors are appointed to each region . Of course , this method is a method applied for practitioners , it is not common for specialist physicians to go to rural areas . To solve this , governments can impose a salary increase on rural doctors or send them in a specific order . Of course , the doctors to be sent in a certain order should be carefully selected , because it would not be right to send doctors who have a child or a family member that they take care of . 
Almost all people want to travel to a new city or country to visit a new place and see new things , but many people cannot travel for many reasons , such as they do not have enough money or the fear of traveling a long distance . However , with all the advanced technology that we have today , everything is possible . Today , we can travel from country to country in a few hours by plane or car . That is what we use to travel , but in the future , everything will be easier than we think . For instance , Artificial Intelligence is a new major in computer science and technology and that will change the way that we travel , to be faster than we think . Moreover , virtual realty makes everything possible , so we can visit any place around the world when we are sat at home . To conclusion , technology makes our lives easier than before , so we can try traveling to any place at any time we want . That is the future of travel . 
Nowadays , almost all children spend their free time playing video games . This kind of entertainment may have positive and negative effects , but it depends on the environment in which the child develops . In my opinion , video games do not have a negative impact on children . On the market , you 're able to get any kind of video game , such as didactic and battle . The positive and negative effects will depend on the atmosphere where the children grow up , then bad behaviour could be slightly affected by the games . In addition to this , there is not any research which shows that video games have negative effects ( psychologically speaking ) , however , there is some research which shows the positive effects on children and some video games have been created to develop their skills . To sum up , video games can have positive effects on children , but everything depends on the development atmosphere and how children are exposed to a certain kind of video game . 
Have you ever asked yourselves about your reasons for learning English ? Indeed , I have and I would like to tell you why it is paramount to learn English , in my opinion . As a matter of fact , English is spoken all over the world . Wherever you go , everyone talks in English . Consequently , by speaking English , I am able to travel worldwide . Besides , English is a fantastic language and not so challenging to learn . With method and motivation , it is entertaining to discover another culture . Furthermore , in my future career , I will have to speak and understand English . Scientific jobs are the quintessence to explain that idea . For instance , all research reports will be in English , because the USA and the UK are significant in research and development . Also , journalism is an illustration of a job for which you need to master English . To put it in a nutshell , not only do I discover a different culture from mine , but I can also meet new people living abroad . What about you ? Tell us about your reasons for learning English ! 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? I disagree . First , I want to mention books ' advantages . Though screen technologies are improving steadily , books are still healthier than tablets and computers . And although books can burn easily , digital books can be lost and corrupted more easily . For instance , a power cut can delete all the data . On the other hand , digital books can be stored more simply and besides , do not require that much care . Also , they can connect to big data . Why should we wait for the latest version when books can receive immediate updates ? Thus , I claim we should maintain both kinds of books . What if there is a fire in the library ? No problem , we have all the same data in our digital books anyways . What if some digital books are deleted suddenly ? Okay , we just have to scan the hard copy versions of those books . What do you think ? 
There are many things that affect our health . If we look from a narrow perspective , only exercise seems important . In addition to exercise , you should eat healthy foods and take care of yourself . In general , TV programs are destroying the facts about health and healthy foods . Therefore , people are believe in some wronges . If a person is fatter than normal or he has some health problems , he should go to a professional dietitian and consist a diet program . Of course you do not have to go , but if dietitians are out of work , global warming can destroy the world . Dietitians cannot survive an hour without driving a Porsche , but you should give them 200 dollars and do not look at You Tube . You do not need to pay that much money to live healthily , however , spending money on your diet and exercise more than alcohol and smoking will be better for you . Finally , please understand the important level of eating healthily and protecting yourself everywhere . 
Keeping animals in zoos or letting them be free is often discussed , yet rarely understood . All animals should live in their habitats , that 's the law of nature . However , what would happen if zoo animals were freed ? Personally speaking , all animals deserve to live freely in their habitats . They must develop their nature far from man -made environments and humans should learn to admire them without hunting them and destroying their ecosystems . On the other hand , what happens with zoo animals ? It is known that many people fight to free animals from these kinds of places , but there are some aspects to consider before doing it , for instance , the fact that possibly the animals which have grown up in zoos would not be able to survive on their own , because they 're used to being fed by humans . To sum up , if we want to admire animals in their habitats freely , humans must learn to look after the ecosystems and the lives in them . Also , we have to provide better conditions for zoo animals and try to make their lives as close to wildlife as possible . 
