I believe that it is better for students to have new teachers each year . I have three reasons for that . First , if the teacher is bad for a student , the student needs to endure them for several years . It is not good situation for an important period of the student 's growth . Second , if the teacher is only one person , it is difficult for the students to judge if the teacher is good or not , because they do not have a person who they can compare them with . As a result of that , if the teacher has unfair thinking , students might be affected badly by the teacher . Finally , one teacher has a limit of view and thinking . A teacher might notice a student 's good point , but the other teacher might not notice the student 's good point . I believe that each student has several different good points . If the student can extend his/her talent from childhood , it is lucky for him/her . 
