Nowadays , it is undeniable that foreign studies have helped a lot of people to speak fluently and have more confidence in languages . At the moment , it is a success for young students . However , this opportunity does not come to everybody . Firstly , getting money is quite tough and it is a crucial part of studying abroad , although you can get a scholarship , which is given to students who do not have the resources to pay for the trip . Anyway , there are few scholarships in our days . Secondly , an important advantage of studying abroad is that you will be forced to listen to native people . Moreover , you will acquire those strange habits and celebrations in that foreign country . Finally , you will meet new people who come from different parts of the world and it is a superb opportunity to develop social capacities , especially if you are shy most of the time . Trust me , you will be so proud of yourself if you get foreign friendships . As a conclusion , I think it will a great experience if you have the opportunity to study abroad , so do not miss it . 
Nowadays , many people , mostly young people , look to study abroad in order to improve their skills . However , studying abroad is not always an easy process . Firstly , there are many options to be able to study abroad . Almost all Universities offer the opportunity to do a school exchange . In this kind of exchange , the students have the opportunity to go abroad without the need to pay and mostly , the foreign Universities are in charge of the tuition fees , food and hospitality . On the other hand , there are some negative factors to take into consideration about studying abroad . Even though the majority of the cost can be covered by the Universities , sometimes students have to cover the cost of the journey and this cost may be expensive . The language is important as well . Students must have a high level of English to be able to communicate with foreign people and another factor is loneliness , something you have to deal with . In conclusion , currently , as a student , the opportunities to study abroad are many . Comparing the advantages with the disadvantages , the students only have to develop some skills before taking the decision to travel and work hard to have a chance . It is expected that in the future , school exchanges will be an easier process than today . 
