I understand that some people believe zoos are good places for people to learn about animals . However , I also believe that zoos are not good for animals . I would like to consider that I replace animals for humans , based on some examples . First , animals in zoos are separated from their parents and children . I cannot put up with that . It is very crucial . Second , animals in zoos finish their lives only in a cage or very limited field . The same as the first example , it is very crucial too . Third , animals in zoos are seen by a lot of people . It is not relaxing . Fourth , there are no options for everything . Animals in zoos cannot choose their food , friends or lovers freely . The situation is not fun for me . I believe that no one has rights to control anyone 's life , including any animal . So I do not agree with the existence of zoos . 
I know that some companies let their employees work in enclosed workstations or cubicles . However , I do not like that way . Moreover , I believe that it is more efficient not to separate employees from each other with walls . If there are walls , it is not easy to talk to co -workers when they need . People feel there is a wall in their mind , the same as the physical situation . If there is no wall and all spaces are free , employees are able to sit down where they like every day . Under expansion of COVID -19 , a lot of companies are applying a remote working style . As a result , many employees do not often get to use their desk in their office . Then the need for individual desks got lower than before . So we do not have the need to make walls to separate each employee . I understand that the situation and efficiency depends on the industry . However , if the company is able to have options , I recommend to put no walls in workplaces . 
Nowadays , schools offer many extracurricular activities to their pupils , which include music tuition . On the other hand , some schools do not offer music in their syllabus . In my opinion , music and arts are crucial in all education systems , and consequently , they should be thought to everybody . Learning music is one of the activities which develops mental skills , especially when tuition initiates in early childhood . There is a lot of social research that supports the positive connection between brain development in children and the ability to play a musical instrument . Some schools , for instance , have introduced music classes in their schedule , however , and unfortunately , only private education institutions can provide these classes because of the high cost of musical instruments that parents might not be able to afford . Another point to take into account is that being considered a music master implies many hours of full -time and dedicated study , and this , obviously , is something that public schools are not able to provide , and probably students either . I consider that music tuition is a must in education , and as societies , we should find ways to benefit our children with something that is part of our history and culture . 
I think that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . If you are rich but are sick in the hospital for a long time , you ca not enjoy your life enough . Even if you are rich , you ca not buy health . When I was young , I thought it was the most important to be rich . But as my lifestyle has changed , I got married and had children , my opinion has changed . To be healthy is the most important factor in my life . I think that if you want to be rich , it is necessary not only to work very hard , but also to have good luck . That is , without one effect , I think good luck is also needed to be rich . But I think that to be healthy it is necessary to take care of your lifestyle yourself . That is , I think to being healthy depends on you . 
