Someone might hope for a shorter life but much more intense . I understand where they are coming from . However , I would like to live a long , calm life . There are three reasons . First , I would like to use a lot of new technologies . As you know , technologies are being developing and innovated every day . I am not able to imagine new technologies in the future . So I am looking forward to using new technologies and living a new lifestyle . They are like dream lands . Second , if my life is long , I will be able to experience a lot of kinds of things . There are a lot of things which I want to do . If my life is short , I will be able to choose just a few things . However , if my life is long , I will not have a limitation . I am able to go where I want to go . I am able to eat whatever I want . I am able to read a lot of the books which I want . Third , the reason why is that I feel happiness when I am calm . I like to drink black tea on sunny days with my lover . I like to lay down on the grass in a park . I like chatting with my lovers and friends calmly . Any way , I have naturally lived like that already . 
Given a choice between a long , calm and short life , and an intense one , I would definitely opt for the former for these following reasons . NA , . there are certain potential drawbacks to leading a fast -paced lifestyle . That is to say , it is highly likely that you would make mistakes and due to a lack of time , you tend to overlook those negative experiences , hence no lessons are learned and no adjustment is made for the better in the future . Also , when people live at a hustling and bustling pace , they tend to overly speed things up . As a result , more accidents and errors would occur . One case on point is the account of surpassing a safe driving speed on the highway , which leads to thousands of road accidents everywhere in the world . , . adopting a lifestyle which is calm and tender could bring about several benefits . Firstly , people would have the time to reflect on their experiences , hence improving the future outcome when the same scenario happens . Secondly , this pace of living would allow people to avoid the probability of being stressed as well as a better chance to relax and recharge their energy . Finally , not every aspect of life could be felt or achieved in merely a single moment . It does take nine months for a pregnant mother until her due day or it takes maybe a lifetime to understand someone . In conclusion , though living intensely with a timetable full of activities sounds exciting , I would choose to lead a calmer lifestyle because of several values it offers . 
