These days , life has become important , some people believe that it depends on their health . While others believe that it is not necessary because they think it 's from magination . This essay will discuss both sides and will draw my personal conclusion . On the one hand , most people prefer a long life , regardless of them suffering and having a hard life . For example , we always went through difficult situations and had hard circumstances , but we are still sticking onto life , because it has family , relatives and beautiful landscapes . On the other hand , all the stories about living a long life are crucial but as people have tended to live longer lives , death has become scary . Studies have proven that when the human lifespan increases , people hope for death over life , especially when their health , body and teeth worsen . So I prefer a short life because it 's the best option and truth of life , and I believe that , after my death , my soul has another life in heaven . Eventually , I love my life but when I see other people suffering from poverty , wars and violence , I am thankful to God and hope to improve the standard life . In conclusion , after a careful analysis of both points of view , I believe that a short life is brilliant , which I consider is a challenge in order to fulfill all my dreams . 
