For a long time , in almost all schools , the students have been required to do some volunteer work . This kind of jobs allow students to obtain some experience , but there are not many places which want to give opportunities to young people or they do not offer a healthy atmosphere for them . Firstly , voluntary work has always been a requirement to graduate from any high school or university . As a student , this kind of job allows to get experience , teenagers are able to apply the knowledge that they have obtained from school and they have a better idea about how life works . However , for students , selecting a volunteer job is not always easy . The range of options for this kind of job is sometimes limited , the timetables are not comfortable , as a volunteer , the student does not receive a salary and some companies exploit the students . To sum up , voluntary work will always be an excellent option for students to get experience , but as something necessary to be able to graduate , the schools should research for good options of volunteer jobs to offer to their students . 
