Following the recent and dramatic development of the Internet , schools have to update their way of teaching . The question at hand is should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? On the one hand , substituting books with tablets could be very useful for students . As a matter of fact , books are generally numerous and heavy . It is consequentially harmful for students ' backs . Moreover , tablets could make the learning more entertaining . There is usually a lot of animation and it is quite fun for the students to discover it . On the other hand , tablets are not flawless . Indeed , they present a major impact on the student 's vision . It is not healthy to be behind a screen all day long . Another point to consider is whether tablets are really reliable . Sometimes , the tablets may cut out or the Internet could stop working . Besides , using tablets significantly increases the risks of cyber -bullying . Of course , a contrary opinion might be that students are grown up enough to behave like adults . To put it in a nutshell , even though tablets are handy , they can be hazardous if they are used on a daily basis . 
Many new electronic products are invented these days . It is not special to see people , even children , using computers at home and tablets in public places anymore . Since these electronic devices are commonly used and network technology is quite steady , schools have started thinking about letting students use computers and tablets for learning instead of paper and textbooks . In my opinion , e -learning should be totally adopted on the school campus . First of all , replacing books with tablets is environmentally friendly . Books are made from paper and some contain plastic , and people have to cut down trees to make paper . Then there is less fresh air produced , the soil would also loosen without the consolidation of tree roots . Throwing away books that contain plastic will pollute the environment , as it is not easily digested in nature . Compared to paper , which negatively affects the environment , electric devices cause less damage to nature , as we would not throw devices away frequently . One must not forget that tablets and computers are easier and more effective for learning than books . Tablets and computers can store as many documents as you need to study . All we need to do is find the location of the document and open it . We can also use them to watch educational videos to have fun while learning . On the contrary , it is difficult for us to find a worksheet in a pile of paper . Added to that , there are no videos in textbooks , only printed pictures for us to take a look at . It is less interesting and effective than using an electric device . In conclusion , I think that schools should take advantage of modern technology in education . It is a fantastic tool to learn and acquire knowledge , as it can broadcast videos and have huge storage . It also saves the planet at the same time , by reducing deforestation and air pollution . Therefore I agree that computers and tablets should completely replace books in school and university . 
INTRODUCTION The aim of this report is to explain what I want to achieve this new school year and to sort out what I will do to accomplish my goals in the future . AREAS OF MY LEARNING THAT I AM PLEASED WITH Firstly , I want to remark on areas that I am happy with , such as literature , as while I am studying it , I find it so rewarding . Also , art is an outstanding area , as I totally fall in love with it when I am in class and also seeing that when I go to a museum , I can understand pictures perfectly well . AREAS OF MY LEARNING THAT I WANT TO IMPROVE Secondly , it is really important to say the areas that I want to improve , seeing that not all things are flawless . Areas such as Maths and Physics are so awful for me , as I do not understand anything and I feel so frustrated when I study them . However , I want to improve them , as I really believe that I could understand them . THINGS THAT I WILL DO TO ACHIEVE MY GOALS It would be beneficial for me to watch tutorials , as I might understand maths and physics better than now . Besides that , I will work very hard to accomplish them . 
My favourite season of the year is summer , because I like it when it 's warm outside . It 's the time when everybody is going on holiday . I can visit my parents , my friends and fly somewhere abroad . It 's my dream to fly to an exotic island , somewhere where it is nice , just sea and blue sky . Last summer I was sick and it was a first year of the pandemic , so I did not have a real holiday . I only spent a couple of days with my boyfriend , not far from home . This year I 'm not sure I can afford a trip , maybe into the mountains . I love climbing in summer , autumn is good too , in spring it is too cold for this kind of activity . I 'd like to change my job , so I probably wo not be able to go anywhere for a long time . I remember the time we were visiting Greg in Barcelona . It was a little cold , about twenty four degrees when we were on the beach , because a cold wind was blowing . Soon we 're planning a trip to the USA . I ca not wait for that . Oh , summer holidays ! 
