My experience of studying on the platform Write and Improve has been great and really useful . What I liked about Write and Improve is the possibility of writing several texts about many subjects , from housework to subjects about work . Another thing I liked was the correction process , in which the Artifical Intelligence had good accuracy and informed me about grammatical errors that I had and how I can correct them . I also liked the fact that Write and Improve had four levels in its workbooks , where these four levels are beginner , intermediate , advanced and business . However , Write and Improve had defects that I did not like . An example is the fail on examine if the text I wrote matched with what the platform asked . Many times I wrote the text correctly that the platform asked , but the system said that I wrote it incorrectly . After using Write and Improve , I can recommend the platform without a problem to my classmates . You will enjoy it a lot . 
' Write and Improve ' is an online writing tool for English language learners of all levels of English including beginner , intermediate and advanced . ' Write and Improve ' gives you topics to write about , and once you finish writing about the topic , you will get instant marking based on CEFR scale ; which stands for Common European Framework of Reference . In addition , ' Write and Improve ' gives you instant feedback on your writing and offers you suggestions on how to correct your mistakes and improve your writing - and that 's what I most like about ' Write and Improve ' . For people who are proficient in the English language , but want to improve their skills in business English , ' Write and Improve ' has a special workbook for business English that gives you writing tasks related to English used in business environments . ' Write and Improve ' is a very user -friendly tool and everything is arranged in categories based on your needs ; for example , if you are beginner , there is a special workbook for beginners which you can use to practise your English . Furthermore , for learners who would like to practise international tests , such as IELTS and Cambridge English tests , ' Write and Improve ' has a feature called ( test zone ) , which contains IELTS academic , IELTS general training and B2 First , which are offered on subscription . The most important feature in ' Write and Improve ' that I appreciate very much is the instant feedback that I get on my writing which has helped me to improve my grammar skills as well as punctuation . Finally , ' Write and Improve ' is an amazing tool to improve your English writing skills . 
