Television entertains , but can it also educate ? Many people love to watch TV , so do I . Sometimes people watch TV for 2 reasons . The first is to entertain , the second is to get knowledge . We entertain ourselves when we are tired , stressed or bored . We put on a show and enjoy it . We also study with it . Many people think that reading everything in books is boring and they prefer to watch some TV about their studies . Both are acceptable . But which is which ? It depends . It depends on the shows and people . Entertainment shows will only entertain , but some educational shows will indeed be a great help . Shows like BBC animal and scientific shows are all useful . It also depends on the people who are watching them . If a person that likes to think watches an entertaining movie , he will also think about the movement and the actions in the show . But if a person prefers not to think and just watch whatever is in the show , give him an outer space discovery programme to watch and he will know nothing after that . 
