Fifty years ago , it was too difficult to imagine a net of daily flights from different European countries to New York or Singapore . Today , this is normal information that an average boy aged ten years can give you . And tomorrow ? In my view , the process is running very fast for future improvements , so to make it easier , each long journey will be by plane instead of by car , train or boat . It will only be a question of business , then we will have a more comfortable way to travel quickly and safely , avoiding traffic jams and other problems related to road accidents . About my romantic view , it is a progress that could remove part of the excitement which you have before a journey . Today , organization is an important part of the same vacation . In the future , I am afraid of how quickly it will be possible to jump this step in a few minutes . 
