I think it is better to have a balance between the years that the teacher has to educate students , where it is neither ideal to have many years with students or have only one year with them . I believe that the teachers need to have the necessary time to build a firm relationship with students . This relationship with students helps the teacher understand the behavior and profile of the students , for the teacher could develop a program of education that can improve the understanding and absorption of content passed on to the students . On the other hand , it 's important for students have a diversification of teachers teaching throughout the years . It 's necessary because the students end up getting used to the teacher that they were already used to and this can disturb their learning . Therefore , to identify a happy medium for this situation is the way to improve the learning of students and their relationship with the teachers . 
The answer is we should not . We must not replace books with new technologies . Here 's why : Books are knowledge gathered by our ancestors and they are much more valuable than gold . Nothing can replace them . Here are some points about why books are treasures that human beings cannot erase . Let 's talk about the benefits of reading a book . First , it lets you think about the scenery or the scene that the author is writing about . It is way more helpful than reading something with pictures and telling you about the settings straight away on a digital device . Secondly , it benefits your body . We all know that books are made out of wood or stone . Digital devices are not the same . They will harm your eyes and brain , making you somehow unable to think probably . It 's fun watching a show on the TV , but it 's difficult reading on a screen . It will somehow distract your concentration . It will also be tedious , as your eyes will get tired and you will be bored . However , books are not the same . Whenever you read a book , even if it is the same book , you will still find happiness and something new that you have not noticed before . 
Someone might argue that it is better for university students to live on their own while they are attending school . I agree with a part of their air gunner . That is because they are able to build their independence and make free time . However , I think that it is better for university students to live with their parents while they are attending university students to live with their parents while they are attending the university on the other views . Firstly , finance . Generally speaking , university students do not make a lot of money by themselves . That 's why they need to depend on their parents in many cases . So , if they live on their own , their parents need to bear the burden more , in addition to their tuition . It is not reasonable for their parents . Secondly , time . If they live on their own , they need to do housework by themselves . They need to study a lot as university students . However , they who live on their own have to spend their time a lot on other things like housekeeping . It is not reasonable . In conclusion , I believe that it is better for university students to live with their parents . 
