Visiting a zoo is one of the easiest ways to learn about animals , even if some people believe that animals belong in nature and it is wrong to keep them in zoos . In the beginning , I would like to mention that zoos are not keeping dying -out animals . In general , we cannot see low -population animal species in zoos . Secondly , zoos are really helpful for increasing the level of knowledge of our children . I think you all know what a lemur is , however , most villagers do not know those kinds of animals . They do not know , since there are no zoos in most of the villages . If we look at their beliefs about animals ' living standards , every zoo has some rules about animals ' living standards . They are living in special and perfect habitats in zoos . In addition to this , the zoo staff are also very lovely people . Lastly , I would like to say that I cannot see any problems with zoos . 
In some schools , music is a required subject and all the students have to study it . However , some schools allow school children to study or not study it . I think that music should be studied by all the students . In my opinion , music should be examined in all the schools and by all the students because it is a beautiful subject which has a lot of benefits for us . Indeed , for some people , music is a way to relax and release the stress that is accumulated during the day . It is a fantastic activity that you can do in your free time , especially when you are bored . In other words , learning an instrument is a great activity to do as it has good efforts on us . Studying music is also a good method and opportunity to establish new friendships as it allows you to know more people . For instance , if you want to know more people or you are searching for friends , you can join a band or orchestra , and this can be helpful even to improve your musical skills . Music can become also a passion for you . Indeed , you can develop an interest in the instrument that you are learning and it can help you to try something new and find something enjoyable . To summarise , music is a subject that should be studied in all the schools because it has a great number of good efforts on our minds . 
