As to my favourite season of the year , I would like to introduce it to you . It is spring . As you know , we have four seasons in Japan . Generally speaking , spring is during March to May , summer is during June to August , autumn is September to November , winter is December to February in Japan . I think that each season has its good points . It is cold in winter and sometimes it snows in Tokyo . Compared to the northern area in Japan , such as Hokkaido , it is much better in Tokyo , but I do not want to go out in winter because it is cold . As it is getting warmer and warmer in March , I am looking forward to seeing the cherry blossom , Sakura . In spring , from the end of March to the first half of April , we can see the cherry blossoms are in bloom in Tokyo . I think that the landscape in full bloom is so beautiful in Japan . So I like the spring , my favourite season is spring . 
From my point of view , it is helpful for me to use Write and Improve for my English skills . As for the Write and Improve service , I recommend you access the website as soon as possible . On the website , you can find that there are courses according to your learning levels , such as beginner , intermediate , advanced , business . You can choose such courses as you would like to learn . A lot of exercises are prepared in each course online . At present , I use Write and Improve every day . Now , I have chosen the intermediate course and am trying to improve my English writing skills . I think that one of the good points of Write and Improve is its good responsiveness . If you compose your English writing in the course and push the check button , you can find where it is not right . After amending where it is not right , you can submit it again . This way , you can learn English writing skills through Write and Improve . Furthermore , Write and Imporve are online lessons so that you can exercise whenever you are available . It is for free to exercise your English writing and speaking online . If you want to improve your English skills , I recommend you try it . 
Which is more important , being healthy or being rich ? That is the question that lots of people try to answer . Some people think to be healthy it is necessary to be rich , but it is not always true . Except when a person has the same condition , being healthy is not linked to being rich . People have had a long , healthy life , even living in underdeveloped countries . So , what has been happening in these countries ? People can buy natural food , or not industrialized food , and it helps their diet considerably . Recent research shows us natural food is healthier and cheaper than processed food . Another important thing is eating less meat and more vegetables . People that do that have a long life . However , it is important to say people need to save enough money for later days . Everybody knows elderly people require specific care and it is expensive . In summary , saving money , eating healthy food , less meat and more vegetables , and saving money , should turn you into a health -rich person in the future . 
Learning a foreign language is not only a requirement , but also it is a competitive advantage in the interconnected world where we live . Furthermore , it is well -known that English is the most useful and recognized language around the world . Bearing this in mind , many people are looking for methods and tools which help them to learn English quickly and efficiently . Speaking personally , one of the best and useful tools for learners of English is Write and Improve , a free application developed by Cambridge in which every learner can practice her or his writing in order to improve her grammar and fluency . Moreover , this application gives you a topic and some questions or points to develop in the text , after one writes the text , there 's a check button and automatically the writing is evaluated . After that , the feedback appears , which comes up with some symbols so as to correct some mistakes or to improve some parts . Additionally , this platform is mainly about writing essays , emails , letters and proposals . Also there are different levels from beginner up to advanced and business level , which you can tailor according to your level to get started step by step and go up and up . In addition to that , the main feature of this platform is the huge variety , which is a boon for every learner so to prepare for any English certification . Another feature is that it gives you all the necessary feedback and a prospective level in which you are , this latter could be B1 or C1 or C2 . However , what I most like about this app is the amiable design to use , the guides to write and the variety of topics . After all , these characteristics are essential for a learner who wants to boost her writing skills . Despite all its benefits , there are some difficulties at the beginning , one can struggle to find ways to be a C1 or C2 . Also a learner can stress herself out when she 's run out of ideas to develop within the text ; but nobody says it was easy to learn and get better in a target language . So , it would appear this platform has its benefits and some challenges , nonetheless I highly recommend this platform to all learners who are seeking a tool to write faster and better . 
My favorite season of the year is autumn . I have four reasons to support the idea . First of all , we can get good foods in the season . We can get a lot of crops , like rice , fruit , fish and vegetables . We are able to cook delicious dishes with these foods . Healthy dishes help us keep a better physical condition . Secondly , the climate is special for exercising . Fall is not too hot or too cold to move our body . If you do some sports , autumn is more suitable than any other seasons . I also like to play tennis and I can play well in the season . The probability of getting an injury is the lowest in a year . Thirdly , we can study very well in autumn . The climate also gives us the best conditions to read books or learn something . It is easy for us to concentrate to start learning . The quality and efficiency of learning might be improved in the season . The final point is that I have a birthday in November , so I usually get birthday presents from my parents . I have emotional memories in this season . I was given board games as birthday presents and my parents and I played the games together . We enjoyed the games and it helped us to keep good communication and a valuable relationship . In conclusion , autumn is the best season to start new challenges because of the climate . Thus , I love this season . 
My favourite movie is Alice in the Wonderland . I really love this film because it explores nonsense situations . Have you ever thought about talking objects ? That film has many situations like that , and sometimes I think it could happen . I would love to explore that crazy world with a white rabbit that was always late . I believe you really should watch it . Once you said to me you like to watch crazy movies , right ? So , as I described to you , this movie fits your description of a film you would like to watch . I recommend this movie to you . After you watch it , let me know what you make of it . 
I think that we have the same problem in Japan . Most medical doctors want to work in cities to earn more money . As the result of this trend , there are not enough doctors in many rural areas . I think that there are some reasons for this problem . One is that there is a regulation that doctors are not allowed to see a patient on the internet in Japan . In Japan , we have to see a doctor face to face , doctors ca not see a patient on the internet because of the regulation . If the regulation is changed , doctors can see a patient on the internet . I think the problem will be solved to some extent . Wherever we live , we can choose a doctor and see the doctor on the internet as a first step . If the regulation is changed , it will be easier for doctors to live in cities . Second is that it is very expensive to be a doctor in Japan . In Japan , if you want to be a doctor , you have to study in a medical university for 6 years and have to obtain the certification by the government . Except public medical university , private medical university is expensive , I think that it is necessary to pay about 5 to 10 thousand dollars per year . I think it is difficult for ordinary people to pay such a high cost . So I think that if there are more scholarship funds , enough to increase the number of new doctors , the problem will be solved to some extent . 
Yes , it is . I think that English is as important as other languages . English is the best all around the world . I like learning English very much . When I was a small boy , I learnt English at school . We learned English with a great teacher Joseph . He prepared a lot of fun things for better learning . Yes , he was a great teacher and I had the same 1 grades . Then it was horrible . At the second school we had a lot of English teachers . They changed during the year . They taught too little of anything to us . During the following years I saw a big difference . I am glad that I am learning English by myself . , every day again and again . I would like to have a B2 First Certficiate . I will pass the exam . I will have passed by next month . I will speak with the British Council . We will see . I was learning English . I am learning English . I am going to learn English . English is my life now . I want to be better every day . Thank you for your attention . Tom . 
Do you believe that school is dull and should be reformed ? Well , education has long been a bone of contention . That 's why I would like to present you with several aspects of school that , in my opinion , will evolve in the future . Let 's travel one century forward ! First and foremost , the first point I would like to raise is that schools will adapt the courses for each student . As a matter of fact , it is nowadays challenging to know exactly at high -school which occupation we want to do . That 's why students will have the opportunity to follow multidisciplinary lessons , which will include sciences , arts , music , technology , languages and literature . Afterwards , in year 12 , they will have to choose several subjects they would like to refine in order to prepare for their studies in college . Another thing to consider is whether the students keep being evaluated with marks . Actually , it is universally acknowledged that is stressful to receive marks for a worksheet . Consequently , a lot of teachers have been thinking about another type of evaluation , with colors . Red if the skill is not mastered , orange if the skill is currently being learned and green if the student has perfectly understood the expectations . One cannot disregard that marks are not always representative of the student 's level . The main goal of these reforms is that students arrive at school in high spirits , willing to learn . To put it in a nutshell , not only will school adapt its courses , but it will also support the students better in their career . What about you ? Tell us about your vision of schools in the years to come . 
High school requirements are strict in many aspects . One of them is the volunteer programme , this kind of requirement could be a remarkable opportunity to learn and gain experience from a different type of work . Nevertheless , this activity can be tedious for students because they have to deal with school stuff and the responsibility of doing this volunteer programme , sometimes they do not have enough time to develop their activities properly because they have extracurricular activities , such as sports clubs or any other kind of activity . Anyhow , I think a volunteer programme is necessary for students to have the experience of working in the community . They have the opportunity to know different environments , to know different life situations in life . Students can also discover what they want to do in their life and what they want to study at university . For those reasons , I think volunteer work to graduate is a tedious but necessary thing to do to graduate because there are many benefits from it . 
My reasons for learning English We live in a globalized world , where all things and people are connected to each other . Communication can be hard if you know only your mother tongue . So , knowing a global language , such as English , is extremely important to be heard and to be understood . Because of that , I decided to learn a new language and I chose English . All people that are playing a role on a global scale use English to communicate with each other . When I noticed it , immediately I started to study English and it become a daily challenge . Studying and learning English is important to me , because I want to live overseas one day . I am aware if I do not master English , I will be in trouble when I face any situation where this language is required . So , in short , people in the globalized world need English and whether I know English or not , the global position will still exist . So I chose to learn it . 
I think that video games are positive for children . Playing video games improves the logical reasoning of children and develops further their creativity and imagination . Logically , children must have the monitoring of their parents about the time that they spend on playing video games . When children spend a lot of time playing video games , what is positive and an advantage may end up turning negative , because the children will have difficulty in school and in their social life . For example , my parents always delineated some rules that I needed follow , like just playing video games if I had finished my homework . This worked and I got good grades in school and yet I had time to play video games . Another observation that parents need to have is observing the games that their children are playing . They have to avoid that the children are playing violent and sexual games . With the follow -up of parents , children can develop , through video games , many positive attributes in their growth . 
There are some advantages of studying abroad . Firstly , the students are able to learn the language of the other countries . The option of jobs will expand because of the conversation skills . Secondly , they are able to learn diversity . It is important to experience it under globalization . Thirdly , they are able to make foreign friends . Those are great treasures in their lives . On the other hand , there are also some disadvantages of studying abroad . Firstly , it might be difficult for someone to fit in the other cultures . Secondly , they might feel stressed . Many of them are not able to talk with people smoothly because of the different languages . Thirdly , they need to go away from their local friends and families . They are not able to spend time with their friends and families instead of being in other countries . That is all I would like to explain about the advantages and disadvantages regarding studying abroad . 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? The recent technological changes in society have brought up an interesting discussion regarding the complete disregard of books in schools . In my opinion , we should get rid of all the books in schools and universities with regard to learning and I will explain why . Books are magic . They tell stories and enable us to practise empathy . However , the main goal of books in education is not the magic , but the knowledge they contain . On top of that , there are some incredible benefits to using technology in schools . Digital learning aids are able to correct the students ' work , saving the teachers a lot of time . Some technologies are even able to send students to an exercise that best fits they current level of learning , enabling personalized learning . Therefore , I believe that books should always be in schools , but not as a means of learning . 
I think that it is effective for me to work in offices in which there are no walls separating employees from other co -workers . In Japan , most Japanese companies have this kind of office , in which there are no walls separating employees from other co -workers . Me , I already got used to work in no separating offices . Because I have to cooperate with my co -workers to do business , it is convenient for me to work in non separated offices . I think that one of the merits of non separated offices is to be able to communicate with each other whenever you want . On the other hand , if a person works by oneself , I think it is effective to work in enclosed workstations . I think that a person who basically works by themself , such as researcher , investment analyst , consultant , gets used to working by themself . If they work in offices where there are no walls separating each other , I think it is not effective for them because they ca not concentrate on their work . 
Recently , I 've discovered a very useful tool for those who are keen on improving their written English . This tool is called Write and Improve . It allows you to write about hundreds of topics , which you can choose freely . Everyone will find something for them ! As I said , by using this tool , you are able to improve your English skills . You just simply write about a certain topic and when you feel you have finished , you send the answer . After some time , you get your feedback from Cambridge ! Then you can either make some changes to improve your work or move on to another topic . For sure , the best part about this tool is that you can get some feedback and continue to improve . It 's , for sure , easier to do so than when you are getting marked by other people . In a short period of time , you can write multiple works . It does not matter if you are currently traveling by train or bus . Write and Improve allows you to write from every device that you own ( it has to be connected to the internet ) ! When it comes to the downsides , it may take a long time before your work gets some feedback . It also has a limited amount of topics , so it may be a problem in the future . Just imagine a situation when after some time you have finished all of the available works and there is nothing left . At least , after finishing all of the works , I believe you will be able to express your opinion about any topic easily . 
In general , people always think that a healthy life is more important than being rich . However , in your close circle , you cannot take an answer like being rich is more important . There is a classic example about the importance of taking care of your health , " no one can buy a healthy body with their money . " Firstly , I can say that your health is more important than being rich . Therefore , we should be aware of the importance of our health . If you have a healthy body , you can live without any pain in your daily life . Besides that , being healthy is also important for a longer life . In addition to this , being healthy is not free and sometimes this can be very expensive . Therefore , sometimes we need to pay a lot of money for our health and being rich is important in that part . If you are rich , you can live an easy life , however , you cannot choose the diseases and the pain level of your health problem . Finally , I can say that being healthy is the most important thing in our life , since we are living in our bodies and we should be careful with them . 
Studying in another country has many advantages for students . The students can learn things that are trending in the world . For example , if a Brazilian student goes to the United States , this student will learn many things that are not yet commented on in their country . Furthermore , studying in another country has the advantage of learning another language , this being very valuable for the professional career of the student . Another advantage is the opportunity for the student to increase their networking , due to the fact this student can meet with people from different countries and professions . However , studying in another country has disadvantages . One of these disadvantages is the fact that the student needs to leave their family , in fact this can destabilize the student emotionally . Another disadvantage is the money necessary to travel and live in another country . Living in another country is expensive , even if the school or university offer a scholarship to the student . In general , the opportunity of studying in another country is unique and must be taken by the student . 
I think that it is an important opportunity for students to do volunteer work . I think that students can have very valuable experiences through volunteer work . In general , I think that one of the meanings of volunteer work is to be able to contribute to the society to which you belong . For example , volunteer work such as a clean up activity in my town . If I participate in this volunteer work , I can contribute to keep my town clean to some extent . I think that one of the meanings of volunteer work is to be able to help others . For example , volunteer work such as supporting handicapped people . If I participate in this volunteer work , I can help handicapped people 's activities . I think that through this kind of volunteer work , I can find various things which I will not find ever . And I think these kinds of experiences are valuable for students for their life after graduation . I also think that it is difficult for students to do volunteer work by themselves . So , I think a condition of some volunteer work being necessary to graduate is reasonable for me . 
Nowadays , a minority of medical doctors want to work in cities , which is not the perfect scenario for rural areas . Let 's have a quick look why it is happening and how it can be solved . The most crucial reason for this is very simple . In cities , especially big cities , they are able to make more money than in rural areas . Everyone wants to be paid well . Another thing which also matters is housing . It 's a lot easier to rent an apartment or a house in a city . Also they can get to their office faster , and as we all know , time matters . Who would want to spend 2 hours of their day just to get to work ? There are a few things which can be done to solve or minimize this important problem . Firstly , we need to reduce the time which is required to get to a doctor . We can achieve it by upgrading our roads and making more roads for bicycles . This solution will help reduce the time spent at the doctor , as well as increase the number of patients , which will boost their earnings . It should also create new opportunities for investors , which will build new housing for doctors and other people . Secondly , we need to show people that they do not have to wait few weeks just to get to a doctor . By choosing a doctor from rural area , they can heavily reduce the time which they have to wait . It 's good for both patients and doctors . Everyone benefits from it . I think that my solutions are not enough to fix the problem mentioned above , but they should easily reduce it . 
Last week I went a music concert here in my city . This concert was awesome . I decided to go because I love this band . They are very talented musicians . And I had been wanting to go to their concert for a very long time . So , I had the opportunity to go . The show was performed by the complete band , all the members were there . They played their musical instruments very well . The leader of the band sang many singles . On some of these singles , he sang together with other famous musicians . I had never seen anything like that . It blew my mind . 
Some high schools have a requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate . In my opinion , it is helpful even for students , the same as for society . We live in times where people need support , and help in any possible way . Our students will graduate and be future professionals and , by realizing volunteer work , they may become better people , and our society needs professionals who , besides their knowledge , has love for humanity . In my personal experience , I did a lot of volunteer work during my time as a students . I went to Africa and saw the people 's needs and , in my simple way , but with all my good feelings , I worked there . We really need to create a better world , and starting with students doing volunteer work may be only the beginning of something bigger , maybe our society can improve and I hope that my generation can be part of it . 
Education is fundamental for humanity and so are schools , which have a significant presence in our lives in a professional way and they even influence our personal growth . As a result , as we advance , schools need to change and improve in order to provide many more benefits to students and society . Apart from that , it is mainly known that the pandemic caused by the Coronavirus brought many changes in many aspects and areas of our lives . One of them is education , specifically in schools . Before , we as students , took classes in classrooms , interacting with teachers and classmates , however now we take classes virtually through platforms such as Teams or Zoom , hence we do not have social interactions , we just barely see our faces . In fact , we only turn our cameras on when we have to present final projects . Despite that , some changes are necessary and it stands to reason that we have to adapt to the circumstances , so it is not so easy . Currently schools have many challenges to face in order to not only maintain their tuition , but also keep their level of education to prepare students in better ways . Additionally , it is important to bear in mind those studies which were done during the quarantine about the academic performance , which show that students do not learn in the same way , they do poorly in academic and social ways and also , the academic charge has doubled , which not only affects students , but also teachers . On account of the previous , schools will have to be different in the future . First of all they must guarantee safety while learning , so they will have large classrooms with appropriate ventilation , they will reduce their room quotas , install safety points with antibacterial gel and schools will prepare protocols in case of covid . Moreover , schools in the future will have to install cameras , which will facilitate students to take lessons from wherever they are . They will use more platforms to explain some topics and to reduce the workload of the teachers . Besides , schools will have to train their teachers to give and teach better in this virtual mode . Another thing schools must change will be the boards . These have to be digital in order to avoid touching directly and so on . Definitely , schools will recreate their facilities and the way they teach , taking into account many strike features , although the main purpose will be to assure the students they will get the best preparation for their futures . 
The way to learn other languages has plenty of obstacles . In the case of English , although so close in our daily routine through the products and culture from the USA , it is not different . Learning comes through training in the four abilities : speaking , listening , grammar and writing . Computer time helps a lot to find tools that have artificial intelligence to contribute to a better and faster process for fluency . I knew , recently , the Write and Improve website that helps me so much to achieve this goal . The website Write and Improve English was a creation of Cambridge University . It has such an interactive and friendly main page . On this page , it 's possible to access a lot of suggestions , like essays at beginner , intermediate and advanced level , where it has plenty of kinds of themes . After this , the first contact is so comfortable and , the first contact is so comfortable and as far as used it 's possible to see this tool is easy use , has automatic correction and it 's possible to follow how many minutes it 's taken to complete the essay . I 'd like emphasise that this tool has a wonderful way to fix the wrong words and grammar used . In this , it 's possible to do some comparatives between what was written and the English level beyond . In addition , you have the possibility to understanding some comparative between what was it write and English level beyond , in adiction , have the possibility for understand the accession for the theme and progress a longer of correction for the essay . In conclusion , it 's possible to say that this tool can be so useful for English students and it is one more among others that can help improve your ability in English . 
Hello Chris ! We will travel to the museum by my father 's car . In the museum there are a lot historical artifacts , they also have a replica dinosaur fossil ; believe me you will be surprised when you see it . You just need to bring your lunch , and everything else my parents will take care of it . Ben 
Hi , I went to a concert last week with my old friends and it was wonderful . We saw a concert banner while we were walking down the street in front of the school and the banner said there was a Will Wood concert on the circus campground . Besides that , the tickets were also cheap for us . Furthermore , there were my other friends from school , however , they only went there to see the place . In addition to this , an acrobat fell when she was zipping on the roof and we helped her to get up again . I hope to see you at another concert with us . See you soon . 
This year , I want to learn language programming , specifically Python and SQL , and also to learn Power BI . I want to learn these subjects because I want to get a job in the data analysis area and to earn my bread and butter . One of the areas that I want to improve is my knowledge in the English language . This year , I want to achieve an intermediate level in the English language . Another area that I wish to improve is my business skills . To achieve these objectives , I will practice every day . For data analysis , I will do projects with Power BI , Python and SQL . I will study Power BI in the morning , Python in the afternoon and SQL after I study Python . For English lessons , I will study every day at night , reading , writing , speaking and listening . I hope to reach my goals this year and further , to improve . 
I think there is not a hierarchy of things related to health about what is more important for our health . That said , there is a balance between the things that are important for our health , where those things are interrelated with each other . Besides exercise , there is mental health . Mental health is essential for our daily performance and , mainly , for our social relationships . Without solid mental health , people are prone to anxiety , depression , aggressiveness and poor performance at work . Furthermore , people with weak mental health have a negative perspective of their future . People succumb to a lack of planning and they are not able to be successful in their lives . To improve their health , people need to have a balance between mental health and physical health . For this , people can do exercise before or after work to improve their physical health and people can meditate early in the morning , do a hobby at the weekend , or they can spend a day with their family to recharge their energy and to improve their mental health . 
I think that it is better for university students to move away and live on their own . I think that it is necessary for university students to be independent . Different from high school students , university students have to choose what they study at university , so they should do everything independently . If you live on your own , you have to do by yourself whatever you do every day , such as making your own bed , making meals , cleaning up your own room , purchasing goods which you need . I think that your family have supported you to live , except to study , when you live with your family until high school . But I think that university students are already a part of social members so they have to be responsible for their own activities including every day life . I think studying is only a part of everyday life . Living on their own is a good opportunity for university students to be responsibility of their own life . But I also understand that it is impossible to live on their own because of some economic reasons . By living on their own , it will be more expensive compared to living with their own family . From my personal experience , I lived on my own when I was a university student in Tokyo . Before that , I live with my family , so except studying , everything was done by my family . But after living on my own , I had to cook by myself , clean up my room by myself , wash clothes by myself , get up by myself . Until getting used to do , it was very tough for me . But I think that this experience was very important for me to be independent . So I recommend university students live on their own as much as possible . 
There was a long period of time when I watched TV like a crazy girl . Each morning , after I finished my homework , I always watched TV between 2 and 3 hours in the morning . When I watched some TV programs , I just thought they had been created to help me recharge my batteries after I 'd done my homework . I still remember laughing so much while I watched a play called " The Black Duck . " But now I 'm older , I 'm a teenager , so I 've been watching some TV programs to help to improve both my knowledge and experience . That has made me change my mind about TV programs . I am learning how to become a good teenager . Some of my friends said they do not agree with their parents and sometimes they shout at their mom and dad . They asked me how to make them become normal . I teach them all of the things they need to do and also let them know where they can find the answers . That is all in the TV shows . 
Dear Sir or Madam of the town council , As of recent , the town council has been taking a bill into consideration which would ban the use of mobile phones on public transport , shops and restaurants . I believe this not to be a wise decision seeing that this may have unforeseen consequences if it came to pass . Because of this , I have decided to outline a number of them so that the council may make an informed decision . First of all , the banning of mobile phones on public transport will not stop the use of mobile phones unless it becomes the responsibility of the drivers to enforce this regulation . Second of all , the restaurants will be put in a difficult situation , either they lose most , if not all , their business customers or they turn a blind eye to the use of mobile phones . Moreover , even if restaurants would want to enforce the ban , who would tell the customer ? Certainly not the waiters and waitresses who depend on the customers ' good will to survive . A similar situation is to be expected in shops . Third of all , this will drive any visitors to the town away in mere minutes . All of the problems are related to the enforcement of such a ban . Nobody within the businesses wants to enforce this ban based on the fact that they will lose them customers and over all make our town less attractive for outsiders . I sincerely hope you take my points into consideration when making your decision . 
Speaking personally , this new year means a new beginning for me , to set new goals and shoot for the stars in different aspects of life , among which there 's school . Hence I want to work on different areas in order to be an exemplary student and learn even more . First of all , I have identified areas of my learning that I 'm pleased with , such as chemistry , maths and science . I regard myself really good at them . Moreover , I enjoy learning about maths and science , as a result I 'll keep my habits of study in those areas in order to get better and to be part of the honor roll . Those habits are the following : do extra exercises every time that I have problems learning new methods , attend the science workshop which is given every semester , go to the library to do my homework and study with friends . On the other hand , I have to admit I want to improve in some areas of my learning , like English and German , in which I 've been struggling since the last semester . To tell the truth , I think languages are incredible and can open doors to awesome opportunities in life . Bearing this latter in mind , I want to improve and make languages a boon in my professional career . So this brings up preparing and planning some actions to do in the short and mid term , so that I will be able to achieve my goals in this new year . For me , the gist of the matter is that I have to practise my speaking and listening . As the saying goes , practise makes perfect , so I will listen to a podcast and a lecture in English every day and a lesson in German . Furthermore , other actions that I have to do is call some friends who know how to speak German and English . It is highly probable that they have a higher level than me , however the higher the better . Owing to this , I will feel pressured and more inspired to learn more and more . Finally , I will program some tests every two weeks in order to evaluate my progress and to be able to evaluate my action plan , I mean if I have to modify something or implement more activities . Overall , I have described a brief about the areas of my learning that I 'm pleased with and others I want to improve . In that way , I will get the best of school and surely I can shoot for the stars . 
Although video games are not one of my favourite pastimes , I know they are very popular with all -aged children . It seems that children from the richest countries have a stronger interest in them and the bulk of their time is spent with them . This is an attitude that makes people worried and understandably angry . What parents are afraid of is their children 's incapacity to socialise with others . This means that children will run the risk of being isolated adults and what is more threatening is the inability to find a good job . I consider it a serious problem that involves not only children , but the entire society . I disagree with those who think that video games could have some beneficial effects , unless we refer to some mental illnesses where video games are suggested as a therapy . In general they are a useless pastime , in spite of children feeling video games make them feel at home . As I see it , there are some side effects , like the risk of suffering from long isolation , that in the most serious cases could turn into a mental illness like depression . Unfortunately , there is an always increasing number of people that need a psychologist to recover from their bad mental state . Another delicate issue that should not be forgotten is dealing with the large amount of violence that children experience through video games . The point that all scientists agree on is children 's difficulties to see the difference between reality and playing and they think life can be window -shopping like video games . To the best of my knowledge , video games have never made people cleverer and the efforts of society should be addressed to preventing children from overusing them . 
Nowadays , zoos are a place where families pass the bulk of their time , because they are under the impression that their children can learn about nature and animals . This is a false impression , because when you want to learn about animals , you have to see them in their natural environment . What I mean is that animals living in a zoo are denaturalised , and you can not learn anything interesting . To the best of my knowledge , when a family has a trip around a real animal 's environment , they learn much more than they do in a zoo . In a zoo there are only a few animals and you cannot see how they behave , for example when they are in a herd . Seeing three or four animals is just a drop in the ocean . You will see how much more exciting it is to study animals in their natural environments . For example , a herd of tigers hunting zebras and smaller animals in a huge area , this is something impossible to see in a zoo . Another remarkable point stressed by environmentalists is that animals are not well treated in a zoo and they suffer living in small cages . In other words , animals need the benefits of a life in the wild . In spite of some proposals to enlarge the cages and the zoo area , these optimism -based statements do not persuade those who want to see animals free in a forest . 
Nowadays , every company has an office . Some of them decide to make enclosed workstations , while others , usually newer ones , do not even make walls separating employees from their co -workers . In my opinion , the shifting meta towards less enclosed offices is very good for workers . Just think about it . Everyone wants to work in a place where there are no barriers between co -workers , no matter the position in which they are . Everybody is easily accessible due to this . More importantly working in such places allows people to feel like they are in their own home . This way allows employees to feel less crowded and just more cozy . Further going , due to reduced stress , people are more efficient and they are more likely to do their tasks correctly . It is a perfect example of a win -win situation . Employers are happy because workers are doing their work right and employees are happy because they are not stressed at all . Unfortunately , like everything , this way of arranging offices has some downsides , so it 's not perfect for every office . Some jobs require employees to be concentrated the entire day . They often have to be precise in the things which they are doing . It 's for sure easier to achieve when you are in an enclosed , quiet workstation . 
In some offices , employees work in enclosed workstations or cubicles . Other offices have a more open design , in which there are no walls separating the employees from their co -workers . Both settings have advantages and disadvantages , so in this essay , I would argue that enclosed workstations are better because it gives more space and privacy which employees need in order to function more efficiently . In addition , offices with enclosed arrangements can allow workers to work in a more organised manner , and it can also prevent workers from talking to each other during work time ; and that will improve work outcomes . However , offices with no walls separating employees can promote instant interactions between employees . At the same time , it could be distracting for employees ; which may result in reduced efficiency and productivity in work . Finally , offices with enclosed workstations are much more convenient than those with an open design because it promotes organisation , discipline and efficiency in the workplace . Unlike open settings in which workers may get distracted by each other ; which may result in decreased productivity in work . 
Music is plays a vital role in our well -being . In some schools , it is compulsory for students to learn and play a musical instrument while , in other schools , there may be no music at all . In this essay , I will argue that music is important for students , but it should not be compulsory . I believe music must be taught in schools because it is a common communication language between communities around the world , and it is also known for its psychological effects , such as relieving stress , anxiety and fears . It is scientifically proven that music can be used as supporting treatment for some neurological disorders ( e . g , Parkinson 's disease ) . Furthermore , music plays a vital role in almost everyone 's life . Some people listen to music for relieving stress or remembering good moments from the past ; such as times spent with friends and family members . Music itself can be a gift for humanity , and we should appreciate it by teaching students how to play musical instruments ; because that promotes their self -confidence and allows them to express themselves through music . I highly recommend music be taught to school students in their early years because it will promote their self -confidence and help build their personalities . 
Some university students live on their own while there are attending school , but others live at home with their family members . I think living on your own as a university student is much better than living with your family while you are studying . I think so because students at university level should learn to be independent in their life matters because , as we get older , we sometimes tend to be far away from our families ; so we need to learn how to deal with that without them . Life is very hard sometimes , so we need to learn how to handle the problems that we face along the course of life . As university is the final stage of education , and it is said to be a transformational stage in which students mentality grow to become more independent . Hence , in this important stage of life , students tend to get to know different environments and form new relationships with others and interact as adults . While living on your own as a university student has diverse advantages , however , living with your family during university can be a good alternative , especially for young or minor students under the age of 19 years old , who are not strong enough to tackle life struggles alone . In conclusion , I would say it is better for university students to live on their own for some time away from family to learn how to handle life problems , but for young or minor students , it is safer for them to live with family members while they are studying . 
Hi Chris , It is really wonderful to be going with you to the Bee museum . There are two choices to get there , you can take a train from Sue to the museum or come to my home to go with us by our car . We will enjoy the way together . The museum shows how bees work and produce honey , also the bees ' kingdom system with quain , workers and eggs . There is so much knowledge about the hard process to get a spoonful of honey . It is necessary to put on gloves and glasses to protect yourself from the bees ' stings . See you on Saturday my friend . Take care . Khawlah 
According to a study by Oxford University , every third child worldwide between six and twenty is overweight . Caused by the inactive lifestyle many young people have today , this shocking number is the indicator for the plan to force university students and school children to do a sporting activity at least 3 times per week . As the options for children and teenager to do recreational activities without having to move are innumerous , the motivation to be active is accordingly low . Therefore , it is necessary to take action , by enforcing physical activity into the weekly schedule of students . Firstly , it is important to argue that this plan is to prevent our modern society from a dangerous and unhealthy development , since obesity in young children can have grave effects on their health . To only mention a few , diabetes , cardiovascular problems and cancer , are illnesses caused by the consequences of being overweight . But this does not only take a toll on the person concerned , but also on the health system . Having to increasingly pay for the medical aid of children and teenagers , the health system is not equipped to endure any more stress . The only way to help is , therefore , to force children to do sports . Equally important is the following aspect concerning the impact sport has on the mental health of students , since sporting activities not only allow children and teenagers to move , which releases the hormone dopamine , but it also enables them to spend time with their peers . Research shows that activities in groups can additionally have positive effects on the students ' grades and help them learn important social skills , such as teamwork and fair play . As a result , the children and teenagers become happier and better members of society . In conclusion , it is important to enforce sports into the students ' weekly schedule , as it not only improves their mental and physical health , but also because it has a great impact on the functionality of society . 
A lot of high schools nowadays require students to complete some volunteer activities . They are necessary in order to graduate . As everything , this strategy has its upsides and downsides . In my opinion , this type of requirement should not exist and it 's not good for students . There are few reasons why I think like that . First of all , everyone is different . Not everybody enjoys having relationships with other people . I 'm that kind of the person . It 's terrible to force someone to do something that they do not want to . Just imagine a situation where you are forced to clean toilets after others - no one would want to do that and no one would enjoy it . It 's that simple . Another reason why I think this type of practice is not optimal is that people who are forced to be a volunteer may not do theirs tasks correctly . If they do something wrong , they can cause some hard problems . In example , this situation may happen when someone is helping an older person and they give them too many pills . It 's probably lethal for this person . Not only will they be dead , but more importantly , it will probably cause some serious mental illnesses for the volunteer . 
Learning to speak a foreign language today is more important than it was in the past . Throughout the years , the world has been changing and becoming globalized . All kinds of businesses converged to speak a common language , in this case English . It does not matter in which part of the globe you are , there will always be a person who speaks English and it is good . The labor market wants employees and candidates for a position who are able to communicate at a high level in English with the world . It did not happen in the past . People would get a job easily without knowing English . However , it has been changing since the businesses reached this global position . They are located in several countries with different languages . So , knowing a foreign language is not a luxury today , it is a need . Even if you want to get new knowledge , a foreign language will be requested . 
It is a very interesting topic . I studied basic school twenty years ago . We had only paper books and it was enough for us . Today is another world . New technologies have grown all around the world . Children can study with more opportunities than we could before . I had only paper , a pencil and pen . I went to school very happy , because we did not know anything else . Today we have a lot of devices , for example a desktop computer , notebook and smartphone . I am very glad that we can use these devices for a better life . I do not think that paper books will be replaced by technologies . I read both paper books and electronic books . We should go with today ages . Schools and universities are modern buildings and people have to use new things there . I will have children and I will want to use new notebooks . I will buy a new home computer next week . I will use this device a lot . I will be satisfied and I will be using everything . It will be better for our future . Do not stop . 
Nowadays , it is well known that having the same teacher for several years is stunning . However , I really remember that it is much better to have new teachers each year , for these reasons . Firstly , it is really essential that if you have new teachers , you will learn other ways of learning skills and also improve your current knowledge in great ways . As a result of that , you would better your skills in the long run . Nevertheless , it is very necessary to point out that if you have new teachers each year , it will be so profitable for you , as you can set up new relationships with your teachers . Consequently , you will be more encouraged to learn awesome knowledge . Last but not least , having outstanding marks should be mentioned , since your new teachers are going to teach you harder , with the aim of you getting wonderful grades , thus it would be so profitable for you in the future . In conclusion , I really believe that having new teachers would be very beneficial for students , as they could learn other ways of learning skills , set up flawless relationships with their teachers and they are going to get the most out of the marks . 
HI -TECH SCHOOL I am very sure that in the future , school will have developed awesome robots which will substitute teachers , thus classes will be more enjoyable and amusing . Also , scientists will set up stunning automatic doors and windows . As well as that , pupils wo not have to knock on the door so many times or open windows all the time . Furthermore , school wo not have books for learning , as they will offer wonderful tablets for students . As a result of that , they could carry the material easily without weight troubles . Therefore , the schoolchild will have at their disposal a lot of delightful electronic lockers which will have an outstanding security system to back up students ' material . Nevertheless , schools will still be the same in the ways of having an amazing canteen for having lunch or a blissful playground where kids will be able to do their mischief ! 
In 2014 , I went to Turkey for ten days to my facation in Istanbul , the capital city of Turkey . On this trip , I went with my friends and we used an airline to travel to this nice country . We had a reservation in a beautiful hotel and our reservation included three meals and in the hotel lobby , there was big and good cafe . We had tea and coffee in it every day . We took taxis and buses when we wanted to go out and we also used the metro sometimes . We went shopping and we hung out in Turkey 's forest . My friends went swimming and we used to have a nice time in the calm park that was near to our room . In my opinion , that vacation was the best holiday I have ever had , because we visited the most gorgeous and very beautiful country in the world . 
Nowadays , in some schools , students must study music . They sometimes even have to learn how to play a musical instrument . In my honest opinion , this type of requirement is not good for students . Let 's have a close look why ! First of all , everyone is different . Not everybody is interested in playing music , they simply might be keen on other things . It might be stressful if they are forced to study music and/or learn to play a musical instrument , even if they do not want to . I was in a similar situation back in primary school . I had music lessons , which I did not enjoy and I had to learn how to play an instrument , which I did not enjoy either . What is more interesting is that , at the time , I was keen on playing another instrument , which was the guitar . It was really satisfying for me . Another reason why not to force everyone to attend these lessons is that some people might get harmed due to high volume music . There are illnesses which even can kill such a person . Going further , some people might get really stressed out . It can easily affect their mental health and possibly cause some suicide attempts . At the end , I think that forcing someone to do things which they do not want to do is bad and might be harmful for them . 
Hey Chris , What is going on ? How are you ? I am already looking forward to seeing you next Saturday , when we will be going to the local museum ! For now , I just want to tell you the basic facts about how we are going to travel to the museum , what we can see there and what you need to bring with you . We are going to take the bus , so we can come to the museum at a proper time . You will need a bus ticket , but you can also buy it directly on the bus by spending about five Euros . Please also take some food and drinks with you . The drinks , as well as the food , are really costly there . Also take your handy or your camera with you . Maybe you will want to take some photos ? The museum we are going to go into , exhibits colossal skeletons of ancient dinosaurs . They also exhibit fossils and other stuff like that . It seems to me that it will be a very interesting exhibition . I am looking forward to seeing you next Saturday ! With friendly greetings , Your friend , Dieter 
Dear Mr Michael , I am writing in reference to your plan on banning the use of mobile phones in some places . As a resident in this area , I have talked with other local residents about their opinions and we would like you to know our points of view . We live in a touristic city , which means that our economy depends mostly on foreign people . Tourists always want to be able to have access to social media , they want to show where they are , what they are doing , what they are eating and how they feel in specific places ; that is why currently restaurants , shops , hotels , parks and public transport offer free internet access . This service has allowed some places to be recognised worldwide ; in consequence , if you decided to apply this law , a lot of establishments will be affected seriously . I am the owner of a restaurant and we did some research about how we would be impacted by the new law . If this law is applied , our affluence of customers will be reduced by approximately 40 % of the total and probably we will have to dismiss some employees . We hope you reconsider not to apply this law , this is in order to protect the economy of our community . Thank you for your time and I look forward to hearing back from you . Best regards , Lucy Miller 
The school of the future will provide more technological resources and virtual freedom to the students in the classroom . This school will be different to the present schools in aspects , as more classes in distance learning will decrease the barriers between geographical distances , making it possible for students of other cities , states or even countries to study in the schools that they dream about so much . Certainly , the school of the future will have virtual classes , where the students will take lessons without the necessity of being present in the school . Another thing that will be present in the future is the massive use of tools that are currently avoided in the classroom , like Google , You Tube , Wikipedia and others . Of course , some things that are present currently in schools will remain in the school of the future . The contact face -to -face with the teacher will continue existing and the physical presence of students in the school will keep being an important factor for learning and relationships between students , teachers and schools . 
Have you ever imagined your life in the future ? What kind of the life would you like ? A calm and longer life or a shorter but intense one ? Some would choose an intense and varied life instead of a calm and stable one ; on the other hand , some may prefer a steady life . The first reason is I am more likely to keep the relationship with my family and my friends . A shorter life , but much more intense , means I would not have enough time to accompany them to create more precious memories , although I would have an exciting or a proud experiment in my life . In addition , I am a greedy man who really desires to live longer to deeply explore this world . The last one is I usually slow down the speed of life so that I can have more time to enjoy this wonderful and beautiful world . Theoretically , I would like some intense movements or things to inspire me and make me feel more energy . , . people need some excitement to make their lives more vivid . Furthermore , an intense life attracts many people to escape from the cycle of boring daily life . However , if only can choose between the two options , I definitely choose the long calm life without any hesitation . I will not regret making the best choice for myself . 
Nowadays , it is well known that television entertains , as a lot of people use it to put off their tasks , but also , I really believe that TV could also educate , for these reasons . Firstly , it is really essential to say that television has educational programs , such as wildlife documentaries , stunning historical shows and superb technology programs , which supply us with marvelous information . As a result of that , all people could really enjoy learning new knowledge . Furthermore , TV has kids ' channels , such as Clan , the Disney Channel and Nikelodeon , where children could learn the alphabet and maths , as there are a lot of wonderful teachers who explain the lessons very well . So , it is a flawless way of learning new things . Last but not least , daily news should be mentioned , since with it we can learn about what is actually happening in the world . As a consequence of this , we can know about recent discoveries , such as new artworks , great technological developments and outstanding information about current wars . In conclusion , I really consider that television can also educate , because it brings blissful educational programs , awesome kids ' channels and delightful daily news . 
Every student must make a decision to either move away and live on their own or live at home with their family while they are studying . I think that moving away from your parents is a better choice . Let 's have a quick look at why I think like this ! First of all , by moving away from your parents , you will have to do more things than just clean dishes . It is for sure good for you . You will also have to set your budget . Making a mistake or not sticking to it might be critical for you ! So , managing your money wisely is a very important thing in adult life . Going further , you will also have to do all the paperwork by yourself . There may not be any person to help you out with it . Additionally , paying taxes is another activity which you will be supposed to do in the future . It sometimes might be tricky , but it 's , for sure , really important and , by doing so , you will learn a lot . Also , you will have to find a house or an apartment on your own . It connects heavily with budget management . All of the things and activities which I mentioned above will help you become more mature and more prepared for you future life . Remember , that in the future , no one will help out you with those things . 
People have always debated the importance of telling the truth . It is a subject which generates opinions crash , but we could say that there are situations when you are forced to tell lies . Personally speaking , over our lives , we deal with a lot of situations which force us to tell lies ; some people think that telling untruths is a characteristic of a bad education , but no one is exempt from inventing stories . As a child , many of us told lied to our parents or teachers to avoid getting into trouble , this kind of behaviour allowed the parents to teach the importance and the benefit of telling the truth , as adolescents sometimes we lied to protect our privacy or to feel free and independent . People use lies as a defence weapon , sometimes when we cannot deal with problems on our own and these lies can be interpreted as call for help . On the other hand , during our development , we learned the consequences of telling lies , we are aware that telling lies could get us into more serious trouble , even though we still lie because , no matter if we are children or adults , we are afraid of what might happen , of not controlling the situations or of being harmed by certain pieces of information . In conclusion , as humans , telling lies is part of our nature . During our development , we learn that telling lies could give us bad consequences , however , sometimes we are forced to invent something to avoid problems , to protect someone or to protect ourselves . 
I have recently found the Write and Improve website and I need to say it has been helping me a lot . Let me describe what is possible to do on the Write and Improve website . First of all , this website is split up into many sections by level of difficulty . We have levels that range from beginner to advanced and business . It is possible to work on the Just For Fun one too . By the way , I 'm working on the intermediate level right now . Another section is the part where you can work on your IELTS preparation , there are two options , IELTS Academic and IELTS General Training . There is the possibility to work together with a teacher and some colleagues , but I am not familiar with this part of the website . How does the website work ? It is pretty simple . Once you are online and have chosen a level of difficulty , the website will give you a topic , and you need to develop a small text . Sometimes it ranges from 0 to 50 words , sometimes it ranges from 140 to 200 words , and after you have finished your task , a robot or an Artificial Inteligence will check your answers and give you some feedback . That feedback will help you a lot , you can try to improve your answer and submit it again . The website gives you a score based on your performance and it is always possible to improve it . So far , I did not have any difficulties with Write and Improve , and my favourite thing about this tool is the feedback . I would like to give you my recommendation , use it ! 
Nowadays , most doctors are willing to work in the cities where they will be able to earn quickly a lot of money . And this in spite of the crucial need for doctors in many rural areas . There is obviously an issue : why are doctors leaving the areas where they are most needed for cities and big towns , which are already full of skillful doctors ? First and foremost , doctors leave rural areas because of the working conditions , as they feel that most of them are underpaid and are willing to make money . Therefore , those doctors will move out of town , in a view to raise their income by having a wider amount of patients - a clientele that will undoubtedly outnumber the one you could ever have in a small countryside village . Moreover , they may feel as if they were stuck in tiny villages lost in the middle of nowhere , and try to get closer to the big cities One of the solutions that could be set up to solve this problem , other than the traditional proposal of raising the incomes , would be to sensitise the doctors to the desperate needs of a medical presence in rural areas . By and large , very few physicians are aware of this need , let alone of the appalling situation in which some of those areas are in . We could , therefore , act in this way , through media or lectures in medicine schools , for instance . 
Dear Sir or Madam , Even though I appreciate new and innovative ideas for policies in our town , I would like to raise some concerns regarding the new proposal to ban mobile phones on public transport , in shops and restaurants . On the one hand , I think most citizens can agree that it is untactful to have loud phone calls in the before -mentioned spaces , but on the other hand , it is not advisable to ban something just because it is rude . It is not a crime to take up place for two on a bus with your legs spread wide , and neither should it be a crime to loudly argue on your phone there . If the culprit is a significant nuisance , the bus driver could tell them to get off the bus , even with the policies that are in place right now . For shops and restaurants , such a proposition is ridiculous . These places are privately owned and thus the owners and staff should decide on their own what is allowed there and what is not . I think anyone would be hard pressed to find any good reason why a regulation of mobile phone usage would be required here . Lastly , I have to mention that this proposal is defined so vaguely that even using one 's phone quietly , for example , listening to music with earbuds or checking one 's e -mails would qualify as an offence . I do not think the public would be in favour of this . I very much hope you take these points into consideration . Yours faithfully , Herbert Herbertson 
In most schools , studying music is optional or there may be no music classes at all . Nevertheless , maybe the students should , in regard to all the benefits they might get from it , have to study music . I think music is to be widely popularized in schools . By and large , people consider music a pleasant hobby or a nice concert to attend . At no time will most of them truly realise all the benefits they may get from music learning , mostly because nobody actually told them . Music can be seen as another way to communicate or express a wide panel of feelings , generally , in a softer way than we usually do , especially when it is about strong feelings and emotions , such as pain , anger or passion . For instance , if you are taking issues with someone and that it makes you angry , then music may help you . Rather than having a fall out with this someone , you could play music - and through it , express all the emotions you are holding in . Furthermore , learning an instrument , although it may be long and hard enables us to improve the learning and pursuance skills of a future musician , with a view to reuse them later . Learning violin , an instrument which playing is not that easy , can be a real challenge , but first and foremost , a real opportunity to reach perfection . Moreover , music can be really helpful for introvert person who find it difficult to interact with others , who prefer to stay back and may feel frustrated by it . It can concern antisocial , shy or less talkative people , but also extrovert and expansive people who might find it difficult to keep their cool and remain calm despite sudden and strong feelings . To sum up , music is really to be popularized . 
Television can educate at the same time as it entertains . Currently , television is facing a disruptive transformation in the way that people watch television programs . Television is further becoming an environment with more influence , political and social , on people . It 's common in the grid of television to see programs talking about events that impact the way society behaves currently . Due to changes in the people 's perceptions , television needs to approach delicate matters , such as environmental damage , homophobia , racism , violence against woman , child prostitution and other critical matters . To educate the public about these topics , television needs be impartial , principally about politics . Television opinions have a deep impact on how people think about certain matters . That is why television needs to be impartial , not to align the thoughts of people . Therefore , television continues to be a relevant way to communicate ideas , news and opinions . If television wishes to remain the main means of communication , it needs to change the way that it acts . 
Dear Sir and Madam , This is Fred Yamada , I have lived in the town for many years . I heard that the town council is studying banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants . So I would like to let you know my opinion . I have objections to the ban . Firstly , please let me know the reason why you want to ban the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants . I think there are no reasonable reasons for banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants . I think that it is reasonable to ban the use of mobile phones in concert halls . Secondly , please let us know the reason why you want to ban the use the mobile phone in shops and restaurants . I think that shops and restaurants are not public spaces , but private areas . Is it possible to restrict the use of mobile phone in private areas by law ? If owners want to ban the use mobile phones in their shops and restaurants , it may be possible for them to ask customers not to use mobile phones . Thirdly , if you implement banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants , in an emergency , how to contact with the people who are on public transport and in shops and restaurants ? Nowadays , we feel that mobile phones make our life more convenient . So it is difficult to restrict the use of mobile phones by law . I sincerely ask you to consider the restriction . Best regards , 
I think that to always say the truth is not so important , sometimes it is necessary to tell a lie . I think basically telling the truth is very important . I think that one of the most important things in business is trust . To grow the trust with stakeholders , including customers , I think it is very important to tell the truth . For example , if a vehicle manufacturer has some business troubles , such as a recall of their vehicles , in general , such a company should apologize to the customers and send a recall notice to all customers . Such a company will tell the truth of the reason for the recall . The reason why such a company takes the above actions is to keep the trust with stakeholders . So I think that it is important to tell the truth in our business . On the other hand , I think we have some situations when it is better to tell a lie . For example , at Cristmas , a lot of children believe in Santa Claus . A lot of children are looking forward to receiving presents from Santa Claus at Cristmas . Although adults know that the parents give the Christmas presents , most adults do not want to tell the truth so that they will not disclose the secret of Santa Claus . I think this lie is a white lie , a white lie will not do harm to anybody . So I think that it is necessary to tell a white lie in some cases . 
These seems to be 2 nice deals , of course , each one has its own advantages and disadvantages . I will explore them clearly before giving my opinion . I will go through the first offer , they offer us to live until 100 years old , enough for a normal life . You will be calm , with not too many attentions from citizens , you would live in the countryside , near the sea . You will hear the waves coming from the infinite ocean every morning when the sun rises . Your life is just going around the town , it is a normal town without sounds , noises from visitors . Your life starts and ends without being noticed by the people around the world . You would have a limited relationship with other people in other towns , in case you go for a vacation . Now , with a more intense life , the maximum years you can live could be 65 . Because it is intense , therefore 35 year less on the longevity . You probably would live in a city , with noises and you would party every weekend , like a university student . Now , I would like to give my opinion , I would choose the second offer . I do not want to live a life without caring people , without technology , without money . I can handle the problem that I ca not live long , but 65 years is enough for me to spend time , happiness and memories with my relatives . I can take care of my family , but if I choose and intense life , I probably would have spare money to pay for them , from the house to the activities . So in conclusion , 65 years , but intense , seems to be a better offer for me . 
Hi , Yeah , it 's a little bit different from your country . Here people always need to make a surprise party for the person who has a birthday . But we usually make some fun of the person and I will tell you how . After we cut the cake , we keep a piece to push it onto the person 's face . That 's the best part of our birthday party . The last thing are the songs , we have our songs that are different from yours . Abdullah 
In my opinion , the best choice depends on the lifestyle of each student when they were brought up and studied at high school , also on their characteristics . Some of them enjoy an independent life , depend on themselves in their studies , their works , but others like to live with their families , they hope that families always support them to achieve their goals and encourage them overcome difficulties in life . For me , parents should be careful and help them achieve their goals . However , they also ought to offer the best environment they can for their kids to be mature and successful in their lives . There are two reasons for me to agree with living on their own . The big main reason is they can live independently so they must face the problems and solve them on their own . The important thing is they must trust themselves . They will learn the way to deal with and overcome the challenges naturally . When they live on their own , they will know and understand their parents ' tough life . From that , they would love their families more and try their best to live more and better . Besides , an independent life will make them contact and interact with many people . They will learn how to maintain and have a good relationship with friends , families and people around them . They will know how to share their love , happiness and lend a sympathetic ear to the poor . On the other hand , they can be keen on the things they like , the work they love and try many new things which they have not experienced yet . They ought to lead their life and make decisions about everything . They also have the chance to relax and convenience to study and follow their educational life . It 's really difficult to cope with the homesickness in the early days when they separate from their families . But if they get over that , they will be more mature and learn a lot of things . In these early days , the parents should be their friends to be broad -minded , give them some useful advice , especially encourage them to be more courageous to follow the path they have chosen . In conclusion , although being alone to be mature and feel relaxed to achieve more in your educational life is significant to more teenagers , following family advice and instructions to deal with any problems is important to their mature life . 
At first glance , it might seem tempting to choose a short and intense life for oneself . 40 years , let 's say , full of romance , excitement and adventure . Just skip the uncomfortable part of life when you get old and need to be cared for . But I think this option might sound much better than it would actually turn out to be . There seldom is a life full of romance without heartbreak , and there never has been a life without any peril . Living intensely not only means to be joyous all the time , it also means to feel deep sorrow and experience crushing stress . I do not think there is a way to only amplify the positive aspects of a life without having any tradeoff and , therefore , I would argue someone who lives and feels intensely also faces intense hardships in their life . A long and calm life , on the other hand , gives you the benefit of more time , and as we all know , time is the most valuable resource there is . If you spend your time wisely , there is no good reason why you would trade any of it away . A calm life does not need to be any less fulfilling than a short and adventurous one , as calm does not equate to boring and living long in no way needs to get dull . There can never be enough time to spend with your family or to engage in a hobby , so I would gladly take 100 years . 
Hello Chris ! I 'm excited about our trip tomorrow . We will go to the museum by car , there is a lot of space so you do not need to worry about not having space in the car . We can see famous inventors like Einstein , and interact with some of the inventions . You will need to bring some water , your ticket obviously , your phone if anything happens , and your backpack to carry it all . I 'll see you tomorrow on our trip . Bye , Chris ! 
Health is the most important factor in human life . The assistance in diseases , in routine an exams and an explanation about better ways to have more health are essential . But although they are so important , some people do not have fair access to doctors . Doctors are more accessible in big cities . A lot of situations contribute to this : salary , conditions of good work are more common problems , but the solution came from more complex actions that only solve these questions . Practising some professions involves things like correct conditions for working and the salary that the worker receives . And , unfortunately , these factors are not good everywhere . The capital and big cities usually have better conditions and this impacts very much on the choice of doctors , for example . A doctor is a profession that involves a lot of social status , how much money they earn and a correct structure for working . But this work has a relation with a passion for life and health too . Regardless of this , a lot of workers just choose this job because of the money . In this situation , it is not easy to compete with the salary because usually there are better bids in the run . For better access for everyone to health and doctors , it 's so important to give better conditions for doctors to work in rural areas and country cities . But it 's important to make a structure for workers in healthcare , like doctors , to have better results and access to a better life outside the capital . In addition , orientation in the choice of work for students can help them understand that a doctor goes where the patient needs to love the job . 
I like to do exercise , five times a week . I do not have a specific time , but I prefer to do it in the morning . I do it at home these days because we have a pandemic , so the gym is closed . You have to be smart when you choose exercises because you have to do a little bit , but keep it up daily . My daily exercise is squat , push , abdominal , hand nerves , and these are my favorite . 
Of course I prefer a short life but much more intense . It is insulting for me to think of a life which does not have anything special to do , but only to live ! In our life , we have to make projects , to establish goals and to work in order to achieve that . We need to understand how important books are for our culture and our knowledge about many sciences , and despite many people not appreciating reading , we need to put in our mind that a book is a friend that ca not speak but can teach us . Nevertheless , I consider that doing physical exercise is a very good way to improve our skills even if we are speaking about mind skills , but the effort related to it can improve in a very strong way the manner that we undertake the problems . I ca not have respect for people that prefer to live with the help of other people and , sorry for my strong words , but this kind of human being is one the biggest disgraces in our world . I hate them with all of my powers and all of us know that many of them ca not respect our likes and prefer to live off our taxes and our efforts . They 're parasites and I respect them as human beings like me and others , but they have immediately to get a job . 
I think that having health is more important than having a lot of money . I am not talking about only physical health , but also mental health . However , having money is essential to keep a healthy mind , due to the fact that having money , principally through work and entrepreneurship , helps people avoid stress and depression from a lack of money . Logically , this only works if people are working in jobs that they like . If not , rather than helping people to keep a healthy mind , this will harm their mental health . It 's no use having money if you have poor health . It 's no use working incessantly if you are getting stressed , frustrated , sick and unhappy . It 's important for you to have a balance between health and money . From the moment that you understand this equilibrium , you will think that the most important thing in your life is having health , a good job and your family beside you . 
