Nowadays , it is well known that some parents feel that video games can have a negative impact on their children , whereas other parents believe that they have positive effects on children , but away from these issues , I really believe that they can have a positive impact on children , for these reasons . Firstly , it is really essential to say that thanks to video games , children develop their logical skills , as video games test children to resolve arduous puzzles . As a result of that , they could improve their logical abilities so much . However , meeting new people is other advantage of video games , as thanks to that , children can enlarge their social ties . As well as that , they can meet stunning friends to play with them and spend an awesome time . Last but not least , improvement of creativity is another benefit of playing video games , as they have a creativity mode where players are allowed to create everything they want . As a consequence of that , children could have outstanding artistic skills in school . In conclusion , video games have a positive impact on children , seeing that they can improve their logical abilities , they can also meet astonishing friends and improve their creativity . 
Nowadays , it is well known that zoos are great places for people to learn about animals , but I really believe that animals belong in nature and it is awful to keep them in zoos , for these reasons . Firstly , it is really essential to say that animals live more comfortably in nature than in zoos , as they can have a lot of space for moving and living wild . As a result of that , they can hunt their dams freely . Furthermore , in nature , animals can build their own habitat for living , without nature animals can build their own habitat for living whitout taking care of the crowded space that they have in zoos . As a consequence of that , they can live independently and more blissfully than in zoos , where they are kept an eye . Last but not least , the survival of animals in nature should be mentioned , as in these places , animals survive more than in zoos , as they have better life conditions than in zoos , where they are locked up and anxious . In conclusion , I really believe that animals should live in nature , as there they could live more comfortably , they do not have a crowded space for moving and they can survive longer than if they live in a zoo , where they feel too isolated . 
My Favourite Season Of The Year What is your favorite season ? Right , I can answer this question for you , saying that summer is a special season for me , as it is very hot , thus I can eat a lot of freezing ice cream . Have your ever tried it ? It is so delicious ! Furthermore , another reason why I really love summer is that when I was younger , I used to be in the street all day playing with my astonishing friends and watching mesmerizing sunsets with them . Such awesome memories ! However , now , summer is still my favorite season , as when it is summer , I can do more things that I do not usually do , such as painting , recording stunning videos for You Tube and learning a foreign language . Also , I can hang out with my friends and go to the beach , where I can spend a superb time with them . It is so blissful ! And you , what is your favourite season ? 
Undoubtedly , being sedentary is extremely harmful and unhealthy for human beings . As a result , some people claim that pupils who are normally and physically inactive should be required to do sports activities three times a week to improve their health . As far as I am concerned , I partly agree with this idea as it has proven the advantages of exercise . On the other hand , doing sports activities should be regarded as personal will and it should not be obligatory . All my arguments will be addressed below . Not only can exercise reduce the opportunity of having a critical illness but it also helps with concentration and mental issues . It has been reported that , after exercising , our bodies will reduce insulin resistance and reduce inflammation , and it results in a decrease in diabetes or opportunities of other diseases . Additionally , our brain will release chemicals , such as endorphins , which help relieve pain and stress . The positive effects of regular exercise can be far better than we anticipate ; because of that , we should suggest young learners do physical activities as frequently as they can . Admittedly , it has been convinced that adequate sports activities can bring countless merits , from physical and mental perspectives , by some scientists . However , we should still respect those learners ’ willingness to do physical activities , as if we are concerned about adolescents with physical challenges who may not be able to act like normal students . This decision could be not reasonable and will turn into a torture for those teenagers with disabilities unless those students are exempted from this rule . To sum up , in my view , compulsory sports activities three times a week are not essential for all young students , in spite of some gained benefits from doing them . In contrast to making regulations , we should encourage the most students to do exercise spontaneously and educate them the importance of sport instead . 
In some schools , students must study music and learn how to play a musical instrument . In my personal opinion , it is a terrific idea , in other schools , it may not be required , which I think it is not good for the students . The most prestigious schools in the world teach music . It is important to learn because it increases your culture . In countries where education is a priority and they have the best students , they must study music and play at least one instrument . I studied music when I was in high school and I can play the guitar , but not everyone has the same opportunity . In my country , schools usually do not teach music . In my personal experience , learning how to play an instrument was very helpful for my personal enhancement . Music is part of the culture of the country and it is part of the history of the citizens . I hope that in the future our congresists may use their power to make laws that encourage schools to organize music classes . 
Everyone is different . Everyone prefers different things , is keen on different things . Everyone differs . There are people who would prefer to live a long , calm life until 100 years old . But , there are also those who would prefer a shorter life , but much more intense . When it comes to me , I would definitely choose the first option . To be honest with you , I 'm not really a social person at all . I do not like talking to people too much , hanging with them , or even texting with them . I am , what is called today , an introvert person . Do not get me wrong , I 'm not against people who prefer to be partying and chilling with friends all the time . For me , it 's just a better option . Let me explain why ! First of all , I would not enjoy dying at an early age . I think that nobody would . You see , having a long life is pretty nice . When you are partying or doing those type of things , it 's really easy to fall into a bad group , which will hustly ruin you . If you are not aware of it , you will probably start taking drugs as a teenager . Maybe it will be more intense , but I do not think that dying before your 30s is an enjoyable thing . , . when you live a long , calm life , it is more likely that you will get more out of it overall . It is way easier to travel , experience things , enjoy life and simply live , when you are not stuck to a bad 24/7 . Summarising , I think that living a long and a calm life is a better and safer option for all people . 
Travel in the future will be more comfortable , faster and safer . With technological advancements , people will have many ways to travel , including virtual travel to another place through a simulation of the desired place . One of the factors that will impact the way people will travel is Artificial Intelligence . Artificial Intelligence will help the travel companies to understand their travelers better . Also , it will be used as a first attendance to customers . Among the things I believe will not change are planes , trains , buses and ships as the means of transport most used to travel . I do not see another means of transport being more used than these in the future . I need to point out space travel . In recent years , we 've seen a growth of interest in that type of travel . Companies like Space X and Blue Origin plan to transport people to another planets . This will have a startling and thunderous impact on the world . 
