I agree with people that believe animals belong in nature and they do not deserve to be trapped in zoos . I know it 's important for people to visit animals in zoos with the purpose of knowing the animals and how they behave better . But animals are born to be free creatures , living all their life in their natural habitat . From the moment that you remove animals from their natural habitat and take them to zoos , the animals end up losing their wild behavior and it is dangerous , because when the animals go back to their natural habitat , they do not know anymore how to act in that environment . It is necessary to point out an exception . Many species of animals are running the risk of extinction and zoos , in this case , are an important environment to preserve these species . Therefore , if the animals are being kept in the zoos because they are in the process of extinction and they need to be taken care of to reproduce , I believe the zoos must be kept for this purpose . 
I have been studying English for about three years . I have studied in English schools and on the internet . I have recently been studying more on the internet , using tools and online pages . I have used a lot of tools . I have recently a new writing tool . This new writing tool is Write and Improve . It is a very useful tool . It is easy to use . Write and Improve is a tool by Cambridge . I write my reviews about interesting subjects . I can choose among beginner , intermediate and advanced . I choose one theme and write a review . Then I must click on check , the page will correct my review and give me advice to rewrite my review . The page also corrects the words the are not written correctly . This way , after checking my review , my writing improves . There is an option to share our writings with other students . The test zone is an interesting option for students who desire to know their level . The reviews receive a level . It can be A1 , A2 , B1 , B2 , C1 and C2 . The level A1 is the lowest level . C2 is advanced . It is very helpful because all students may use it . A beginner student can learn the structure of the phrases . An advanced student can improve their vocabulary using more sophisticated words . I highly recommend Write and Improve . I have been using it for five months and have improved my writing . I recommend this fantastic tool to students that intend to take a taste of getting a visa . To all readers of this magazine , I recommend Write and Improve . 
