It is true that it is more important to be healthy than to be rich . With good health , we can do anything we want in our life . We know that money is also an important thing in life . With money , we can buy food , a house , lots of things for our standard life . However , I think that having good health is better than money . First , physical health has a big affect on our work , so improving physical health every day can help you have good strength to do lots of work every day . For example , physical health is quite important for students , who have to do a huge amount of homework every day . Second , we always have to keep our mental health in a good state , therefore we always have motivation for work , free time , family and friends . Without good mental health , everybody 's emotions will be upside -down , so then we can lose our mind and this may cause lots of big problems , because bad mental health is the reason why relationships between people break down . The finally , if we have good health , you must protect it . When you have got a disease , you 'll know money ca not bring your health back . In short , money and health have the same importance in our life . However , we should know how to balance money and health . 
I 've known Write and Improve for about 3 years . Back then , of the four skills , writing was my worst skill , but I did not know how to improve that . Fortunately , I found this website by my brother 's suggestion . And that was the first time I tried it out . I 've been practising my writing since I was 8 . During the time I used it , I saw that it has lots of functions that the others do not have . First of all , it classifies into 5 small groups , that are : Beginner , Intermediate , Advanced , Business and Just for fun . You know the purpose you need it for , also you are the only one who could know what your level is . So , it will give you the exams that are related to your level . After you know what your level is , you 'll go on to that page . There are lots of topics , problems that people have been solving . Therefore , that makes your brains need to work really hard . When you finish your test , click " Check " so it 'll mark it and you 'll know what level are you at , C1 , B2 , C2 , etc . It will indicate you where you went wrong , also how to fix that . Therefore , these are the things you 'll get when you use Write and Improve . For me , it does not have any mistakes , it 's perfect and I saw my writing skills are going up . Some advice that I want you to know , when you do the exams , please try to use your own words , do not Google , therefore you 'll know exactly what your mistakes are . I hope you enjoy it when using this website . 
Most medical doctors want to work in the cities so they will make more money than in the countryside . This means , in rural areas , there are not enough doctors . So what are the reasons for this problem here and how to improve it ? In my opinion , they like that because the salary paid in the countryside was lower than in the cities , therefore they all want to work in the metropolis . I know that everyone loves money , but each person uses money for different purposes . So do medical doctors . Because of this , there are not enough physicians in rural areas . There are some civilians living in mountainous areas . If they have some problems , they could not get to hospital in time . Therefore , they have to die . For me , the best way to solve this problem is all doctors getting the same salary , the best way to solve out this problem is all doctors will get the same salary , even though in the cities and countryside . When a medical student becomes a doctor , he or she has an opinion which is " I have to work in a big hospital . " So , I hope that our government spends more money on building more hospitals in remote areas . Pay the physicians the same as the doctors in the cities . Mobilize young medical doctors to work there and tell them that there we need doctors more than ever . 
