I guess what I am writing is something that the bulk of students do not agree with , but my favourite season is autumn . I really like it for several reasons and the most important is that I like the atmosphere , with a touch of sadness and the grey sky , and I love it when the weather is not hot and there 's no more dryness around . I like it when the weather turns fresher and wetter . For me , autumn is a metaphor for life , with the days becoming progressively shorter and nature loses its colours . I think people are a little weak and they undergo the darkness of autumn , but this is a wrong attitude , and all of us should begin to love the less bright seasons . As well as that , I 'm happy to go back to school , where I have steady relationships and school gives me a steady growth . I remember at the beginning I went astray because of the fog , but in the end I had no more fear of going to school by myself . Autumn helped me to develop my braveness , and now I can roam around for the entire day . 
