It is right that a book is an important part when you study , bringing you knowledge about the world . Besides traditional books , there are also e -books on computers and tablets . E -books are now popular with a big part of students nowadays . With e -books , students can study everywhere with their computers or tablets . However , e -books should not replace books in schools and universities . First , to use e -books , we need an Internet connection , so this may be a bad thing for students to study without it . For example , when students go somewhere where there is no Internet connection , but they have to search for information , they ca not find anything . Second , everyone knows that using a computer or tablet too much can harm your eyes , so when you use an e -book it can harm your eyes too . Finally , using a computer or tablet can distract you , because you may use another app and not really concentrate on studying . In conclusion , e -books can bring benefits to us , but they should not replace books 
Today , English is becoming a world language . If you know English , you can succeed in every sphere of life whether you are doing business or a job , or if you are a student , you need to have fluency in English in both speaking and in writing . Many people feel that their English is not good and they do not want to join any classes or course , but now , we have a website that can improve your English . This website helps to improve both your English reading and writing skills . The name of the website is Write and Improve . I think this is the best website to improve English ever developed . It has different levels to improve your English . If you are a beginner , then do not worry this website has a level for the beginners also . The other levels are intermediate and advanced . The best thing is that it has a correction section in which you can see your mistakes and correct them . It has a progress graph in which you can monitor your performance . It also has a section of IELTS for the people who are preparing for IELTS . The best part of the website is that it has a workbook section in which all your previous work is stored so you want to see your progress and you can easily monitor it . If you want to see your previous work , you can see it easily . Now , I will tell you the best part of the website is that it 's completely free . A website having so many features and that is also without any cost is like having a cake with ice cream for free . It also has its own community where the person can register themselves and can interact other like -minded people and you can also chat and answer their queries regarding the difficulty they are facing in learning English . So all of you who want to improve their English join the website today and improve your English . 
