Let 's start with the advantages first . I think the best advantage is studying in another country . It can give you experiences that you ca not find in your country and you can go to a country that can offer you the best study solution . It can give you an understanding of another culture , politics and way of living . I think it can make you understand more what another culture thinks . It gives you a vision than you ca not find in your home country . Sometimes it can give you an experience that you never think you will receive . But , you need to open your mind , because if you do not , you ca not understand what other people think . And , the disadvantage is sometimes people ca not live in a culture they are not familiar with and it can make them feel bad about themselves . The most important thing is it can fool you with the good things that you ca not have in your country and make you look down on the people in your country . It makes you think you 're better than the rest of the people in your country . 
