I started using a new learning tool to improve my written English called Write and Improve . This website , in my opinion , is very helpful to improve your English . It has a lot of topics to write about and different levels of difficultly to choose from , besides it has a big community of users where you can make new friends and help each other to improve your English . To use this website , you just have to register and then you can select which level of difficulty you want to choose . It has Beginner level / Intermediate level / Advanced level and then it also has a Business section and a random section called Just for Fun . I also saw that you can do some tests , however , I ca not speak about this due that I have never done one , although I have planned to do some of them soon . The only problem that I found is the auto - corrector , due that I would rather have a correction from a teacher because he can give you some feedback and help you to find the mistakes that you might have made , and besides , he can help you to find solutions to these mistakes . However , in general terms , I think that Write & Improve is a good tool to practise your written English and improve it . 
