We live in a historical era where the medical sector has made huge steps in the direction of keeping you alive for 100 and even more years . The lifestyle and the diet we follow in our lives are two of the main factors that influence our life and , for living a long life , you must make sacrifices . I am a person more into the idea of living for a shorter time , but much more intensely , instead of living a long and calm life . In my mind , the expectation I have for a long and calm life is for something without any experience and without taking any risks . Experiences are fundamental moments in the life of any person and are good moments for personal growth and to be a better person in this selfish world . I cannot imagine myself in a calm life without the crucial experiences that completely changed my life . Living abroad in a country with a completely different culture from mine or the idea of moving from my hometown to study at the university that I have always dreamed of had some risks of destabilising my life , but are intense and unforgettable experiences that I would do again . A life without any risk is a life that is not lived because risks are part of the game we are experiencing . Risks exist and must be fought if you want to reach your goal and not be at the same point forever in your life . 
