When talking about mobile phones , they are a very common thing for modern people . Because of the phone , we can enjoy various kinds of convenient technology . But there are some negative effects happening at the same time . For example , people walk on the street and use their phone . This is a very dangerous thing , not only for himself or herself but also the driver next to him or her . Because when the walker puts their attention on the phone , they may not see the car pass by and easy to be crashed . Therefore , I think the government can build a policy to restrict using the phone when they are on the road . It can be a monetary punishment or a safety class to instruct them about security . But there are some convenient things that need to use the phone on the road , like taking a phone call , sending a message , or even booking a restaurant for a sweet date when you forget to book it before you went out . It is very important that the goal of the policy is not use it to ban everything about the mobile phone , but just prevent public people from dangerous accidents happening on the road . To sum up , I support the government restricting the mobile phone by building a policy which wo not cause inconvenience for us . 
