One survey from a famous magazine showed that a middle -aged man tells more than twenty lies per day . Some people think that lies are normal in our society , others think that lies should be avoided . I think that lies are normal and essential to human beings , we cannot only tell the truth . A scientist made an experiment , during twenty -one days , he told only the truth . He lost all his friends , his relationship and job . It means that the truth is hard , but it sets you free . There is fake news , lies that people say on social media , these lies can be harmful to some people . I think that some lies are acceptable , lies that do not harm other people . We tell some lies for convenience , to look more attractive to a girl you like . During a job interview , the most common lie is when a person does not want to be punished for a mistake . I sometimes tell some lies too . Sometimes , I receive invitations and I do not want to attend , then I say I am busy at the moment , but what I am really doing is lying on bed . When you are in love , you will always lie to impress the other person . It happened to me when I met my wife , I lied a little about things to impress her . But as my mother always said , lies do not last long and she knows me very well now . My point of view is that you can lie but your lie should not harm other people . 
