In this flat world , every country has to open to the world if that country wants to push themselves forward and the way to connect to the world is language . English , not by word , was chosen to become a global language , no country can deny it . For example , the first president of Singapore , Lee Kuan Yew , chose English to be the national language over Chinese , history proved that his choice is a brilliant move . People who know English can communicate with business men from the western world , students who know English can contact with high quality education material . The fact is , in just about two decades , Singarpore has become one of four dragons in Asia with a high living condition , the highest density of millionaires in the world . So , if we want to become a global citizen , we must learn English , especially for communication . In some companies , they only hire people who have basic English skills , or if they have some certificate in English , like TOFL or IELTS . Mastering the four English skills gives you an enormous opportunity to advance in your career and explore new horizons . I learn English everyday , you should do it now . 
