In my opinion , I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room . There are some reasons for my choice . Firstly , I think sleeping in a dark and quiet room will improve the quality of it . In a room like this , I can get to sleep more quickly than in a room with a small light . And if there is some noise , it will keep me awake . Secondly , I think if I sleep with some noise , I will become used to it . And if I set an alarm , maybe I wo not hear it since I always sleep with noise . However , when sleeping with no sound , not only can I sleep soundly , but also I can wake up with the first ring of my alarm clock . So , the reasons why I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room are it improves the quality of my sleep and I wake up when I hear the alarm . 
