As one of the users of Write and Improve , I recommend this learning tool to everyone who wants to study English writing skills . It is especially convenient and useful for people who study English by themselves and try to check their making sentence ' collectness . Learning another language , there are some difficulties to judge your own answer . For example , we can easily study reading and listening by solving testbooks and checking their answer sheet . However , we have a hard time to study writing and speaking because writing and speaking do not have a correct answer due to their plentiful expression . Moreover , it has a high cost to take a lesson with a native English language user . By using Write and Improve , students can study English more conveniently and economically . Although Write and Improve has an ability to judge the sentences accurately , there are some difficulties for users to understand why the sentence is not correct . Sometimes , students do not have enough knowledge to revise the text , so they need some hints to think about the reason for their mistakes . So I think it is one weak point to use Write and Improve . But this great tool will support to learn English those who want to improve their writing skills . 
