In my opinion , the office where an employee works every day is crucial for his mind and for the results of the company because the environment could influence the employees , and the increases or decreases of the business depend directly on their productivity . I think that it is very important to have an open design office in which there are no walls separating the workers . A satisfactory office could influence the employees ’ energy , their focus capacity and mainly their teamwork . First of all , workers need to feel strength , willingness and the desire to help a teammate from their team . An open design of the environment could influence people to establish collegial relations . When an employee sees all the time the others , he could be more motivated to work hard because the competition for the best results would intervene in this situation . Moreover , owing to the lack of walls which separate the employees , they could create a happy workplace with their capacity to make friends or to become colleagues with close relationships . On the other hand , enclosed workstations create stress , anxiety , nervousness , tiredness for employees because they spend all their time alone in their office and they fail to exchange stories , opinions or experiences with their colleagues . They do not have a motivating environment because they do not have enough time to know each other . As a consequence , the employees will come to work without enthusiasm and they will not be productive . All of this should influence their mind and their capacity to work . In conclusion , an office with a more open design is defining for the positive trajectory of an employee and it could transform a stressful and displeasure experience at work into a motivating , lovely and friendly one which influences people in a good way . 
My favourite season of the year . My favourite season of the year is the summer , because you are always on holiday . In this season , you can do a lot of things and the weather is always good due to there being more hours of light . You can go to the beach or swimming pool , although you can go to the mountains . That 's the perfect season to hang out with your friends and do a barbecue . Otherwise , you can travel different countries and enjoy their food and take a lot of pictures . In fact , you have many offers to travel to any place . If you can imagine it , you can go there . However , the summer seems the shortest season , because you enjoy it a lot . Moreover , if you have children , you can go to different places , such as zoos or aquariums , to see wild animals . Finally , I believe that the summer is the best season of the year . 
