Do we need music in our lives ? That 's the question . Are there times when music is important ? I 'm sure , for example , in the Cold War times , music helped the soldiers with fighting their enemies . They did not give up because of music . How does music make us feel ? There are a variety of types of music , some of them make us happy , other ones make us sad . But definitely music plays a huge part in our feelings and emotions . What would life be like without music ? We ca not say exactly , because people have been making music forever . They were making operas even in ancient Greece ! That 's why life without music could not be as good as with it . That 's why I 'm pretty sure that we need music in our lives . People always wanted it in the past and they also need it now , because life without music is not the same life . 
