This review describes Write and Improve , a new writing tool for learners of English . This tool provides short leveled writing tasks for language learners . The website ’s artificial intelligence provides feedback to users who are encouraged to edit resubmit their writing until it receives a 5 out of 5 rating . Students get immediate feedback on their mistakes . Much of the feedback is basic vocabulary and grammar mistakes , which is very useful . The second type of feedback is when students do not answer the questions or follow the task instructions even if their English is accurate . Both types of feedback are useful to students before they consult the teacher . The biggest problem is that the cost is 2.50 pounds per student per month paid BY THE TEACHER . They need to find a way for teachers to assign students to buy a semester subscription . Overall , I would recommend using this site for pre -intermediate and intermediate students when you have full use of a computer lab or students have their own devices with good Wi Fi connections . You should try the free version . At the moment , I cannot recommend the paid version for teachers , but I hope they make some small changes to make the paid version more useful . 
Yes , there are so many moments when you need to listen to music . For example , when you have a bad day , a way not to think about it is with some music , or if you want to work out , music is an excellent way to warm up your body and spirit . Well , depending on the kind of music that I listen to , it makes me feel one way or the other . I usually listen to music while I walk , but also I listen simply for pleasure or for sleeping . Also , there are a lot people that like to play an instrument and it is their way of living . A life without music would be so boring and grey . Everything would be monotonous and I think that people would be more lonesome and colder . I think that human beings need the music to live . 
Good morning , I am writing to share my opinion about your last proposal . I read in the newspaper about your new proposal of banning mobile phones on public transports and in shops and restaurants . First , I would like to congratulate you for being so brave , you will be strongly criticised by those people who cannot live without a mobile phone . I am writing to you to say that I totally agree with your proposal . I think we live in a time where socializing is difficult , people prefer to use their mobile phone than talking to other human beings . I sometimes go out with co -workers after work time . Most of them spent the whole night using their mobile phone , texting messages to other people instead of talking to a person no less than one meter from them . It is affecting our relationships as a society , I am afraid that the next generation will not be able to have a normal life because they will not have the same experience as we have today . Most of my happy memories are spending time with people that enjoyed spending their time with me . Something that worries me is how people are easily distracted using their mobile phones in public places , I saw a car accident because a pedestrian was distracted using his phone and crossed the street without looking at the traffic . This really scares me when technology causes fatalities , I am glad to share my opinion with you with you mister town council , I hope your proposal may be accepted . Thank you very much for your attention . 
