Today , I want to introduce you to my home town , Nam Dinh . Nam Dinh is an ancient town . The Tran Dynasty was there for a while . Nowadays , the Tran 's Palace has become the Tran Temple , a really famous place for many people in my country . One more popular location is Nha Tho Do . It is right beside the sea , so if you come there , you also can enjoy lunch with fresh seafood caught on the day . Nam Dinh is a small town , that 's why you can go to both these locations in one day . In the afternoon , you can go to the city museum . There is also Cot Co , a historical place . I think my home town is really a heaven for street food . There are many kinds of them : banh goi , pate bread , nem nam , xoi xiu and so on . Also , if you come to Nam Dinh , you ca not forget about enjoying Pho . Pho Nam Dinh is really famous all over this country . In the evening , Vi Xuyen Park is a perfect place to take an airing . The residents often go there to play and do some exercise . There are also many things in Nam Dinh that will impress you . Let 's come here and experience them . 
