In my free time I do things like play video games or read action books . I read a book often , usually twice a week on Mondays and Thursdays and once on weekends . I like playing video games , because I forget about the time , to get rid to get rid of my problems . I can work with my mind for a solution to the game . Yesterday was Sunday , I played a video game with my nephew . The last time I read a book was on Thursday . 
Do we need music in our lives ? The simple answer to the question above is yes . I cannot imagine a life without music at all . Without music , life is meaningless and has no color . Music is very important for me on many occasions , for example , when I am driving my car from home to work and vice versa , or when I am studying or doing exam preparation . Music has become very crucial when I feel sad or demotivated . Music lifts me up and reminds me that I am not alone . Life without music would be so boring and we would be depressed so easily , because according to some scientific research , music could bring peace and tranquility to people 's minds . It helps us to stay sane when we are in difficult times . Music brings positive emotional brainwaves to our mind , which help us to stay calm and relaxed . That is why in every spa center , you will hear music playing in the background , because it can make you calm . I personally live my life with music . I cannot live without it . 
My favourite season is autumn . For me , it 's the most special season in the year - the leaves are falling and it 's getting colder . But I would like to tell you a bit more about it . First of all , it 's good to know that the autumn is also called “ the golden season “ . Why ? It is really easy . In October , all the leaves which are brown and gold are falling from the trees . The second fact is that these days are the last days , when the sun 's shining with its whole power and the sun is golden too . Those are two reasons why it is called the golden season . Why do I like the autumn ? Well , especially in October , as I said , the sun is really nice and all the leaves are falling . I really like to go through the park and play with all the leaves . In my opinion , a second reason is that the temperature is really nice . It means that it is not too hot like in the summer , but it not too cold like in the winter . So for me , it is perfect ! 
In contrast to the previous decades , today 's technology is evolving and widespread computerisation is happening all around the world . Therefore , many people have suggested that books should be replaced by digital devices . In my opinion , it is a good change for the world and will provide so many benefits . The first and foremost benefit is that it enables us to do less tree -logging and deforestation . As many forests have been cut down for the production of paper , using a computer or phone will reduce the rate of logging . As a consequence , it can totally have a good impact on becoming a sustainable environment . The second advantage of using computers or tablets instead of books is that they can provide a tremendous amount of information through the internet . Moreover , not only are computers compact and portable , but also give good access to different kinds of e -books . Therefore , it is really easy and convenient for students and youths to study every subject by themselves through a digital platform . In conclusion , using computers and tablets in place of the paper -based material would be a good solution for both the environment and all students . 
Life cannot be only a meaningless fight to survive , it needs more , it needs something to bring beauty and purpose and I personally believe that music plays an important role in it . Music is one of the most popular ways to express our emotions and thoughts regarding a lot of real -life matters . In fact , music is so important for us , that every single civilization in the world has its music , with its peculiarities and expression . Music makes us feel better about life , about ourselves and even reality . Sometimes the best medicine that we could take is a good song that will enhance the betterment of our mood . In my opinion , life without music would be an error . I cannot imagine a world where music is not present in daily life , helping with emotions and giving meaning to relationships . 
I think music is something really special . Music has a long history and all the people who lived before us made music . So in my opinion , music is one of the most important things in life . It makes us feel better when we are in a bad mood , or when we are bored , music helps us to calm down . There are a lot of other reasons why music is good for us , but I think these are the most i m facts . In our lives , we often listen to music . Scientists say that we listen to music about five hours a day . Speaking for me , I would say that I listen to music about one or two hours a day . Especially in films , in ads or in podcasts , it 's really important to have some music in the background . Life without music would be boring and quiet . It would make us unhappy , depressed and we would not feel balanced . In my view , music is one of the most important things in life . 
I certainly think that doing some volunteer work is really good for society in general . Everyone should spend a part of life doing that . On the other hand , I do not think doing volunteer work is something I should receive graduating for . I think when you graduate , it is important to focus on your knowledge or your work . Doing your own project or things like that are more important for graduates than being a volunteer . Being a volunteer is really good because you help the people or some company and that 's a really generous job . However , you have to devote your time to it and when you study hard , it is not that easy . Time is fundamental for studying and doing your work at school . As you have to do homework , write essays , learn for passing a test , study to get into another school , you do not have much time . And the year of graduating might be a bit stressful . In conclusion , I think that completing a certain amount of volunteer work should not be a requirement to graduate . And that is because it takes your time to really focus on graduating itself . 
People are divided in the purpose of information resources . Some people think books should be taken over by electronic devices , such as notepads and gadgets , while others consider them as valuable items to tell the era or culture of the time when they were published . In my opinion , the existence of books will be preserved from now on . It is obvious that technology plays a significant role in our life . With the advancement of technology , it has become possible to connect people and their culture and in business , make communication easier and faster . In other words , it would not be possible for human beings to live a day without technology . On the other hand , there has been a great variety of things , even though they are no longer the latest . One of those representatives could be books . Not to mention , books provide immeasurable benefits for the young generation to the elderly . For example , some people will remember that their parents read different varieties of books when they were little or younger . It can be said that reading various kinds of books can lead to raising not only the imagination , but also communication skills . Therefore , thousands of works have been published all over the world . In conclusion , although the power of technology is indubitable , books produce a great deal of merits for our community . I strongly believe that books play a significant role in this modern society . 
