Dear head or member of the town council , About your policy about banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants , I think it is not wise to make this legal . I do not know why you think banning the use of mobile phones because I do not see the reason in the letter you gave me . If you write the reason on it , I still think it is still not good to ban . It goes against our rights I think because if we are not using our mobiles in an illegal way we can use them wherever we want and you have no right to ban us from doing so . I encourage you to reconsider your policy , or if you need to show us why this thing came to your mind , you need to tell us more about what the problem that you have with using mobiles on public transport and in shops and restaurants is . In my opinion , I think you need to provide Wi Fi for free in public places , not banning them to use our phone . I am still waiting for and I think your think you aspect will need to be worth it for me to consider your point about your policy . If you do not have more information to give to us , I will consider your policy is against our rights and I think you need to reconsider your dictator policy . If you do not reconsider , I think we ca not accept your new policy and I will do whatever it takes to stop you to public this . 
Music is very important for our mental health . Music makes us feel calm and relaxed . So we need to listen to music in our daily life , so music is essential for a human being . " A life without music will be like not having a brain in our body . " According to doctors and psychologists , music has many benefits , like music boots our brain and mental health . Music releases a huge amount of dopamine , also called the feel -good hormone . Music is also good for motivation . When we listen to music , our motivation will be at a high level . We need to listen to music in the morning . It is very beneficial for boosting mental health and also avoiding depression . Nowadays , many young stars suffer from depression . So we need to avoid depression for good mental health . So be calm and listen to music . It can change your life . Thank you . 
Music is an important tool to conduct life better . This art expression usually have action in all people , independent of what they want . The contemporary normal life and routine deep every all people in stressful acts where it is easy to be far away from the good feelings that music can wake up to again . Songs , singles and chords are artistic expressions that have a strong relationship with all people . Hearing is an involuntary process and it is impossible in most moments to choose what to listen to . On the other hand , it is very accessible , because we do not need expensive tools to use it and sometimes it is available in parks and streets . Music is the most popular cultural activity . Music helps to connect with good vibes through the chords and songs . In routine life , it can help to reflect on actions and up to political situations , economics and social problems , with words that wake up ideas . Music is a very important cultural activity that supports humankind active . A life without music would be with less colours and without rhythm . 
