Music I like listening to music very much . Every day I listen to music , when I have a bath , have breakfast , do sport ... Music makes me feel better . There are different kinds of music and there are people who like only one or two kinds of music , but there are other people who like all kinds of music . When you listen to music , you feel different senses . There is music that makes you feel happy , sad , melancholy or could move your legs . In different moments of our life , when we celebrate things , we look for a kind of music for this moment , because the music helps us in that time . Music is a natural manner in our life . There is music when birds sing , when you walk in a forest , listen to the river , the air , etc ... Music is life and must go on . I hope you agree with me . 
If I were asked about my life expectancy , preferring to have a 100 -year and calm life or have a shorter lifespan but with much more fatigue , frankly , I would rather take the first one , having a long life and living as cool as a cucumber . There are two main reasons corresponding to family and the individual . To begin with the first reason , I am convinced that the ultimate journey of each person is to build a beautiful family . Furthermore , spending more time taking deliberate care of our children as human beings is also considered a magnificent habit of a human being , thus , the more time we have , the more care we give to our children and the more joyfulness we gain in return . Additionally , if I am blessed to live until that age , I will hold my spouse 's hand , take a stroll in our garden , evoke our good old days and thank her for her sacrifices for our family . Moreover , I can imagine the distinction between living a long calm life and a short intense one . From my perspective , I presume this is about the grief of passing away too soon to see our children grow up , or even worse , witnessing our beloved ones struggle lonely for the family livelihood . If I were in this circumstance , I would not forgive myself because of my impulsive incidence . Importantly , I prefer a long lifespan coinciding with being patient as this is my temperament , influencing others to seek a meaningful life and , literally , encourage society to be better . 
In modern society , the passive lifestyle has reached its peak popularity . There are various reasons for that . For instance , long work hours at sedentary jobs and addiction to technology , such as smartphones and TV . As a result , many believe that mandatory exercise thrice a week must be introduced in educational establishments , including both schools and universities . And while I do agree that people should be more physically active , I am opposed to the idea of doing it forcefully . To begin , it is obvious that most of the children and youth prefer to watch a TV or play a video game in their spare time , rather than spend it outside playing with peers or merely taking a walk . Consequences of such decisions include obesity and related illnesses . Thus , physical activity is needed in order to reduce health problems and maintain a healthy lifestyle . Moreover , according to various studies , exercising multiple times a week decreases the chance of developing diseases like diabetes , blood pressure , as well as a cardiovascular conditions . Furthermore , it is stated that being active improves psychological health and prevents stress and depression . It is also believed that playing sports helps to relax mentally . Therefore , it increases study performance . However , I strongly disagree that exercising must be obligatory due to the following reasons . First and foremost , making anything compulsory decreases pupils ’ and students ’ interest in participating in it , as it is accepted that young people see such actions as a limitation of their free will . Hence , their motivation plunges . Secondly , during PE lessons , teachers compare students ’ accomplishments with each other , rather than comparing their results individually . Being set against others , who might have a better physical training background , could negatively affect an individual ’s self -confidence and lead to mental disorders , such as stress , depression and body dysphoria . In the final analysis , I believe that being physically active is essential in order to maintain a healthy lifestyle . Although , I do not agree that PE lessons must be compulsory . From my point of view , exercising and playing sports give better results when individuals themselves show interest in participating . 
The majority of people have a belief that we will always be telling the truth in our society . In my opinion , we can skip telling the truth to others to have good communication with them . Unfortunately , there are both pros and cons to both statements . In this essay , I will illustrate with relevant examples to elaborate further . To be honest , it is not easy to tell the facts all the time in society . While speaking genuinely , you may face struggles at initial phases . But , in the future , you will have a better relationship with each of us . In addition , you never feel any guilt inside when you are honest . Furthermore , people will also appreciate your loyalty . For example , you have to be truthful to all my friends and family , which built trust in their hearts , because you are with them for your whole life . Even though it hurts you , you will be loyal to them . However , telling the truth is going to be risky on some occasions . Certainly , we have to lie to escape from critical situations . Moreover , to make others happy , you will tell lies in certain situations . For instance , an office is not the safest environment to speak facts all the time . It builds a negative impression on staff , which effects badly on their work . At certain times , you have to skip to have healthy and prosper interactions with all your colleagues . In conclusion , I would like to say that we have to speak truth with our well -wishers such as friends , relatives , etc . At the same time , you can tell lies to strangers . At the end of the day , you have to maintain good and healthy relationships with each and every one . 
I believe that young people should not be forced to do sports activities , although it 's healthy and necessary for them . These days , people , especially young people , are not doing sports activities anymore because now their lifestyle is sedentary . Lifestyles have changed a lot in the last few decades . Young people are not interested anymore in sports . They 'd rather use their devices such as mobile phones and computers than go outside and play football or basketball . Teens need to play sports because they are developing and this would help them develop more healthily . It has been shown that teens who do sports at least 3 times a week develop more healthily and happily . In this period of time , teens start developing their muscles and doing sports is going to help them to be more muscular . Sports could help children develop their social skills and be able to make friends . Socialising is necessary for the mental health of children . These days , children have forgotten to socialise because electronic devices stole their attention and time . Indeed , the times have changed , but children must not forget about sports and socialising . Indeed , it 's very important for young people to do sports , but they should not be forced because they are going to lose their interest in sports . Instead , children should be encouraged to do sports activities . Like advertising more in schools , organising more activities , such as football championships , basketball matches or running competitions with prizes . If we take these measures , we will be able to increase the interest in sports among young people . They would love to do sports if they will find it interesting and engaging . They are the new generation , are not they ? 
Last week I went to the biggest event in the Middle East , It was a concert event held in my country . People from all around the world had come . It was crazy . I was excited about only one artist , it was DJ Alan Walker . and he made us go crazy and jump up and down . He was covering his face as usual and a lot of the audience dressed like him . I got the chance to meet him backstage and he signed a poster for me and I took a picture with him . It was an amazing experience and I really wished that you had been there . 
The start of a school year is always fun . You reunite with your friends that you have not seen in a while . You meet your new teachers as well and most importantly , you write your goals down for the new year . In school we have several subjects . Some of them I am good at . Others need some improving . Let us take a look at them and find out my plan for the next year . I love languages , whatever the language is . It is always fun and delightful to learn languages , because it makes us able to communicate with other people in another parts of the world . But of course there are some subjects that I do not like that much , in short , they are chemistry and physics . It is not that I do not like the practical aspect of them , because it is so interesting . The problem is their theoretical aspect . I think that this aspect needs a lot of work this year . Now , my plan to achieve my goals is pretty simple . I can summarize it in two points , work smart not hard , and organize your time . 
Hi Chris , Thank you for inviting me to go to the museum with you . I 'd like to go there by underground . We can see a lot of old things in the museum . We need to bring some water and food . 
Hi Chris , We are looking forward to seeing you on Saturday . We are taking the bus , so you can meet us at the station . Be prepared to see a lot of great cars . And do not forget your corona mask . See you . Andrew 
It is crucial to go on a vacation once in a while . It helps us release the tension and stress that we all suffer from in our lives . Some of these vacations are remarkable , maybe because of the place that we went to , or maybe because we were so tense back then and the vacation was necessary for us . Today I am writing about one of these delightful vacations . Two years ago , I went to Spain at Christmas . This holiday was the best one I have ever had . I went to Valencia and it is a beautiful city on the coast of the Mediterranean Sea . The most amazing thing about Valencia is the mixture between the past and the present . We saw monuments that belonged to the period of Muslim rule . I visited the Mestalla Stadium as well . This stadium belongs to Valencia Football Club , which I am a huge fan of . This visit was the highlight of my holiday . This was the best holiday I have ever had for two reasons . First of all , because I love the city . Second of all , because I was drowned in work that year and I needed a holiday like that to relax . 
We went to Shanghai Wild Animal zoo , it is a nice place to look at nice animals . I went to the tiger area first . The tigers were very strong and they were very lively . They were not like the other tigers in the normal zoos , it was not just that they sleep in a big area . Then , I went to the monkey area . The monkeys were very naughty . They were playing games in the playing area , and sometimes they played jokes on the other . I saw a lot of animals and that is the reason that I enjoyed the trip . 
Dear Frank , I have one favorite movie , the name of which is ' Transformers ' . The movie has three more sequels . I would like to watch all of them on the same day . Each movie is four hours long ; I would need a full day to watch them all . The movie is an action one with cyber robots , and the cars transform into giant robots . The robots travel through space looking for the origins of where they come from . Well , I think you will like those movies , you can use one weekend to watch them . 
Health is the most important thing in our lives . If our health is poor , then we will not be able to enjoy life anymore . Many wealthy people had untreatable diseases and died . Their money could not help them . Exercise is a huge part of healthy living . It is crucial to do sports on a daily basis , or at least on a weekly basis . Sport is vital for our bodies in so many ways . But , is exercise the only thing that we should do ? The answer is , absolutely not . Sport is essential , but it is not enough . Cutting unhealthy habits might be more important than exercise . Also , eating healthy food is critical . The worst unhealthy habit ever is smoking . The problem is that it does not just affect the people who smoke . It also affects their surroundings . It is proven that smoking kills millions of people every year , so we have to cut it out of our lives . Healthy food is necessary to keep our bodies and minds healthy . It includes fruits , vegetables and grains . Eating healthy food also means that we should not consume junk food a lot . 
Learning to play instruments can be a wise way to spend your time - it improves memory and exercises your brain to focus better . Studying music , combined with testing your abilities to play , have quite a few positive outcomes . To start with , the majority of students like to complain about the lack of enthusiasm and action in schools , as well as there being no place to expand your creativity . What could be a better place than a music class ? Music itself has power to form new passions or even relationships . Studies have shown that listening and playing have amazingly surprising impacts on one 's brain . In a music class , when you meet new people and share your interests , you cannot only make new friends , but also develop a better understanding of how sound works . It can be useful for physics students ! Moreover , having a music class in between other lessons can make you feel more focused after . After all , music class should be about discovering new genres , artists and instruments , which is not only developing for a brain , but also relaxing . With a more stable and quiet state of mind , students are proven to perform in other classes much better . Thirdly , learning to play new instruments can make one uncover new passions , which , in the future , can result in finding a new job or just impressing potential partners with one 's abilities . All in all , I think music classes are a perfect opportunity to try something new and come upon people sharing similar interests . Nonetheless , I understand how some of the students are against it , arguing they already do not have enough time for basic classes . My opinion is that the classes should be extracurricular , to actually gather people who want to learn new skills . 
Unlike traveling in the past , it is easy to travel today in our modern world . There are many kinds of vehicles , cars , airplanes , ships and trains . All of these have made our life easier , but , is that all ? In my book , I see the future travelling as different in lots of aspects . I think that the vehicles will be safer and faster . These two things are the most important when talking about vehicles . Safety comes first and speed comes second . I also think that the shapes of the vehicles will be different too . The purpose of these changes will be to make them more comfortable and safer . I tend to believe that the roads will be different as well . I cannot imagine the changes that are going to happen to the roads , but I do not think they will be the same . As there are changes , there are also some things that will stay the same . I assume that the kind of vehicles will not change , but the changes will affect the vehicles themselves . 
Hi Leyla , I 'm sorry I could not go to your birthday party . What ’s up ? Was everything , OK ? What happened at the party ? Did you see anything that you liked ? By the way , I would like to invite you to the theater next weekend , there will be three plays , one about Shakespeare , another about T . S . Eliot and finally , a Star Trek movie . If you want to pick the play , which one do you prefer ? See you soon . 
Music could represent many things , depending upon who is listening to it . For some people , music represents a way of expressing ideas , feelings and culture . To others , it is a means of entertainment , or could even represent a career . Also , music can be a way of life , and it involves many other jobs and activities behind that are complemented with music . So yes , music is definitely important . It makes us feel energized , relaxed , excited , even sad sometimes . As history shows , music is related to some of the most important events , like protests , war , a way of intimidating your enemies . Music is one of the most effective ways of communicating and without it , probably , the whole world would behave and express itself so differently . Last , think about memorable moments that you have had in your life . Probably , for a few of them , music was part of them . 
Dear Chris , How are you doing ? I hope you and your family are doing well . Welcome to Thailand in advance . I would like to take you and your family to the local museum next Saturday . On Saturday morning , I will pick you and your family up at the airport in my car and then we will come to the local museum together . The reason why I am taking you to visit the local museum is because there it 's point of heritage in Thailand and you can see antiques such as pottery . And on that day , you will need to bring your camera to take some photos and a notebook in which to write what the interesting things were there . I am looking forward to meeting you soon . Best regards , Ainee 
Given the unhealthy lifestyle of students and importance of exercise , I agree with the idea that students are forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . Firstly , many students these days do not do sports activities actively . While a few decades ago , it was ordinary for students to spend their free time doing sports as there were not many other options . However , with the emergence of technology , many young people started to play games and be on social media rather than moving their body to do sports . This change in youth 's attitude toward sports is certainly not desirable as doing sports while they are young is extremely important to stay healthy and live longer . Young ages are biologically more suitable for making their body strong as it is when body cells are more actively proliferated . When people reach a certain age , making numerous cells would be no longer possible and thus start to . Therefore , it is critical for people to build a strong body while they are young so that they can retain the good condition for longer . Considering how students are doing sports activities less and less , forcing them to participate in sports would be a great measure for the sake of students . Another point is that doing sports would be a good opportunity for students to build a strong bond with each other . Many sports require people to team up and compete with against the other teams . These characteristics make students learn about the importance of cooperation because otherwise they would not be able to win the game . In addition , since team members have to be cooperative , even if the team members were strangers to each other , they would eventually be able to be friends . Moreover , doing sports could affect other aspects of students ' lives positively . It is known that by doing exercise , people feel more refreshed and they can focus on studying more than when they did not . Thus , an overall improvement , including physical and mental , could be well estimated . 
I believe that speaking English has always been important , because it is the way that you have to communicate with other people . Speaking English is as important as it was in the past and I believe that it will never change . The difference now and in the past is that before it was more difficult , because you did not have all the tools that you have now and you had to look for the way you had to learn English . Before , you did not have all the applications that you have now . For example , you have several tools that can help you to study the structure and grammar tenses in English and you also have another application that help you to communicate with other people and that can help you to practice your pronunciation . Today you can find a web page on the internet where they help you to practice your listening with a podcast . You have a lot of content in English that will help you in all the processes that you need for learning English . But there are many people that do not want to learn English , because they think that all the tools that we have now are enough to communicate and it is not true at all , because all the tools can help you in a specific moment , but not in all cases . 
Hi brother , I am writing to you about my favorite film . This is Cast Away with the actor Tom Hank . I like this movie because it is very coincident with my experience . Love vanishes , the truth disappears , but life goes on and carries on with new meaning . Apparently , it is a romantic movie , but it is not . I am sure you will like it . 
Absolutely we need music for our life . I ca not imagine what will happen without music some days . For sure , music is for everyone , for every single age and its reputation is well -known everywhere on the earth . Music for sadness , music for happiness , music for studying , music for motivation ... there are lots of kinds of music . I usually listen to music about 3-4 times in my typical day . First is when I wake up to make up my mind after a long night . In my opinion , chill music is the best one for these moments , its slow melody is going to help you with more focus . The second time in on my commute . I just want to listen to cancel the noise in the street that could make you stressed . The third time is when I do a workout at the gym . Music gives me lots of motivation for lifting . And the last one , before going to sleep , a little ballad music makes me feel better after a long day . Conclusion , music is an important thing in life . 
Hi Chris ! I will travel to the museum by bus , then by taxi . You can see pictures in the museum and famous sculptures . My favourite picture is Las Meninas and the paintings of Goya . You need to send for your ticket on the web . Best regards , Bye , 
We will go to the museum by bus . We can see a lot of laboratory equipment that scientists made . The only thing you need to bring is you yourself . 
Hi Andy , How are you ? I went to a music concert last week . It was the concert of my daughter 's piano school . I was a camerawoman for the concert , so I went there early in the morning . That was great , the instructor 's performance and kids were so cute . My daughter played well , but she fell down after the performance . I was surprised , but she did not cry , so I gave her a great cheer . If you want to listen to the concert , I will give you a DVD . I recommend that the playing of the senior students was so good . Please let me know how you feel . See you next week . Kuroneko 
Considering the globalization of the world , learning to speak a foreign language is more important than ever before . Firstly , most international business is done in the global language , namely English . With the help of technology and transportation , the market has now expanded from the nation to the world , which means that there are greater needs for people to be able to communicate with those of foreign countries . Since language is the only means for people to convey their thoughts , learning a foreign language is significant in order to succeed in business . Another point is that more cooperation with other nations is needed to solve the global issues . Currently , the world is faced with global warming , overpopulation and numerous other problems . These are grave enough to threaten the whole planet and all living creatures . To deal with such immense issues , nations should have constructive conversations , which can be possible with the smooth understanding available with a common language . Given that immediate actions for the planet are necessary , the necessity to learn new language to discuss the solution is higher than in the past . Overall , the importance of learning a foreign language is higher than in the past . 
Medicine is a noble specialization , it needs considerate , kind , and nice people to work within , but they are also humans like all of us , and they need to earn money . In order to implement that , they work in cities , leaving the rural areas with a limited number of doctors , causing a problem , what is the solution ? Before we dig into the solution , we should understand the reasons . It is obvious that cities are more profitable for doctors , and we can not blame them for their desire to earn money . Yes , medicine is a humanitarian job , but that does not mean that they should earn less money than everyone else . If we think about it , we can see that it is not just about doctors . Rural areas are less profitable for most of the other jobs , because there are fewer people there , which means less demand for everything . Now , what is the solution ? Actually , solving the doctor problem in rural areas is part of solving the whole rural area problem . The government should make legislation which encouraged doctors to move to rural areas . They should also give them monthly incentives as a reward for their effort in solving this problem . We cannot blame doctors for this one . It is the government 's duty to solve these kinds of problems . 
Although many people say that it is very bad for the health of children to play video games for a long time , for me , if excess is never good , today video games are a big part of the culture and the life of people . Video games will prepare the professional life of children . Rather than doing nothing , this is a better way to learn how to manage a digital environment . There are many applications in a professional life , for example to drive a crane , or an escavator , or a fighter jet . Before that , when children read a lot , nobody is afraid of this situation . Reading a book can be compared to this activity of video games . There is just one limit , the mental health of children when they do too much of something . Life must be balanced with other activities , like outdoor activities like jogging or football . For me , you must encourage children to be the best in video games . 
Hi Leyla , I 'm so sorry , I could not go to your party . As you know , my sister was sick on the day of your party . I needed to be in my home to take care of her . But I 'm interested in the events at your party , what happened ? I heard our friends made a lot of mess in your living room . However , I 'm writing to you to invite you to go out with me next weekend , what do you think ? 
The shape and design of our work spaces is critical . It is proven that those two things affect our productivity and psychological status at work . Now , some offices have cubicles , which are an enclosed workstation , while other offices work in open work spaces . Which is better ? I believe that the worst design for an office ever is the one including cubicles . Cubicles make the employees feel like they are arrested and their cubicle is their own cell . When the employee feels this way , you cannot expect him to do a superb job . In order to make your employee more productive and concentrated , you should make him feel like he still has some of his freedom . Even though he has to work seven or eight hours per day . I think it is obvious that I do not prefer enclosed workstations . Instead , I love open ones , because it is going to give the employee a better feeling about his job , rather than him thinking of it as a jail . So within the design of our offices , we should send a message to our employees that this place is theirs , this feeling could help them be more productive and invested in their jobs . 
There are different positions of people about animals in zoos . For me , that is a difficult problem between the well -being of animals and the need for people to better know animals . All people can be against the freedom of animals and you must find a balance to give an animal a good quality of life when they are in a zoo . Could you imagine a zoo with a big area where the animals can be like in the wild forest ? I think all the discussions about zoos and the freedom of animals become less important if the zoos have adapted their conditions to keep the animals happy living in this place . This condition will be the only solution to allow us to reconcile the animal 's life and the need for people to discover these different animals near their home . I propose that all zoos be adapted for each animal they want to keep . 
Hi Rie , Yes , I am going to your house . I will go on my bike . My house is next to yours . I like to eat pasta . Italian food is very good . I will see you soon . 
Hi Leyla , I 'm grateful to you for the invitation . I was not at my house yesterday ; I was working . I even arrived home early to my house , but I was tired . What happened in the party ? I heard someone had a fight in the party with Maria , because she drank a lot of alcohol . Her brother was yelling at her , is that true ? I invite you next weekend to go to a bar to drink something and you can talk to me about all the details from the party . 
I believe that there are activities a person should do at least once in their life . Public speaking , painting a wall , conquering a fear , and volunteering . Why volunteering ? I read about some high schools which require the student to complete a certain amount of volunteering time in order to graduate . I really respect and love this idea , and I think I am going to send these schools a letter thanking them for this superb gesture . Volunteering is the best activity a person can do when they are young . It helps them appreciate the value of time . Today , most of the young people spend an enormous portion of their time on social media , which is a total waste of time . When they volunteer , they will understand that their time could be spent on more beneficial activities . Volunteering , also , can change their thoughts about several subjects . That happened to me personally , volunteering helped me see the world in a more merciful way . A complaint must arise from the some students who do not want to volunteer , what they did not think about is that going to school is a privilege , because not everyone can afford it , so they are lucky enough to be at school . And I assume that if they thought about it for a while , they would not reject it anymore . 
Offices vary from each other mostly with designs and atmosphere surrouding the designs and atmosphere surrounding the place . Do these two have any connection ? Apparently , yes ! People are herd animals - work is more effective in groups or pairs . An open space in the office has many benefits , one of them being people learn to be more cooperative and trustworthy . Coworkers can get to know each other better , which will benefit them in the future . While working on important projects , workers have to join forces and brainstorm together . Without previous socialization with one another , the work would not be effective . No walls in the office is a fantastic idea from a psychological view , too . Workers do not feel confined by the small , almost claustrophobic cubicles . It leads to a betterment of the mental health and overall well -being of the employees . Interacting with others - from consulting and analyzing to telling jokes and spending time together - results only in positive effects . Happy employees equal quality work - that is why it is important to remember the company 's building design . 
Many people like to study near their home to see their family each evening . For me , I prefer living abroad to discover new people and areas . The second choice is very difficult , because you need to change your habits . That is also the goal of studying , to have occasion to do different new things and find new situations . I 'm definitely going to study abroad , because you learn in a new situation . That 's not something abstract , but very practical and specific . With this way of studying , you memorize situations and languages easily . You have also more occasions to meet interesting and open -minded people , because these types of people like people different from others . In general , these people are very courageous to be able to meet people from different countries . Often , these people have another way of thinking , sometimes have another color of skin , another religion and customs . The big advantage to studying abroad is beginning to think differently , to be able to travel and live all over the world . You will become a world citizen . 
Hi Ana , How are you ? Yes , I have been studying English for a few months . Well , I 've been studying English for several reasons . First of all , I want to be able to read several academic articles because my job , so another language will help me a lot . And the principal reason is that I wish I could go to another country to study . 
Nowadays , people have access to a lot of information . The variety of human preferences is huge and vast . In my opinion , every person is unique , so everyone could have different options regarding their life . I tend to think that a calm and long life is my desire . On the one hand , the person 's behavior means a lot to their type of life . In general , people have had their actions made depending on their attitude . I would like to argue that it is crucial to enjoy every moment . Furthermore , the most relevant aspect is to choose your own lifestyle . If it comes to my feelings , I will say that I appreciate a calm life because of my character . If you have an outgoing personality , you will probably tend to choose a more intense life . On the other hand , as far as I am concerned , in general , humans wish for a long life . I would like to argue that the longevity of life does not matter in a choice related to life intensity . If I aspire to a peaceful and harmonious life , I will have this preference despite its durability . Moreover , people have their activities felt in a different way . As far as I know , the more intense an action is , the happier you are . Nevertheless , a calm and long life could offer numerous pleasant activities which can be equal to a short , but deep and energetic life . In conclusion , human preferences could be so different . A long and calm life can always be the best choice because you have the opportunity to make many extraordinary memories in such a lengthy and relaxed life . 
I know one specific thing , birthdays in my country , Brasil , are happier than in yours . They are totally different . We sing a lot , scream , we have a party , yeah , in a short time , we can do this . We celebrate like it is the last birthday we will ever have . We have a barbecue with a lot of beer , each person takes one thing , beer or it can be meat or sausage , among other things . 
It is never acceptable to tell a lie . Why do we keep telling lies anyway ? It 's a terrible thing to do and it 's a terrible precept to live by . It 's important to always tell the truth , always be honest with yourself and with others . When a person lies , they first of all are lying to themselves and this is a terrible mistake . For example , when I first lied to my mom about what I was feeling , I was not able to make a connection with her . She could not help me with my mental health issues , so I kept lying , but at the end of the day , that was killing me inside because it only kept us apart . Furthermore , it 's not a good choice to lie and , in some countries , it is a crime punished by law . With lies , you can destroy people 's lives and this will come back to you way stronger . We never like it when people lie to us , a fake person is never welcome in our environment and whenever that happens we feel betrayed and that person is not seen as a good person at all . In addition , honesty is an important value that we should keep in our thoughts and reflect about our attitudes towards others and the consequences of our lies , because it causes serious damage and no one likes it . 
Music is important for everybody , not only for pleasure , but also for entertainment . Everyone has to struggle in their lives . At that time , they need to reduce their stress . There are many ways to be relaxed . Among them , listening to music is one of the best ways to relax or to boost our mind . Moreover , we can have different ideas , different feelings , different rhythms and different creativity by listening to music . It makes us feel happy and softens our heart too . Without music , probably life would be boring or not interesting at all . In addition , there would be no place for composers or singers to express their feelings . In my point of view , music is essential for everyone . It supports us to be happy , to be refreshed , to get the energy for our life , now and forever . 
When I have free time , I spend it with my family . Together we play a game or cards . Usually I have time on Fridays . 
Approximately , all of us hear music on a daily basis , and everyone has their own taste . The common thing is that music helps us get through the day , and although some music might make us sad and a little down , it does help us in one way or another . When I was a student , our school had a music class in it . We all liked it , because it was not the kind of class that needed concentration , it was a little rest in our busy day . Back then , we thought that every school teaches music ; later we found out that it is not true . So the question that pops into our head would be : Is it important to teach music in schools ? I believe in the importance of teaching music in schools , but it should be an option for the students , because not all of them are interested , like they are not all interested in physics or math . When I was a student , music class was mandatory , so I did not have the chance to take it or leave it . I might not be interested in music , but in my book , I think it is important for students to have the opportunity of learning music . Music is a delightful form of art , and it is important to give the interested children a chance to learn it . 
Hi , What do you think about going to my house today , at 4 pm ? If you bring your video game , we 'll play it the whole afternoon . To come to my house , you should take the number 4 bus at the Pinhais 's Terminal . 
Hi Sam , I know you 're coming to my house tomorrow evening , that 's great . Please , come around nine p.m . , and do not forget to bring a pizza . Remember you can get to my house if you take the bus number A2 and get off at the mall station . 
Dear Sam , Come to my house at 3:00 pm . I will arrive at my house at 11:00 am . I will make a meal . Could you bring rice and two tomatoes for the salad ? My house is near the church on the street called Lis Marinho Street . Come by car , I have a garage and you can put your car in it . 
Hi Sam , I was delighted when I heard you will be visiting my house . I will be at home the whole day tomorrow . By the way , what time will you arrive here ? If I know the time exactly , I 'll come and pick you up at the airport . When you come , you need to bring sunglasses , sun cream and loosing clothes because the weather is really hot here . You can get to my house by taxi . I hope you will have a great time here . See you soon . Susan 
Hi Sam , I cannot wait to see you tomorrow . Could you arrive at 6pm ? If it is possible , could you also bring some wine ? My house is the one on the corner and it is the only one with a red door , so it will be easy to find it . See you , Izabela 
When we grow up , we start taking care of ourselves . We cannot stay under the umbrella of Mom and Dad forever , and that is the normal thing to do . It is a sign of maturity . While studying at university , some students move away and live independently in different cities away from their parents . While others study in their hometowns and stay with their families . So , which is better ? In my book , I think the best idea is to move away during college time . Yes , it may be hard at first , but that is an experience that will teach you how to live without someone looking out for you all the time . You are on your own , you will learn to cook , clean , do the dishes , and all of these tasks that you probably would not know how to do before . It can also teach you financial independence , but it depends on how you earn money . If you get it from your parents , then you will learn a little . But if you earn it working yourself , then you will be more flexible about dealing with money and such . The experience of living on your own during college is important and helpful . You should stay away from drugs and crazy things , but other than that , I advise you to go for it . 
Hi Sam ! How is it going ? I ca not wait to see you tomorrow ! I was thinking that you could come to my house around five o 'clock and you could bring something for us to eat while we are watching a movie or something . What do you think about it ? My mum is going to pick you up and take you to my house . See you ! 
Dear Sam , First of all , I am glad that you are coming to visit me tomorrow . Feel free to come any time after 5pm , and do not worry about food , just bring some beers . The best way to reach my house is by bus , just get the line 37 . Kind regards , Tego Dago 
Hi Sam ! I ca not wait to see you again ! I 'm getting home at 7:00 p.m . so I prefer you to arrive a half hour after me please , so that you would give me time to prepare the snacks . By the way , could you stop by the store and bring a soda ? Remember that you have to take the second street after the mall and down that street is my house . See you tomorrow ! 
Hi Sam , You can come to my house after 3 pm . You can bring your video tapes or some snacks . And just to be sure , my house is just beside the supermarket on Xing -Yi Road . See you , Mazynga 
I 'm curious and I like to learn a lot of things , but my favorite subject that interests me is networking with social media . This year I would like to improve my knowledge in this field . My goal is to reach a high level of mastering digital networking and become a reference in this area . I would like to use this competency to build a community in a natural bio product like soap . As I 'm a soap maker , I have very good knowledge of the product and how you make a well -made bio soap . In a second stage , I will need to create an e -commerce platform where I would be able to sell products to my community . To be able to do that , I 'm planning to study web -marketing for six weeks at Growth Tribe school . All the lessons are online . Thanks to this , I will be very focused on my goal during this time . I hope I will achieve this project in March 2022 . That is a great challenge for the second part of my life before retirement . 
Music is universal and it has some common language for all of us . Even if we do not know the words or it is written in another foreign language , its melody catches us , making us feel some emotions . I think music is another feature in our lives . Everybody has different music tastes and when they go through some situations , music will always be there for them . When they are happy , they play joyful music and have fun , sometimes with themselves and sometimes they share this happiness with their close ones . When they hurt , or their heart is broken , they listen to music because it has some healing effects . Even in medical care , sometimes doctors try music as a treatment for their patient 's psychology . To conclude , I do not know what life would be like without music , because I have never had the experience , but I assume it could be boring and a big blank in our lives . 
Most young students do not work out . That is why most universities want to force their students to work out at least 3 times a week . Universities want to make sports a must -do activity at school and if you do not do sport 3 times a week , you have to do the year over . I think young students should work out at least 1 time a week . However , I do think the rule of doing the year over goes to far . Even though working out is good for you physical and mental . That is why universities should make sport obligatory 2 times a week . Firstly , because sports are good for your physical and mental . You get in better shape and feel better . You also find more peace and can focus better at school , but also at home . Secondly , it should be obligatory 2 times a week , owing to all the students who struggle with their weight . It would be a great opportunity for them to learn about their weight and do something about it if they want to . If working out is an obligation , there should also be a class to learn about food and how your body responds to food and sports . However , I do think making sport an obligation is for some students too much . Because nobody knows if 3 extra classes every week is something that is realistic . Since not everyone has a great home situation , some students have to work after school or have to help with cleaning at school . So these students could get overworked . All things considered , making sports an obligation would be a great idea to make students feel better . But some students will get overworked and tired , because they have other things to do after school which takes a lot of energy . 
