I think that music is an important part of our lives , because through music , we can get joy and connect with other people . Music can also make you happy . For example , when you have had a hard day at work , you can listen to music and maybe it will cheer you up . Music is also socially important , because people sing songs together and go to concerts together , which improves their relationships . If there was not any music in the world , I think the world would be a lot more boring , because music is an exciting thing and if you are really good at it , you could also make it your job , how fun is that ! Without music , a lot of people would lose their hobby and their passion . Music is also a big economic thing , because a lot of money is put into the music industry , so that is also an important thing about music . So what I think is that music is important for our lives and our mental health . 
Although people consider travel as an action of going from one point to another point , I prefer to consider travel as an experience that begins from a point and continues between to reach the other point . For me , in the future , we will rediscover all of the parts of travelling between these two points . Why ? Because with the new environmental requirements , we will travel less far away than before to reduce the carbon emissions and we would find advantages in each part of this trip . For me , this behaviour will give an opportunity to discover the whole patrimony around where you live . You will see the beautiful monuments , but also the creativity of the people . This attitude will change considerably the meaning of travel . First that will promote our own culture and stop us thinking that all is better in another country . Second it will allow people to build with other people around where you live . For example , you will know there are delicious apples on the farm near your house , or do business with people you meet at a fair in your region . Travel will become more human in the future . 
