In my opinion , music has an important role in everyone 's life . First of all , there are several kinds of music and each one can have a different impact on your mind . For example , there are some songs which are made for sensitizing people , whereas other ones are made in order to lift the mood . Another key point to remember is that a particular song can be part of a special moment of someone 's life , therefore , that song has a special meaning for that person . Some research has stated that a song can really change a life , for instance , it has been proved that it can really help a person get out of a state of depression . In summary , life without music would not be as great as it is , since the rhythm and lyrics can really have a huge impact on people 's minds . 
Music is definitely important to humankind . It indicates how our lives are going from the past to present . Humans have learned to be human through music and its lyrics , for example , politics , religion , culture and love . Music is one of the crucial parts of our lives , so it plays an important role in alleviating people 's feelings when they encounter tough situations , or encourages them to show their true feelings in terms of affliction or political issues . That is the reason why that life cannot be lived without music . It there was no music , life would not be lively and people would not have imagination or creativity to create magnificent lyrics or songs . As a result , it is doubtless that knowledge or religious teaching would be difficult to convey to people . From my point of view , I could not live without music , because music always soothes my temper when I feel frustrated with my problems . Moreover , it helps me to have more concentration while I am working or reading books . 
Although many people think that school in the past was better than today , I believe the needs of people through time are different and the ways to teach people must be different . For this reason , the school of the future will be more connected and more human . Access to information will increase rapidly and the teacher 's role will need to be more interactive and based on reflection , to help students to think . This last point will be crucial , because the huge amount of information bombarding people in their everyday life must be chosen and selected to make the best choice in your private or professional life . School must teach psychology and sport as a balance in your life . The teachers must become like a coach , to prepare their students to fight against their own thoughts and to be benevolent with their colleagues , teachers and parents . Therefore , the future school must be based more on knowing how to be rather than to knowing what to do . 
I firmly believe that you should always tell the truth or at least do not lie . It is one of the rules from Jordan Peterson 's book and I have been acting upon it for a while with great results in my mental health . Of course , you ca not push it to the extremes . You should not ignore the purpose of he white lies . I still believe that children should believe that they are receiving Christmas presents from a little Jesus , and that if they misbehave , they will be taken by a devil . There is a complicated dichotomy in the case of leadership . Your people deserve the truth , but on the other hand , they should be spared from some of the deeds of your own boss . It is about the morale of the team . An extreme example may be at sea . Sailors in the middle of the ocean on their transatlantic voyage with not enough food . Should the sailors be informed about the situation or should it be kept a secret ? Is the possibility of mutiny less important than the truth ? The only hope of survival is to proceed on and hold on with maximum effort . Telling the truth is the opposite . So this is an example of when the proper solution is not telling the truth , but simply to be quiet , and with that , not telling a lie . 
