Although many people think TV is only a recreation activity , I am convinced that TV can also teach a lot of things . Because there are many TV shows with different subjects , like science , religion , literature , nature ... you have opportunities to better know these themes and be able to talk about them . These TV shows can be the basics of study in school or university and at least the first step to raising interest in a subject . With the development of TV channels , TV is also an open mind on foreign and linguistic culture . For children , that is a convenient way to learn a foreign language when they watch movies or other TV shows . Proof of that , in the north of Europe , where English TV channels are better developed than the south of Europe , people speak and write more fluently in English than the southern people . 
Music is essential in human beings ' lives , because it lets all people express and liberate their inner emotions . Music is a means of expression and can influence people 's moods , having different senses . People without music would not have a filter to express and share their feelings and thoughts in peace , because music allows people to show personal sides of themselves . Music is important because it can determine the mood in a place or the formality of an event , because depending on the music played , people can behave in one way or another . Music opens a wide range of opportunities to experience new sensations in different places and get to know people with different manners . For example , the behaviour in a concert is not the same as the behaviour in an opera . Music allows people to have those kinds of feelings and environments with their different music styles , and the best part , it is not necessary to be an expert . Life without music would not allow people to create and find a place of expression and they could not develop their creativity . To conclude , music is one of the best resources for people 's expression . 
At my work , there are both of those variants . I have an enclosed office , which I am sharing with one of my colleagues , and the rest of our teams are in another bigger office . Other teams are as a whole in one office together including their leader . In my case , there is the benefit of privacy . I can work without distress and , when I need something from my team , they are two doors away . When I need to talk with someone in confidence and privacy , I can invite them to my office and have the talk . On the other hand , there are times when we are working on a mission , and those are times when I need to work close with my team . I need to task them and , at the same time , I have to check their work . On those occasions , I wish we were together in one big office . Those days are rare , but at the same time , the most important . 
In my opinion , it is imperative . As we see , the more life modern , the more person lazy . And that has negative effects on health because of an inactive lifestyle , particularly many people do not intend to change their lifestyle unless it comes to limitattion . Therefore , I think all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week because it has many benefits to them . Sports activities have a great importance in your life . It helps you to be healthier than before you did that , drop pressure , suffer from less various health problems than . Suppose that you worked continuously for 5 days , I dare say that you feel tired . And then some people will reward themselves with a cup of tea or a cup of coffee . But they don < u00B4 > that it has a negative effect on your health like memory loss , dark eyes , etc , although it helps you to be conscious for a short time . Instead of using it , you should do exercise because it has more benefits than drink tea or coffee , such as being more alert , having flexibility , increasing performance or so on . Sometimes , doing exercise makes our create ideals . Scientific research says that a person who always does exercise rarely less from health problem than lazy person . Why should students or children do exercise 3 times per week ? Simply , children have to learn many subjects and are under pressure from their parents , their teacher or even their classmates . Therefore , they need to do it to drop them , stretch their body , relax their face , etc . On the other hand , it makes students create healthy habits , and then enjoy their lifestyle , find smiles after the stressful class time . In conclusion , sports activities are important to our lifestyle . Scientific research says that people who love sport always love themselves more than the others , and they also suffer from various problems involve to healthy too much . 
In my opinion , I think that medical doctors need other colleagues to do their job as well as they need the best equipment possible . Another reason why medical doctors want a different kinds of services to live . Whereas , this service in rural areas is enough for them . In rural areas , fewer people live than in cities . According to the experts , it 's more probable for you to need a doctor in the city than in rural areas . I think to solve this problem more people would have to live in villages and they would have more services and better equipment . Even if rural areas are far from cities , that 's not problem , because they can have one doctor for almost a hundred citizens . To sum up , the best solution , that 's to increase the population of the rural areas , will make more doctors want to live in these areas , therefore this problem will change in the future . People always choose to live in cities , but with the pandemic situation , most of them have come back to the small towns . 
In my country , Myanmar , there are only three seasons , summer , winter and the rainy season . All of them have their own beauties and signatures . And if I have to choose my favourite one , that would definitely be winter . I really hate hot days . Also , I do not like being wet all day . Therefore , winter is the only season I feel comfortable in . No matter how cool it is , I love it . Besides , both my birthday and Christmas are in winter . So I usually get many presents and this is one of the reasons why I love winter very much . Moreover , I always go hiking with my friends in winter . As we all get Christmas holiday , I can meet with all of my friends , including from other towns . And going hiking with them is always adventurous and fascinating . And the most important thing is that I met my first love in winter . And it was very sweet , although it was just a one -sided love . And for these reasons , winter has become my favourite . 
Most medical doctors want to work where they will make much more money . Why is that ? What a naive question . Of course , they want to work in the cities . They want the money and the patients . It is something different to care about a farmer who works long days and nights in fields than when your patient is a city office worker . The question of how to solve this is the proper one . I think that , for some medical doctors , the money is more important than the work and , for others , it is vice versa . So we have to focus on those who prefer money in front of easy work . On those doctors , we can focus our attention with benefits based on working away from the capital . Of course , this would not solve the problem , only the symptoms . On the other hand , I am from Czechia and , to be honest , this problem is not really important for us . Employers are obliged to pay for health insurance for all their employees and it is free for those who are not working . 
Even though it is one of the most searched and studied subjects , we can never know what is going to happen in the future , we can predict , but we can never be sure about it . Although it is unknown , people try to plan their future , and every one of us has our own preferences . Some people feel that it would be better to live a long calm life while others consider a short intense life to be more appealing , so what is better ? It is the kind of question where there is no right or wrong answer . If you asked me , I would not have a definite answer . Both of the choices are tempting , and have their own advantages and disadvantages . The first choice is tempting because it is a satisfying kind of life , you study , graduate , marry , have kids , then you probably see them entering the same cycle that you were in , except for some minor changes . Maybe it seems boring , but it is nice to be able to live calmly , and get old while watching your grandkids play and have fun . The second choice is a nice one as well . You just live twenty or thirty years , you do the things you love that cannot be long -term , then die calmly after finishing what you wanted to do . I believe that I would choose a mix of the two , even though I cannot really choose anything . Simply because fate happens . 
Hi Sam , I 'm writing this mail to invite you to my house tomorrow evening . Come as soon as possible , I 'd prefer 4 p.m . You should bring some snacks and some toys that you like . You can go by car , motorbike or bike . Hope to see you tomorrow evening . Vicky 
In my opinion , it 's a shame that they must complete some volunteer work in order to graduate . I think that all students have to do some volunteer work because they want to not only because it 's a mandatory requirement . I believe that young people today throw away a lot of time doing nothing . All day , they are connected to their smartphones or playing games , instead they could help other people or do something for the community . I hope in the future young people think that spending their time . Because it is more useful to help other people than to stay connected for hours on the Internet . Finally , I think that this high school is doing a good thing for the community to demand students complete some hours as a volunteer . I 'm sure that young people learn a lot during their time as a volunteer and they repeat the experience . 
Write and Improve is a useful site where you can improve your English skills with helpful feedback from experts . This site gives the opportunity to write reports , essays , etc . about any subject you want . After your writing work , there is a check and , after , you can see your mistakes . With the mistakes , the site gives you a mark from 1 to 5 and the level of your English knowledge ( such as B1 or B2 , for example ) . I have tried to write some essays and I really appreciate this website . It is so useful . There are tree levels , for beginner students , for intermediate and for advanced too . It 's a big opportunity to improve in a useful way your English skills and to prepare university exams . At the end , I would recommend this website to my classmates . It 's an easy way to improve and have fun with English . Sign in with your email and password and ... go to improve your English ! 
Health is important for human life . Doing exercise is one the most important things for a happy and healthy living . But there are also other important things , such as a good diet , for example . I , sadly , am not an athletic girl , but I try to keep in shape . I go running every day , weather permitting . I run and walk one hour and a half . Exercise is not the only thing that can keep me in shape . I try eating only healthy food , such as lot of vegetables and fruit , I have eliminated all junk food and all soft drinks . In my opinion , exercise helps to lose weight , but also is an economical way to clear your mind of stress . Doing exercise improves blood flow and regains some energy and calmness too . In my opinion , though doing exercise and eating well are good things from a medical point of view , losing weight for aesthetic purposes is the worst thing a person can do . 
Nowadays , television is an important part of our life . I agree with the fact that television entertains , but I have some doubts that television can also educate . Now , on television , sadly , there is only reality TV , which I call " trash TV . " In my opinion , these programmes cannot educate . There are not many documentaries that can involve young people to watch them . There are also a lot of cooking shows , which can educate people to cook , but it 's ephemeral education in comparison to culture . NA , . TV schedules ought to air more documentaries , cultural programmes . Another possibility is showing new films and not black and white films . TV schedules can also air reality TV , but not like this . I know that reality TV can raise the share , but these programmes can maybe entertain people , but I 'm sure that they cannot educate them . I prefer to watch a three -hour documentary than reality TV ! 
In my opinion , I think it 's better to move away during your university time . If you move out of your home , I 'm sure that those students will improve more than the students who are with their families at home . The reason is that you must make your own meals and go shopping every week , whereas for the other students , everything is done by their parents . The responsibility that one student needs far away his home is bigger than the other group of students . On the other hand , studying time is different when your are living out of your home , because you need to be more organized . You need to have a schedule with the all tasks that you should do every day , you need to clean your room , the kitchen and the bathroom too . It 's hard to clean all the time and you have less time to study , but you will be ready for the future . 
My favourite season of the year is summer . I love summer , because first of all there is no school , so I am free . There is no homework , no extra work , no studying . I can play computer games , I can hang out with my friends . Second , in summer I can swim in the pool or sea . When I swim in the sea or pool , I have so much fun . In addition , water is good for me . Also , I like hot and cool weather . In this weather , I need to cool down , so I swim in the sea . Third , we can go on holiday to the western cities of Turkey , for instance , Antalya , Bodrum and Muğla . We can go on cruise holidays , hotel holidays with aqua parks and hostel holidays . Also , we can go abroad . To sum up , summer makes me happy . This season is comfortable and this season is my favourite season . 
Hi Sam , What about you ? Have you forgotten our appointment ? I have not , I am really excited about it . I live outside the city . You can come by car , but I think that we spoke about taking the train . The station is Winston . I will cook your favorite pasta dish . If you want , you could bring some wine . Well , I expect your visit . 
I disagree that we should replace books with computers and tablets in schools and universities . I know that computers and tablets are very convenient and are not bulkier than books . However , students should use books , because they can check the pages bother them quickly . In addition , we can mark a colour directly on the pages and make notes on the pages of books directly . Currently , computers and tablets may do same things , but you ca not erase completely what you write in books and the books get dirty , which make some people confident because we can see study records . Other reasons , students should be more familiar with print type than digital type . My opinion is that print type expand our imagination and that 's a bigger chance after becoming an adult . Therefore , books have more advantages than disadvantages and I recommend that students should use books in schools and universities . 
