Although people think paper books wo not be replaced by e -books , I believe readers will be sharing between both of them , because they are two different experiences . A paper book is a pleasure to touch the paper and feel its grain and its smell . An e -book is very practical , you can take more than thousand books with you , you can copy and paste expressions and sentences to make a presentation , you can show this book during a meeting ... That is very convenient and cheap . But there is also a disadvantage . You need to have electricity when your battery is flat . You do not have all books in digital format . In fact , when you are relaxed and in your library , you like to look for books and take time finding them . Often it is less tiring to read a paper book . During this time , you usually read a paper book , but when you are at your office , you prefer to use digital ones , because they are very practical . I think e -books must be easier for students to use for preparing lessons , but when they are researching any information from the past , the paper book will be unavoidable . 
Are you musical ? Have you ever thought about how important music is for most people worldwide ? How often they listen to it or why they listen to it ? There are so many moments in life in which music is our sole companion . For example , when we travel by car . However , there are also many others when we enjoy music together with our friends , our family or even unknown people at live events , such as concerts . Music is important to help us pass the time while we wait for something , to cheer us up when we are a little bit down or to celebrate when we have a good reason . The sound we hear and the lyrics of the songs have the power to make us change our mood , to feel lively and energetic , or to calm us down . Personally , I ca not imagine the world without music . I 'd be like a forest with nothing but bare trees . 
In my opinion , studying music should be an obligation in all schools . And I have this opinion because music is not only an art , but also a way to improve the neural connections of the brain . There are multiples studies and research which demonstrate this . All around the world , psychologists , doctors , musicians and several other professionals get to these same results : studying music is one of the best things to raise the brain 's capacity . Musicians also have the possibility to socialize with people . It is very difficult to find someone who does not like some kind of music . Whatever the style of music is , there is always somebody singing a song . I imagine that music , in fact , is something really good for the brain and for the mind . And , the best of all : music is a kind of art which almost everybody may learn since kindness . Children almost always like music , be it singing it or hearing it . Or simply appreciating it . It 's for all this that I agree with the idea of applying music for all students , whatever their level of learning at school . In my city , for example , almost all the school already inserted this subject into their curriculum . I am sure that it only has the goal of improving several aspects of the students ' lives . I had the happiness of learning music when I was a child . In my school , those classes began when I was 10 years old . Since I started to stay involved with these subjects , I never forget about how good it was for my whole life ! And since I discovered the amazing world of music , I never let it go anymore ! My suggestion about this essay is : Dear teachers ! ! For sure , if you can do that , all of you will contribute a lot with the complete mental development of many people in the world ! 
I would like to present , in this essay , the things that I do in my free time . I work in a school , I am a teacher , so I am always around children , that is to say , the level of noise is quite high . I try to spend my free time with my friends , who are less noisy . My free time is limited to weekends and vacations , and in that time I like to go out , read , go to the cinema or have a coffee while sharing a good conversation . 
