Most of the people work for the money . If there is a chance to have a higher income when doing the same things , then who would give it up ? Nowadays , most medical doctors choose to work in cities rather than work in rural areas which do not have enough doctors . It is all because of the difference in incomes . As we can see , some people who live in rural areas donu2019 t have enough sources of medical . When they need to go to the doctor , they have to go a long distance , that is okay when it is not urgent . But what about the urgent times ? We cannot predict all accidents , and many people die because they cannot get their treatment immediately . After saying that much , what is the solution for this problem ? Someone might say that governments can distribute more funds to the hospitals which open up in rural areas . But I think that does not make sense , the people who live there are absolutely not as many as the people who live in cities . If the government distributes more funds , that might be not fair to the others . Then what should we do ? I think that we can improve the transportation there . The shorter the time they have to spend to go to the hospitals , the chance of them being able to get treatment immediately will be higher . At the same time , people who live in cities wo not feel unbalanced because they can use those transportation too . Not only medical problems , there are actually lots more problems in the rural areas like this , and I think our governments should face the problems or not just keep ignoring them . There are lots of solutions currently , and it is only decided by what they want or not . The government definitely knows these solutions too , but they do not care because solving these problems cannot bring them much benefit . Reality is cruel , a problem like this will only be solved after a long time . 
I think it is still important for the other countries that do not use the English language in their daily life . There are a lot of books , movies and other things that if you can understand English , you will have access to them . There are a lot of jobs in the world that require attendance to better understand the English language . And if you are a lover of another language , or if you really want to understand other than the English language , no matter what your reason is , then the other foreign language is still important to you . Nowadays , we have no device or something that can translate a language that we do not know in a correct and immediate way . If you know many languages , it will help you to access other content that is not in your own language . No matter what reason others give us about learning foreign languages , I still think that it is always important to learn other languages you are not familiar with . 
