Music is the best thing we can have in our lives . This thing can make us to feel better any time . Firstly , when you are sad , you listen to music , when you are happy or mad , you keep listening and that makes you forget every problem in your head . All sadness goes if you listen to the right song . Secondly , if you want to live in another land , to just find happiness , you have to listen to music . Even your friends do that , even your parents or your grandparents . Music is a guide in your life . A life without music has no sense . Every time when you listen , you are happy instantly . Do you think that is a good way to live ? I think it is the best way . You need to listen every day . Also , music can improve our motivation or can make us more productive . When you learn something or when you want to be more productive , you need to listen to orchestral music . That improves all your skills and makes your brain assimilate everything you want . 
My favourite season of the year is the fall . The fall in Japan is the best season for food , like potatoes . I also think the fall is the best season for tourists , because of the changing colors of the leaves . I love to see the changing colors of the leaves around Tokyo station . Every fall , there are a lot of people to see them . And the moon is big and shiny and very beautiful ! The weather is pleasant , at around 20 degrees . The air is cool , but the wind is bracing and the sky is blue . The weather of spring in Japan is the same as the fall . However , spring in Japan is a difficult time for hay fever sufferers , as there is a lot of cedar pollen in the air . I wish that fall lasted longer , but in the past few years , it has gotten shorter and shorter . 
