Music is an art form . From the beginning of humanity , music has been a means of communication . The first example of music appeared during the prehistoric times , when humans started to communicate with their similars . With time , music changed with the abilities and the evolution of communication . Music became a way to promote ideas , to send messages , to fall in love and to fight against enemies . In my life , music plays a fundamental role . It is a friend that fills my silences . I often listen to music when I feel alone . Music is a companion to my magic moments . There are several songs that have a special meaning for me . When I listen to those songs , I live again special moments of my life . Music is an opportunity to meet people and to make new friends . Nothing is as special as attending a live concert . A life without music would be like a life without colours . 
Based on some TV programs , social media and other kinds of entertainment , the idea of living an intense life is the most ideal option even when this is something harmful to our own bodies or to other people 's feelings . They say it 's your obligation to give yourself the best of this world and all its pleasures as well . On the other hand , living a long and calm life is sold as something boring and old -fashioned and even meaningless , which is not the case at all . But , as a marketing product that does not receive enough attention , this kind of lifestyle seems not good or even wrong , at a first glance . Doing so , all the mass media is trying to lead our decisions and , maybe unintentionally , also our future . Based on all of the previous words , I prefer to live a long , calm and indeed better life . 
