My favourite season of the year I do not have a favourite season , I like all four seasons . But it is true that we can enjoy each season in a different way , doing enjoyable activities , both indoors and outdoors . When it comes having fun , I am very sure that summer is the best season . People can go outside without being afraid of bad weather , storms or facing pouring rain . There are plenty of activities available , such as doing sports , camping , taking a walk or even swimming in a river or lake . Being associated with a country club could be a great idea in the summer season . The summer season is also nice , because we can keep in touch with nature . It is a nice time to have ice cream , juice and tropical fruits , such as a banana , papaya , melon and cold watermelon , that is such a delicious fruit . However , all seasons have pros and cons , but there are a lot of possibilities to explore and it is always possible to get the best of each one . 
