Life choices In modern society , people can easily live to 100 if they live healthy lives , but most people do not live to 100 , which means they have chosen not to live healthily all the time . Understandably , it is not possible to always think about the future . Firstly , humans are animals , therefore they cannot think about their happiness in the future , but about their present peace of mind . So , people are not not always able to take bright decisions and there is nothing wrong with that as long as they enjoy their lives . I would rather have a short pleasant life in which I had a lot of fun than a long dull life and live to 100 . Secondly , coming back to the first argument , nobody will be happy about living a long wholesome life without any pleasure . Everybody would rather have a shorter live in which they have enjoyed life and they can say : " Wow , my life was awesome , man , I do not regret anything . " Instead of having a dreary life , they will say : " Well , if I had walked 10 more steps every day , this would not have happened " In conclusion , I rather have a short , but joyful life than a long but drab life . Since I will be able to look back at my life on my deathbed and think , wow what an amazing life I had . 
The event was one of most unique and marvelous . After years of listening to J Cole 's music , his song have become my playlist . Attending this concert was a unique event that I will always remember fondly , because of the atmosphere , the amazing performance and the sense of connection to the artist . He was all smiling and laughing as he played the songs . Following the performance of some of the song tracks from his recent album , the chords to my favourite song of all time happened . I lost the ability to breathe for a moment . After the concert ended , I felt slightly empty . Going to his music concert was an unparalleled experience that I will always cherish . 
The effective type of room arrange depends on jobs that the employees usually deal with . In my case , sometimes , a workstation or cubicle type of workspace is better than an open space one . Because we have to focus on our job to make equations or program to do the simulation of the functions of our product to check if the functions work well or to improve them or to find what the wrong points are . But after making equations or programming , we have to discuss the results if they match the other parts of the product . So we also need open rooms . Considering the above points , our office should have an open design to easily ask or discuss something with other colleagues . But it is better if we also have a space which has some enclosed stations to focus on our own jobs . Employees must use a laptop to easily move to their desk according to the tasks they need to deal with . 
My favourite season is Winter . It 's the best season in my opinion . The cold is better than the heat . This means that there are fewer people in the street and the world is calmer . There is more rain . It is so relaxing and one of my leisure activities is reading while it is raining outdoors . It means that I am embroiled a lot in the text . Also , it is the season when there are more events , when the family get together and have more ad hoc meals . The city is lighter than the rest of the year and the people are happier and they help each other . It 's a good time to make a list of your goals for the future and to see all that you have succeeded in over the year and finally , hanging out with your friends in the house and seeing films or playing board games while drinking and eating is the best way to spend the afternoon . 
