Mr . President of the council , When it comes to improving the lives of all citizens , every decision is important and welcome . Your decision to ban the use of mobile phones in some places is excellent . However , I suggest only a changing when it comes to do it in some places , like shops and restaurants . I will explain why . Banning mobile phones in public transportation will be excellent ! Inside the buses , trains or taxis , it is necessary to respect other passengers , and maintain silence , as much as possible . I think nobody wants to be disturbed by people who do not get to speak in a low voice , neither by others who only want to listen to music at a loud volume . So , your decision to ban cell phones in these places is really welcome . On the other hand , I ask you to reconsider your idea of banning them in shops or restaurants . Think about those people who are all the time working , and the cell phone is their main work tool ! They continuously are in contact with clients and several other people , and almost always do their activities during lunch or in a cafe , for example . If those people can not use their mobile phones in restaurants or shops , they ... So , I suggest you think better about the restrictions that this council intends on applying to all citizens , if it 's possible , of course . I guess that a great part of this town have the same opinion I do . And we believe that this point of view of ours , if it can be accepted , will improve the lives of all people . Thanks for your attention . 
I 've been using Write and Improve for a couple of months and it 's definitely my favourite tool to learn English . The platform is filled with workbooks , you get to choose the level you feel comfortable with , whether it is beginner , intermediate , advanced or business , there 's workbooks for everyone . In your account , you 'll be able to see every workbook you have done so far to see how much you are improving . There 's a kind of score , from A1 to C2 , that measures your proficiency and how you write a text about a topic that 's been given to you . Furthermore , you have a test zone with training to practice your English even more . The website is helpful because we have a task help with some feedback that appears as soon as we finish checking our work and then they point it out the changes you should make to improve your English and make more achievements . They stimulate us to do even better every day . We can see our progress through the years , I think it 's easy and good for me because I was already at an intermediate level of English so it was not hard to get used to it and it 's so helpful because I used to lack in writing and now I feel confident with my workbooks . I recommend you to use it because it definitely will help you improve your English by showing ways to do it , with the encouragement and tools you need . 
The best thing would be a mix of the two options . Living your life as a rock star or taking care of your garden . At my age , I have a wife and two kids , life is more intense than you can imagine . Although it not as a rock star life . Living your life much more intensely , you can get a lot of experience in a short time , but you wo not have time to remember your actions . such as an extreme sport , and you will have to stay in hospital some time of your life . Whether you think a shorter life is better , your family will miss you for a long time , and you do not have to have children because you wo not take care of them in the future . On the other hand , if you prefer a long and calm life , whether a lot of experience many times with your family and friends . Despite not having a Youtube channel showing your life , I 'm sure that a picture book will be the best memory that you could have . Therefore , you can have an intense life from your desk because , on TV , you can live a great experience such as watching a football match or movies . In my opinion , life is always too short and we have to enjoy it a lot . Because you should think that you can do very intense things and , at the same time , life a long time with your loved ones . 
It goes without saying that , when it comes to healthy living , there are a large number of things we can do to maintain it . My thoughts concerning that matter are going to be displayed in this writing . To get started , I would like to point out some paramount actions which should be accomplished by each and every individual who is willing to have a healthy life . To begin with , drinking at the very least two liters of water daily is something pivotal if we want to get rid of the toxic particles our blood and body contain . Another issue to have under consideration is the food we eat . I cannot help but mention that we all feel attracted to tasty food , nevertheless , the one we find tastier is not usually the one that provides us with the vitamins and characteristics needed . Fast food should be avoided as much as possible . Instead , we ought to eat plenty of fruit and vegetables in order to get fit . Nonetheless , we often find ourselves failing in the task of keeping fit , due to the fact that we do not usually count on the required time to fulfill that aim . We live in a deeply stressful world nowadays . Last but by no means least , I would like to conclude by bringing focus to the fact that our body is our most valuable treasure , therefore , it is essential for us to put it in first place . 
