Offices workspaces Currently , office workspaces are a very important feature that can influence the employees ' productivity and behavior . Choosing which design suits better the workplace is more important than hiring the right person to do the job . Enclosed workstations can be very depressing and some people can face these cubicles as a threatening space that can betray their creativity . However , on the other hand , an open design office should give the employees an idea that they can do what they want at anytime , but just in case , they are not familiar with that design . Open design offices have been used in several industries and countries for many years and since it started , it has been working . Although it is very important that this kind of office is used in the right way . For example , it is a good idea using open design offices for marketing , sales , advertising or another informal business . But there are some industries where working in enclosed stations may be necessary such as accounting firms , law offices and any fields where concentration and silence are an important requirement for the workplace environment . Maybe own these two options could be a good idea , it would suit booth needs in only one office . I guess it is very common today . Office buildings are being built with these two designs , if employees need it , it will be available . 
