Which is better , that university students move away and live on their own while they are attending school or live at home with their family while they are students ? I think it is up to their personalities and conditions of their family . Each of them has different merits and demerits . Therefore , there is no absolutely correct answer . The independence of a university student from his/her family may lead to growth in his/her personality . This experience helps him/her to live after graduation . However , it has many financial burdens for them and their family . Some need to help their family , and it may make it difficult to study in university . If the students ca not afford to live alone , they perhaps should live at home with their family . The less concerns they have , the more they can live freely . It may lead to their growth . For the reasons stated above , I ca not choose which is better , but I think they should select what they think better so that they can study well . 
