Nowadays , speaking another language is really important and useful for most students . This is the reason why they choose to study in another country . I strongly believe that living in a different country helps them to improve faster in the fact of learning a new language . They can meet and go out with other foreign speakers in order to practise speaking with native people . Furthermore , they can see and learn the culture of the country . Without doubt it ´s a great experience with a lot of advantages for the students . On the other hand , I think that there are some disadvantages regarding missing their families or their friends . As you all know , being in a different country means being away from your family . However , they have a lot of ways to be connected with them , such as Skype , Zoom , etc . To sum up , there are more advantages than disadvantages , so if you are thinking about studying in another country , you should go . If I have the opportunity to study in another country , I would like to go to France . What about you ? 
The first step is define what is the truth and what is a lie . That is extremely important because often we think too simply because people think that is obvious . In fact , there is no ambiguity when the situation is simple and the answer is black or white ! After these details , you can have discussions on this subject . Truths or lies are moral rules given by society to drive relationships between people . Rules are crucial because they are the cement of society but there is no legal sanction in relationships . Moral rules come from education and are also dictated by religion . When the people in a state are very educated , the rules are much better respected . Because people know that if there are no moral rules in the state , there will be anarchy . For this reason it is important to improve education of the people and teach civic education . This will be a guarantee for quality of life and strong economic development . It is important to understand that life and economic relationships are based on trust . Trust is an important value . Nothing can be built without mutual trust . Therefore , it is important to tell the truth . But sometimes , there is an exception to this rule when you tell a lie to avoid a critical situation . For example , when someone else 's pride is threatened , it is better to tell a little lie ! 
