My favorite movie is ' Assassination Classroom ' , it is an action and anime movie . There are also some comedy parts in the movie . NA , . there is a guy , whose name is Koro , who has destroyed half of the moon , and now he is going to destroy the Earth . But it is so easy for him so he feels and thinks about something fun to do before destroying this beautiful planet . He becomes a teacher in the worst class , class 3 -E , and promises that within a year , if none of the students in the class can kill him , he will destroy the whole Earth . Throughout the film there are all kinds of games that class 3E devises to kill Koro -sensei ( the dear name that the class gives to their teacher to kill him forever ) from guns , daggers , and bombs to traps . Through each failed supervision , they learn more from their experiences and become more mature from each of Koro - sensei 's teachings , which were added into each game . The movie takes the audience through many kinds of feelings whenever they see the daring and elaborate plans of the 3E students . Through failed surveillance , they discover their own potential , like a potion girl becoming a poison expert , a forgetful class couple becoming a sniper duo , an average student turning into a great leader . Each individual is a story of their own , waiting for the viewers to discover it . In the end , Koro -sensei was killed , and the class was sad , they would miss the days they studied with Koro -sensei , but just some seconds later , Koro -sensei appeared behind the students , and it turned out that everything was fake and the assassination mission continued . It is the best movie I have ever seen ; it has a part 2 already but I have not had time to watch it , I hope that I can watch it soon . I recommend you watch it , it is very nice . 
