MY FAVOURITE SEASON OF THE YEAR When somebody asks me which is my favourite season of the year , my answer is always the winter . Without doubt , I really believe that it is the most beautiful season of the year . However , I know that for most people , their favourite season is the summer . In my case , I really enjoy the winter . I like spending time at home when the weather outside is bad . There are a lot of things to do at home , like watching a movie , playing video games , reading an interesting book ... Furthermore , you can do some outdoor sports , such as ice skating or snowboarding . However , you can go to the cinema as well as shopping , if you do not really enjoy these outdoor activities . On the other hand , in winter it is Christmas , a beautiful time that you can spend with your family and friends . To sum up , there are several things to do in winter , even if you do not like the weather . 
