I like to sleep with a small light on because the small light makes me feel safe . In the dark I cannot see anything , I feel that there are some things in the dark , so I feel that I am in danger . It would be more difficult for me to sleep without a light . I do not mind about noise when I am sleeping . On the contrary , noise lets me know that there is someone outside , I feel that I am protected by other people ; I feel that I am safe so I can remove vigilance and have a sleep . To me , noise and light make me feel that I am safe and protected ; it is easy for me to sleep when I have noise and light . 
A lot of doctors say that sitting and doing no sport is the new smoking and is really bad for you . This inactive lifestyle has many negative effects on health . This is why I would discuss if all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . I agree that university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . The first argument is that it will help to become a better team . This means that sport , especially team sports in school or at university , will help you and your classmates to become a team , because in some sports activities , you learn to work together and be a good and fair team player , which will help in the end to form a better team in class too . The next thing is that it helps you to have more focus on things . Because of the motivation and mental strength which you need to do sport , you learn these skills which help you not only in the sport . These skills will also be useful in other parts in your life or important skills too for learning at school for exams and focusing on what you are doing or what you would do in the future . The last and the best point is that sport has much effect on your health . To be healthy , some studies say that you should do at least 10000 steeps every day . So it is important for everyone to do sport every day . It is not so important what sport you do , it does not make so much difference in the effects . More important is that you do a sport which you like so that you are motivated to do your sport every day and do not quit after some days or weeks . These are my arguments why I think it is important for university students and school children to do at least 3 times per week sport . 
