I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room , but if there is a small light , I do not mind . Sometimes when there 's a bit of noise , I can sleep without any trouble . I ca not sleep when the room is cold or when the room is hot . When I watch TV I like to sleep for a little while . If my neighbor is having a party with loud music , it does not cause me any problems . I am a heavy sleeper . 
It is argued that today 's teens are the least active generation in the past decades . This statement is sustained not only by the increasing number of young people with different illnesses associated to obesity , but also by the worrying amount of fast food businesses , which raises year by year . I believe we should all be aware of the negative consequences an unhealthy diet might cause us and try to move out of our comfort zones , which we are so familiar with . Although it might seem a drastic measure , I am profoundly urging teenagers and students to attend sport classes at least three times a week , for their own benefit . I will sustain my view with multiple arguments . Firstly , the actual syllabus seems to be insufficient to ensure a proper balance between in class or outside sport activities and a healthy life education . The coach is usually focused on following the school programme . If the amount of classes are to be raised , he would be more willing to diversify the educational programme , therefore some nutrition advice or examples of exercises to be done at home might be of their interest . Then , the students could be determined to take part in additional sports competitions if they felt they are prepared enough for them . More rehearsal means more self -confidence . And a well -trained teenager is more likely to become a professional sportsperson . Another important factor is the self -esteem the teenager could improve , by reshaping their body within the sports room . Some might argue that if someone wants to lose weight , then it 's up to them , but in reality , it is very challenging and difficult to stick to the plan if they are on their own . A class group engaged in sport activities would be far more effective and efficient , with visible results . Sports benefiting young people is undeniable and the entitled authorities should play their part in supporting them . 
