Exist a list of conditions which I usually want they should stay present in my workstation . One of them is silence . I would often rather be alone to develop my tasks . I do not hate my co -workers , at all ! But , when it comes to choosing a type of workstation , if I could , I would actually prefer to stay alone . When I am doing my activities and there is no one next to me , my mind works smoothly and the results become better . So many voices at the same time around me take my concentration , and I run the risk of not paying attention to what I was doing . More than this : a great part of the people do not get talking in a low volume ... they always do this in a high voice , and they ignore the moment to stop their speeches and return to their own activities . This makes me feel annoyed , and I need to control myself : I almost always have the impulse of being impolite . In a nutshell , these are the reasons I would rather work isolated . When I am alone , in a cubicle ( not too small , of course ! ) or separated by walls , I feel more productive , my mind works better and staying far from the amount of co -workers ' voices takes me to more tranquility . When I am alone , I may even listen to pleasant music while I am developing my tasks . ( You must agree with me : Working this way is much more difficult if the place where you are working is full of people talking about several subjects not related to your tasks , right ? ) . So , I will ask you a thing ... if someday you want to give me an opportunity to work with your employees , please ... let me do it in a cubicle , or in a place with walls separating me of my co -workers , OK ? I promise I will have friendship with them , but at the moment of working , I need silence , peace and maximum concentration ... And my results will be the best ! 
From : Philip Subject : My favourite film My favourite film is The Last Holiday film . It is rated 4.9 stars on IDBI and was also one of the highest grossing films in the USA . I just love the film because it is both funny and the main character is having a great time at a luxurious hotel and eating luxurious food . There is a oposite name named Kraken , who is a boss of a big company and is really grumpy . He always wants to compete against the main character , but in the end , he learns his lesson . After knowing that she is going to live a bit longer , the main character opens a restaurant that attracts billions of customers . 
Today , in Sweden , there is a huge variation between how many young people do sports activities . Because of the negative effects on health of an inactive lifestyle , all university and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . First of all , it improves your learning . When exercising , the blood flows to your brain and the rest of your body . Studies state that you are more concentrated after being physically active for at least 30 minutes . This means that exercising during school time will help focus during lessons and therefore lead to increased grades . Secondly , it helps to reduce the risks of mental illness . Mental illness is an increased problem in our society . Not only among adults , but also among children . Loneliness is one cause of mental illness which can be avoided by joining a team . When you join a sports team , you will be a part of a group . You may also make new friends . Problems can be shared with a friend and make you feel better , and thereby it improves your chances of not being mentally ill . I understand that not everyone will agree at first . Why be forced ? My answer to that is that now we see a problem with many children 's inactive lifestyles and to solve that problem , we need to make it easier to live an active lifestyle . So , how could we make it easier ? To start with , I think it is necessary to force students to join sports teams in school because then they will not have any excuse . Children and teenagers will find new favorite activities that will last them forever . To improve learning , reducing risks of mental illness and making it easier to live an active lifestyle , all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . 
Young people and sports Sport is fun , sport is teamwork and sport can be the spark you need to be active . But today 's day many people like students and school children are only gaming and not playing around a pitch . A repercussion because of that is that the health of those among us is getting bad , very bad . So the youngsters among us need to be forced to do sports related activities at least 3 times a week and this is why . Health negatives The phenomenon of gaming has become an ordinary thing in today 's society , but only not with any benefits , most of the consequences are bad , very bad . Firstly , teenagers who are near the ages of 15 or 16 are having a bow in their posture due to staring for hours and hours at a monitor . Another side effect of watching for hours and hours the same screen is that more and more children or students need glasses with the result that the prices for glasses are rising speedily . 
I believe that efficiency should depend on the type of work performed in the office . For example , an accounting office is not the same as an advertising office . When your work is creative , the design of the space is an important part ; colors , rooms to relax , having meetings with clients or talking with other colleagues are important . You also have to think that some people work better in silence , others need music to be creative and all those elements must be considered in the design of the office . Now , if we talk about a more routine type of work , comfortable seating and a good coffee station are elements to consider . However , if we want to reach a real efficiency in the design of the workspace , we must talk to the people who work in that office , what do you need ? How do you feel most comfortable ? Their opinion is important to determine if we let a mistake pass on the design . In conclusion , together : workers , design experts , contractors , must be listened to in order to reach an agreement on design effectiveness . 
