Working as a volunteer , a part from being a requirement to graduate , is a great opportunity for all students . In my opinion , completing a certain amount of volunteer work has a lot of advantages for them . On the one hand , this experience allows students to learn and improve their skills and knowledge . Furthermore , employees can help students and teach them how the professional world works . On the other hand , students can see if they like this type of work or not . This is an important fact that will help students in the future , when they are looking for a job . However , I know that not all students have the time to work as a volunteer , because they have a lot of homework to do and a lot to study in order to pass their exams . In spite of this , I strongly believe that this requirement is an amazing experience for students . They should appreciate it as much as I do . 
