My town is small because it only has 200 inhabitants . There are many restaurants . I have eaten dinner there with my family , but not with my friends . There are two parks . The first park we call " parque do rizzo " there are not a lot of things there , but we can go running and we can throw some rocks in the lake , it is a lot of fun . The city does not have any night -time entertainment , we call it a dormitory city . I play football with my friends there in July . I go running in the park every day in the morning before work . 
I think that we should not choose the way we live our lives . I think that a person should be able to choose the way to live his life . I prefer to live a short but intense life than to live a long and boring one . At this moment , because I am trying to change my work place , I am making lots of effort so I can have a very strict schedule so I have enough time to learn . This way I manage to learn in the morning and in the evening every day . It is very hard for me to wake up in the morning and to start learning for the IT web developer course . I think this investment in me is the best thing in my life and I really hope that , in the near future , I will have the possibility to change my life and also my life . I hope that , in the near future , I will find colleagues that are more open -minded , that are nicer than the ones I do not have . I would be glad if I were able to understand all the information that Sasha is teaching and maybe , in the near future , I will be strong and confident enough so I will change my life . Until then , I am preparing myself every day and I try to do my best to learn English and to understand the IT web developing course . 
