Sleeping is one of the best human qualities and there are people who prefer sleeping in a dark and quiet room , while other individuals enjoy it with a small light on and do not mind noise or loud music . In my case , I would rather sleep in a dark , small and quiet room to be able to rest the entire night without any bother . First of all , to sleep well I need many things to let the room be appropriate to rest in . For instance , I enjoy sleeping in a silent room and with a soft mattress , and sometimes I like to get into bed and use my cell phone , and sometimes I like to get in the bed and using my cell phone , in the meantime listening to my favorite songs . 
I enjoy watching TV shows and movies in my spare time and I usually do it twice a week , but , on the weekends , I spend more time watching series and sitcoms to have fun . Basically , this activity is good for me , because I love spending my free time watching new movies and keeping myself updated about the entertainment world . So , the last time I watched a movie was one week ago and I watched a series which was a sci -fi thriller . 
It is an intriguing question : is a short but intense or long but calm and ' grey ' life , and with no bright colours , better ? I think that even if it seems hard to decide , at a closer look , maybe most people believe that they would prefer a short but intense life . And probably it is mainly for one reason : the intensity of the feelings that a totally involving experience carries with it , in a special way carries on a time distortion . That is to say , time passes very slowly when you are going through a very intense experience . You remember every minute of the time passed , and every minute lasts a day long . This is the result from psychology science : time is not absolute but has a different duration from one to another , with respect to his or her feelings at the time . Our mental processes enhance some situations and they thus appear longer than other moments of poor mental activity . And those special situations , despite their real duration , are thus impressed in our mind that they appear much longer in time . And we can understand the common phrase " better a day as a lion than one hundred as a ship . " It is the sensation of having spent intensely all the time in your hands , not one second lost , which makes you happier . And we all would like to have a good time . A good time is not more time , but a better one . 
My favorite indoor activity is reading , because I want to learn about history . I can use my imagination with it all . Now I 'm not reading any books because I do not have any free time . I was reading twice a day . I like to read history and action novels . My favorite writer is King ; his best book is Carrie . 
I have heard that considering young people who have a bad habit that may affect their health , the universities and schools have to set rules to force students to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . For the sake of strengthening the physical and mental health of students , I agree with this latest policy , and my reasons is as follows . Firstly , many students are addicted to their own mobile phones . Although young people do not have the ability to control them by themselves , most students at school nowadays have their own phone . As a result , a lot of students do not sleep until mid night because of their phones , and it will make them energyless . If the school sets rules to force them to do sports , it can help them stay away from mobile phones and improve their health condition . In addition , it can also enhance students ' academic performance . According to a study , the students who do sports have better scores than those staying at home . Secondly , doing sports regularly can help students make more friends , which is beneficial to their mental health . Many sports activities are a kind of test of teamwork , and through the progress of team work , students can cultivate their ability of cooperating . For example , basketball , football , soccer , etc . Students can make true friends while they are fighting with their teammates together . After the sports activities , they can also discuss the problems they meet with their friends , which is really good for their mental health . Friends are an important company for all students . On the other hand , schools cannot always force students to do sports . What is important is to make them love doing sports so that they will do sports activities regularly by themselves instead of by others ' enforcement . And that is the final purpose . To sum up , in my opinion , it is necessary that all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week . It could avoid the negative effects on health of an inactive lifestyle . But enforcement is not the final purpose , schools should teach them to mix sports into their lives . 
In the last years , technology has increased very quickly , especially with regards to computers and tablets . These devices have become more and more popular , in particular , the tablet has became a little laptop . It is really versatile and easy to carry . It is said that computers and tablets will replace paper and books in the near future . It could be an advantage . Using digital books will avoid a waste of paper , and it is a good thing for the environment . Moreover , digital books are only popular with young people , who are used to reading on a tablet . They are used to various applications to read texts easily . However , many adults do not agree . They think that it is more difficult to focus on the text and they believe that it is more tiring and boring than a real book . Finally , I think that tablets and computers could not replace books , because many people are used to reading from paper . It is easier and more pleasant . On the other hand , it is a pleasure to turn the next page and touch the paper . 
In my free time I study for my English class . Very often I download English commercials and I edit the audio so that I can listen to them every time I need to . This activity can provide me with lasting teach . This is the way I can improve my pronunciation and writing . Last Sunday , I downloaded five English videos from You Tube . 
When we become adults , life changes forever . And all the things around us change , too . When we are children or teens , we almost always depend on our parents to do everything . We even depend on their money to buy simple things we want , or to go out at weekends ' night . So , when we become adults , we have to look for situations which allow us to grow up in every direction . Then , it 's very interesting that university students , for example , already start walking with their own resources . Some of them move away and live on their own when they go to university . At same time , there are others who live at home with their family during this period of the life . I think that after a person gets older , it is better for them not to depend on anyone . People need to understand that they will not have their parent 's protection for their whole life . Protection is very good ( and even useful ) during some years of the childhood and teenage years , but there is a moment in which we must learn to guide our own steps , because we wo not have other adults to protect us for the rest of our lives . So , I believe that the best choice for university students when they go to university is trying to build their own academic lives on their own . If some extreme need situation happens , these students may ask their father to help them , but in my conception , this only may occur if extremely necessary . My idea about this has nothing to do with students ' lives becoming difficult . Never ... My idea is about making them able to see how hard real life is out of our homes when we are older and we decide to have our lifestyle . It seems that everything our parents acquire falls from the sky . So , may they begin to understand soon that life is difficult , and the first difficulty starts when we go to university ! 
