Speaking the truth is indeed a great life skill , and it plays an integral role in the life of several individuals . It is recommended to be honest in life as it defines the character and moral values of each person . This essay intends to highlight the reasons why I think it is absolutely necessary to speak honestly throughout life . To commence with , being honest is an excellent virtue in life , and some people are born with this innate quality , whereas , others learn this skill from family or teachers . As this quality describes the social image of a person in society , therefore , it is essential to tell the truth in all circumstances of life . To demonstrate , since I absorbed various moral values such as honesty and punctuality from my father , it has always helped me to deal with challenging situations in a stronger way . Even though it is hard to not to lie during tough times , it is recommended to communicate in an honest way as one can develop a bad habit of lying , which can have several detrimental effects on individuals and society . Moreover , people can get involved in several troubles when they cheat on others . To illustrate , a close friend of mine was habituated to telling lies , which negatively impacted my image in college , and eventually , I decided to end my friendship with her . Hence , it is advisable to tell the truth on all occasions as this trait is a building block of one 's personality and image in the community . To conclude , it is absolutely vital to communicate in a fair and transparent way for the well -being of society . Furthermore , it helps people to be real and natural in their own ways . 
Life expectancy is unpredictable and destined . If I am asked to choose between living a long calm life until 100 years old and living a short lifespan but much more intense , interesting , and fatigued , frankly to say , I will choose the former for some of the reasons below , although some people like me in the teenage phase would like to have an intense life now . The first reason why I would prefer live longer is to learn more knowledge about this world . The world is full of many interesting phenomena and principles , which deeply lure me to observe the change in the world regarding politics , economy , art , science , culture , etc . Besides , the process of change of knowledge and cultural and scientific phenomena may last so long that I have much time to learn much more about the principles of this world than the ordinary if I could live up to 100 years old . Additionally , the second reason why I prefer to live longer is related to my characteristics . I 'm a little conservative , quiet , and slow -paced person compared to most of my peers so I 'm usually inclined to live in a slow tone of life like taking a stroll on the road for one afternoon , sitting on the balcony leisurely and seeing the pedestrians crossing by the roads , and having a tasty drinks in a coffee shop while reading traveling magazines . Moreover , the most critical reasons for me to choose living longer is my lovely family . If I have my own family , I 'm eager to accompany with my dad , my mom , spouse , wife , children as long as I can . I would like to spend the rest of my time taking care of them , watching them growing healthily , and allowing them to have their own families finally , which is the biggest satisfaction of my life . In general , after considering the above benefits compared to living a short lifespan , I would prefer to live longer even though it may not be imaginable in my destiny . 
Nowadays , I 'm working in an office that is in a building on the 12th floor . I always work there , I feel really anxious because it seems there wo not be a way to leave , to get out of that room . Besides that , when it does not have any energy to support you , you 'll have to go down the stairs . It would be terrible , mainly if you work on a high floor , mainly if you work in the higher floor kind of 12 < u00BA > 12th like me . As that space is not so big , you 'll have to allow for all the employees who work in that tiny place . In order to remove or increase the sounds , you 'll have to create walls , that is you 'll spend more money if your company has a great deal of employees . An example , in my work , is when someone tries to get in touch with other people by telephone or video chat , they need to change the room to reduce the sound so that all the sounds , mainly other subjects , are not received by person across the video or the line . There 's another problem which no one is talking about , it is about privacy . It depends on the meeting or subject , but if you need to talk about a specific thing to other people , such as you are firing someone or you are talking about money , you wo not have any privacy to talk about it . All of this is because of the lack of privacy that there has been since they designed the office . 
In my opinion , to always tell the truth is one of the fundamental ways to make and keep a good relationship with others . Even though everyone feels good telling a lie , it is not good because they must feel worse when they notice it is not true . To apologize when you miss something is also important . People are not perfect . It is normal to make mistake sometimes . So to apologize for the mistakes and how to recover from them is very important . In business , to always tell the truth and to apologize are very important to build and keep a good relationship with customers because business people always have a responsibility for something and they do not want to fail in their jobs . So they have to build and keep a good relationship with customers based on them . Even though there are difficulties in you business , it becomes easier once you can get a good relationship to continue to tell the truth and apologize for a mistake and recover from it . Personally , a good relationship makes people feel worth living and a member of group . People always think about their worth and meaning to live . So it is very important for people to to feel them . For the above the reason , I always think that to always tell the truth is very important and the key to making good relationships with others and make life better . 
Dear Sir/Madam , I am writing to express my dissatisfaction regarding the new policy of the administration which abstains the usage of cellular phones on public modes of transport such as trains and buses , as well as in stores and eateries . Since digital phones have become a necessity in life , it is not recommended to ban the usage of them in all the above -mentioned places . As we all are aware smartphones have proven helpful to people in several ways , such as tracking known people , namely family members and children , and for ordering commodities online , hence , the utilisation of this gadget should not be banned in public places . Moreover , this invention has helped individuals to perform their daily activities with less effort . Not only have mobiles been helpful in reducing distance -related issues , but they have also been helpful in overcoming time -related problems . Although society has become habituated to using cell phones , which can lead to many detrimental effects , it is important to understand that this device can assist the human race in many ways if it is used appropriately . Considering the above -stated points , I request you not to disallow the usage of mobiles on public transport and common places because this device plays a key role in the life of the people and assist society to deal with their hurdles pertaining to time and distance . 
