Working in an open or closed space . Which one is the best ? Working in privacy will increase the work performance or an open space should bring out the worker 's responsibility . In this essay , I will argue which will be the better solution furthermore the benefits and prejudice . Working in a closed space would help the worker 's focus , also their privacy . It is really annoying when we are on the phone and near is someone listening to what I ´m saying . The prejudice I note is that help would not be provided because of the isolation . Furthermore , it would not be or can be difficult to share doubts . Working in an open space could bring benefits to sight , we can watch if the worker is working or just surfing on the net . How long is that worker on his coffee break . But for the worker , it can be an opportunity to share and clarify some doubts or fears . In my opinion , both kinds of work space have benefits , but also harms , and what will be the best for company should be analyzed . 
