The art of learning music When I went to school , I did not study music because we did not have a teacher music . I think that having a possibility to learn to play an instrument is very important because the children could develop their talent . However , there are many students without talent or vocation , but they choose to study music although they are not good at it . For instance , I liked to play the flute and the guitar in high school , but today , I ca not learn because I do not have the time , it is for this reason I believe that studying music should be required at schools . Moreover , it is a beautiful way to give to know art to the children . I love music , and I would like my son to study music , he likes to play the drums , and I think that is his talent . 
I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room . Before I go to bed , I want to listen to a story or talk with my mom , I like to drink hot cocoa before bed too . Sometimes I ca not sleep immediately , so I must wait until I can sleep . I like to sleep in a dark and quiet room because I ca not be disturbed in my sleep and I can fall into sleep easily . I do not like to sleep in a noisy room because it is hard to focus on sleeping . 
