My favorite season of the year . My favorite season of the year is the spring and it is because I love cold weather and the wind . I live in a village surrounded by mountains and hills and it is very beautiful to feel and see this kind of weather in this season . It is incredible how you can see changes in people with the seasons . That reminds me how nature affects us . When I walk in the streets , I see friendly and hateful people , but in this season , you will see children playing and having a good time with each other and their parents only have to keep their eyes on them . If you pay attention , even the animals are more active and wild in their environment and I know that because I usually walk in the mountains and I can see and feel that kind of energy in nature . 
