From : me To : Alex Subject : Party on Saturday My dear friend , I am sending this e -mail to you only to thank you for the invitation to the party next Saturday . You are a great friend . We have known each other for many , many years , and I also know that you would never forget to invite me to this important moment . We are almost brothers , and I know how important this event is to you , and I know what it represents to you too . Despite this , I am using this virtual space to say that I will not be present at this important moment of your life . I apologise , because I would like to participate in this moment by your side . I 'm so sorry about this , and I will explain the reason I will not be there , and I hope you understand me . During this year , almost all weekends , I had been to several parties ( including four or five with you , right ? ) However , since last month , I decided to focus part of my life on learning essays which can change my financial life forever . I bought some classes of financial education , and this has been my occupation in the last days . I have classes on Fridays , Saturdays and Sundays , usually in the evening ( two hours each class , at 7:00 p.m . ) so it will be impossible to be at your party . These classes are very important , because they are changing my point of view on money , finances , emotional intelligence , personal growth and several other essays which can change our lives forever . I bought classes for an entire year , and their prices were so high . We can say that it was an investment for my life . My focus at this moment is on acquiring financial freedom , because I intend to retire when I am 45 . I know that this cannot justify my absence at your event , but I hope you forgive me . Soon , I will be free again to be at other events , and I want you to understand me . It means that , for a while , I do not have any idea about when the next opportunity to be at this kind of event will be . Please , forgive me , my friend . I sincerely hope that you might be successful in your event next Saturday . Best regards , 
