It is of the utmost importance to be a trustworthy person . The majority of people believe that on no account should someone tell a lie . From my personal perspective , I confirm the aforementioned statement . This is my firm belief , based on two plausible reasons . In this essay , I will explore the main advantages of telling truth . Furthermore , I will denote how a lie could ruin the credibility of an individual . These justifications will be elaborated in the subsequent paragraphs . First and foremost , honesty is one of the significant traits . In all cultures , religions and cults , being honest is robustly recommended . Furthermore , all poets , social thinkers , as well as philosophers , highlight the necessity of telling truth . Importantly , they delineate that this general rule has no exception . In other words , under no circumstances , should the truth be dismissed . If someone had concealed a truth , they would have to continue to add lies in order to prove the primary fallacious statement . Therefore , as it is mentioned in Quran , the holy book of Muslims , salvation is nothing but in truth . Hence , by telling truth , you may help yourself to go through difficult situations . Secondly , lies can destroy the reliability of a person . It is highly accepted as a social norm that decent people , who eagerly believe in their integrity , avoid telling something unbasis . To make it less grandly , if an individual deliberately made an erroneous claim or distorted a fact , or intentionally tried to cover an act up , whatever it could be , his or her authenticity would be damaged , as the truth will finally reveal itself . If it is the case , in similar situations , even when insisting on the truth , it will barely be feasible for audiences to confide in an infamous liar . Thus , never do we have to invoke misinformation . To conclude , the truth will invariably prevail in all possible conditions . It is like a shed light which eradicates the darkness of lies . Accordingly , no one can hide a lie for a long period . Consequently , we will always adhere to the truth in order to be an honest person and to keep ourselves credible in the eyes of our relatives . 
Hey Alex , Thank you for your invitation . I wish I could come to this party to meet our friends . It 's been a very long time since graduation day and we have not any opportunities to meet each other . I miss our classmates and our memories of student life so much and it would be such an exciting party . Unfortunately , I have to go to Vietnam this Firiday , before the day of your party . I want to resolve some important business there . The first crucial business is doing the process for closing my company in Vietnam , because finally , I have decided to settle down with my family in America . Although I will be unable to come , I still want to contribute some money for our class 's fund and ask you to say ' hi ' to everyone and talk to them about my absence . It 's so hard for you to set up this party alone . But there 's no chance of delaying my trip . Last , I hope everyone has a fantastic party . Speak soon , Hunters 
Dear Alex , Thank you very much for inviting me to your birthday party . I still recall your last birthday celebration and that was a mesmerising occasion to meet your friends and family . I wish you a very happy birthday . Unfortunately , due to an important official meeting , I wo not be able to make it . I cannot believe how fast time goes by . Your last birthday occasion seems to have been just a few months ago ! I wish I could have been present to wish you happy birthday in person this year as well . Unfortunately , my office is going to hold an annual board meeting and that usually takes the whole day . We have invited some key personnel to the meeting and my presence is utterly important , considering the role I play . There is no way I can skip the meeting or leave early . Regrettably , your birthday is on the same day . I would , however , like to meet you next Saturday and give you your birthday gift . Save my birthday cake until then . I look forward to meeting you soon and wish you a very pleasant birthday . Yours , Mahtab 
