I almost advocate that computers should replace books in schools and universities . At the present time , information technology and computers are increasing greatly . All the scientists and inventors always make an attempt at learning about or exploring technology , due to its excitement and changes in the world . In terms of laziness , nowadays , humans are couch potatoes and do not want to go outdoors . People do not have a drink and also do not read books in the library , nevertheless , they decide to put their feet up , go on the Internet and read a book online instead . What a relaxing and chill -out scene ! As far as I know , it 's an advantage not to have to pay any charges when we read a book online at home . That 's extremely comfortable and convenient ! In addition to this problem , it 's tremendously bad for humans ' health , as it 'll be harmful to their eyes to spend lots of time only looking at a computer screen . Coming to the end , try to read books online only if you 're busy with work . You should spend more time outdoors and especially in a library , to refresh the mind and get a change of scenery to read books . 
