My experience using grammar during the last month . During this time , I have been using this page for almost 2 or 3 hours per day . At this point I have an idea about all this and I can give a review about what you could expect once you enter . My suggestions are , when you are writing , whatever you cannot identify that you have done badly , I mean when you are checking your report , once you get your mistakes , you can see some suggestions , but in a more precise way you ca not see what your mistakes are . That is something that I would like to change on the system . On the other hand , the system is very good for those who are not native English speakers and who want to spend their time improving their grammar skills and discovering new ways to write , and vocabulary . In my recommendation , I would like encourage you to complete all the tasks you can do , there are many exercises about many cases . I would recommend it to anyone who has a computer and he or she wants to improve their grammar skills . 
Hi Alex ! I 'm terribly sorry , but I ca not come to your party on Saturday . I was really looking forward to it , but sadly I wo not make it . My sister 's boyfriend had a work -related accident and ended up in hospital and my sister has to go there to take him home . It 's a two -day drive , so she 'll be away for four days and asked me to babysit her child when she 's away . Well , I ca not bring a four -year -old to your party , can I ? I hope you understand . I hope we 'll meet and catch up . My sister 's coming back on Monday . Maybe I could take you out for lunch on Tuesday ? Or do you prefer to meet next weekend ? I 'd love to see you and hear all about your new job . Looking forward to hearing from you ! Love , xxx PS : Have fun at the party ! Again , I 'm really sorry I ca not be there . 
Hi Alex , I do not know how I can tell you this . I apologise to you because I wo not be able to attend your party next Saturday afternoon . Although I 'm feeling very sad , I 'm thinking about how I can repair this situation . Perhaps you will be able to do this party another weekend . Every party you do is very amusing and I do not like to miss it . I will have some spare time in September . If you want , we could talk about that . I want to help you to talk with all your supporters and I am ready to prepare all the things you will need to have a crazy party . You know I was a spoilt boy , but nowadays I 'm very charming and thoughtful . Sometimes I am a bit absent minded , therefore you must look at my activities , because I can forget some things , I 'm a bit clumsy . Pastries were brought to the last party for you . I will be able to bring some this year , wo not I ? I look forward to your reply . Kisses 
