Hi Alex , l can feel that it 's an important party for you on Saturday . You 've been waiting for this moment since last month , l know . But l have to tell you some bad news . I 'm so sorry that l cannot go to your party . My grandmother is sick and my mom needs to go and take care of her , so l will go with my mom to Grandmom 's house for a week . Do not worry about me . I 'll be fine there . The doctor said my grandmother just needs a few weeks to let her body get over the virus . It 's a common sickness , but also dangerous for old people . Sorry to let you down . I 'll will cheer for you on the other side . But , there 're still some solutions . I 'm going to leave on August 10th , so if you can , maybe you can change the date to the day before . Then , l guarantee that l will definitely show up at your party . Best regards 
The number of people who always use computers and tablets is increasing day by day . Because of that , technological tools are always in our lives . We can manage our work with these tools easily . While many people prefer to use computers and tablets , other people choose to use books in their school life . In my opinion , using technological tools can sometimes be efficient , but we should use books instead of computers and tablets . Computers and tablets can be distraction in our school lives . These days , so many people use these tools to take notes and study . I believe that this can affect our concentration . Our focus time is decreasing . In conclusion , a lot of people prefer to use technological tools , but they do not know that they will lose their concentration . We should not replace books with computers and tablets . 
