Hi , Last night a friend asked me what my favorite film was . I thought I 'd share my answer with you . You know I 'm not a movie fan , but if you insist that I pick one as my favorite , I 'd go for AI , Artificial Intelligence . I do not think it 's a famous one . What I like about it is its emotional aspect that really got me . Knowing you , I 'd say you wo not dislike it if you watch it . Or maybe you have watched it . Let me know what you think . Homeyra 
