Music is something exclusively recreational , but totally necessary for our lives . I could not live without music , because I really love music . I love going to a concert , I love discovering a new good artist and read about him and his career . Unfortunately , I ca not play the guitar because I am not talented , but I do not care , I love music in the same way . I like to follow local artists and I think that in my country we have excellent music , but it is not appreciated by the local people . I love music because it can make us feel better or worse about our feelings . Life without music would be sadder , all people would be sad in every moment without the possibility of getting better , because we would not have music . But also , I think this would be impossible , because music is the same being human . It is like a born ability of humanity . 
