What will the school of the future be like ? This is a really hard question to get a correct answer to , because schools are changing every day and more with the last pandemic , when schools had to implement online courses or something different , because students and people could not go out . So now , schools have a new way to teach and more resources . Maybe in the future , schools could be hybrid , a face -to -face half and an online half . Or also it could be only face -to -face lessons and online lessons as an extra for the students who want to keep learning and studying . But to answer , I think that schools will remain practically the same . We have a way to teach , we as society have used it for many years and now this is very difficult to change . The easiest way to teach is to keep teaching in the same way . 
I think that any devices are bad or useless , the problem is how we use them . Television could be educational , but it depends on the way we use it . There are many educational shows , like documentaries . Also , television could be a great tool to learn a language . For example , I use it to learn English . I watch an episode per day totally in English to practise my listening and vocabulary and also I enjoy the episode that I am watching . It is the most important example that I can give you to show how television can be an educational device . It 's like video games . It also could be an educational way to learn something . Or even music . It all depends on how you use the thing and what you want to learn with that device or activity . I enjoy my routine of practising English with a TV show a lot . 
