Our goal in life is to be happy . Happiness is the greatest life goal and to reach it we have to do many things . Maybe to reach happiness we must earn money and buy things , or maybe it could be reached doing sports or reading many books . The method to reach happiness could be so different for each one of us , but something is transversal , without taking into account who we are . We have to be healthy . If we do not have health , then we ca not reach or do any of the activities that were named before or any other activity . If you ca not stand up or walk , you wo not be able to travel around the world or do any sport . Then , because of that , you must take care of yourself and be sure that you are doing things in a good way to remain healthy . 
It 's commonly said that you are learning English because you want to travel around the world or because you want to get a better job , but for me , the main reason for learning English is because I want to be able of read , listen or see a lot of information in its original language . English is the language of the world , so if you want to learn about one topic or read an interesting book , you maybe have to read it in English . A lot interesting books or funny series are in English , or have more quality if you see them in English . Obviously , I take account of other reasons , like if you want to travel around the world you have to learn English , because with that you will be able to talk with others and get whatever you want to buy or solve any doubts . 
All the staff in the business room had a discussion about what style of new room will be replaced yesterday . Two styles of business room are traditional rooms with enclosed workstations or cubicles and modern rooms with open designs will be decided by staff . In my opinion , I think modern rooms with open designs are better than others . First , most companies rent offices for working at present . The open design will help save space for working by the thick walls between rooms . Rooms are separated by glass walls , mezzanine partitions or panels . We do not have much money for renting . Besides , an open design mean one room for all staff , we do not need to buy a lot of equipment for each staff , all equipment is shared by all staff . Secondly , an open design makes an active working environment . Staff can see each other so they can easily communication together , it will make they feel like a team . Finally , an open design will help raise the effectiveness of working . Managers can easily check what the staff are working on . Besides , the staff will limit their personal job during their time of working . So the staff will work more effectively . 
First of all , I decided go to the concert to spend a great time with my girlfriend and I thought about the concert as a gift to her and to me . The selected artist was Cepeda , a Colombian singer who sings romantic music . The concert was amazing , because Cepeda sings so well . It is as if you are listening to it via CD . The concert lasted close to two hours , with her whole songs ' repertory . I left the concert very happy with the experience . I am convinced that next year my girlfriend and I are going to go to another concert of Cepeda . 
There 're four seasons in a year , Spring , Summer , Autumn and Winter . There 're many flowers in spring . It 's very colourful and fresh at this time . The weather is very hot and sunny in summer and we need to hide from the strong sun . The temperature is not very hot and it 's not very cold in autumn . Winter is very wet and cool and many children like to play in the snow with their partners , so they will be lucky and happy . My favourite season is summer . I like to go swimming during this period and I can exercise my body in the swimming pool or the sea . I may go windsurfing at the beach , although it 's dangerous sometimes . If I can have an excellent and successful performance , I 'll win the competition , so that I should become the winner of this event . I 'll continue to participate in this match and I 'll try my best to finish it and I 'll achieve my goal finally . I 'll have a wonderful and amazing result in the future and I believe that I should overcome a lot of difficulties and some problems . I do this sport with my best friends and we 'll improve our abilities or have a healthy body ourselves . We should be confident and we must have some confidence in our heart . We enjoy the air conditioner and we feel comfortable and happy with this modern technology . 
Learning to speak a foreign language is more important these days than it was in the past . This is because nowadays we can communicate with any person around the world with our cellphones or computer . Then we can work , play , write and more with other people and to do that we need to speak with them . In the past , we did not have this possibility . Then we just had to speak our native language . And of all foreign languages , the most important is English . You must know English nowadays if you want to have a great job or travel around the world to any country , because with English you will be able to talk with any person . If the other countries do not have English as their native language , then some people will learn English and you will be able to communicate with them . 
I do not believe that computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities . Books are a beautiful way to touch knowledge . With a book , you can feel the knowledge as an object . Instead , on a computer , you only see letters on a screen . With a book , you are the owner of a part of knowledge . Another thing is that with a book you will take care of your eyes . Instead , on a computer or tablet , the screen will hurt your eyes with time . Also , I like reading a book more than on a screen . I read on screens because I do not have any books or because I do not find the information in a book , but in general I prefer reading in a book , real paper . I do not have any more to say about the topic . I prefer books , but I know that computers are more needed than books . 
I had a discussion with my parents about if students should live with family when they are studying at university or they should move away and live alone yesterday . In my opinion , I think students should live with their family until they graduate from university . First , students , who are studying at university , are aged between 18 to 22 , they are young and do not have enough experience in life , they are not clear about social life , they easily believe strangers . A lot of people are tricked for money by scammers or their friends when they are students at present . Secondly , students live with their family when they study at university which is a way to decrease the burden of money for their family . Students must pay a lot of money for four years studying at university . Besides , if students want to move away and live alone , they must pay money for their cost of living every month . However , most of students are financially dependent on their family , so most of the money is paid by their family . It is a great burden for each family . They do not have knowledge about the value of money in life and how hard it is to get it . Finally , if students want to have financial independence when they move away and live alone , they must find a part - time job to have money , The job is spent almost time of their . They do not have enough time for studying and joining volunteer work . It will affect their learning outcomes at university . 
