Music is probably one of the best things that people once began to get interested in . I think that almost everybody around the globe really enjoys time listening to music . Listening to music started being a common thing throughout people 's lives . Whatever people are doing , if there is a chance to listen to music while doing it , they usually do it . People listen to music while they are cooking or working out or just commuting to their destinations . The fantastic thing about music is that it can somehow change people 's moods . Depending on what kind of music a person is listening to , it can make them feel happy , excited , energetic and also sad . So even though people might be in a bad mood one day , music can change it completely . Another thing about music is that in the lyrics of music , there could be a lot of hidden sense that you could realize while listening to it and that could affect you as well . I think that our lives would be entirely different without music . It would probably be a lot more boring and not exciting to do things without music . People who make music would not be able to express themselves in music , and so they would likely be more closed to others . Also , they would not be able to make money from music . If there were no music at all , the bad thing about it is that every moment of the life that contained music in it would not be remembered as well as it might . Just listening to music could remind you of a lot of things from the past , either it would be happy moments or sad moments . I personally really enjoy these feelings you get when you listen to music that was playing at that time . It is incredible . From my perspective , the world without music would be definitely not as good as it is now . 
What is my favorite season ? It is a hard question nowadays , because all seasons are very similar to me . But when I was at school , my favorite season was obviously Christmas , because I received gifts and I got vacations at the same time . But nowadays I work all year and I have to request my holidays , so I ca not choose a season for the holidays . The other reason does not matter either , because as I am an adult now , I do not receive gifts anymore . Maybe one or two , but not the number that I received in the past . So I do not have a good reason to choose a season with my current style of life . Maybe it could keep being Christmas , because I enjoy this season . I enjoy the lights , movies and more things in this season . 
