Dear Matt , I will be really happy on that Monday because we have not had a chance to meet up after the last summer exam . If you need any help with maths and history , please tell me as I have an older brother who has really brilliant talents in school subjects , so I can please ask him to help you if you need any help . My English has improved while a few months because I have practiced every day , for six hours a day at least . I have trained my listening skills in the morning when I used the British Council Learning website and BBC news from You Tube . In the evening , I took a nap and a few minutes after that I read novels , stories and other online sites for reading skills . I have not made any pravite times for my speaking skills because I always used to with my friends , roommates and other friends . 
Learning a new language is still so important . I am a student at university right now . Our department always uses English materials . And we have to learn these . The international language is English . And this is so important . At least , it may cause information confusion . If there is a conference , everyone knows that all people speak English . This is so important for the science world . Of course , everything is so easy right now . We can translate as hear or copy . Learning a new language is always important . We can easily translate but it does not change the importance of language learning . It is a way to pass the time . And it may be a benefit . English and other languages are so important . Each language always has new people and new cultures . Learning new languages , like in the past , is still important . Communication is always the most important thing in our life . 
My favourite indoor activities are gymnastics . I practice fit book and swimming . I last practised them on Monday . We sometimes go jogging or play basketball ; our family likes this sport . They often go jogging in the park . I will go to a mountain to go climbing , I was there with my friend Tatry . If on Sunday it is sunny , we will go to a mountain in my car , but if it is not sunny , we will stay at home . 
Hi Billal , I 'm happy to tell you about my trip I went on last week with my class . We went to the Maritime Museum of Quebec . It was really interesting . There are 2 boats to visit . The visit to the boats was absolutely extraordinary . The guide 's explanations throughout the tour of all the floors , from the engine room to the upper deck , were clear . On the deck of the boat , the view was beautiful . The St -Lawrence River stretched as far as the eye could see . For me , this trip has been very instructive . I learnt a lot about the boats . I learnt a lot about the sailor 's work . See you soon . 
There are four seasons in a year . These are spring , summer , fall and winter . The seasons are just the opposite in the Northern Hemisphere and Sourthern Hemisphere . For instance , if you are in the Northern Hemisphere , summers are hot , however , the other Hemispere is cold . The seasons have an effect on the psychology of people . People feel sad and depressed in winter and fall . They drink their coffee under their blankets , looking out of the window . During spring and summer , people become more active and full of life than other seasons . I like being active , therefore my favorite season is spring . There are two reasons why I like it . The first reason is that the weather is neither cold nor hot . The mild weather does not make you sweat or shiver . The second reason is that the nature renews itself in spring . For example , animals migrate from the cold countries to warm areas , trees and flowers bloom . All these changes make people feel energetic . Therefore I like spring . 
Hello Rie , Thank you for inviting me to dinner and I really appreciate your favour . If you do not mind I want to requeste to you that what I would like to eat is pizza , made by your mother who is the best chef for me . 
I have a discussion with my parents about if all university students and school children should be forced to do sports activities at least 3 times per week in the present . In my opinion , I agree with that idea . Firstly , strokes have been on the increase recently , and the main cause of strokes is an inactive lifestyle . Some new research in a sports magazine shows that anyone who does not do enough or does exercise less than 150 minutes each week has a stroke sickness rate higher than normal , so people should do at least 150 minutes of exercise each week . In the present , the amount of young adults , who are students , that have an inactive lifestyle is increasing more than in the past . Most of the time they are just using their smartphone , looking at the internet and social media online . The morbidity rate of stroke sickness in young adult increases every year . Secondly , doing exercise makes people have a nice body , good strength and good mental . Scientists , who have done the main research about sport , show that people who do exercise everyday have a longer and stronger life than people who do not do it . If you want to live a long and healthy life , you must do exercise every day . Besides , it helps people relax after a hard working day , increases the focus ability and intelligence of mankind . Finally , students , who do exercise at school , have a chance to train soft skills like team work , communication , plan making . Doing exercise at school are joined a lot of people so students can chatting and playing together , they have a chance to practice communication and team work . In addition , some sports have a win -lose spirit , it makes the people who join the match have to have a plan to be winners , so students have a chance to practise plan making skills . The idea that students must do sport activities at least 3 times a week is the right decision . 
Hi , I hope you 're doing well ! I wanted to let you know about a movie I watched recently with friends . I really had fun watching it , that 's why I think you should watch it too . It is called " Johnny English " and tells the story of a rather naive British spy . He does constant exercises to be as good as the best agents of MI6 , but achieves only the greatest mistakes ( and the funniest too ) . The story in itself is quite simple . A French guy tries to become King of England , with a view to transforming it into a huge prison . But Johnny English and his partner will try to stop him , which leads to a chain of hilarious mistakes . I hope you 'll have fun watching it ! Enjoy your weekend . 
