Nowadays , most of the people seem to be obsessed with their mobile phones , and it is crucially awful . And that will be outstanding to make people less immersed into their social lives . And I appreciate any town council 's attempts to prompt it , but the idea of banning the use of mobile phones on public transport and in shops and restaurants altogether seems to me too bad a decision . And that type of measure needs to be rethought and replaced by something less strong and more pleasurable . And for that , there are a couple of reasons . The first one is that some people do need to use mobile phones due to the important messages or calls , and they just ca not wait until a receiver goes out and answers it . The second reason why people might need to use a mobile phones in those cases is that they might need to look something up on the internet or write a note . However , in multiple ways , people just use their phones to entertain themselves during the boring parts when they are at that places . And I think that the best that the council may do is redesign the council 's ban . The council should place a rule in those places that will declare that people must just turn off the volume of their phones and use them in a way that do not interrupt others . And in addition to the rule , the council should create an environment in these places that will get visitors immersed and make them forget about phones . That will be a gorgeous action on the council 's side for most of the people . 
Thank you very much for looking after my house . You will find the keys under the flower pot on the balcony . After your first visit , you can take the keys with you . I have got a copy of my keys . Please , water the plants once a week . Feed my cat once a day . Put the mail on the table in the kitchen . I deeply appreciate your availability . 
Hi Ana , I hope it 's going well for you . Yes , I am learning English . I would like to go on a trip to the United States this summer . I have cousins in New York . I want to visit them but I find it difficult to communicate with them . If I improve my English , it will be easier to communicate with them . Call me if you have time . I would like to talk with you . 
The reason for the problem that rural areas do not have enough doctors for their people is that a doctor can earn more money working in big cities . If you were a doctor and you had the possibility to work in a city or in a rural area and you would earn more money in the city then , what option you would choose ? I can be sure that most of the times people will choose working in the city without thinking about the benefits that people can get if they work in a rural area . First of all , if you work in a rural area , then you will have a more relaxing life than if you work in the city . Also it is true that you will earn more money in the city , but you will also spend more money in the city , then in the end , you will earn close the same money in both places . 
Should computers and tablets completely replace books in schools and universities ? I think it is not possible . Books were the most important source of information for centuries . In our day and age , it is still like this . But the Internet has replaced books on some issues . Books are still an important source of information , but the internet is more accessible and easier to use . If you want to access some information , you do not have to go to a library , just sit and write on Google whatever you want . So computers and tablets can be useful . But I think they will not replace books . That ca not be . Yes the Internet is very useful , but also has a lot of wrong information . Sometimes you ca not distinguish wrong or right information . Also , reading a book is culture . The opinion that computers and tablets will replace books scares me , everything transforming into technological things . Sometimes old things are just something we need . 
The name of my home town is Montmagny city . Galeries Montmagny is a shopping center in Montmagny . You can find many clothing stores there . You can also find a sport store . In Montmagny city , there are 2 restaurants : Normandin and La Rive . In these restaurants , the food is very delicious . 
It 's true that two different types of office that companies manage exist . One type is an office with cubicles where people only see their screens and no more and the other type is an office that does not have any cubicle and all the people can see the others because they do not have so many walls . I think , and I can be closely sure , that the best option is an open office because , with that , people are happier and if people are happier , then they will work efficiently . I ca not believe that many companies nowadays keep managing their employees in closed offices . That kind of office is really awful and maybe it was very popular in the past but now are other times . Now people need open offices to work comfortably . If you are casually a boss with employees in one of this closed office , please change that immediately and improve your company with an open office . 
Some high schools have a requirement that students must complete a certain amount of volunteer work in order to graduate . In my country , and specifically in my school , this practice is implemented . I had to do volunteer work with the buses of my school helping the most little children to carry their backpacks and open the doors of the buses . I think that it is a good practice because , with that , many people can get some help that maybe if volunteer work in schools did not exist , then these people would not have this appreciated help . I know that this volunteer work could be helping children with their homework or simply helping to study some hard subjects like maths or a language . I consider volunteer work a good practice because , with that , we use the time of our teenagers and we teach them that helping is a good thing and maybe we must help people frequently . 
I think that studying music in school is an enormous plus for the school that implements these classes . If I had a child , I would prefer his school to have music classes . I think that it is a good thing because it could be a great practice to entertain the children with a good and healthy thing . And in the future , they will thank us for having taught them to play an instrument . Playing an instrument could be a really difficult activity but if they start to study that since they are children , then they will learn to play a guitar , for example , easier than an adult . It something similar to learning English or another language . If you learn this when you are a child , it is better than learning it when you already are an adult . Another important thing is that I think that music is happiness and , with that , we are giving happiness to our children . 
The varied types of seasons allow us to experience different sides of the year . All of them have their own distinctive features . For example , summer is known for its heat and holidays , winter for its snow and autumn for its leaves falling from the trees . All four of them are good , because they are in a limited time frame and they leave their place to the next in the end . But spring has always had a special place for me since I was just a tiny little child . I presume the reason that I keep it apart from the others is the getting rid of the colorlessness and coldness of winter . It wo not show me that I hate that time of the year . Especially snowy days and snowball fights are delightful . But most of the time this is just not enough . In the spring , the sun appears more vividly , revealing all the beauties of nature , the cheerful chirping of the birds reminds me that life goes on in any case and a situation can never be bad after the insincere weather of winter . 
