Books have been important since paper was invented . Knowledge , feelings and ideas have been transferred with books along the ages . With computers and tablets becoming popular , recently the use of books has been reducing . Computers have taken the place of books in many fields . In my opinion , computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities , due to the ease of use , easier portability and environmental reasons . First of all , tablets provide easy access to information . We can find any information that we want with one click of a button . Students buy their textbooks on the internet and they can read them on tablets . Most of my classmates use tablets instead of books . Another reason is that tablets are more portable than books . We can fit billions of books on a tablet . A tablet weighs approximately 500 grams , while an average book weighs about one kilogram . When we consider that a student carries more than three books a day , this makes a huge difference . Lastly , millions of trees are cut down in order to make books every year . On the other hand , tablets and computers never use trees . So they do not cause any damage to forests . 
Hello Alex , Thank you for the invitation to your party . Unfortunately , I will not be there , because I have to attend some friends ' wedding ceremony this Saturday . I am sorry for my absence . They have been friends for almost 20 years and my other friends and I will play music at their ceremony . Could you let me know if you have time to meet us ? Kind regards , Sue 
Some university students move away and live on their own while they are attending school , but others live at home with their family while they are students . I think that the best choice is to go to another place and live the complete experience of being a university student , but if you do not have the opportunity to do that , you do not have to regret that because you can have a great experience also living with your parents . And this choice has other benefits . If you live with your parents while you are studying at university , then you will be able to focus on the exams and projects from university because you wo not have to think about house things like cleaning or cooking . You will only have to think about exams and no more . And if you choose living in another place , you will have total independence and this is one of the greatest things in the world . 
