This letter is addressed to the town council and it is regarding the new idea of banning the use of mobile phones on public transportation and in shops and restaurants . I really think that it is a really bad idea . I could not find a reasonable reason to think that this new idea could be a great idea . We ca not simply not use our phones . People spend a lot of time in public transportation or waiting for something in a shop , we even have to wait our food in a restaurant and we use our mobile phones to make time better . We use our phones those times when you do not have anything to do because you have to wait for something . I think that it is not a bad practice and we need to use our phones . Also another reason to not realize the idea is that maybe people could need their phones for an emergency . We do not know when we could need our phone because our mom or any relative had an accident or maybe if a relative needs some money right now , then we could need the phone to communicate with them . There are a lot of situations when people could need their cellphones and the town council ca not forbid the use of mobile cellphones . I think that it will be like a dictatorship or something similar . 
I think that the world could be a great place if all of us were good people , but it is impossible because bad people exist . Something similar occurs with lies . Maybe the world would be a better place if people did not tell lies or fewer lies . I think that , in some cases , we can tell some lies , but this is only acceptable when the lies do not do any bad things to the other person . I think that big lies are unacceptable . Big lies like being unfaithful , committing a robbery or doing something that could hurt another person . I am sure that if people were more worried about the situation of other people , we could have a better place to live because we could be sure that no one wants to do something bad to us . We could go outside without the fear of being robbed or something worse like a rape . We all know that people around the world could be very evil and we always have to prevent that and keep ourselves safe . It would be wonderful if we could walk without worries . This is the world that I dream about . I know that many times people do these things because they are in bad economic situations , but I think that it is not an excuse to do bad things to others . All of us have our own problems . 
I want to speak about sleep . Some people like to sleep in a dark and quiet room . Other people sleep with a small light on and do not mind noise . It is a choice and it is fine , how people are comfortable with their sleep , it is important I think . I am from the group of people who like to sleep in a dark and quiet room because when other people speak I am not able to sleep again for an hour , which is my reason for sleeping in a dark and quiet room . 
