In my opinion , I prefer to sleep in a dark and quiet room than sleep with a small light on . I prefer that because of two main reasons : The first reason is that I had gone to school for five years . That matters because my teacher does not allow us to make any noise and she turns off all the lights while we sleep . Also , the majority of time in the day is spent at school . The second reason is that when you sleep at night and nothing makes a noise , your body will soon adapt to that and then you will have to sleep in a dark and quiet room . Mainly for the two above reasons , I prefer to sleep in a dark and quiet room . 
Hello everyone , I was asked to write an article about the question what my favourite season of the year is . It is easy to say it is the autumn , but it would not be an article when I only answer the question in one sentence . So I will describe in the following text why I like the autumn so much . One reason for it would be the colorful trees . It is really special , in no other season do you have this and I like it so much , when the leaves turn from green to yellow or red . And the best of it is when the wind blows and the colorful leaves fall like rain to the ground . It is difficult to describe how beautiful it is . Another reason why I like the autumn so much is the weather . I would say it is the perfect mix between cold and warm . You have a warm rainfall sometimes , or you have low temperatures , but a sun which warms you up . It is really perfect . 
Some scientists argue that computers and tablets are beneficial to students at school and at universities . Such devices combine pleasure and work and even improve the way students learn hard topics . However , I strongly disagree with these scientists and believe that tablets and computers cannot replace books in school and universities . My point of view is that electronic devices are not helpful to learn hard topics . since their main objective is advertising to people . For example , I owned a tablet when I was younger and I never used it to learn anything related to any lectures I had . Before the invention of tablets and computers , students did not have any computers or tablets and they were as clever as we are right now , whereas we have tons and tons of websites , such as wikipedia . It 's important to teach students how to find the information by themselves . With tablets and computers , it is easy for them to do some research on the internet and get the answer in under a microsecond . To sum up , I do not believe that such electronic devices are helpful and have a positive impact on a student 's way of learning . I even think the opposite . 
People nowadays tend to be less active and consume more unhealthy food than they used to back in the day . And as many researchers show that the less a person does activity during the day , the worse their health become . And there is a huge problem with the young population who spend hours and hours a day siting at home and playing video games , which have a negative impact on their health . It is crucial to be active during the day and spend more time outside rather than inside . Because human organisms are not used to spending that much time inactive . They used to do lots of activities and work during the day . And now , we need to find the ways to get people realized and encouraged to work out at least three times per week and spend more time being active . But it is bad idea to force people into doing sports activities because it may cause a big problem : they will be discouraged and obligated to do it . And eventually , that may end up in them being fed up with , and they will give it up . It is essential to show them that it may be not only good for their mental and cognitive health but also fascinating and worth -spending time on . The best way to do it is to build up a more developed sports sphere that will provide people with lots of opportunities to be active and spend time beneficially . For instance , the government may open up more gyms in the cities and provide them with brand -new appliances and good staff with lots of knowledge to train and encourage people to work out . It is extremely essential to not force anybody to do sports activities . They need to be encouraged and have willingness to do it themselves . Otherwise , it may end up with bad results . 
Hi Alex ! I hope you are doing great . I am sorry , but I 'm afraid I wo not be able to go to your party on Saturday . I forgot it 's my brother 's birthday on Saturday and my parents have organized to go on a trip . All my family is travelling to Brazil to celebrate it , and there 's no chance I could stay here in Argentina . We will stay there for a week , if I am right . However , we could meet next week , if that 's OK with you . We could hang out , go shopping to Rosario or maybe cycle . Otherwise , my parents have allowed me to have a party at home the week after we return to the country . If you like , we could do it and we could invite all our school friends . Tell me what you feel about it and let me know as soon as possible so we can start planning everything . Your friend , Iva . 
When our parents went to school , they could only use a book as a tool to study and follow lessons . However , in our current society , all that 's changed , thanks to technology . Indeed , computers and tablets have become more accessible for everyone and as a consequence , a large percentage of students should have one or both of them in their respective houses . They are useful , since you can surf on the Internet for words or processes you did not catch . I did it especially when I had to understand the main steps of a biochemical process . On the other hand , it 's considered by many parents that these devices could be a distraction during studies . It occurred because these devices allow us to do other activities , such as watching videos and listening to music . In each thing there are pros and cons , but we make the most of doing it in the correct way . According to me , computers and tablets wo not replace books in school and university . The explanation is they could raise our inattention inevitably , getting worse marks compared to studying with books . 
