I can sleep anywhere because I am usually very tired . I am not very sensitive to my room situation ; I can sleep both in a dark room and a light room . I do not understand everythings when I sleep , this is a simple way to sleep . Indeed , you should work hard during the day and you will be tired with this action , and you wo not need to sleep in a dark quiet room . I hope you sleep comfortably forever . 
In people 's lives , what they do and what they achieve defines their whole life . People always talk about what has recently happened to them or what they have done when there is a get -together . Joyful and fulfilled occasions always stay with people . As for starters , personally , I believe a shorter but more intense life is better than a very long and calm life . Of course , I want to live long , but if my only choice for a long life is living " calm " and doing nothing , it is a dealbreaker . Furthermore , I want to do lots of things such as travelling , going out most nights instead of sitting at home doing nothing , trying out new things . I want to make the most out of my life , I want to make significant memories . As long as I am happy with my life and think that I have achieved what I have wanted to , it does not matter at what age I die . To move on , for me , a calm life means stability , but dull time -spending as well as an intense life means a busy but joyful journey . For example , just like most people , I want to have some kind of stable life like having a big comfortable house , but I do not want to spend my whole life in that house . I want to travel , work hard , try out new things . I want to have a good intense life . In conclusion , how much you live does not define the quality of your life . However , how much you 've achieved does . Live fast , die young . 
My favorite food is pizza . I usually eat this food for dinner ; it is delicious food . It is made very fast and for this reason , I like this food . 
