Even more important than exercise , in my personal opinion , our diet is the main thing to worry about in terms of healthcare . Without a proper diet , our body ca not work properly , as the diet provides the nutrients and energy necessary for people to carry out their daily activities . Also , most people do not realise how important sleeping is . Usually , to be considered a good night 's sleep , a person needs to sleep between 6 to 8 hours a night . Furthermore , not only the quantity , but the quality of our sleep is really important , so make sure to eat healthily , do exercise , and being emotionally stable is so important . 
